NK126(cho)001:1: // sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bee ro tsa na'i rnam thar 'dra 'bags chen mo bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)001:2: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:3: de la chos thams cad kyi chos nyid ni /
NK126(cho)001:4: sangs rgyas sgam pos ma mdzad /
NK126(cho)001:5: sems can sgrin pos ma bcos pa'i dus na /
NK126(cho)001:6: ngo bo gnyis su med pa /
NK126(cho)001:8: snang ba sgyu ma yin pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9: sems can rnams rkyen bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag dang ma 'phrad pas /
NK126(cho)001:10: ngo bo gnyis med las gnyis su 'khrul /
NK126(cho)001:11: mtshan nyid rang rig la rang rig tu ma go ste /
NK126(cho)001:12: snang ba sgyu ma la yang dag par zhen pas /
NK126(cho)001:13: 'gro ba rigs drug gi las dang 'bras bu myong ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:14: dper na dang po chu'i rang bzhin de rkyen dang
NK126(cho)001:15: bral ba 'khyag pas chab bram ltar du snang ba
NK126(cho)001:16: bzhin no // de lta bu'i sems can la sngar
NK126(cho)001:17: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag khong du ma chud
NK126(cho)001:18: bzhin no // pas / 'gro ba rigs drug tu
NK126(cho)001:19: snang bas sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ma bcos par
NK126(cho)001:21: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can la bde bar
NK126(cho)001:22: gshegs pa thugs rje chen la thabs mkhas pa des
NK126(cho)001:23: / nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen
NK126(cho)001:24: por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs
NK126(cho)001:25: / so // de yang gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis su 'dus te /
NK126(cho)001:26: de yang sde snod gsum du 'dus so //
NK126(cho)001:31: kun byed le'u bcu pa las /
NK126(cho)001:32: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum byung ste //
NK126(cho)001:33: de dag 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:34: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong ste //
NK126(cho)001:36: yang gzugs dang sgra dang dri ro reg bya las /
NK126(cho)001:37: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug rnam gsum byung //
NK126(cho)001:38: de dag 'dul ba'i gnyen po sde snod gsum //
NK126(cho)001:39: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen po gsungs pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:40: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:41: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:42: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:43: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:44: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:45: dug gsum cha mnyam 'dul ba'i gnyen po ni //
NK126(cho)001:46: sde snod gsum pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:47: spyi ru brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa las //
NK126(cho)001:48: dug gsum gnyen por 'dul phyir gsungs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:50: de yang snod kyi rim pa dang sbyar na rab 'bring tha ma gsum ste /
NK126(cho)001:51: de yang re re la yang gsum gsum ste dagu'o //
NK126(cho)001:52: de yang cis mngon zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:53: kun byed le'u lnga pa las /
NK126(cho)001:54: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:55: bstan ni rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK126(cho)001:56: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK126(cho)001:59: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:60: zhal nas gsungs pa'i theg pa de rnams kyi mdo bzung mkhas pas mdzad pa la /
NK126(cho)001:61: bstan bcos sam rab tu 'byed pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:62: 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:63: zhal nas gsungs pa'i rgyud lung las mkhas pas mdzad pa'i man ngag gam /
NK126(cho)001:65: de la mdo sde zer na sprul pa'i sku'i zhal
NK126(cho)001:66: nas gsungs pa de don mdo ru bsdus pa la
NK126(cho)001:67: tshig sder longs pa'i phyir ro //
NK126(cho)001:68: rgyud zer na sku gsung thugs rim par brgyud pa'i phyir ro //
NK126(cho)001:69: de la bstan bcos mtha' dag don rnam pa lngas bstan te /
NK126(cho)001:70: dgos pa bsdus dang tshig don dang //
NK126(cho)001:71: spyi yi don dang yan lag dbye //
NK126(cho)001:72: brgal brtags bcas te brnyad par bya //
NK126(cho)001:74: man ngag mtha' dag rtsis mgo lngas 'chad do //
NK126(cho)001:75: rgyud mtha' dag phun sum tshogs pa lngas 'chad do //
NK126(cho)001:76: de la theg pa chung ngu nyan thos kyi phun sum tshogs pa lnga ni /
NK126(cho)001:78: gnas wa ra na si'i gling ngam /
NK126(cho)001:79: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal lam /
NK126(cho)001:80: mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra bar bshad /
NK126(cho)001:81: dus lnga brgya phrag dang po la'o //
NK126(cho)001:82: 'khor dge slong dang dge tshul pho mo'o //
NK126(cho)001:83: bstan pa nges don du 'dul ba lung sde bzhi /
NK126(cho)001:84: drangs don du mdo sde skyes rab sam /
NK126(cho)001:88: sdus pa po kun dga' bo //
NK126(cho)001:89: yang rang rgyal gyi phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang mi ldan te /
NK126(cho)001:91: sangs rgyas rnams kyang mi bzhugs shing //
NK126(cho)001:92: nyan thos rnams kyang zad pa na //
NK126(cho)001:93: rang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni //
NK126(cho)001:94: brten pa med par rang las byung //
NK126(cho)001:96: theg pa chen po dbu ma'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga ni /
NK126(cho)001:98: gnas bya rgod phung po'i ri /
NK126(cho)001:99: dus lnga phrag gnyis pa'i dus so //
NK126(cho)001:100: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' sdom pa 'dzin pa'i 'khor rnams bzhi'o //
NK126(cho)001:101: bstan pa nges don du shes rab phyogs sras yum bcu bdun /
NK126(cho)001:102: drang don mdo sde 'bum la sogs pa theg pa chen po'i mdo mtha' dag go //
NK126(cho)001:103: sdus pa po 'phags pa kun dga' bo'o //
NK126(cho)001:104: mdo sde zhes ci'i phyir bya zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:105: gnas rnams dang ni mtshan nyid dang //
NK126(cho)001:106: chos don ston pa mdo sder bshad //
NK126(cho)001:108: yang 'dul ba zhes ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:109: ltung dang nges par 'byung ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:110: bca' bzhi dang ni rab 'byed dang //
NK126(cho)001:111: de nyid 'dul ba nyid spyod pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:113: mngon pa zhes ci'i phyir bya zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:114: mngon du bya phyir yangs nas yang //
NK126(cho)001:115: zil gnon rtogs pas mngon pa'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:116: zhes pa sde snod gsum gyi nges tshig gi /
NK126(cho)001:118: dang po ston pa kun rigs rnam par snang mdzad /
NK126(cho)001:119: 'og min gyi gnas nas dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang la gnas pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:120: la s+ya dkar mo la sogs pa phyag rgya'i lha mo bzhi dang /
NK126(cho)001:121: mchod pa'i lha mo la sogs pa'i skur bzhengs nas /
NK126(cho)001:122: thugs rje rgyun chad ma mdzad par /
NK126(cho)001:123: d+hu pe la sogs pa brgyad kyis mchod bstod bskur ba mdzad pas /
NK126(cho)001:124: kun rigs rnam par snang mdzad du bzhengs nas rgyud gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:125: chos nyid ngang la ma rnal ba //
NK126(cho)001:126: 'gro ba'i don la longs skur bzhengs //
NK126(cho)001:127: thugs rje rgyun chad ma mdzad par //
NK126(cho)001:128: 'gro don sngon gyi dam bcas yal bar 'chi //
NK126(cho)001:131: byed pa bya ba'i rgyud kri ya ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:132: ston pa rigs kyi bdag po gsum gyi yang /
NK126(cho)001:133: gtso bo rnam par snang mdzad nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK126(cho)001:135: rigs khyad par can gyi 'khor rigs gsum mgon po dang /
NK126(cho)001:136: dus ni lnga brgya phrag gsum pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:138: spyi bo nas thon pa dbu gtsug tor gyi tan tra /
NK126(cho)001:139: dpung pa g.yas g.yon nas thon pa kri ya dpung bzang gi tan tra /
NK126(cho)001:140: thugs kar nas thon pa thugs rigs pa mchog gi rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:141: lte ba nas thon pa su pe ti ka ra'i rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:142: zhabs nas thon pa zhabs 'khor lo sdom pa'i rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:143: de la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:144: sdud pa po gtsang ma lag na rdo rje gnas
NK126(cho)001:145: 'dod khams lha'i gnas chos bzang lha'i pho brang du
NK126(cho)001:146: bshad / de nas mi yul du ni ston pa sh+aakya thub kyis /
NK126(cho)001:147: gnas dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal du /
NK126(cho)001:148: dus lnga brgya phrag bzhi pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:150: sdud pa po lag na rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:151: bstan pa yang snga ma nyid do //
NK126(cho)001:152: la la dag sdud pa po kun daga'o yang zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:154: dpal nam mkha' sgo mang gi rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)001:155: gnyis ka rgyud kyi u pa ya //
NK126(cho)001:156: 'di yi spyod pa nges pa ma mchis pas //
NK126(cho)001:157: lung la'ang nges pa med par bstan //
NK126(cho)001:158: de bkod gling bzhi'i gong 'og gnyis pos shes //
NK126(cho)001:159: phun sum tshogs pa de ltar bstan du med //
NK126(cho)001:161: sems dpa' rnal 'byor yo ga'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga ni /
NK126(cho)001:162: ston pa rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i rgyud dang mthun /
NK126(cho)001:163: des na rnam par snang mdzad kun tu zhal /
NK126(cho)001:165: 'khor rgyal ba rigs bzhi nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor /
NK126(cho)001:166: sems dpa' sems ma ni rig khyad par can gyi 'khor ro //
NK126(cho)001:167: dus lnga brgya phrag lnga pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:168: bstan pa ni mu la tan+t+ra rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:170: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba /
NK126(cho)001:171: dpal mchog dang po la sogs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:172: sdud pa po dpal 'byung lag na rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:173: bar du 'dod khams lha yul du /
NK126(cho)001:174: rig 'dzin grub pa rnams la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:175: mi yul du gnas me ri 'bar ba'i rtse la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:177: dus lnga brgya phrag drug pa la'o //
NK126(cho)001:180: sdud pa po kun dga' bo'o //
NK126(cho)001:181: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa yi /
NK126(cho)001:182: bstan pa la mdo sngags gnyis ka gsungs pa mi rigs zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:183: de la dgongs pa 'dus pa'i le'u bdun pa las /
NK126(cho)001:184: lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK126(cho)001:185: gsang ba'i bdag po sprul pa'i sku thub pa'i dbang po 'di /
NK126(cho)001:186: sangs rgyas gang gi sprul pa'i sku lags /
NK126(cho)001:187: gsang ba'i bdag pos bka' stsal pa /
NK126(cho)001:188: 'di ni rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa bsam gyis
NK126(cho)001:189: mi khyab pa'i dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi kyang
NK126(cho)001:190: brjod kyis mi lang pa'i nang nas sprul pa cha
NK126(cho)001:193: chos sku la longs sku rnam snang gis smra ba'i seng+ge rdo rje sems dpa' la bsgo ba /
NK126(cho)001:194: sgyu 'phrul nas rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK126(cho)001:195: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK126(cho)001:196: rdo rje rigs gtso thams cad dkyil //
NK126(cho)001:198: sprul pa bkye ba cha gcig sh+aakya thub la sogs pas gsang sngags gsungs par rigs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:200: yang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i mi mjed kyi
NK126(cho)001:201: 'jig rten 'di na sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa zhes
NK126(cho)001:203: theg pa che chung gi chos dang /
NK126(cho)001:204: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:205: gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid ston to //
NK126(cho)001:207: des na mi yul du bshad pa sh+aakya thub pa nyid do //
NK126(cho)001:208: 'o na rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga bstan pa gang gis gsung zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:209: de yang sku gsum brgyud de gnas 'og min chen po ste /
NK126(cho)001:212: rin chen gzhal yas bkod pa nas //
NK126(cho)001:214: ston pa kun tu bzang pos yum kun tu bzang
NK126(cho)001:215: mo la gnyis su med par sbyor bas chos skur
NK126(cho)001:216: thim ste / sgyu 'phrul bye brag bshad pa'i rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)001:217: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK126(cho)001:218: de ni rdo rje chags can spyad //
NK126(cho)001:219: rig mar bcas te zhu bar 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:220: chos sku byang chub sems su gnas //
NK126(cho)001:222: de la lha mo bcu drug glus mchod dang bstod bskul mdzad pa yis /
NK126(cho)001:223: stong pa nyid kyi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK126(cho)001:224: snying rje rgyun chad ma mdzad par //
NK126(cho)001:225: 'gro ba'i don la sku bzhengs cig /
NK126(cho)001:227: a cang gsung gi phyag rgya las //
NK126(cho)001:228: phyag rgya chen por sku bzhengs nas //
NK126(cho)001:229: lha dang lha mo klu mo rnams //
NK126(cho)001:230: 'dod pa ngas bshad nyon cig ces //
NK126(cho)001:231: zhes gnang nas rgyud gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:232: des 'khor nyi las mi gzhan pa rgyal ba rigs
NK126(cho)001:233: lnga yab yum rigs khyad par can gyi sems dpa'
NK126(cho)001:234: dang sems ma khro bo dang khro mo /
NK126(cho)001:235: sprul pa dang yang sprul lo //
NK126(cho)001:237: lha yab gtso bor byas pa thabs la brten pa pha rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)001:238: lha yum gtso bor byas pa shes rab la brten pa ma rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)001:240: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa spyi rgyud do //
NK126(cho)001:241: bsdu na de gsum du 'dus so //
NK126(cho)001:242: phye na rigs lnga po de dang /
NK126(cho)001:243: phyir gsungs pa sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad las kha tshar
NK126(cho)001:244: dang sbyar nas rgyud kyi rgyal po drug las shar
NK126(cho)001:245: ba'i rgyab brten zla gsang thig le sangs rgyas mnyam
NK126(cho)001:247: gzi ldan 'bar ba mtshams kyi rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:249: zhi ba bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:250: rgyas pa yang dag tshe dang bdud rtsi gsum gyi rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:251: dbang ni pad+ma dbang chen gyi rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:252: drag po la ma gshin phur gsum gyi rgyud do //
NK126(cho)001:253: slad ma sngags kyi mdo lnga'i rgyud do //
NK126(cho)001:254: sdud pa po drag po dpa' brtul lag na rdo rje'i /
NK126(cho)001:255: dus lnga brgya phrag bdun pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:256: bar du lha gnas gsum du grags te /
NK126(cho)001:258: thub pa'i dbang po gsang ba'i bdag /
NK126(cho)001:259: byis pa'i spyod pa de bor nas //
NK126(cho)001:260: sprul pa rdo rje 'dzin gyi rgyal //
NK126(cho)001:261: lha gnas gsum du grags nas yang //
NK126(cho)001:262: gsang sngags gter gyi bdag po mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:264: de nas mi yul du ji ltar byung ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:266: ston pas thub pa'i dbang po des //
NK126(cho)001:267: skye rgu'i tshe lo brgya par 'byung //
NK126(cho)001:268: sde snod gsum dang kri yog gsum //
NK126(cho)001:269: de nas sku mya ngan las 'das par dgongs te /
NK126(cho)001:270: yangs pa can du 'khor mang po dang thabs gcig tu dbyar zla gsum ngo 'das te /
NK126(cho)001:271: ston zla gnyis kyi ngo la 'khor rnams la gdams ngag gsum bzhag pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:272: rdzu 'phrul can khyed cag dngos la nga yis 'khor du phyogs pa kun sdus shig /
NK126(cho)001:273: nges par bzhag pa dag yod de //
NK126(cho)001:275: 'khor gyi nang nas rdzu 'phrul cher spyod kyis 'di skad du /
NK126(cho)001:276: rgyal ba'i zhing gyur rigs drug gang su dag /'du bar nges shing phyogs pa kun nyon cig /
NK126(cho)001:277: de ring rgyal bas bdud rtsi'i gsung 'jog gi //
NK126(cho)001:278: dug gsum 'joms par 'dod pa kun 'dus shig /
NK126(cho)001:282: grogs pa dag shes pa gyis shig /
NK126(cho)001:283: chos thams cad ni mi rtag pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:284: 'byor pa thams cad ni mthar rgud pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:285: dngos po thams cad nges par 'jig pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:286: gang zag gi srog gi 'khor lo la skye shi yod pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:287: nga yongs su mya ngan las 'das pas /
NK126(cho)001:288: su dag the tshom ma chod pa ni dri ba dris shig /
NK126(cho)001:290: 'khor de'i nang nas rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po kuny+dza
NK126(cho)001:291: ra zhes bya ba byung nas rang gi stan las
NK126(cho)001:292: langs te / ston pa la seng ge'i blta stangs kyis bltas te /
NK126(cho)001:294: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK126(cho)001:298: khyod ni 'jig rten sgron mer shar //
NK126(cho)001:299: lha mi'i 'jig rten thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:300: mun pa'i dkyil 'khor kun gsal nas //
NK126(cho)001:301: sems kyi dkyil 'khor gsal mdzad pa //
NK126(cho)001:302: sa dang rnam thar lam spyod pas //
NK126(cho)001:303: byang chub thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:304: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum la //
NK126(cho)001:305: gang dag rim pa bkod lags na //
NK126(cho)001:306: mnyam pa blangs dor med spyod pa'i //
NK126(cho)001:307: nges shing gsal bar ma gsungs na //
NK126(cho)001:309: dus der bstan pa tshul ma lags na //
NK126(cho)001:310: phyis bshad kyi bar lung bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:311: nga ni 'di nas mi gnas nas //
NK126(cho)001:312: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis na //
NK126(cho)001:313: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:314: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK126(cho)001:315: dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams na //
NK126(cho)001:316: mi ni skal ldan rigs can gyi //
NK126(cho)001:317: sngon du bstan pa'i gnas gyur pa //
NK126(cho)001:318: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK126(cho)001:319: grogs kyi dam pa legs pa'i lus //
NK126(cho)001:320: lang+ga'i bdag po la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:321: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:323: sku yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
NK126(cho)001:324: de nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad nas mi yul du gsang sngags byung lugs ni /
NK126(cho)001:326: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK126(cho)001:327: phyag na rdo rjes lung bstan te //
NK126(cho)001:328: za hor can gyi nye 'khor na //
NK126(cho)001:329: mthu stobs zhabs bcag ma la ya //
NK126(cho)001:330: gnam lcags yod pa rtse mo ri //
NK126(cho)001:331: rtse la rtsal khyi rgyal po gnas //
NK126(cho)001:332: ngos la brag dkar khyi tshug brgyan //
NK126(cho)001:333: rtsi sna rtsa brgyad tshang bar 'khrungs //
NK126(cho)001:334: shar na sh+ri a su ra //
NK126(cho)001:335: ngo mtshar ri mo zla gam sgo //
NK126(cho)001:336: nang na rin chen zur brgyad la //
NK126(cho)001:337: nyi zla dkar dmar ri mo snang //
NK126(cho)001:338: spyi bor ka lan ta ka ni //
NK126(cho)001:340: don de yis ni tshangs bcas pa //
NK126(cho)001:341: skal ldan rnams kyis bsgrod cing thar //
NK126(cho)001:342: skal med rnams kyis yangs mi thar //
NK126(cho)001:343: de lta bu yi ri gcig yod //
NK126(cho)001:344: gnas der rgyal po dzas gzigs pa //
NK126(cho)001:345: dang po rgyal po rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:346: ri bo de yi rtse mo na //
NK126(cho)001:347: phyag na rdo rje'i pho brang bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:348: sku yi 'od kyis thams cad bsregs //
NK126(cho)001:349: gsung sgra 'brug tu stong gsum sgrogs //
NK126(cho)001:350: thugs las rdo rje nyi zla shar //
NK126(cho)001:351: nyi 'od bdag gi spyi bo thims //
NK126(cho)001:352: zla 'od rkang pa'i mthil du thims //
NK126(cho)001:353: snang srid lto ru zos shing rmi //
NK126(cho)001:354: nam phyed rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:355: sangs rgyas rnams dang chos kyi don //
NK126(cho)001:356: nyi zla zhon nas 'gro bar mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:357: 'khor 'das sna drangs 'gro ba kha lo bsgyur //
NK126(cho)001:358: de lta bu yi rmi lam byung //
NK126(cho)001:359: tho rangs rnal ba'i rmi lam ni //
NK126(cho)001:360: nam mkha' sna tshogs 'od kyis khengs //
NK126(cho)001:361: cho 'phrul sgra snyan sna tshogs sgrogs //
NK126(cho)001:362: rin chen sna tshogs sprin ltar btibs //
NK126(cho)001:363: rin po che yi char pa bab //
NK126(cho)001:364: snang srid gsal ba'i glog stong 'gyu //
NK126(cho)001:365: rin chen sna tshogs bsdus shing rmi //
NK126(cho)001:366: de yi nang par bsams te bsdad //
NK126(cho)001:368: srod cig rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:370: rin chen sgron mas mun bsal nas //
NK126(cho)001:371: bdud rtsi sman gyis gcong snying sbyangs //
NK126(cho)001:373: 'jig rten khyab par sgrogs shing rmi //
NK126(cho)001:374: nam phyed rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:375: sprin dang nyi ma'i 'od byung nas //
NK126(cho)001:376: de las rin chen sgrom cig byung //
NK126(cho)001:377: rin chen smug po'i sgrom bu nas //
NK126(cho)001:378: rin chen gser gyi glegs bam la //
NK126(cho)001:379: beed+aura zhun mas nan gyi bris //
NK126(cho)001:380: de ni skar mda' bzhin du bab par rmi //
NK126(cho)001:381: tho ras rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:382: glegs bam mang po de dag la //
NK126(cho)001:383: byang chub sems dpa' rig 'dzin lha //
NK126(cho)001:384: kun gyis klogs cing skor ba byed //
NK126(cho)001:385: de yang nang par bsams te bsdad //
NK126(cho)001:386: yang cig srod la rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:387: 'di skad zer ba'i sgra ni bar snang khams nas byung //
NK126(cho)001:388: las dang skal bar ldan pa yis //
NK126(cho)001:389: sngon du lung bstan rgyal po dza //
NK126(cho)001:390: bsod nams ldan pa'i grwa ma khyod //
NK126(cho)001:391: sprul pa po ltar lung bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:392: da lta dus 'dir mngon shar gyi //
NK126(cho)001:393: 'khor ba'i snying po rtogs pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:394: nga yi cho 'phrul byin brlabs kyis //
NK126(cho)001:395: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK126(cho)001:396: skal ldan khyod la bstan par bya //
NK126(cho)001:397: de skad sgrog pa'i rmi lam byung //
NK126(cho)001:398: nam phyed rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:399: ma la ya zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK126(cho)001:400: dgon pa chen po'i gnas zhig na //
NK126(cho)001:401: ye shes snying po can rnams kyis //
NK126(cho)001:402: blang bar bya ba dam pa zhig /
NK126(cho)001:403: yod kyi de la nan tan gyis //
NK126(cho)001:404: de la sems kyi me long ltos //
NK126(cho)001:405: mngon par gsal bar rtogs gyur na //
NK126(cho)001:406: sangs rgyas sa nyid skal ba mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:407: bde ba can gyi zhing khams su //
NK126(cho)001:408: 'od kyi rgyal po zhes bya bar //
NK126(cho)001:409: rin chen de rigs bde chen 'grub //
NK126(cho)001:410: de ltar bu yi rmi lam byung //
NK126(cho)001:411: tho ras rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:412: rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba yi //
NK126(cho)001:413: dam pa'i mdzod gsum rmi lam du //
NK126(cho)001:414: rdzogs par bris pa khyod ltos la //
NK126(cho)001:415: lha dang mi yi rigs 'dzin la //
NK126(cho)001:416: rim par brgyud la grags pa gyis //
NK126(cho)001:417: de lta bu yi rmi lam byung //
NK126(cho)001:418: nang par sad nas rab dgyes te //
NK126(cho)001:419: 'khor kun bsdus te rmi lam bzlas //
NK126(cho)001:420: khong nyid rtogs dang ldan par dgyes //
NK126(cho)001:421: 'khor gyis ngo mtshar zhes gsol lo //
NK126(cho)001:422: der rgyal po ri rtser phyin te gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:423: rmi lam dang mthun par cho 'phrul mthong nas /
NK126(cho)001:424: dgyes te bskor ba dang mchod pa byas te /
NK126(cho)001:426: sngon tshe gang nas bsgrub pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:427: las kyi mjal ba'i lha mchog khyod //
NK126(cho)001:428: nam zhig gtan du mi spang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:429: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:430: 'dren pa mchog gi dpal du grags //
NK126(cho)001:431: mos pa'i gzung du lha mchog 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:433: rgyal pos yang bsam pa btang nas /
NK126(cho)001:434: ma la ya yi ri 'di ni //
NK126(cho)001:435: grub rtags 'di dang ldan pas na //
NK126(cho)001:436: gsang bdag pho brang nges pas na //
NK126(cho)001:437: rig 'dzin grub pa'i gnas yin phyir //
NK126(cho)001:438: gcan gzan gdug pa mi gtse bas //
NK126(cho)001:439: bkra shis yin pas bsgrub par bya //
NK126(cho)001:441: gzugs la brten te zla gsum bsgrub pas /
NK126(cho)001:442: dus der po ti mang po sngun du bab /
NK126(cho)001:443: dgyes te bltas pas brda ma mjal /
NK126(cho)001:444: ma dgyes te rgyal po bshum pa las /
NK126(cho)001:445: cung zad lon nas des mi phen dgongs nas a
NK126(cho)001:446: tsa ra mkhas pa cig bangs chen pa spyan 'dren
NK126(cho)001:447: du rdzongs nas / o rgyan dang za hor la sogs pa yo ru btang pa las /
NK126(cho)001:448: a tsa ra kun mthun par 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:450: ma shes na zhal bzhu bar dgongs nas 'byon par ma bzhed do //
NK126(cho)001:452: der glang chen dang ma he la bkal te kun
NK126(cho)001:453: gyi spyan snga brim pas bstan bcos dang kri yog
NK126(cho)001:454: mkhan kun gyis gzigs kyang ma mkhyen nas /
NK126(cho)001:455: slar rgyal po yi phyag tu phul lo //
NK126(cho)001:456: yang thugs mug te bshums so //
NK126(cho)001:457: yang cung zad lon nas bsams pa /
NK126(cho)001:458: nga ni sgrib pa ma byang /
NK126(cho)001:459: tshogs ma rdzogs pas nyes so dgongs te /
NK126(cho)001:460: der rdo rje sems dpa' zla ba gsum bsgrub pas /
NK126(cho)001:461: der 'grub ste zhal dngos su mthong /
NK126(cho)001:463: rgyal pos bdag ni glegs bam 'di rnams kyi don rtogs par 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:465: der chags shing dang 'khor lo lag tu gtad de gnang ba byin no //
NK126(cho)001:466: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid nam mkha' la thim mo //
NK126(cho)001:467: de nas glegs bam rgyal pos gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:468: yi ge 'bru gcig ma lus par mkhyen te de nyid tu dgyes pa skyes so //
NK126(cho)001:469: de nas rdo rje sems dpa' bsgom te /
NK126(cho)001:470: rdo rje gsor zhing 'di skad brjod do //
NK126(cho)001:471: h+aum h+aum h+aum rdo rje 'du bar 'dus pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:472: rig ma yin pa rig mi 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:473: skal pa can rnams rig par gnas //
NK126(cho)001:474: thams cad rdo rje gsang bar rol //
NK126(cho)001:475: yak+sha kro ta tsit+ta dz+wa la ram /
NK126(cho)001:476: yak+sha kro ta dz+wa la ram /
NK126(cho)001:477: zhes brjod pas 'jig rten gyi dreg pa can rnams 'khor du 'dus te /
NK126(cho)001:479: gsang sngags kyi snod du rung bar byas so //
NK126(cho)001:480: de nas rang rang lag cha lag tu gtad /
NK126(cho)001:482: rnal 'byor pa'i grogs bya bar dam bcas so //
NK126(cho)001:483: de nas bsgrub pa lung gi gsang sgo phye te /
NK126(cho)001:484: rgyud rnams snod dang sbyar nas bsgrags so //
NK126(cho)001:485: de'i dus su rgyal po dza la lung bstan rdo rje zhes bya bar btags so //
NK126(cho)001:486: de ni phyag na rdo rje dngos su sh+aakya thub pa nyid do //
NK126(cho)001:487: des na bstan pa 'di yang sh+aakya thub pas brgyud nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:488: de'i dus lnga brgya phrag brgyad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:489: des ni ma h+aa yo ga dang a nu yo ga bshad de brgyud pa'i glengs gazhi'o //
NK126(cho)001:490: bde gshegs dgongs pas brgyud pa /
NK126(cho)001:491: lha mi rna bar brgyud pa /
NK126(cho)001:494: rgyu 'bras theg pa'i glengs gzhi dang /
NK126(cho)001:495: byung khungs bstan pa'i skabs de dang po'o ////
NK126(cho)001:496: da ni rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i theg pa rdzogs pa chen po bshad na /
NK126(cho)001:498: a ti yo ga 'di'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK126(cho)001:499: a ti yo ga sgra la 'bru bshad na /
NK126(cho)001:500: kun byed le'u brgya dgu pa nas /
NK126(cho)001:501: a ni ma skyes chos nyid rnal du bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:502: ti ni ma stsal lhun gyis grub par bstan //
NK126(cho)001:503: yo ga shin tu rnal 'byor rdzogs pa che //
NK126(cho)001:504: zhes pa chos nyid skye med rtogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:505: ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pa'i spyod pa ting nge 'dzin mtha' dag gi zhe phugs /
NK126(cho)001:506: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa de la rdzogs pas ma 'dus pa med do //
NK126(cho)001:507: rdzogs pa chen po zhes pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:509: chos sku byang chub sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:510: sangs rgyas rdzogs la sems can rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:512: bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis med rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:513: theg pa rdzogs la chos nyid rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:514: yod mtha' rdzogs la med mtha' rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:515: gcig rdzogs gnyis rdzogs thams cad rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:516: che ba gnyen po med pa che //
NK126(cho)001:517: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa de la rdzogs pas che //
NK126(cho)001:519: des na shin tu rnal 'byor la zhugs pa yang de la slob pa'i phyir ro //
NK126(cho)001:520: a ti rdzogs chen ming tsam bshad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:521: 'di la yang mdo byang bdun pa nas /
NK126(cho)001:522: rgyal po mnyes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:524: dad mos yod dam med dam /
NK126(cho)001:525: nyams bskyed pa'i sems sde dang /
NK126(cho)001:526: bka' phyin ci ma log pa'i gsha' ma'o //
NK126(cho)001:527: 'dra min la yang rgyud 'dra min dang /
NK126(cho)001:529: nyams bskyed la yang snga 'gyur lnga /
NK126(cho)001:531: bka' gsha' ma rgyud sde drug bcu tham pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:532: de la bam po nyi khri bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)001:533: de lta bu'i rgyud 'di la bshad lugs gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:534: sku gsum ston pa'i bshad lugs dang /
NK126(cho)001:535: byang sems man ngag gi bshad lugs gnyis so //
NK126(cho)001:536: kun byed le'u nyer gcig pa nas /
NK126(cho)001:537: byang chub sems ni ye nas rdzogs pa che //
NK126(cho)001:538: rdzogs pa che la bshad lugs rnam pa gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:539: sku gsum ston pa'i bshad lugs rnam lnga ni //
NK126(cho)001:540: byang chub sems ni rgyu 'bras 'das pa la //
NK126(cho)001:541: gtan tshigs don gyi bshad lugs rnam lnga bshad //
NK126(cho)001:544: don gyi bshad lugs rnam lnga ni //
NK126(cho)001:545: lo rgyus don gyi bshad pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:546: rtsa ba don gyi bshad pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:547: yo ga don gyis bshad pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:548: dgos ched don gyis bshad pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:549: tshig gi don gyis bshad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:551: lo rgyus don la gsum te /
NK126(cho)001:552: rang bzhin byin brlabs kyis bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:553: don gyi sgra tshig bsdeb pa'i bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:554: de gnyis thun mong lung gis bshad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:555: khyad par rdzogs pa chen po bka' gsha' ma'i bshad pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:556: badz+ra kha sa mu tra'i tan tra nas /
NK126(cho)001:557: chos rnams thams cad gtan la phab pa'i le'u nas /
NK126(cho)001:558: chos sku drang thad du bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:559: bstan pa ma lus ci snyed kun //
NK126(cho)001:560: bshad pa'i yan lag gsum gnyis gcig /
NK126(cho)001:561: rang byung ma bcos rnal du pheb //
NK126(cho)001:562: ces pa gsum gnyis gcig bsnan pas drug ste /
NK126(cho)001:563: lo rgyus kyi khung bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:564: don gyi snying po rtsa ba'i bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:565: rdzogs pa chen po thams cad rnal 'byor du bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:566: rang byung ma brtsal rang la rdzogs par bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:567: tshig bral yi ge med par bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:568: tshig dang yi ge'i don gyis bshad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:569: longs sku'i bzlog ste bshad na /
NK126(cho)001:570: de rtogs bya phyir gcig gsum gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:571: bzlog pas ci bzhin rnal du pheb //
NK126(cho)001:573: gcig gsum gnyis brtsegs pas drug ste /
NK126(cho)001:574: khungs kyis ma yin ngo bo nyid kyis bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:575: rtsa ba ma yin thams cad 'bras bur bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:576: rnal 'byor ma yin ma 'dres kun rdzogs su bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:577: rtsol bral ma yin brtsal bas 'byung bar bshad pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:578: tshig bral ma yin ming tshig ldan par bstan pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:579: tshig ldan ma yin ming tshig don la stong par bstan pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:580: sprul sku'i thabs ldan du bshad pa la /
NK126(cho)001:581: brda sgo lnga dang rim pa brgyad //
NK126(cho)001:582: yang dag rdzogs pa'i snying por ldan //
NK126(cho)001:583: bshad pa'i sgo ni bcu dang bzhi //
NK126(cho)001:586: sprul sku la gsum ste brda lnga /
NK126(cho)001:588: a ti la rim pa med /
NK126(cho)001:590: phun sum 'tshogs pa lnga nang du //
NK126(cho)001:591: chos kyi skus ni byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad //
NK126(cho)001:592: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus ni rang gi ngo bos ston //
NK126(cho)001:593: sprul pa'i skus ni don rnams tshig tu ston //
NK126(cho)001:595: de'i don mdo tsam du bdun mod nas /
NK126(cho)001:596: byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:597: rang bzhin chos dbyings gzhal yas nas //
NK126(cho)001:598: ston pa kun tu bzang po ni //
NK126(cho)001:599: mtshan ma'i sku gsum mi mnga' bar //
NK126(cho)001:600: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:601: bzang ngan blang dor med pa ru //
NK126(cho)001:602: kun bzang nyid tu byin brlabs nas //
NK126(cho)001:603: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs la brgyud //
NK126(cho)001:604: de ni byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad //
NK126(cho)001:606: snang srid byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su rang snang bzang ngan med /
NK126(cho)001:607: de phyir blangs dor med par 'dus par ston /
NK126(cho)001:608: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:609: skye med dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK126(cho)001:610: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' des //
NK126(cho)001:611: mtshan ma'i sku gsum mi mnga' bar //
NK126(cho)001:612: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:613: skye 'jig med pa'i ngo bo dang //
NK126(cho)001:614: rdo rje nga yi ngo bo ru //
NK126(cho)001:615: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan la //
NK126(cho)001:616: rig pa 'og min gnas su bshad //
NK126(cho)001:617: rang gi ngo bos bshad ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:618: 'di ltar snang srid chos nyid rang snang ba'i rtags su /
NK126(cho)001:619: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka nas phyag na rdo
NK126(cho)001:620: rje 'thon te tshig sdebs sbyor legs pa'i sgo nas
NK126(cho)001:621: bshad pa ni / dzam gling rgyud drug gnas 'di na //
NK126(cho)001:622: sprul pa'i sku dang ldan pa'i gang zag de //
NK126(cho)001:623: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:624: skye ba med pa'i tshig brjod nas //
NK126(cho)001:625: skye med don gyi ngo bo de //
NK126(cho)001:626: rin chen gser gyi glegs bam la //
NK126(cho)001:627: beed+aura zhun mas rang nan te //
NK126(cho)001:628: tshig dang yi ge sdebs nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:629: phyi rab rnal 'byor don du bshad //
NK126(cho)001:630: tshig sdebs legs pas bshad ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:631: zhes pas tshig sdebs sbyor legs bshad de /
NK126(cho)001:632: de yang 'di ltar lha'i bu de wa bzang skyong
NK126(cho)001:633: nyid bya ngang mo gser gyi gshogs pa can du
NK126(cho)001:634: sprul te / sras mo pa ra ni'i sras /
NK126(cho)001:635: ston pa dga' rab rdo rje sprul ste /
NK126(cho)001:636: des ri rab kyi rtse nas phyag na rdo rje spyan drangs te /
NK126(cho)001:637: rdo rje sems dpas gsung te dga' rab rdo rjes bsdus pa la bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:638: de la rgyas par bshad na /
NK126(cho)001:639: sku gsum re re la yang lnga lnga ste /
NK126(cho)001:645: ston pa sku gsum gyi don rgyas par bshad na /
NK126(cho)001:646: kun byed le'u bcu pa las /
NK126(cho)001:647: chos sku'i rang bzhin bstan pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:648: ma skyes gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang bzhin bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:650: ston pa chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin ni /
NK126(cho)001:651: rang gi sems nyid ma bcos pa'i gnas lugs mnyams
NK126(cho)001:652: pa nyid 'di ka chos sku'i ngo bo yin te
NK126(cho)001:654: mi rtogs mnyams pa nyid du gnas pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:655: spros bral chos sku'i ngo bo de //
NK126(cho)001:657: de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK126(cho)001:658: rtog med mnyam nyid chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:660: yang le'u bac+wo lnga pa las /
NK126(cho)001:661: sangs rgyas bya ba gzhan med rang sems de //
NK126(cho)001:662: rang sems ma bcos pa la chos kyi sku ru bshad //
NK126(cho)001:665: kun bzang rgyal ba mchog gi lha //
NK126(cho)001:666: byang chub mchog gi snying po yin //
NK126(cho)001:667: kun gyi ston pa byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:669: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)001:670: mi gnas chos kyi sku ru bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:673: ston pa chos sku'i bstan pa 'di lta ste //
NK126(cho)001:674: gsang ba bskyed dang gsang ba rdzogs pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:675: gsang ba rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin gsum //
NK126(cho)001:676: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin gsang bar bshad //
NK126(cho)001:678: bskyed pa ma h+aa'i theg pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:679: rdzogs pa a nu'i theg pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:680: rdzogs pa chen po a ti'i theg pa dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:681: chos sku'i bstan pa gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:683: ston pa chos kyi sku yi ni //
NK126(cho)001:684: rang bzhin gzung 'dzin bral bar bstan //
NK126(cho)001:686: rdzogs pa chen po gsang ba las /
NK126(cho)001:687: spros bral rtsol sgrub bral bar bshad //
NK126(cho)001:690: ston pa chos sku'i 'khor bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:691: nga yis byas pa'i 'khor rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:692: nga yi rang bzhin chos kyi sku 'khor yin //
NK126(cho)001:693: sangs rgyas sems can snang srid snod bcud kun //
NK126(cho)001:694: ston pa chos sku'i 'khor du ma 'dus med //
NK126(cho)001:696: ston pa chos kyi sku'i 'khor ni /
NK126(cho)001:699: rgyud drug gi sems can thams cad 'khor yin te /
NK126(cho)001:701: ston pa chos kyi sku 'khor ni //
NK126(cho)001:702: dus gsum sangs rgyas bzhugs pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:703: khams gsum rgyud drug sems can la //
NK126(cho)001:704: 'brel pa phun gsum tshogs par bshad //
NK126(cho)001:707: ston pa chos sku'i gnas ni 'di ltar te //
NK126(cho)001:708: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang de //
NK126(cho)001:709: yang dag don gyi 'og min de ru bshad //
NK126(cho)001:711: rang gi sems nyid mtha' dbus med pa nam mkha'
NK126(cho)001:712: lta bu 'di nyid ston pa chos sku'i bzhugs gnas
NK126(cho)001:713: yin te / de yang mdo bcu las /
NK126(cho)001:714: ston pa chos skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:715: nam mkha'i mtha' klas chos kyi dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:716: mtha' dang dbus med gnas kyi mchog /
NK126(cho)001:717: spros med gnas kyis kun tu khyab //
NK126(cho)001:718: kun bzang chos sku'i gnas chen po //
NK126(cho)001:721: ngas bstan 'khor gyi nang nas khyod sdud dang //
NK126(cho)001:722: gnyis med don nyid nga yi bstan pa gsum //
NK126(cho)001:723: 'tshogs pas dus gnas rang bzhin de la tshangs //
NK126(cho)001:725: ston pa chos sku'i 'dul ba'i dus la ni /
NK126(cho)001:728: da lta gsum bya ba med de /
NK126(cho)001:729: dus gsum ston pa mdzad pa la /
NK126(cho)001:731: snga ma phyi ma da lta gsum /
NK126(cho)001:732: khyad par med pa'i don 'di bstan //
NK126(cho)001:733: dus gsum med de khyad par gcig /
NK126(cho)001:734: kun bzang ye shes mchog thugs la //
NK126(cho)001:738: ston pa chos sku'i 'dul ba'i zhing khams na //
NK126(cho)001:739: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' yas klas pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:740: nam mkha'i khams kyis ji ltar khyab pa de //
NK126(cho)001:741: chos kyi sku yis 'dul ba'i zhing khams yin //
NK126(cho)001:743: nam mkha'i mthas khyab tshad de /
NK126(cho)001:744: ston pa chos sku'i 'dul ba'i zhing khams yin te /
NK126(cho)001:745: 'di tshod gcig chos sku'i 'dul ba'i zhing khams yin zhes bya ba'i tshad bzung du med de /
NK126(cho)001:747: ston pa chos sku'i byin gyis brlabs nas bshad //
NK126(cho)001:749: ya ki rgyal ba kun tu bzang po nas /
NK126(cho)001:750: ma ki 'jag mig gi srin bu yan chad bzang
NK126(cho)001:751: ngan blangs dor med par kun tu bzang por byin
NK126(cho)001:753: de yang mdo bcu'i bdun mdo las /
NK126(cho)001:754: byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:755: rang bzhin chos sku'i gzhal yas nas //
NK126(cho)001:756: ston pa kun tu bzang po ni //
NK126(cho)001:757: mtshan ma'i sku gsum mi mnga' yang //
NK126(cho)001:758: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:759: bzang ngan blangs dor med pa ru //
NK126(cho)001:760: kun bzang nyid du byin brlabs nas //
NK126(cho)001:761: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs la brgyud //
NK126(cho)001:762: byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:765: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)001:766: ji ltar 'dod pa'i longs spyod rdzogs par bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:769: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la longs spyod tshad bstan pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:771: rang bzhin 'byung ba skye ba'i cho 'phrul de //
NK126(cho)001:772: 'dod pa 'byung ba'i longs spyod rdzogs skur yin //
NK126(cho)001:775: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa yang //
NK126(cho)001:776: ye shes sku yi rang bzhin gyis //
NK126(cho)001:777: chu zla snang shel me long gi //
NK126(cho)001:778: ma bsgrib pa yi ngo bo la //
NK126(cho)001:780: rang byung ye shes rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)001:781: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:784: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i bstan pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:785: bya ba byed pa'i phyi pa sde gsum ste //
NK126(cho)001:788: u pa ya'i theg pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:789: yo ga'i theg pa gsum ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i bstan par gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:790: spros pa med pa'i rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:791: gsang ba rang brgyud dag pa yang //
NK126(cho)001:792: spros pa med pa'i rdo rjer bshad //
NK126(cho)001:795: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i 'khor ston pa //
NK126(cho)001:796: mos spyod bzhi yi sa la 'das nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:797: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa mnan nas //
NK126(cho)001:798: sa bcu chos kyi sprin gyis sa pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:799: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i 'khor du bstan //
NK126(cho)001:801: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad ni ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i 'khor yin te /
NK126(cho)001:803: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs 'khor ni //
NK126(cho)001:804: mi rtog ting 'dzin bcu sbyangs pas //
NK126(cho)001:805: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub la //
NK126(cho)001:806: nyon mongs mi gnas shes bya sbyangs //
NK126(cho)001:807: ye shes tshogs dang thugs rjer 'brel //
NK126(cho)001:810: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i gnas bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:811: 'jig rten mtshan ma kun gyi stengs gyur pa //
NK126(cho)001:812: gnas kyi 'og min khang bu brtsegs pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:813: gzhal yas khang de gnas kyi 'og min bshad //
NK126(cho)001:815: rigs drug gi gnas kyi 'og min yin te /
NK126(cho)001:816: sum bcu rtsa gsum lha'i gnas kyi stengs rin po
NK126(cho)001:817: che'i khang bu brtsegs pa'i gzhal yas khang der bshad
NK126(cho)001:818: pa yin te / mdo bcu las /
NK126(cho)001:819: ston pa 'jig rten gnas chen dang //
NK126(cho)001:821: rin chen gzhal yas bkod pa na //
NK126(cho)001:822: rin chen khang bu brtsegs gnas so //
NK126(cho)001:824: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus 'dul ba'i dus
NK126(cho)001:825: la yang snga ma phyi ma da lta gsum bya
NK126(cho)001:826: ba med de / kun byed las /
NK126(cho)001:827: 'dul ba'i dus la snga phyi phye ba med //
NK126(cho)001:830: snga ma phyi ma da lta gsum //
NK126(cho)001:831: khyad par med pa'i don 'di bshad //
NK126(cho)001:832: dus gsum med de khyad par gcig /
NK126(cho)001:835: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i zhing khams ni //
NK126(cho)001:836: rang las byung ba'i gzugs sgra dri ro reg /
NK126(cho)001:837: ji ltar 'dod pa'i longs spyod spyad pas 'dul //
NK126(cho)001:839: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la longs spyod pa thams
NK126(cho)001:840: cad ston pa la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yis
NK126(cho)001:843: longs spyod rdzogs pa rang gi ngo bos bshad //
NK126(cho)001:845: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i zhing //
NK126(cho)001:846: khams gsum rgyud drug gis sems can thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:847: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:849: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:850: skye med dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK126(cho)001:851: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK126(cho)001:852: mtshan ma'i sku gsum mi mnga' bar //
NK126(cho)001:853: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:854: skye 'jig med pa'i ngo bo dang //
NK126(cho)001:855: rdo rje nga yi ngo bo ru //
NK126(cho)001:856: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan la //
NK126(cho)001:857: rig pa 'og min gnas su bshad //
NK126(cho)001:858: rang gi ngo bos bshad ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:861: ston pa sprul sku'i rang bzhin bstan pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:862: ci ltar 'dul ba'i sku ru sprul nas gnas //
NK126(cho)001:864: 'gro ba'i don sku ci ltar yang sprul nas 'gro don sprul skus mdzad de /
NK126(cho)001:866: thugs rje sprul pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)001:867: rnam pa cir yang sprul te bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:870: thugs rje sku ltar 'dul ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK126(cho)001:871: de ni sprul pa'i sku yi ngo bo yin //
NK126(cho)001:874: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi bstan pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:875: nyan thos rang rgyal theg chen mdo sde gsum //
NK126(cho)001:877: rigs drug gi gnas su ston pa sprul pa'i sku yis /
NK126(cho)001:878: gang la gang 'tshams gang la gang dgos su sprul nas /
NK126(cho)001:879: bstan pa mtshan nyid sde gsum gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:881: ston pa sprul skur bzhugs tsam nas //
NK126(cho)001:882: sems can 'dod pa'i rang bzhin gyi //
NK126(cho)001:884: bskam chags lnga yi rnam smin de //
NK126(cho)001:885: rgyud drug gnas su nges par ston //
NK126(cho)001:886: lha dang lha min gnas ris su //
NK126(cho)001:887: che ba'i nga rgyal 'joms par bstan //
NK126(cho)001:888: shes pa mi yi gnas ris su //
NK126(cho)001:889: dge sdig rgyu 'bras sde snod bshad //
NK126(cho)001:890: gti mug byol song gnas ris su //
NK126(cho)001:891: rig pa shes pa'i chos kyang bstan //
NK126(cho)001:892: ser sna yi dwags gnas ris su //
NK126(cho)001:893: ma chags tshims pa'i chos kyang bshad //
NK126(cho)001:894: sdug bsngal dmyal ba'i gnas ris su //
NK126(cho)001:895: snga phyi dran pas zhen pa bzlog /
NK126(cho)001:898: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yis 'khor bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:899: mu steg mu rdug rgyang 'phan phyal ba bzhi //
NK126(cho)001:900: bla med byang chub lam las gtan gol ba //
NK126(cho)001:901: dbang po sems bsgyur thugs rjes byin brlabs nas //
NK126(cho)001:902: dge slong pho mo dge bsnyen pho mo bzhi //
NK126(cho)001:903: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi 'khor du bstan //
NK126(cho)001:905: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can thams cad ston pa sprul pa'i sku'i 'khor du gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:907: ston pa sprul pa'i sku'i 'khor ni /
NK126(cho)001:908: sku sprul thugs rje drug snang bas //
NK126(cho)001:909: 'khor yang rgyud drug sems can no //
NK126(cho)001:910: las dang thugs rje 'brel pas na //
NK126(cho)001:913: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi gnas bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:914: sprul pa'i sku ni rabs bdun sh+aakya thub //
NK126(cho)001:915: gnas ni bya rgod phung po'i gnas bstan te //
NK126(cho)001:916: yang dag thugs rje sprul pa nges med gnas //
NK126(cho)001:918: ston pa sprul pa'i sku sh+aakya thub pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:919: gnas bya rgod phung por gsungs pa las /
NK126(cho)001:920: ston pa sprul pa'i sku spyi'i gnas la nges pa med de /
NK126(cho)001:922: ston pa sprul sku'i gnas chen ni //
NK126(cho)001:923: rgyud lnga'i lam dang 'gro drug gnas //
NK126(cho)001:924: khams gsum thugs rje sprul pa'i gnas //
NK126(cho)001:925: thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:926: gnas la 'di zhes nges pa med //
NK126(cho)001:928: ston pas sprul pa'i skus 'dul ba'i dus ni /
NK126(cho)001:931: da lta gsum bya ba med do //
NK126(cho)001:933: 'dul ba'i dus la snga phyi phye ba med //
NK126(cho)001:936: snga dang phyi dang da lta gsum //
NK126(cho)001:937: khyad par med pa'i don 'di bstan //
NK126(cho)001:938: dus gsum med de khyad par cig /
NK126(cho)001:939: kun bzang ye shes thugs mchog las //
NK126(cho)001:941: skye 'gags med par khyad par gcig /
NK126(cho)001:944: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yis 'dul ba'i zhing khams ni //
NK126(cho)001:945: dzam bu gling ni bye ba phrag brgya las //
NK126(cho)001:946: rang byung ye shes thugs rje rgyud drug 'dul //
NK126(cho)001:948: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di na dzam gling bye ba phrag brgya /
NK126(cho)001:949: dzam gling bye ba phrag brgya po re re na rdo rje'i gdan bye ba phrag brgya na /
NK126(cho)001:950: sprul pa'i sku bye ba phrag brgya bzhugs pas /
NK126(cho)001:951: de'i bye ba phrag brgya po de ston pa sprul
NK126(cho)001:952: pa'i sku gcig gis 'dul ba'i zhing khams yin no
NK126(cho)001:954: sprul pa'i sku yis tshig dang don sdebs na //
NK126(cho)001:955: gang zag rna ba'i dbang por tshig don ston //
NK126(cho)001:957: sprul pa sku yis tshig dang yi ge sdebs bshad pas /
NK126(cho)001:958: ci ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:959: ston pa'i ngo bo ston pa ma rig ste //
NK126(cho)001:960: ston pa zhes pa'i khyad par 'dod sprul pas //
NK126(cho)001:961: don rnams tshig dang yi ge sgra brjod pas //
NK126(cho)001:962: tshig gi sgra des don rnams go byas nas //
NK126(cho)001:963: don de tshig sgras de yis bshad pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:965: don sprul pa'i skus tshig sdebs sbyor legs mos don go bar byed do //
NK126(cho)001:967: tshig sdebs sbyor legs par bshad pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:969: sprul pa'i gang zag skal ldan de //
NK126(cho)001:970: chos nyid skye ba med pa 'o //
NK126(cho)001:971: skye ba med pa'i tshig brjod pas //
NK126(cho)001:972: skye ba med pa'i don rtags su //
NK126(cho)001:973: rin chen gser gyi glegs bam la //
NK126(cho)001:974: beed+aura zhun mas rang nan gyis //
NK126(cho)001:975: tshig dang yi ger bris sdebs nas //
NK126(cho)001:976: phyi rab rnams kyi don du bshad //
NK126(cho)001:977: tshig sdebs legs pas bshad ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:979: chos sku'i ston pa spyi dang khyad par ro //
NK126(cho)001:982: stong pa mtshan ma med pa nam mkha' ltar 'dod /
NK126(cho)001:983: khyad par chos sku'i ston pa snang ba ma bcos pa /
NK126(cho)001:984: chos sku'i chos nyid rang snang ba la ma bcos pa /
NK126(cho)001:985: spang la sha mang rdol ba lta bu /
NK126(cho)001:986: gnas ni 'og min chos kyi dbyings so //
NK126(cho)001:987: 'khor yang snang srid snod bcud sangs rgyas thams cad do //
NK126(cho)001:988: de las 'dus shing 'phel ba'i phyir ro //
NK126(cho)001:989: dus ni dus gsum dbyer med pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:991: thugs rje byin gyis brlab nas bshad pa ste /
NK126(cho)001:992: de yang rin chen klong dgu'i rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)001:993: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung //
NK126(cho)001:994: 'dod lnga kun tu sbyor ba yang //
NK126(cho)001:995: sangs rgyas thugs rjes sprul pa shar //
NK126(cho)001:998: dmyal ba yi dwags byol song dang //
NK126(cho)001:999: lha dang lha min srin po mi //
NK126(cho)001:1000: bde sdug khyad par ci snang yang //
NK126(cho)001:1001: de dag thugs rje chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1004: nad dang mu ge mtshon dang gsum //
NK126(cho)001:1005: me chu rlung gsum nam mkhar stong //
NK126(cho)001:1006: de dag rim par ci snang ba //
NK126(cho)001:1007: thugs rje rmad 'byung rol pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1009: 'jig chags stong gnas kyang thugs rje chen po'o //
NK126(cho)001:1010: de kun la ma khyab pa'i skyon ni /
NK126(cho)001:1012: thugs rje chen pos ma khyab na //
NK126(cho)001:1013: las dang thugs rje 'brel pa med //
NK126(cho)001:1015: 'brel pa med pa 'dod thog zer na yang //
NK126(cho)001:1016: grol thar med pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:1018: kun la thugs rje mi snang na //
NK126(cho)001:1019: thugs rje dbri bkol can du thal te /
NK126(cho)001:1021: gang dang gang snang de dag la //
NK126(cho)001:1022: thugs rje chen po mi snang na //
NK126(cho)001:1023: thugs rje chen po yal lam ci //
NK126(cho)001:1025: la la snang la la mi snang na //
NK126(cho)001:1026: yang sems can la khyad par ci zhig yod //
NK126(cho)001:1029: ston pa spyi dang khyad par ni /
NK126(cho)001:1030: theg pa spyir mtshan des dang rgyan cha tshang ba /
NK126(cho)001:1031: byang chub sems kyi spyod yul lo //
NK126(cho)001:1032: khyad par du rig pa rang gsal du longs spyod pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:1034: rig pa ma sbyangs longs spyod rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1036: rig pa gnyen po ma sbyang pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:1039: rin chen gzhal yas bkod pa na //
NK126(cho)001:1041: grangs kyi 'og min dor ba'i don gyi 'og min no //
NK126(cho)001:1042: 'khor ni sa rim pa bcu la gnas pa'i sems can te /
NK126(cho)001:1044: dgongs pa sku dang ye shes bshad //
NK126(cho)001:1046: dus ni snang ba'i bskal pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:1047: ston pa ni rang gi ngo bos bshad pa ste /
NK126(cho)001:1048: kun byed le'u nyer lnga pa nas /
NK126(cho)001:1049: byang chub sems kyi ye shes te //
NK126(cho)001:1050: ston pa sa yi skur byung nas //
NK126(cho)001:1051: tshig dang yi ge mi ston te //
NK126(cho)001:1052: rang gi rang bzhi kun ston pa //
NK126(cho)001:1053: bdag tu mi rtog gzhan mi rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:1054: mi rtog mnyam pa'i dgongs pa ston //
NK126(cho)001:1055: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1056: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1057: rtsol ba'i chos nyid ma brtsal 'grub //
NK126(cho)001:1058: byang chub sems kyi ye shes de //
NK126(cho)001:1059: ston pa chu yi skur byung nas //
NK126(cho)001:1060: tshig dang yi ge mi ston te //
NK126(cho)001:1061: rang gi ngo bos chos ston pa //
NK126(cho)001:1062: bdag tu mi rtog gzhan mi rtos //
NK126(cho)001:1063: mi rtog mnyam pa'i dgongs pa can //
NK126(cho)001:1064: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1065: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1066: rtsol ba'i chos ni ma brtsal 'grub //
NK126(cho)001:1067: byang chub sems kyi ye shes de //
NK126(cho)001:1068: ston pa me yi skur byung nas //
NK126(cho)001:1069: tshig dang yi ge mi ston te //
NK126(cho)001:1070: rang gi ngo bos chos ston pa //
NK126(cho)001:1071: bdag tu mi rtog gzhan mi rtog //
NK126(cho)001:1072: mi rtog mnyam pa'i dgongs pa can //
NK126(cho)001:1073: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1074: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1075: rtsol ba'i chos ni ma brtsal 'grub //
NK126(cho)001:1076: byang chub sems kyi ye shes de //
NK126(cho)001:1077: ston pa rlung gi skur byung nas //
NK126(cho)001:1078: tshig dang yi ge mi rtogs te //
NK126(cho)001:1079: rang gi ngo bos chos ston pas //
NK126(cho)001:1080: bdag tu mi rtogs gzhan mi rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:1081: mi rtogs mnyam pa'i dgongs pa ston //
NK126(cho)001:1082: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1083: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1084: rtsol ba'i chos ni ma brtsal 'grub //
NK126(cho)001:1085: byang chub sems kyi ye shes de //
NK126(cho)001:1086: ston pa nam mkha'i skur byung nas //
NK126(cho)001:1087: tshig dang yi ge mi ston te //
NK126(cho)001:1088: bdag tu mi rtogs mi 'byed pa'i //
NK126(cho)001:1089: mi rtogs mnyam pa'i dgongs pa ston //
NK126(cho)001:1090: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1091: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1092: sngon 'byung ston pa de rnams kyis //
NK126(cho)001:1093: rang gi ngo bos chos 'chad pa //
NK126(cho)001:1094: 'di yis kun kyang rig par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:1097: gzugs sgra dri ro reg pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:1098: 'gro drug sems can thams cad rigs pas ston /
NK126(cho)001:1099: rang gi ngo bos bshad ces bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:1101: ston pa spyi dang bye brag go //
NK126(cho)001:1102: theg pa spyi ni thub pa drug la 'dod //
NK126(cho)001:1104: thugs rje'i mkhyen pa shar tshad sprul pa ste /
NK126(cho)001:1106: thugs rje sprul pa'i sku ru shar //
NK126(cho)001:1108: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' nas //
NK126(cho)001:1109: sems can dmyal ba yan chad la snyam snyoms su snang ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:1110: gnas 'dul ba'i dbang gis ma nges te //
NK126(cho)001:1112: thugs rje'i gnas la nges pa med //
NK126(cho)001:1116: khyad par du sa bcu nas khams gsum gyi sems can no //
NK126(cho)001:1120: dus ni sgron ma yangs su bkod pa'i dus so //
NK126(cho)001:1121: bstan pa spyi dang khyad par ro //
NK126(cho)001:1122: theg pa spyi mtshan nyid sde gsum //
NK126(cho)001:1123: khyad par du longs sku'i bstan pa tshigs su brjod pa kri yog gsum /
NK126(cho)001:1124: chos sku'i bstan pa bskyed rdzogs gsum /
NK126(cho)001:1125: tshigs su brjod pa mtha' dag gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:1126: sprul pa'i sku'i tshig sdebs sbyor legs par bshad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:1129: bshad lugs gnyis gtan la phab pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:1130: de ci ltar brgyud de byung ba'i khungs bstan pa ste /
NK126(cho)001:1131: bde gshegs dgongs pas brgyud pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:1132: kha sa man ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)001:1133: mi dang lha yi yul nas rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bstan cing mthar ston /
NK126(cho)001:1134: rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i theg pa ma byung ba'i sngon rol du /
NK126(cho)001:1135: sum bcu rtsa gsum lha'i yul du lha de wa
NK126(cho)001:1136: bzang skyong la bu gsum pho bo kun dga' snying
NK126(cho)001:1138: bzang skyong gis kyang brtags nas /
NK126(cho)001:1139: skye zla na tshod nas shes bzhin du kun las khyad par du 'phags pa'i rigs byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:1140: lha gzhan dag rang rang gi rdzings bu dang /
NK126(cho)001:1141: 'du khang du bskor yang kho pho brang du /
NK126(cho)001:1143: gzhan dag 'du tshal du rtsed 'jo byed kyang /
NK126(cho)001:1144: kho sku dang gtsug lag khang la bskor /
NK126(cho)001:1145: gzhan dag rol mo glu dang gar byed kyang /
NK126(cho)001:1146: kho chos grwa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgoms /
NK126(cho)001:1147: lha gzhan dag rang rang gi gnas khang du nyal yang /
NK126(cho)001:1148: kho 'khor lo dbur khang nang du nyal ba cig byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:1149: de la lha'i bu sems lhag can bya bar grags so //
NK126(cho)001:1150: lan gcig nyal ba'i srod kyi mtshan ma la lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis sna drangs te /
NK126(cho)001:1151: lha rnams kyis rin po che sna lnga'i khri la bzhag nas /
NK126(cho)001:1152: bskor ba byas pa mang du bsdad de /
NK126(cho)001:1153: kho'i spyi gtsug tu zhu zhing thims par rmi'o //
NK126(cho)001:1155: nyi ma'i 'khor lo gcig tu gyur nas /
NK126(cho)001:1156: srog shing gi rtse la babs pas khos blangs pa'i mtshan ma byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:1158: tho rangs kyi mtshan mar lha mchog ma h+aa de
NK126(cho)001:1159: ba ni 'jig rten gzhan na dbang che ba yang
NK126(cho)001:1160: khos zos te btang bar shar ro //
NK126(cho)001:1161: nang par lha'i dbang po brgya byin la bzlas pas /
NK126(cho)001:1162: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis ma mkhyen te /
NK126(cho)001:1163: badz+ra sa ma ya dza zhes pas /
NK126(cho)001:1164: sprul pa'i lha'i dbang po brgya byin spyan drangs te /
NK126(cho)001:1166: srod kyi de ni dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa thugs su chud pa'i rtags yin no //
NK126(cho)001:1167: nam gung de ni rgyu 'bras la bzla ba'i theg pa nyid la 'char te /
NK126(cho)001:1168: 'od nyi ma ltar dro ba 'ong ba yin no //
NK126(cho)001:1169: tho rangs kyi de ni dug gsum rtsad nas bcad
NK126(cho)001:1170: nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa yin no
NK126(cho)001:1171: // zhes mtshan ma bzang bar lung bstan no //
NK126(cho)001:1172: der lha'i dbang po brgya byin shin tu dgyes te /
NK126(cho)001:1173: zhal phyogs bzhir gzigs shing bskul ba /
NK126(cho)001:1174: khyod ni gsung gi rdo rje bdag /
NK126(cho)001:1175: rgyu 'bras thegs pa mthar phyungs nas //
NK126(cho)001:1176: rtsol med thegs pa mi gsungs pa //
NK126(cho)001:1177: thugs rje chen po su tra ha //
NK126(cho)001:1178: gdul bya mchog ldan yod pa na //
NK126(cho)001:1179: rtsol med lhun grub bshad du gsol //
NK126(cho)001:1181: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad nam mkha' la sprin
NK126(cho)001:1182: gtib pa bzhin du 'dus nas de nyid snyan du
NK126(cho)001:1183: bsnyad do // kun gyi bgros te mgrin gcig tu /
NK126(cho)001:1184: rdo rje sems dpa' la 'di skad ces basgo'o //
NK126(cho)001:1185: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1186: thugs kyi rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:1187: sangs rgyas kun gyi mdzad pa shar //
NK126(cho)001:1188: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1189: ye shes rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:1190: thams cad ye shes gsal bar mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:1191: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1192: sku yi ngo bor khyod ldan pas //
NK126(cho)001:1193: rmad byung rol pa'i sku ru shar //
NK126(cho)001:1194: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1195: gsung gi bdag nyid rig pa'i gsung //
NK126(cho)001:1196: rmad byung rol pa'i gsung du shar //
NK126(cho)001:1197: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1198: mdzad pa'i rang bzhin nyid ldan pas //
NK126(cho)001:1199: tshig gi don kun rdzogs pa'i bdag /
NK126(cho)001:1200: rin chen 'phrul gyi snying po skor //
NK126(cho)001:1201: skal ldan rnams la gcig par bskul //
NK126(cho)001:1202: ces sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngas bstod do //
NK126(cho)001:1205: rin chen 'phrul gyi thabs ldan pas //
NK126(cho)001:1206: gang 'thad mthun pa'i sgo de nas //
NK126(cho)001:1207: rtsol med dbyigs dang sprad par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:1209: la bzla ba'i theg pa gsungs ces par bskul lo //
NK126(cho)001:1211: dang la tshig tu smros shig pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:1213: byang chub sems kyi dngos po la //
NK126(cho)001:1214: brjod pa'i tha snyad kun bral yang //
NK126(cho)001:1215: ma rtogs blo la tshig go nas //
NK126(cho)001:1216: gsung gi sgron mes gsal bar gyis //
NK126(cho)001:1218: bsgo ba'i don go de rdo rje sems dpa' skad
NK126(cho)001:1219: cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin las thugs ka nas phyag
NK126(cho)001:1220: na rdo rje dngos su 'thon nas /
NK126(cho)001:1221: rin po che rang 'bar gyi 'khor lo lag tu gtad de /
NK126(cho)001:1223: gnyis med ye shes gsang ba'i don //
NK126(cho)001:1224: byar med mi rtsol ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:1225: dbu ma chen po drangs po'i lam //
NK126(cho)001:1226: 'dus pa'i tshogs la khyod kyi ston //
NK126(cho)001:1228: de nas phyag na rdo rjes 'di skad khas blangs so //
NK126(cho)001:1229: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK126(cho)001:1230: tshig gi spyod yul ma yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:1231: bdag gis bsgro bar rnam par dka' //
NK126(cho)001:1232: ma rtogs blo la tshig bsgo nas //
NK126(cho)001:1233: mtshon nas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:1234: ci rigs par ni rnam par bsgro //
NK126(cho)001:1235: zhes khas blangs dam bcas nas phyag na rdo rjes
NK126(cho)001:1236: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyis dgongs pa dang mi
NK126(cho)001:1238: dus gsum sangs rgyas rigs lngar 'dus la /
NK126(cho)001:1239: rigs lnga'i dgongs pa nyams su blangs ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1240: shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams rdo rje rnam par gnon pa'i zhing khams na /
NK126(cho)001:1241: bde bar gshegs pa rdo rje gsang ba rdo rje'i brag stengs na bzhugs nas /
NK126(cho)001:1242: mi phyed pa'i 'khor la gsang sngags kyi de kho
NK126(cho)001:1243: na nyid dus gsum du ston cing bzhugs pa la
NK126(cho)001:1244: zhus pa / sems nyid rdo rje lta bu las //
NK126(cho)001:1245: skye dang 'gag pa ci ltar byung //
NK126(cho)001:1248: sems nyid mi 'gyur rdo rje la //
NK126(cho)001:1249: skye 'gag yod pa ma yin te //
NK126(cho)001:1250: rnam rtog blo las skye 'gag byung //
NK126(cho)001:1251: ces gsungs pas the tshom bcad do //
NK126(cho)001:1252: lho phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams rin chen snang ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK126(cho)001:1253: bde bar gshegs pa rin chen 'byung ldan rin po che rang 'bar gyi gdan la bzhugs nas /
NK126(cho)001:1254: mi phyed pa'i 'khor la gsang sngags kyi de kho
NK126(cho)001:1255: na nyid dus gsum du ston cing bzhugs pa la
NK126(cho)001:1256: zhus pa / byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin las //
NK126(cho)001:1257: rgyu rkyen rtsol bas ma bsgrub pa //
NK126(cho)001:1261: dag sha ka yi rgyan bzhin du //
NK126(cho)001:1262: rgyu 'bras mthar phyin gzhi nas rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1263: thams cad rang byung snying po'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:1264: gsang ba thabs kyi rtogs gyur na //
NK126(cho)001:1268: nub phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams pad+ma can zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK126(cho)001:1269: bde bar gshegs pa pad+ma'i 'od ces bya ba dri ma med pa pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs nas /
NK126(cho)001:1270: mi phyed pa'i 'khor la gsang sngags kyi de kho
NK126(cho)001:1271: na nyid dus gsum du ston cing bzhugs pa la
NK126(cho)001:1272: zhus pa / sems nyid pad+ma ltar dag la //
NK126(cho)001:1273: gzung 'dzin dri ma ci ltar byung //
NK126(cho)001:1277: 'dam gyi skyon gyis gos pa med //
NK126(cho)001:1278: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo de //
NK126(cho)001:1280: rnam rtog blo las 'khor ba byung //
NK126(cho)001:1281: zhes gsungs pas the tshom bcad do //
NK126(cho)001:1282: byang phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams rnam dag grub pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK126(cho)001:1283: bde bar gshegs pa don yod grub pa rgya gram
NK126(cho)001:1284: gyi gdan la bzhugs nas dgongs pa mi phyed pa'i
NK126(cho)001:1285: 'khor lo // gsang sngags kyi don kho na nyid
NK126(cho)001:1286: dus gsum du ston cing bzhugs pa la zhus pa
NK126(cho)001:1287: 'khor lo // / rtsol med sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK126(cho)001:1291: rang byung ye shes rtogs gyur na //
NK126(cho)001:1292: mdzad pa byin gyis brlabs la 'char //
NK126(cho)001:1293: zhes gsungs pas the tshom bcad do //
NK126(cho)001:1294: dbus phyogs kyi 'jig rten khams mtha' dang bral ba'i zhing khams na /
NK126(cho)001:1295: bde bar gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad /
NK126(cho)001:1296: 'khor lo'i gdan la bzhugs nas dgongs pa chos nyid
NK126(cho)001:1297: las mi g.yo bar nyid kyi 'khor khyad par can
NK126(cho)001:1298: dang dgongs pa mi phyed pa la gsang sngags kyi
NK126(cho)001:1299: de kho na nyid dus gsum du ston cing bzhugs
NK126(cho)001:1300: pa la / thugs las sprul pa'i phyag na rdo rje des zhu bar rngo ma thogs te /
NK126(cho)001:1301: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis zhabs drung du bsdad pas /
NK126(cho)001:1302: rnam par snang mdzad kyis mdangs gsal te gnang ba /
NK126(cho)001:1304: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs kyi bcud //
NK126(cho)001:1305: ye shes gsang don rtogs par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:1306: don de nges par ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:1307: bim pa ra yi 'bras bu bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:1310: de nas phyag na rdo rje rang gi stan las langs te /
NK126(cho)001:1311: seng ge'i lta ltangs kyis zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:1312: khyod ni mi 'jigs seng ge ste //
NK126(cho)001:1313: ye shes gsang don ma rtogs par //
NK126(cho)001:1314: bim pa ra yi 'bras bu bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:1316: ye shes gsang don rtogs par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:1317: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag khyod kyi gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:1318: ding dus bdag gi ma rig pas //
NK126(cho)001:1319: ye shes gsang don bstan du gsol //
NK126(cho)001:1322: ye shes gsang ba'i ngo bo ni //
NK126(cho)001:1323: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK126(cho)001:1324: nam mkha' bzhin du kun la khyab //
NK126(cho)001:1325: ma rig ye shes tha dad med //
NK126(cho)001:1326: ma rtogs rtogs pa lam du gcig /
NK126(cho)001:1327: ye shes gsang ba'i rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)001:1328: rang rig 'od gsal rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:1329: rnam rtog ye shes nyid du gsal //
NK126(cho)001:1330: gzhi bzhag rang lugs rin chen mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:1331: rang byung ma brtsal gdod nas dag /
NK126(cho)001:1332: ye shes gsang ba'i dam pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:1333: sna tshogs snang la ngos bzung med //
NK126(cho)001:1334: mi dmig sgyu ma lhun grub yin //
NK126(cho)001:1335: rtag par gsal na lta ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:1336: zhes gsungs pas the tshom bral te /
NK126(cho)001:1340: 'bras bu rgyu la rag ma lus /
NK126(cho)001:1341: lam la rim pa med par gting rnyed do //
NK126(cho)001:1343: bde bar gshegs pa dgongs pas brgyud pa'i skabs te gsum pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:1344: de nas lha gnas gsum du babs te /
NK126(cho)001:1345: phyag na rdo rje'i sprul pa des /
NK126(cho)001:1346: thugs kyi sprul pa grangs med bkye ste /
NK126(cho)001:1347: skye mched mu bzhi'i gnas su /
NK126(cho)001:1348: gzhi mtshan des ni rnam pa gsum //
NK126(cho)001:1349: mun pa chu dang nyi mas bstan //
NK126(cho)001:1351: ngo bo gnyis med smag gi mun rum ltar bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1352: mtshan nyid nyi ma shar ba ltar /
NK126(cho)001:1353: snang ba chu yi nyer ma ltar bshad de /
NK126(cho)001:1359: srog gi dbang po la brten pa las /
NK126(cho)001:1360: thugs rje bstan pas yid kyi lhun grub gsum du go zhing gding rnyed do //
NK126(cho)001:1363: gzugs med khams ni dngos med grub //
NK126(cho)001:1364: yul med chos la med bzhin blta //
NK126(cho)001:1365: gzung 'dzin med pa'i rigs pa'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:1366: ston pa'i sku dang gsungs dor de //
NK126(cho)001:1367: mi gnas mtshan ma'i yul las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:1369: thugs rjes yid ches par gang zhig rtogs so //
NK126(cho)001:1370: de nas gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun du /
NK126(cho)001:1373: gzugs khams kyi lha la 'di skad do //
NK126(cho)001:1375: tshig dang don la snyabs kyi sbyar //
NK126(cho)001:1377: ngo bo gnyis med me tog ltar /
NK126(cho)001:1378: mtshan nyid rang gsal mar me ltar /
NK126(cho)001:1379: rnam pa gnas skabs 'bab chu ltar bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:1380: gzugs kyi khams ni chags pa'i gnas //
NK126(cho)001:1381: nga rgyal chags pas mngon grub pas //
NK126(cho)001:1382: gzugs la nga rgyal ltar mi 'os //
NK126(cho)001:1383: ston pas bstan pa gsum du ston //
NK126(cho)001:1384: ltung bas chags med gsum du ston //
NK126(cho)001:1386: lha tshangs pa la sogs pa'i bsam gtan bzhi la bcu gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:1387: gtsang ma rigs kyi lha lnga ni //
NK126(cho)001:1389: bsam gtan dang po dag na med //
NK126(cho)001:1396: gzhal yas khang dang dus mnyam du skye /
NK126(cho)001:1397: 'chi ba'i tshe yang 'ja' tshon yal ba ltar 'gro /
NK126(cho)001:1399: snang ba tsam du lhun grub gsum du go zhing gding rnyed do //
NK126(cho)001:1400: de nas 'dod khams lha drug la /
NK126(cho)001:1401: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas ri rab kyi steng /
NK126(cho)001:1405: grong khyer chen po lta na sdug /
NK126(cho)001:1406: de'i dbus na rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang na /
NK126(cho)001:1408: rtsigs pa rin po che sna lnga /
NK126(cho)001:1411: de'i rtse srog shing gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu bslang ba /
NK126(cho)001:1412: der sngar gyi lha'i bu de ba bzang skyong /
NK126(cho)001:1413: bu kun dga' snying po la bstan /
NK126(cho)001:1414: thugs kyi sprul pa phyag na rdo rje ni /
NK126(cho)001:1415: srog shing gi steng na yar ta la bdun srid tsam gyis steng na /
NK126(cho)001:1416: dgongs pa mi g.yo ba gsal ba /
NK126(cho)001:1417: phyag gser mdog can brgyang ste 'od zer spros nas /
NK126(cho)001:1418: rgyal byed kun dga' ra ba nas sam gtan las bslang ste /
NK126(cho)001:1420: srog shing rtse mor gser gyi 'khor lo'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK126(cho)001:1421: rin po che rang 'bar gyi 'khor lo'i gdugs phub ste /
NK126(cho)001:1424: ngo bo ma grub kun gyi chos //
NK126(cho)001:1426: rnam pa cir yang ma 'gags shar //
NK126(cho)001:1427: ces pas lhun grub gsum mo //
NK126(cho)001:1428: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK126(cho)001:1429: gdams ngag 'phrul gyi lung bcu phog /
NK126(cho)001:1430: thig le chen po'i dbang bskur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1431: sems nyid 'gyur med kyi gdams ngag phog /
NK126(cho)001:1432: mi 'gyur bstan pa'i dbang bskur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1433: spyod lam rig pa'i gdams ngag byin //
NK126(cho)001:1434: sgra tshig rig pa'i dbang bskur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1435: ye shes ngos bzung gi gdams ngag byin //
NK126(cho)001:1436: lhun grub gsum gyi dbang bskur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1437: sku gsung thugs 'phrad kyi gdams ngag byin //
NK126(cho)001:1438: gnyis med 'brel pa'i dbang bskur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1439: phyag rgya chen po'i gdams ngag byin //
NK126(cho)001:1440: rdo rje lung 'dus kyi dbang bskur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1441: rgyal tshab bskor ba'i gdams ngag byin //
NK126(cho)001:1442: ces de ltar dbang dang 'brel ba'i gdams ngag bdun byin /
NK126(cho)001:1445: rgyal tshab la mi yul du bstan pa sgrogs shig par lung phog go //
NK126(cho)001:1447: brtsol med gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:1448: lha gnas gsum du bsgrags gyur nas //
NK126(cho)001:1449: sprul sku gang zag thugs sras kyi //
NK126(cho)001:1450: dzam gling dbus su rgyas par byos //
NK126(cho)001:1452: 'dod lha la yang rgyal po nyi ma rin chen ltar //
NK126(cho)001:1454: ngo bo gnyis med rgya mtsho'i gting ltar mi g.yo bar bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1455: mtshan nyid rang rig nyi ma shar ba ltar /
NK126(cho)001:1458: 'phel gyi nor bu dgos dgu ldan par ltar bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:1459: 'dod lha rnams kyis lta ba'i gdings rnyed do //
NK126(cho)001:1461: dgongs pa sangs rgyas snyegs so //
NK126(cho)001:1463: lha gnas gsum du ci ltar grags pa'i skabs de bzhi pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:1464: rgya gar yul du ci ltar babs pa na /
NK126(cho)001:1465: dbus rdo rje gdan gyi shar phyogs /
NK126(cho)001:1466: yul rgya phub d+ha na ko sha'i gling /
NK126(cho)001:1468: mda' bdag rgyal po d+ha na ta lo la /
NK126(cho)001:1469: sras thu bo ra tsa hasti /
NK126(cho)001:1470: sras mo pa ra mi tra /
NK126(cho)001:1471: tsha bo bde byed pa ra mi tra bdag po las /
NK126(cho)001:1472: sras mo de dge sems lhag par che ba /
NK126(cho)001:1473: dad pa dang brtson 'grus kyi chos dang mi 'bral ba /
NK126(cho)001:1474: rab tu byung ste dge slong ma'i khrims thams cad rdzogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1476: dge slong ma lnga brgyas bskor ba /
NK126(cho)001:1477: de la ston zla ra ba'i nya'i tho ras nyi
NK126(cho)001:1478: ma gcig shar nas spyi bo nas thim zhing rmi
NK126(cho)001:1479: / zla ba gcig shar nas rkang mthil nas khang du thim zhing rmis /
NK126(cho)001:1480: rtogs pa skyes nas mtsho ku kra ka lar phyin nas khrus byas te /
NK126(cho)001:1481: chos spyod rdzogs nas kha shar du bltas nas bsdad pas /
NK126(cho)001:1482: bya ngang pa lnga bab ste khrus byas bzhi nam mkha' la 'phur nas song /
NK126(cho)001:1483: gcig slar log ste sras mo'i thugs kar chags nas
NK126(cho)001:1484: gser gyi gshogs pa can des thugs kar mchu len
NK126(cho)001:1485: gsum gtug nas thugs kar gser gyi rdo rje rtse
NK126(cho)001:1486: lnga pa 'od 'bar ba zhig bzhag go //
NK126(cho)001:1487: der dgyes pa skyes te yab la sogs pa 'khor yan chad bsags te /
NK126(cho)001:1488: rmi lam dang bya ngang pa'i gtam bsnyad pas kun dgyes so //
NK126(cho)001:1489: yab shin tu dgyes te sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa zhig 'ong nges gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:1490: nya ra dang rim gro cher mdzad nas /
NK126(cho)001:1491: zla ba lnga nas sras shig thugs ka nas bltams te /
NK126(cho)001:1492: lag na rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK126(cho)001:1493: ngag tu yang rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhes sgrogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1494: zhal bzhad mdangs dang ldan pa byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:1495: der yab 'khor rnams gros byas te /
NK126(cho)001:1496: bram ze mtshan mkhan la mtshan zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:1497: 'di ni thog ma nas rgyal po yab sras dang
NK126(cho)001:1498: 'khor rnams bzhi dgyes shing mdangs dang ldan phyag na
NK126(cho)001:1500: ngag tu yang rdo rje'i tshig sgrogs pas /
NK126(cho)001:1501: dga' rab rdo rje mtshan btags so //
NK126(cho)001:1503: gzhon nu'i rol rtsed la sogs pa mdzad pa mtha'
NK126(cho)001:1504: dag mthar phyung rgyal sa bzung ba'i khrims kun byas
NK126(cho)001:1505: nas / thugs rang rdol du byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:1507: tho cho dang ras chod du song gi dogs nas kun gyi mngon sum du /
NK126(cho)001:1508: re ma ti lcags kyi dre'u rta rkang gsum zhon pa zhig bangs chen du bardzongasa nas /
NK126(cho)001:1509: nam mkha' la phyag na rdo rje mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa zhig spyan drangs te /
NK126(cho)001:1510: de la gdan dgu brtsegs bting /
NK126(cho)001:1513: des dbang dang 'brel ba'i gdams ngag gsum /
NK126(cho)001:1514: sngon lha gnas ltar du dbang bskur /
NK126(cho)001:1517: dbang rtags gser gyi chags shing zhig lag tu gtad do //
NK126(cho)001:1518: dga' rab rdo rje rgyal tshab tu zhog la bstan pa sgrogs shig par bka' basgo'o //
NK126(cho)001:1519: phyag na rdo rje tu sku sprul thugs rje sku yis stong gsum zil gyis gnon /
NK126(cho)001:1520: gsung gi rig pas gsung gi bstan pa rgyas par bshad //
NK126(cho)001:1521: rang byung ye shes thugs su ma chud med //
NK126(cho)001:1522: rnam pa rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum //
NK126(cho)001:1523: ma bcos bde bar lhun gyis grub //
NK126(cho)001:1524: sgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1525: sku gsung thugs la rten mi 'cha' //
NK126(cho)001:1526: rig pa blo yis ma spyad na //
NK126(cho)001:1527: rang bzhin thog tu pheb par gyur //
NK126(cho)001:1528: ces gsungs nas nam mkha' la gshegs so //
NK126(cho)001:1529: des mngon shes lnga dang ldan pa'i dga' rab rdo rje la bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:1531: bdag ni dga' rab rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:1532: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan //
NK126(cho)001:1533: mngon shes sha yis spyan gyis ni //
NK126(cho)001:1534: stong gsum 'jig rten sa ler mkhyen //
NK126(cho)001:1535: mngon shes lha yi spyan gyis ni //
NK126(cho)001:1537: mngon shes shes rab spyan gyis ni //
NK126(cho)001:1538: chos nyid skye 'gag med par mkhyen //
NK126(cho)001:1539: mngon shes chos kyi spyan gyis ni //
NK126(cho)001:1540: ye nas ye sangs rgyas par mkhyen //
NK126(cho)001:1541: mngon shes sangs rgyas spyan gyis ni //
NK126(cho)001:1542: lhun grub gsum gyi gding rnyid nas //
NK126(cho)001:1543: sangs rgyas sa gsum dus gsum dus gcig non //
NK126(cho)001:1544: skye 'chi med pa'i chos sku thob //
NK126(cho)001:1545: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1546: sems las skye 'gag med pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:1547: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas te //
NK126(cho)001:1548: de las ma brtsal bzhag na bsgoms pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1549: nam mkha'i dbyings nas nam mkha'i cho 'phrul shar //
NK126(cho)001:1550: rang byung rang zhir bzhag na nam mkha' nyid kyi dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:1551: sems kyi klong nas sems kyi byung tshor byung //
NK126(cho)001:1552: rang byung rang zhir bzhags na bsgoms pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1554: des sgrib pa rnam gnyis byang nas mkhyen rab gsal
NK126(cho)001:1555: ba'i 'jam dpal gyi dngos grub brnyes pa'i 'jam dpal
NK126(cho)001:1558: nga ni 'jam dpal bshes gnyen te //
NK126(cho)001:1559: sgrib pa rnam gnyis sngon nas byang //
NK126(cho)001:1560: yon tan mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal //
NK126(cho)001:1561: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dngos grub thob //
NK126(cho)001:1562: chos nyid mnyam par chen por don rtogs so //
NK126(cho)001:1563: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1564: 'byung ba lnga dang rigs kyi yum lngar mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1565: phung po lnga dang rigs kyi yab lngar mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1566: rang sems kun bzang rdo rje sems dpar mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:1567: de ltar rtogs na mnyam pa chen po ste //
NK126(cho)001:1568: mnyam pa'i don las ma yengs bsgoms pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1570: des byang chub kyi sems yang dag par rtogs pa'i rgyal po d+ha na ta lo la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1572: bdag ni d+ha na ta lo ste //
NK126(cho)001:1573: sems ni nam mkha'i dbyings dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:1574: nam mkha'i dbyings la mtha' dbus med //
NK126(cho)001:1575: nam mkha'i dbyings la gzhi rtsa med //
NK126(cho)001:1577: nam mkha'i dbyings la skye 'chi med //
NK126(cho)001:1578: sems kyi dpe ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:1579: byang chub sems la mtha' dbus med //
NK126(cho)001:1580: sems kyi ngang la gzhi rtsa med //
NK126(cho)001:1582: rtogs na lta ba ma yin bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1583: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1584: sems la mtha' dbus med pas bsgom bya bsgom byed med //
NK126(cho)001:1585: sems la gzhi rtsa med pas bsgom pa'i gtad 'dzin bral //
NK126(cho)001:1586: sems la 'pho 'gyur med pas bsgom pa res 'jog med //
NK126(cho)001:1587: sems la skye 'chi med pas bsgom bya blang dor med //
NK126(cho)001:1588: de ltar rtogs pa'i don las med yongs na //
NK126(cho)001:1589: bsgom pa bya ba de las gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:1591: des rigs rgyud mi chad par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:1592: sras thu bo ra ts+aa bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1594: bdag ni ra tsa ha sti ste //
NK126(cho)001:1595: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa'i rigs //
NK126(cho)001:1596: rang rig byang chub sems kyis 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:1597: dus gsum sangs rgyas rigs kyang byang chub sems kyis 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:1598: rang rig skye med byang chub sems kyi don //
NK126(cho)001:1599: sangs rgyas bo d+hi rig 'dzin sa gsum dus gcig non //
NK126(cho)001:1600: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1601: rang gi sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas te //
NK126(cho)001:1602: sems dang sangs rgyas gnyis med rtogs na bsgoms pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1603: sems la 'pho 'gyur med par rtogs na sa gsum cig tu non //
NK126(cho)001:1604: de ltar rtogs na ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1606: des chos nyid kyi don rtogs nas mnyam par sbyor
NK126(cho)001:1607: ba'i phyir sras mo pa ra mi ta la bshad
NK126(cho)001:1609: bdag ni sras mo pa ra mi ta ste //
NK126(cho)001:1610: 'byung lnga rigs kyi yum lnga gnyis med mnyam par sbyor /
NK126(cho)001:1611: phung po lnga dang rigs kyi yab lnga gnyis med mnyam par sbyor /
NK126(cho)001:1612: rang sems kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis med mnyam par sbyor /
NK126(cho)001:1613: de ltar rtogs na sbyor ba yang dag yin //
NK126(cho)001:1614: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1615: sems la skye 'chi med pas 'byung ba lnga ni skye ba'i rgyun yang bcad //
NK126(cho)001:1616: sems la 'gag pa med pas phung po lnga ni 'gag pa'i mtha' las bsal //
NK126(cho)001:1617: skye ba'i rgyun bcad 'gag pa'i mtha' bsal bas //
NK126(cho)001:1618: bsgom pa chen po'i klong du ye nas bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:1620: des dregs pa can 'dul ba chags pa can bsal ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1623: bdag ni klu yi rgyal po 'jog po te //
NK126(cho)001:1624: dug gsum ma spang sku gsung thugs //
NK126(cho)001:1625: dug lnga ma spang ye shes lnga //
NK126(cho)001:1627: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1628: sems dang bag chags gnyis su med //
NK126(cho)001:1629: gnas su dag na snang ba mtha' yas yin //
NK126(cho)001:1630: mtshan mar chags na 'dod chags yin //
NK126(cho)001:1631: dug gsum g.yos na sku gsum thugs //
NK126(cho)001:1632: g.yos pa nyid na sku gsum g.yo ba med //
NK126(cho)001:1633: de ltar bzhag na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1635: des chags pa spang ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:1636: thams cad dbang du bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1637: gnod sbyin mo byang chub mo la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1639: bdag ni gnod sbyin byang chub ste //
NK126(cho)001:1640: rang gi sems ni rdo rje sems dpa' yin //
NK126(cho)001:1641: rdo rje sems dpa' gud na bsgom du med //
NK126(cho)001:1642: rang gi sems ni chos kyi sku yang yin //
NK126(cho)001:1643: chos kyi sku ni gud na bsgrub tu med //
NK126(cho)001:1644: de ltar rtogs pa'i dbang du kun yang 'du //
NK126(cho)001:1645: de ltar rtogs pa'i dam la kun yang gnas //
NK126(cho)001:1646: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1647: rang sems rdo rje sems dpar rab rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)001:1648: rtogs pa'i don las ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1649: bsgom par bya ba de las gud na med //
