NK126(cho)001:1651: des thag lta bas chod cing spyod pas la dor ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1652: smad tshong ma bdag nyid ma la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1654: bdag ni smad tshong bdag nyid ma //
NK126(cho)001:1655: lta ba'i rgyal po byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:1656: sems la pho mo med pas sbyor yang nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:1657: sems la skye 'chi med pas bsgral yang gnas mi lci //
NK126(cho)001:1658: snang srid bdud rtsir shes pas gtsang sme ye nas med //
NK126(cho)001:1659: de ltar rtogs na lta bas thag chod pas /
NK126(cho)001:1660: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1661: rang gi sems ni ye nas sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:1662: de la ma brtsal bzhag na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1663: rang gi sems rtogs ye nas bdud rtsi yin //
NK126(cho)001:1664: bdud rtsi gzhan nas btsal te bsgrub tu med //
NK126(cho)001:1665: de ltar rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1667: des ye shes kyi rig pa rtogs shing don dang mi 'gal ba bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1668: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1670: bdag ni kha che'i mkhan po rab snang ste //
NK126(cho)001:1671: chos kun phyi nang gsang bar bshad na don dang mi 'gal lo //
NK126(cho)001:1672: ston pa'i lung la rig pa tshad mas bshad na don dang mi 'gal lo //
NK126(cho)001:1673: bsam dngos gnyis ldan tshad ma bzhi dang 'brel bar bshad na don dang mi 'gal lo //
NK126(cho)001:1674: de ltar rtogs na lta ba'i don rtogs so //
NK126(cho)001:1675: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1676: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas te //
NK126(cho)001:1677: bsgom par bya ba de las gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:1678: bsgom bya de las rig pas rtags mi bya //
NK126(cho)001:1679: sems nyid sangs rgyas don la ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1681: des nges pa'i lung rtogs shing rig 'dzin sa la 'god par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:1682: u rgyan gyi mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dza la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1684: bdag ni ma h+aa r+aa dza ste //
NK126(cho)001:1685: 'byung ba lnga ni rigs kyi yum lngar nges //
NK126(cho)001:1686: phung po lnga ni rigs kyi yab lngar nges //
NK126(cho)001:1687: rnam shes yul ni sems dpa' sems mar nges //
NK126(cho)001:1688: yul sems rig pa kun bzang yab yum nges //
NK126(cho)001:1689: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1690: rtogs pa'i don las ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1691: nges pa gcig gi don rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)001:1692: bsgom pas rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK126(cho)001:1693: ma bsgom pas kyang stor bral med //
NK126(cho)001:1694: mnyam par bzhag na bsgom par yin //
NK126(cho)001:1696: des bsgrub pa'i gzhung dang mthun cing dngos grub nye
NK126(cho)001:1697: bar bya ba'i phyir sras mo go ma de byi
NK126(cho)001:1699: bdag ni go ma de byi ste //
NK126(cho)001:1700: 'byung ba la ni rigs kyi yum lnga la //
NK126(cho)001:1701: phung po lnga ni rigs kyi yab lnga yin //
NK126(cho)001:1702: khams dang skye mched sems dpa' sems ma la //
NK126(cho)001:1703: kun gzhi kun tu bzang mo la //
NK126(cho)001:1704: yid ni kun tu bzang po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1705: yab yum thabs dang shes rab ldan na gzhung dang mthun //
NK126(cho)001:1706: gnyis med mnyam par sbyor na dngos grub thob //
NK126(cho)001:1707: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1708: kun gzhi ma bcos ci bzhin pa //
NK126(cho)001:1709: yid ni ma bsgrib de bzhin pas //
NK126(cho)001:1710: kun gzhi yul ni yid kyi mthong //
NK126(cho)001:1711: yid dang kun gzhi gnyis su med //
NK126(cho)001:1712: de las ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1714: des thabs la mkhas pa'i spyod pa dang mthun par
NK126(cho)001:1715: bya ba'i phyir a tsar+ya a lo ke la bshad
NK126(cho)001:1717: bdag ni a tsar+ya a lo ke /
NK126(cho)001:1718: sgrol ba'i thabs la mkhas pas skye ba'i rgyud yang bcad //
NK126(cho)001:1719: sbyor ba'i thabs la mkhas pas 'gag pa'i mtha' yang bsal //
NK126(cho)001:1720: phrin las thabs la mkhas pas bya bstsal gnyis ka spang //
NK126(cho)001:1721: dngos grub thabs la mkhas pas gzhan la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1722: bsgom pa thabs la mkhas pas rnal ma ci bzhin bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:1723: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1724: khyad du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:1725: spyod mtha' mang na rtogs mtha' che //
NK126(cho)001:1726: ma spyad mnyam par bzhag na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1728: des rig 'dzin gyi sa la bkod cing skye 'chi med pa la thag chod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1729: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku ra dza la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1731: bdag ni ku ku ra dza ste //
NK126(cho)001:1732: sems la skye 'chi med pa rdo rje sems //
NK126(cho)001:1733: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku ni kun la khyab //
NK126(cho)001:1734: nam mkha'i dpe ni mtshon du med //
NK126(cho)001:1735: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1736: rang sems rdo rje sems dpar rab rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)001:1737: rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1739: des rigs byed yan lag bdun dang ldan cing ye
NK126(cho)001:1740: shes kyi rtsal rdzogs bya ba'i phyir drang srong sa
NK126(cho)001:1743: bdag ni drang srong sa ra sha ti ste //
NK126(cho)001:1744: 'byung ba lnga ni rtsal ni nam mkha'i dbyings su rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1745: srid pa gsum gyi rtsal ni chos kyi dbyings su rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1746: theg pa dgu yi rtsal ni a ti yo gar rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1747: dus gsum sangs rgyas rtsal ni byang chub sems la rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1748: byang chub sems rtogs rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:1749: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1750: sems la rdzogs pas sems nyid sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:1751: sems la mtha' dbus med pa brdal ba chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1752: sems la skye 'gag med pas dngos grub chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1753: bsgom pa bya ba de las gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:1755: des chos rigs yum gyi mkha' zab mo'i ngang nyid
NK126(cho)001:1756: yin pa'i phyir smad tshang ma bdag nyid ma la
NK126(cho)001:1758: bdag ni smad tshong bdag nyid ma //
NK126(cho)001:1759: 'byung ba lnga ni rigs kyi yum lnga'i mkha' //
NK126(cho)001:1760: de nyid kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' //
NK126(cho)001:1761: kun tu bzang mo chos kyi dbyings kyi mkha' //
NK126(cho)001:1762: rang rig kun gzhi kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' //
NK126(cho)001:1763: de ltar rtogs na nam mkha' dbyings zab bo //
NK126(cho)001:1764: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1765: byang chub sems ni mkha' la zla shar 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:1766: rang rig rtogs par ldan na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1767: sems la sems bsgom ma g.yos dbyings las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:1768: de ltar rtogs na bsgom pa chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1770: des bde ba chen po'i don rtogs shing sa nas
NK126(cho)001:1771: sa ru spar bar bya ba'i phyir na ga 'dzu
NK126(cho)001:1773: bdag ni na ga 'dzu na ste //
NK126(cho)001:1774: skye med chos kyi sku la phung po med pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:1775: gsung med rig pa'i gsung la 'gag pa med pa bde //
NK126(cho)001:1776: thugs med ye shes thugs la skye 'chi med pa bde //
NK126(cho)001:1777: de ltar go na bde chen don rtogs so //
NK126(cho)001:1778: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1779: bde chen byang chub sems la dngos po mtshan mar bsgom du ye nas med /
NK126(cho)001:1780: bsgom du med pa'i don las ma yengs bsgom //
NK126(cho)001:1782: des sngar ma rig pa rig par bya ba'i phyir khyi'i mkhan po phyi ma la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1784: bdag ni khyi yi mkhan po d+ha h+au na //
NK126(cho)001:1785: ma rig 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:1786: rig pas brtags na byang chub chen po gcig /'byung ba lnga dang phung po lnga //
NK126(cho)001:1787: lha dang lha mor rab rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)001:1788: gnyis med sbyor ba rtogs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1789: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1790: yid kyi yul ni kun gzhi ste //
NK126(cho)001:1791: kun gzhi'i yul ni yid kyi mthong //
NK126(cho)001:1793: gnyis med 'dres na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1795: des rig gnyis brgyud pa dang gus pa'i rtags bstan pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1798: bdag ni 'jam dpal phyi ma ste //
NK126(cho)001:1799: rigs gnyis sbyangs ba'i yon tan dang //
NK126(cho)001:1800: sbyongs pa'i 'phro dang grub pa'i mthu ru ldan //
NK126(cho)001:1801: da lta nyid nas 'bras bu mngon sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:1802: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1803: sems kyi rtsa ba chod nas ma yengs na //
NK126(cho)001:1804: bsgom par bya ba de las gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:1806: des nges pa'i lung rtogs shig /
NK126(cho)001:1807: man ngag gi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1808: de ba ra tsa mu ne btsun la bshad de /
NK126(cho)001:1810: bdag ni de ba ra tsa ste /
NK126(cho)001:1811: a ti yo ga kun tu bzang po'i lung //
NK126(cho)001:1812: lung las brten nas bshad pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK126(cho)001:1813: sems kyi gting du bcangs la khar mi 'byung //
NK126(cho)001:1814: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1815: stong pa'i chos la stong pa'i sems kyis gnas //
NK126(cho)001:1816: stong pa chen por yin par rab rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)001:1817: stong pa de nyid mi 'gyur chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:1818: de las ma yengs pa ni bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1820: des ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don shes pa'i phyir b+hud+d+ha gusta la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1822: bdag ni sangs rgyas gsang ba ste //
NK126(cho)001:1823: byar med ye sangs rgyas pas rgyud 'bras gdod nas med //
NK126(cho)001:1824: rang sems ye nas sangs rgyas yin pas kun la gsang //
NK126(cho)001:1825: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1826: rang sems bya bstsal med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:1827: ma yengs brten pa bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1829: des lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1832: bdag ni sh+ri seng ha ste //
NK126(cho)001:1833: 'dod chags gsung ste snang mtha' yas //
NK126(cho)001:1834: zhe sdang thugs rje rdo rje sems //
NK126(cho)001:1835: gti mug sku ste rnam snang mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:1836: dug gsum ma spangs sku gsung thugs //
NK126(cho)001:1837: dug lnga ma spangs ye shes lnga //
NK126(cho)001:1838: 'khor ba ma spangs ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:1839: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1840: dug gsum rtsa ba byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:1841: sems kyi chos nyid stong pa la //
NK126(cho)001:1842: sku gsung thugs kyang brtags pa tsam //
NK126(cho)001:1843: de las ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1845: des theg pa dgu'i don a ti yo gar 'dus pa las /
NK126(cho)001:1846: de rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:1847: dge slong ma kun dga' mo la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1849: bdag ni dge slong kun dga' mo //
NK126(cho)001:1850: dper na chu bo chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:1851: chu bran thams cad 'dus par ltar //
NK126(cho)001:1852: theg pa rim pa dgu bstan yang //
NK126(cho)001:1853: rdzogs chen a ti yo gar 'dus //
NK126(cho)001:1854: a ti yo gar ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:1855: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1856: chos rnams rtsa ba sems su 'dus //
NK126(cho)001:1857: sems ni rang gi ma bcos 'od gsal ba //
NK126(cho)001:1858: de don ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1860: dus der dge slong ma bud med kyi rang bzhin snod dang ma ldan te /
NK126(cho)001:1861: chos tshang dus kyi 'dom ltar bslad de lan gcig 'chal lo //
NK126(cho)001:1862: des snod dang skal bar ldan pa'i phyir bi ma la mi tra la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:1864: bdag ni bi ma la mi tra ste //
NK126(cho)001:1865: sgrib pa'i dri ma kun dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:1866: sangs rgyas bstan pa ci snyed pa //
NK126(cho)001:1867: sde snod gsum dang rgyud gsum dang ldan pa //
NK126(cho)001:1868: theg pa rim dgu bstan pa kun //
NK126(cho)001:1869: nga yi sku gsung thugs su 'dus //
NK126(cho)001:1870: phyag rgya chen po'i sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:1871: bsgom na 'byung ba lnga la rag ma lus //
NK126(cho)001:1872: 'byung ba nam mkha' stong pa'i rgyan //
NK126(cho)001:1873: chos nyid rol pa bsam yas chos sku'i rgyan //
NK126(cho)001:1874: rgyan des 'dus byas rnam rtog gnyen pos bshig tu med //
NK126(cho)001:1875: sangs rgyas ye shes spyan la gzigs su med //
NK126(cho)001:1876: snang med ye shes gsal ba la /
NK126(cho)001:1877: sangs rgyas bcos par mi mdzad do //
NK126(cho)001:1878: de bzhin ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1881: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gsum gyi
NK126(cho)001:1882: dgongs nyams rin po che'i phreng ba ltar du brgyud
NK126(cho)001:1886: dpal kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1888: kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa'i don rdo rje sems dpas /
NK126(cho)001:1889: byang chub kyi sems ci ltar du gnas pa de /
NK126(cho)001:1890: ban+d+ha gsum 'dus pas go zhing rtogs te /
NK126(cho)001:1891: kun tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i sa la sangs rgyas so //
NK126(cho)001:1894: rang gi ngo bos brgyud pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:1895: a ho zhes bka' stsal pa /
NK126(cho)001:1896: a ni skye ba med pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1898: skye 'gag dbyer med don la gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:1899: dgongs pa nam mkha'i klong la zhog /
NK126(cho)001:1900: ye shes bar do chos skur sbyor //
NK126(cho)001:1902: klong dgu bam po nyi khri pa'i don bsdus pa gcig tu go zhing rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1905: snyan khung nas snyan khung du brgyud de /
NK126(cho)001:1906: brtags pa thams cad don med sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK126(cho)001:1907: tha mal shes pa snying gi dbus su sad //
NK126(cho)001:1908: tshogs drug ngang nas bde ba rgyun mi chad //
NK126(cho)001:1909: bsgom du med kyi gnyug ma'i ngang du zhog /
NK126(cho)001:1911: rtsol bsgrub med pa'i don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1912: de rgyal po d+ha he ta lo la gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1913: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:1914: gzung 'dzin byas pa 'du 'bral can du bslad //
NK126(cho)001:1915: rang gi sems la dpyod la rtogs par rum du sod //
NK126(cho)001:1916: des 'du 'bral med du rtogs na bsgom du ye nas med //
NK126(cho)001:1918: don rnams rtogs ye shes su rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1919: des sras thu bo ra dza ha sti la gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:1920: sems ni ye nas chos sku chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:1921: gzung 'dzin ye nas med pas rnam rtog ye nas med //
NK126(cho)001:1922: 'khor 'das chos sku nyid du thag chod pas //
NK126(cho)001:1923: bsgom du med kyi tshogs drug lhug par zhog /
NK126(cho)001:1925: rang sems chos skur thag chod par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1926: des sras mo pa ra ni la gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:1927: gzhi dang rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK126(cho)001:1928: rgyu dang rkyen gyis ma bskyed rang byung yin //
NK126(cho)001:1929: ma bcos ngang du gsal ba ye shes yin //
NK126(cho)001:1930: de la gnas su med pas bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1932: rang gi sems rang byung gi ye shes su rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1933: des klu yi rgyal po 'jog po la gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1934: yul drug ma 'gag bde zhing rgyas par spyod //
NK126(cho)001:1935: ci ltar rol yang byang chub bgos su che //
NK126(cho)001:1936: rang rig rgyal po'i dbang thob gding ldan pas //
NK126(cho)001:1937: tshogs drug lhug par bzhag na bsgoms pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1939: rang gis sems bsgom du med par rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1940: des gnod sbyin mo byang chub mo la gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1941: 'gyur med dbu ma de la gnas pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:1942: sgo gsum spyod pa ci ltar spyad pa kun //
NK126(cho)001:1943: rang byung ye shes rol pa chags med snang //
NK126(cho)001:1944: gang ltar spyad kyang tshogs gnyis rdzogs par yin //
NK126(cho)001:1946: 'bad rtsol can gyis spyod pa dbyer med par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1947: des smad tshong ma pa ra ni la gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1948: yang dag bsgom tshe 'jug pa med //
NK126(cho)001:1949: gal te 'jug na bslad pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1950: ci yang yid la mi byed na //
NK126(cho)001:1951: ma nor don la phebs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1953: rang gi sems gzung 'dzin gyis bslad du med par rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1954: des rgyal po de ba ra tsa la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:1955: kun gzhi chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:1956: sgo lnga ye shes rtog med gsal //
NK126(cho)001:1957: rin chen gser gyi gling du phyin tsa na //
NK126(cho)001:1958: rnal ma'i blo skyes ga la srid //
NK126(cho)001:1960: rang gis sems thig le nyag gcig tu don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1961: des smad tshong ma 'bu tha ku tha ma la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:1962: ming du btags na rtogs pa nam kyang skye //
NK126(cho)001:1963: de la rjes su bzung na bzang ngan nam kyang 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:1964: ming las log na 'khor 'das gnyis ka rdzun //
NK126(cho)001:1965: btags pa log na chos nyid ma dang 'phrad //
NK126(cho)001:1967: rang gi sems 'khor 'das su btags pa las dben par rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1968: des khyi'i mkhan po ku ku ra tsa la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:1969: ming dang btags pa kun gyis ma bslad na //
NK126(cho)001:1970: tshogs drug ye nas rang grol chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1971: de yi don la gnas na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1972: yid chos bsten na chos sku thob pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1974: rang gi sems 'bras bu la the tshom mi za bar don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1975: des rgyan gyi mkhan po ma ha ra dza la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:1976: ming dang tshig tu kun gyis btags pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:1977: 'khrul pa yin te chos nyid mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:1978: rang grol don la su zhig gang gnas pa //
NK126(cho)001:1979: de ni chos sku chen po thob pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1981: rang gis sems chos sku mngon du gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1982: des sras mo go ma de byi la gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:1983: dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa chos sku thig le nyag gcig ngang //
NK126(cho)001:1984: lam la bsgrod du med de rang grol gcig gi ngang //
NK126(cho)001:1985: chos nyid bshad du med de tshig gi mtha' dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:1986: chos nyid rtogs su med de bsam brjod mtha' dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:1987: de'i phyir ni bsgom du med //
NK126(cho)001:1989: rang gi sems bsgom du med par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1990: des a tsar+ya a lo ke la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:1991: sa dang rnam thar 'dod na byang chub nyid las 'gyong //
NK126(cho)001:1992: bde ba thob par 'dod na sdug bsngal chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:1993: mi rtog thob par 'dod na de ga rtogs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:1994: de ltar rtogs na brtsal du med par zhog /
NK126(cho)001:1996: rang gi sems la btsal du med pa'i don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:1997: des khyi'i mkhan po phyi ma la bshad pa //
NK126(cho)001:1998: gzhi lam 'bras bus phye bas 'khrul pa bsam las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:1999: yul sems gnyis med rtogs na rtogs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2000: de gnyis gnyis med rtogs na ye shes yin //
NK126(cho)001:2001: 'byung 'jug med par rtogs na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2002: snang ba 'dzin med go na bsgom gyi ngo bo yin //
NK126(cho)001:2004: rang gi sems snang ba thams cad rang grol du thag chod par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2005: des drang srong b+ha shi ta la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2006: skye 'gag med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2007: snang ba rang bzhin med pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2008: bsgom du med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2009: rnal 'byor bde ba nyal na btsun //
NK126(cho)001:2011: rang gi sems brtsol ba med par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2012: des dge slong ma bdag nyid ma la bshad pa //
NK126(cho)001:2013: ci yang yid la mi byed na //
NK126(cho)001:2014: shes rab chen po rtogs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2016: bsgom pa klong du pheb pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:2018: sems 'du shes can 'khrul pa yin par thag chod par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2019: des n+aa ga 'dzu na la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2020: btags na stong par btags kyang 'chings //
NK126(cho)001:2021: chags na yi dam la chags kyang 'chings //
NK126(cho)001:2022: brtags na chos skur btag kyang 'chings //
NK126(cho)001:2023: bsgom na mi rtogs bsgom yang 'chings //
NK126(cho)001:2025: rang gi sems bcings grol med par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2026: des 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2027: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyi stong na stong pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2028: de la 'dzin pa med na stong pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2029: ming dang tha snyad log na stong pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2030: de la gnas na stong nyid bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2032: rang gi sems stong pa nyid du thag chod par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2033: des de ba ra dza la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2034: khyung dang seng ge bzhin te btsol bsgrub nyams nga med //
NK126(cho)001:2035: bu chung ri bo bzhin du 'dzin med yul mi bzlog /
NK126(cho)001:2036: smyon pa gar mkhan bzhin de thogs med 'gro don byed //
NK126(cho)001:2037: nor bu nyi ma bzhin de thugs rjes gzhan don mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:2039: rang gi sems lta bsgom spyod 'bras la thogs rdug med par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2040: des b+hud+d+ha gusta la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2041: de bzhin nyid du thag chod na //
NK126(cho)001:2042: gang ltar byas kyang mi rtogs skye //
NK126(cho)001:2043: rang sems chos sku thag chod na //
NK126(cho)001:2044: ci ltar snang yang bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2046: rang sems the tshom dang nyam nga med par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2047: des dge slong ma kun dga' ma la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2048: rang byung ye shes ma yin pa //
NK126(cho)001:2049: 'khor ba bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2050: chos nyid bde chen ma yin pa //
NK126(cho)001:2051: myang 'das bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2053: rang gi sems 'khor 'das su 'dzin pa 'khrul pa yin par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2054: des sh+ri sing ha la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2055: bya ba btang ba'i sems bzhin du //
NK126(cho)001:2056: ci ltar snang ba de ltar zhog /
NK126(cho)001:2057: de ltar dran pa'i stobs ldan na //
NK126(cho)001:2058: sangs rgyas dgongs pa yin par nges //
NK126(cho)001:2060: rang gi ci ltar gnas pa thig le nyag gcig las ma g.yos par don rtogs par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2062: snyan rgyud rin po che'i phreng ba man ngag sangs
NK126(cho)001:2063: rgyas mdzub tshugs su bstan pa'i skabs te drug pa'o
NK126(cho)001:2064: //// yang dga' rab rdo rjes 'di skad du /
NK126(cho)001:2065: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la bka' stsal pa /
NK126(cho)001:2066: byang chub sems ni mi nub rgyal mtshan te //
NK126(cho)001:2067: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje sems dpa' yin //
NK126(cho)001:2068: sems kyis kun la khyab pas kun tu bzang po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2069: snang srid 'khor ba'i chos dang mya ngan 'das pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:2070: sems ni kun nas snang bas rnam par snang mdzad yin //
NK126(cho)001:2071: che ba'i yon tan 'byung ba rin chen 'byung ldan yin //
NK126(cho)001:2072: sems kyi rang bzhin ci yang snang ba la //
NK126(cho)001:2073: gza' gtad dmigs pa med pas snang ba mtha' yas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2074: byang chub sems ni ye nas sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2075: btsal bas med par grub pas don yod grub pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2076: sems nyid stong pa'i rang bzhin pas //
NK126(cho)001:2077: stong pa'i ngang las gzhag pas chos rnams byung //
NK126(cho)001:2078: rang byung rang zhir bzhag na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2081: rgyal po d+ha he ta lo la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2082: byang chub sems ni 'byung ba chen po lnga //
NK126(cho)001:2083: snang med kun la khyab pas nam mkha' yin //
NK126(cho)001:2084: sems la sangs rgyas 'grub pas ye shes pa //
NK126(cho)001:2085: rtogs pa'i bag chags 'khrul pas ye shes chu //
NK126(cho)001:2086: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma bsregs pas ye shes me //
NK126(cho)001:2087: ma bskyod gnas su phyin pas ye shes rlung //
NK126(cho)001:2088: sems kyi yon tan 'byung ba chen po lnga //
NK126(cho)001:2089: de ltar snang yang sems la mtshan ma med //
NK126(cho)001:2090: mtshan ma med pa'i dngos grub rang byung rang zhir bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:2092: rgyal po d+ha he ta los sems kyi don bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:2093: byang chub sems ni dus gsum sangs rgyas te //
NK126(cho)001:2094: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyang sems nyid yin //
NK126(cho)001:2095: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK126(cho)001:2096: sems nyid min pa gcig kyang med //
NK126(cho)001:2097: slad kyi byon pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK126(cho)001:2098: sems kyi rang bzhin rtogs par snang //
NK126(cho)001:2099: dus gsum sangs rgyas sems su gcig /
NK126(cho)001:2100: sngon med phyi med gdod nas byung //
NK126(cho)001:2101: de yi ngang la bzhag na sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2103: sras thu bo r+aa dza ha stis sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2104: byang chub sems ni chos sku ste //
NK126(cho)001:2105: sems la phung po med pas dar zhing gud pa med //
NK126(cho)001:2106: sems la skye 'chi med pas bsad cing bcad du med //
NK126(cho)001:2107: thams cad sems su 'dus pas chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:2108: de ltar rtogs na sangs rgyas dgongs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2110: klu yi rgyal po 'jog pos sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2111: byang chub sems ni mi nub rgyal mtshan ste //
NK126(cho)001:2112: mtha' la thug pa med cing dbyings la bri ba med //
NK126(cho)001:2113: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pa'i g.yung drung ste //
NK126(cho)001:2114: 'khor ba'i g.yul las rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan yin //
NK126(cho)001:2115: de ltar rtogs na rtogs pa'i rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2117: gnod sbyin ma byang chub kyis sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2118: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK126(cho)001:2119: rang byung chen po bcom ldan 'das //
NK126(cho)001:2120: sems la 'khor ba med pas ye nas rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:2121: sems la 'pho 'gyur med pas mi 'gyur byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2122: de ltar bu yi don rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)001:2123: sangs rgyas dgongs pa kho na'o //
NK126(cho)001:2125: smad tshong ma bdag nyid mas sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2126: rgyud las ma byung 'bras bu byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2127: lung las ma byung man ngag byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2128: sems las ma byung sems nyid byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2129: snang rgyu med pa'i nam mkha' byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2130: kha dog med pas 'di zhes dmigs su med //
NK126(cho)001:2132: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang gis sems kyis don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2133: sems nyid stong pa chen po'i ngang las ni //
NK126(cho)001:2134: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams thams cad byung //
NK126(cho)001:2135: ci ltar byung yang sems la 'bri ba med //
NK126(cho)001:2136: sems nyid mtshan ma med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK126(cho)001:2137: mtshan ma'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs ci skyes kyang //
NK126(cho)001:2138: sems kyi de nyid mtshan mas bskyed du med //
NK126(cho)001:2139: ci ltar skyes kyang rang byung rang zhir bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:2141: u rgyan mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dzas sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2142: sems las bsgom pas bsgom pa'i yul las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:2143: sems la bltas pas mthong ba ci yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2144: mthong med mthong ba de nyid mthong ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:2145: mthong ba'i don las ma yengs bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2147: sras mo go ma de ba'i sems kyi don bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:2148: sems la brtags na snang ba ci yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2149: snang ba med pas sna tshogs cir yang snang //
NK126(cho)001:2150: ci ltar snang yang sems las g.yos pa med //
NK126(cho)001:2151: ma g.yos mnyam par bzhag na bsgom pa'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:2153: a tsar+ya a lo kis sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2154: sems kyi des ni nam mkha' yin //
NK126(cho)001:2155: sems kyi yul ni chos nyid yin //
NK126(cho)001:2156: sems kyi ngo bo chos sku yin //
NK126(cho)001:2157: sems kyi 'bras bu sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2158: de phyir sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos na //
NK126(cho)001:2159: mnyam pa chen po'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2161: drang srong b+ha shi tas sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2162: sems nyid stong pa chen po'i rang bzhin las //
NK126(cho)001:2163: gzugs dang kha dog phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor byung //
NK126(cho)001:2164: ci ltar byung yang sems las g.yos pa med //
NK126(cho)001:2165: ci ltar snang ba thams cad chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:2167: d+har+m+aa r+aa dzas sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2168: sems la dngos po med pas nam mkha' stong pa'i ngang //
NK126(cho)001:2169: sems la mtshan ma med pas chos nyid dbyings kyi ngang //
NK126(cho)001:2170: sems la skye 'chi med pas skye med chen po'i ngang //
NK126(cho)001:2171: sems la 'du 'bral med pas thig le chen po'i ngang //
NK126(cho)001:2173: smad tshong ma 'bu ta pa ma tis sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2174: sems la ye shes shar bas nam mkha'i nyi ma shar //
NK126(cho)001:2175: stong par lhag ste ma rig mun pa sel //
NK126(cho)001:2176: sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pas ma btsal lhun gyis grub ste rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NK126(cho)001:2177: 'khor 'das sems su gcig ste khyad par so sor med //
NK126(cho)001:2179: na ga 'dzu nas sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2180: sems nyid chos sku yin pas 'khor ba'i bdud rtsi yin //
NK126(cho)001:2181: rang gis sems ni bdud rtsi'i rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2182: de ltar rtogs na 'khor ba'i g.yul las rgyal //
NK126(cho)001:2183: sems nyid rgyal ba yin par yid chos so //
NK126(cho)001:2185: dge slong ma kun dga' mos sems kyi don bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:2186: rang gi sems ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:2187: nam mkha'i rang bzhin stong pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2188: rang gi sems ni sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2189: sangs rgyas rang bzhin skye 'chi med //
NK126(cho)001:2191: 'khor ba'i skyon gyis gos pa med //
NK126(cho)001:2192: rang gi sems ni rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:2193: che ba'i yon tan rang la byung //
NK126(cho)001:2195: khyi'i mkhan po phyi mas sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2196: sems la sems kyi ming du btags pa'i ming dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:2197: sems la dpe yis mtshon kyang dpe med mtshon dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:2198: sems la dmigs pa bcug kyang dmigs pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:2199: sems la rtogs pa bcug kyang gnyen pos bcos su med //
NK126(cho)001:2201: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi mas sems kyi don bstan pa //
NK126(cho)001:2202: nam mkha'i rgya ni dbus med de //
NK126(cho)001:2203: byang chub sems la mtshon du med //
NK126(cho)001:2204: mtshon du med de byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2205: brtsol med ngang la bzhags na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2207: rgyal po de ba r+aa dzas sems kyis don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2208: sems nyid 'du 'bral med pa'i rtogs pa chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2209: sems las rigs pa shar bas rig pa'i rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2210: sems la 'khor ba med pas bdud rtsi'i rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2211: sems la mtha' dbus med pa dkyil 'khor chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2213: b+hud+d+ha gub+tasa sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2214: snang ba med pa'i sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2215: snang ba'i don la brten par bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:2216: rtsol ba sna tshogs sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2217: ma brtsal bzhags na bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2218: 'gyur med sems kyis rtsa ba ma chod na //
NK126(cho)001:2219: sangs rgyas gzhan nas tshol ba tshi re chad //
NK126(cho)001:2221: sh+ri sing has sems kyi don bstan /
NK126(cho)001:2222: mtshan ma'i rgyu las 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2223: mngon sum mi gnas snang srid kun la khyab //
NK126(cho)001:2224: tha snyad med pa'i sems la ming gis 'di zhes bstan pa med //
NK126(cho)001:2225: rdo rje sems dpa' mtshon du med //
NK126(cho)001:2227: bi ma la mi tras sems kyi don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2228: chos nyid bsam du med pas nam mkha' che //
NK126(cho)001:2229: nam mkha' bsam pa kun dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:2230: bsam du med pa'i sems nyid las //
NK126(cho)001:2231: chos nyid bsgoms pas rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK126(cho)001:2232: ma bsgom pas kyang stor bral med //
NK126(cho)001:2233: ma bsam snyams pa'i don nyid bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2236: 'da' ka ma'i zhal chems mdzub tshugs su bstan pa'i skabs te bdun pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:2237: yang de'i skabs su rgyal po d+ha he ta los do ha rdo rje'i glu /
NK126(cho)001:2238: tsan+dana nags tshal du nam gyi gung la blangs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2239: h+aum 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2240: kun gzhi ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2242: mi snang gzugs med byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2243: cir yang mi dpyad rtogs pa mi bzung zhing //
NK126(cho)001:2244: sems kyi rang bzhin bsam med mkha' 'dra la //
NK126(cho)001:2245: ma bslad ma yengs bcos pa med par bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:2246: des na bsgom du med pa'i chos nyid dbyings chen las //
NK126(cho)001:2247: bsam du med pa'i rig pa ma yengs zhog /
NK126(cho)001:2248: de la bsgom du rdul yang med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2249: e ma rgyud nas rgyal po bdag skyes te //
NK126(cho)001:2250: bdag 'dra d+ha he ta lo nga rgyal bcag pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:2251: sngon chad byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK126(cho)001:2252: sems dang chos nyid 'dres pa 'phro blang zhing //
NK126(cho)001:2253: sgyu ma'i phung po 'di ltar bsnyil ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:2254: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar //
NK126(cho)001:2255: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh zhes gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2256: sras thu bo ra dza ha stis /
NK126(cho)001:2257: do ha rdo rje'i glu tsan+dana gor shi sha'i kha ru nam gyis stod la gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2259: rang byung ye shes mkha' mnyam chen po'i ngang //
NK126(cho)001:2260: tshig dang yi ge'i sgra las 'das pa kun tu bzang //
NK126(cho)001:2261: sems dang chos nyid mnyam nyid dbyer med na //
NK126(cho)001:2262: lus ngag yid gsum mtshan ma ci bslad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:2263: chos nyid byang chub sems la 'pho 'gyur med //
NK126(cho)001:2264: rnam rtog rgyu rkyen bral ba'i kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2265: ma bcos pa yi ngang las bsgom pa gud na med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2266: sgyu ma'i phung po da ltar bsnyil ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:2267: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la babs //
NK126(cho)001:2268: go ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2269: sras mo pa ra nis me tog ku mud ta'i
NK126(cho)001:2270: tshal du nam gyi cha la do ha rdo rje'i
NK126(cho)001:2272: kun gzhi ye nas byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2273: rgyu dang rkyen gyis ma skyes 'jig 'dral med //
NK126(cho)001:2274: rang byung lhun gyis grub pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK126(cho)001:2275: gzung 'dzin kun las 'das pas rdo rje sems pa'i thugs //
NK126(cho)001:2276: ye nas ma bcos chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:2277: rang byung rang gsal rig pa ye shes kyis //
NK126(cho)001:2278: ma bcos ma bslad ngang du bzhag pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:2279: rdo rje sems dpa'i dgongs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2280: bdag gi bsgom pa 'di las med par mjal //
NK126(cho)001:2281: sgyu ma'i phung po da ltar bsnyil ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:2282: kun bzang thugs kyi gter chen bdag la babs //
NK126(cho)001:2283: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2284: klu yi rgyal po 'jog pos rgya mtsho'i gting du
NK126(cho)001:2285: skya ring shar tsa na do ha rdo rje'i glu
NK126(cho)001:2287: mtha' dang dbus med nam mkha' lta bu'i thugs //
NK126(cho)001:2288: smra bsam yul las 'das pa chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:2290: ma bcos rnam par dag pa kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2291: ma btsal mnyam par bzhag pa bsgom pa'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:2292: rig pa chos kyi dbyings su ma bcos na //
NK126(cho)001:2293: rnam par grol ba'i lam mchog gzhan na med //
NK126(cho)001:2294: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa nyid //
NK126(cho)001:2295: dpag cing gzhal yang 'di las med par mjal //
NK126(cho)001:2296: bdag gi phung po gdos bcas 'di snyil phyir //
NK126(cho)001:2297: kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa la mchi //
NK126(cho)001:2298: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2299: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dzas /
NK126(cho)001:2300: rgya mtsho'i gling na skya ring gnyis pa shar tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:2301: do ha rdo rje'i 'gur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2303: ye nas lhun grub kun tu bzang po'i ngang //
NK126(cho)001:2304: gsal la mi rtog spros bral byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2305: mi 'gyur mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK126(cho)001:2306: rig pa mi 'gyur ma bslad mnyam bzhag na //
NK126(cho)001:2307: ci la'ang mi gnas gang la'ang mi sems pa //
NK126(cho)001:2308: mchog tu gsang ba'i byang chub sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2309: rna bas nyan pa la sogs spyod yul yod ma yin //
NK126(cho)001:2310: kun gzhi mi 'gyur dbyings chen la //
NK126(cho)001:2311: rig pa mi 'gyur ma yengs bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:2313: khams gsum rang sar grol bas btsal zhing bsgrub mi dgos //
NK126(cho)001:2314: re zhing dgos pa med pas bdag nyid sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2315: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2316: n+aa ga 'dzu nas rgya mtsho phyi gsal gyi gnas su /
NK126(cho)001:2317: skya ring gsum pa shar tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:2318: do ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2320: snang ba thams cad ye nas dbyings chen la //
NK126(cho)001:2321: rig pa 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dur btab nas //
NK126(cho)001:2322: dbyings nyid mi 'gyur rig pa ma bslad de //
NK126(cho)001:2323: ma yengs mi 'gyur mkha' ltar dag pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2324: ma bcos yang yang gsal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:2325: bsgom pa ming du btags pa gud na med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2326: bdag gi phung po 'di la brten nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:2327: dbye ba med pa'i sa la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:2328: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2329: ku ku r+aa dza phyi mas rgya mtsho'i gling na /
NK126(cho)001:2330: dmar ring dang po shar tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:2331: do ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2333: chos dbyings byang chub sems ni 'byung ba lnga yin te //
NK126(cho)001:2334: ma bcos rang bzhin gsal bas mkha' ltar dag /'gro ba'i gzung 'dzin bsreg pa me ltar gnas //
NK126(cho)001:2335: dmigs med gdod nas dag pas rlung ltar gnas //
NK126(cho)001:2336: cis kyang bskyod du med pas sa ltar gnas //
NK126(cho)001:2337: gzung 'dzin ngo bo med pas chu ltar gnas //
NK126(cho)001:2338: 'byung ba lnga ni ye nas chos nyid byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2339: gdod nas dag pa'i nam mkha' 'dra ba la //
NK126(cho)001:2340: dmigs pa med par ma yengs gnas pa las //
NK126(cho)001:2341: bsgom pa 'di las gud na med par rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:2342: phung po gdos bcas 'di la brten nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:2343: sems ni dbye ba med pa'i sa la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:2344: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2345: gnod sbyin mo byang chub mos rgya mtsho'i gling na /
NK126(cho)001:2346: dmar ring gnyis pa shar tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:2347: do ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:2349: chos nyid byang chub sems la lta zhing mchis //
NK126(cho)001:2350: lta ba'i gzugs med yongs la gsal bar snang //
NK126(cho)001:2351: cis kyang bcos su med de bslad du med //
NK126(cho)001:2352: sems kyi rang bzhin ci la'ang mi gnas te //
NK126(cho)001:2353: rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)001:2354: ci ltar bslad kyang dbyings las 'gyur ba med //
NK126(cho)001:2355: dbyings nyid rig pas mi btsal te //
NK126(cho)001:2356: byang sems mkha' ltar dag pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:2357: ma bcos rang bzhin med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2359: bdag gi phung po 'di bsnyil nas //
NK126(cho)001:2360: kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa la 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:2361: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2362: smad tshong ma b+hu ta sa ma tis /
NK126(cho)001:2363: shing nal byi pa la'i rtsar /
NK126(cho)001:2364: dmar ring gsum pa shar tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:2365: do ha rdo rje mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2367: e ma hoh chos nyid byang chub sems la brtags shing dpyad du med //
NK126(cho)001:2368: btsal zhing gnyen pos bcos su med //
NK126(cho)001:2369: sems las sangs rgyas log na med //
NK126(cho)001:2370: btsal bas mi rnyed sems las sangs rgyas med //
NK126(cho)001:2371: sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2372: gdod nas ma btsal byang chub snying po la //
NK126(cho)001:2373: ting 'dzin ma bsgom ngang gi gsal ba las //
NK126(cho)001:2374: sangs rgyas dgongs pa gud na med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2375: phung po 'di las brten nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:2376: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar //
NK126(cho)001:2377: g+hi ta ma ko la hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2380: srod kyi thun la bzhengs nas /
NK126(cho)001:2381: do ha rdo rje'i mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2383: kun gzhi yangs pa'i dbye thang la //
NK126(cho)001:2384: rang rig dag pa'i klong nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:2385: ye shes nyi ma rang la shar //
NK126(cho)001:2386: shar ba'i dus na nub pa med //
NK126(cho)001:2387: shar bas ma bcos gsal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:2388: sangs rgyas chos nyid snga phyi gsum //
NK126(cho)001:2389: gang du btsal yang rnyed mtha' med //
NK126(cho)001:2390: chos nyid kun gzhi yangs pa las //
NK126(cho)001:2391: rig pa chos sku'i nyi ma shar //
NK126(cho)001:2392: de nyid bcos su med pa'i rtogs pa na //
NK126(cho)001:2393: sangs rgyas dgongs pa yin par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2394: myong na sems kyi bdud rtsi myong //
NK126(cho)001:2395: blta na rig pa ye shes blta //
NK126(cho)001:2396: g+hi ti ma pad+ma ka la sha a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2398: dpag bsam shing gi grib ma la /
NK126(cho)001:2399: nam tho ras kha la mnyam bzhag las bzhengs nas /
NK126(cho)001:2400: do ha rdo rje'i glu 'di gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2402: byang chub sems ni nam mkha' lta bu'i klong //
NK126(cho)001:2403: gsal la rtog pa med pa'i ye shes ni //
NK126(cho)001:2404: phyi dang nang med kun la gsal bar gnas //
NK126(cho)001:2405: gdod nas dag pas nam mkha'i klong 'dra las //
NK126(cho)001:2406: rnam par rtogs pa'i ye shes gsal bar shar //
NK126(cho)001:2407: skye 'gags dbyer med rang bzhin med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2408: sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di las med par mjal //
NK126(cho)001:2409: za na sems kyi bdud rtsi za //
NK126(cho)001:2410: gon na chos nyid chos su gon //
NK126(cho)001:2411: e la ka sha ya hoh ces pa 'di ni gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2412: u rgyan gyi mkhan po d+ha hes /
NK126(cho)001:2413: rin po che'i gling la nam gung yol nas do ha rdo rje'i mgur gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2415: sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2416: sems las sangs rgyas log na med //
NK126(cho)001:2417: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK126(cho)001:2418: rig pa mi 'gyur rang bzhin med pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:2419: zab mo chos dbyings don dam mi brjod gsal //
NK126(cho)001:2420: rgya mtsho che ltar chos dbyings zab mo la //
NK126(cho)001:2421: rig pa mi 'gyur gdon nas gsal bar shar //
NK126(cho)001:2422: kun gzhi gtan nas gsal bar sbyar ba'i nyi chen po //
NK126(cho)001:2423: mkha' ltar dag pa yangs la khyab par brdal //
NK126(cho)001:2424: chos nyid ye nas dag pas sbyong du med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2425: rig pa mi 'gyur gdod nas gsal bar shar //
NK126(cho)001:2426: phyin ci log gis ma bslad gsal bar shar //
NK126(cho)001:2427: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa 'di las med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2428: chos nyid nam mkha' chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:2429: rnal 'byor rig pa'i khyung chen lding //
NK126(cho)001:2430: ka ma ko la sha ya hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2431: drang srong b+ha shi tas nya gro ta'i dgon par
NK126(cho)001:2432: nam srod yol ba'i dus su do ha rdo rje'i
NK126(cho)001:2434: ma bcos mkha' la gza' skar kun 'phyo ba //
NK126(cho)001:2435: gdod nas dag pa'i mkha' ni mi bskyod ste //
NK126(cho)001:2436: byang chub sems ni mkha' ltar dag pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2437: rnam rtog mtshan mas ci bslad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:2438: rnam rtog sems kyi dbyings las 'pho 'gyur med //
NK126(cho)001:2439: chos dbyings dag pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor las //
NK126(cho)001:2440: rig pa ye shes dur btab pas //
NK126(cho)001:2441: gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar shar //
NK126(cho)001:2442: shar ba nyid kyi don de ma yengs las //
NK126(cho)001:2443: sangs rgyas nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di las med //
NK126(cho)001:2444: rig pa ye shes rlung chen gyis //
NK126(cho)001:2445: rnam rtog rdul phran med par phyags //
NK126(cho)001:2446: a ko la sha a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2447: sras mo go ma de ba'i r+aa dzas bsgom gnas
NK126(cho)001:2448: su nam gung yol nas do ha rdo rje'i glu
NK126(cho)001:2450: sangs rgyas dgongs pa yi ge rang bzhin a //
NK126(cho)001:2451: a yi rang bzhin ye nas dngos med de //
NK126(cho)001:2452: bde gshegs dgongs pa yi ge a //
NK126(cho)001:2453: bden gnyis la sogs snang srid ci snang yang //
NK126(cho)001:2454: a yi dngos gzhi ye nas byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2456: smra bsam yul las 'das pas dbyings nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:2457: a ltar skye ba med pa'i rig pa byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2458: ma bcos ma yengs mnyam par bzhag pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2459: bdag gi bsgom pa 'di las med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2460: chos dbyings dbye thang chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:2461: rig pa ye shes rta pho rgyug /
NK126(cho)001:2462: ka pa la ka la pa sha a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2463: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang brten gyis tsan+dana sdong po'i rtsar /
NK126(cho)001:2464: nam gung thun la do ha rdo rje'i mgur gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2466: byang chub sems ni ye nas chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:2467: mkha' dang 'dra bas kun la khyab par snang //
NK126(cho)001:2468: snang ba nyid kyang stong pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:2469: stong pa'i cho 'phrul ci snang yang //
NK126(cho)001:2470: bsam du rdul tsam med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2471: stor bral med par ma yengs zhog /
NK126(cho)001:2472: chos nyid sems kyi bdud rtsi yis //
NK126(cho)001:2473: khams gsum 'khor ba'i nad pa gso //
NK126(cho)001:2474: ka pa la ko la a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2475: lha'i rgyal po d+ha ba r+aa dzas grong khyer dpal yon du /
NK126(cho)001:2476: srod thun la do ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2478: snang srid chos rnams mngon du rtogs pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:2479: yang dag nyid du 'di ltar bsgom bya ste //
NK126(cho)001:2480: snang srid thams cad ye nas kun tu bzang //
NK126(cho)001:2481: kun bzang gud na med de ma lus snying po'i rgyu //
NK126(cho)001:2482: snang ba mtha' dag skye med bdud rtsi sku gsung thugs //
NK126(cho)001:2483: skye med ngang las ma yengs mnyam bzhag pas //
NK126(cho)001:2484: bsgom par bya ba 'di las gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:2485: lus ni sgyu ma'i phung po mi gtsang ste //
NK126(cho)001:2486: sems ni ye shes chen por shar //
NK126(cho)001:2487: tsan tra d+he ba ko la pa sha a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2488: d+har+m+aa r+aa dzas me tog ku muta ta'i tshal du nam gyi cha stod la /
NK126(cho)001:2489: do ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2490: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas mdzod chen la //
NK126(cho)001:2491: gang ltar btags shing ci ltar snang ba kun //
NK126(cho)001:2492: 'byung 'jug rgyu ba thams cad ye nas kun tu bzang //
NK126(cho)001:2493: de ltar gnyis su med pa'i rig pa de //
NK126(cho)001:2494: byang chub sems ni kun tu bzang po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2495: bsgom zhing bzlas pa 'di na med //
NK126(cho)001:2496: e ma hoh ma rtogs snying re rje /
NK126(cho)001:2497: rang sems rtsol med sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:2498: sa lam bsgrod nas rgyu 'bras ltos pa'i blo //
NK126(cho)001:2499: rmi lam zas nor rjes su tshol ba 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:2500: e ma bdag nyid rang sar grol ba a la la //
NK126(cho)001:2501: rdo ha ko la pa sha a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2502: b+hud+d+ha gustasa bde ba chen po'i gnas su /
NK126(cho)001:2503: do ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2505: chos rnams ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2506: ye nas kun tu bzang po la //
NK126(cho)001:2507: bcos pas gsal bar gyur pa'i byang chub sems de la //
NK126(cho)001:2508: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pas mi bslad de //
NK126(cho)001:2509: rnam rtog rang byung rang zhi nas //
NK126(cho)001:2510: gnyen pos bsgom du med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:2511: lta na sems kyi me long ltos //
NK126(cho)001:2512: prad dz+nya ko la pa a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2513: sh+ri sing has bsam gtan gyi khang par tshogs kyi mchod pa'i dus su rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:2515: ci ltar bsam yang bsgom du med //
NK126(cho)001:2516: ci ltar spyad kyang spyad du med //
NK126(cho)001:2517: ye shes chen po'i dbyings nyid las //
NK126(cho)001:2518: rgyu rkyen med par 'od gsal ba //
NK126(cho)001:2519: bsam du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:2520: yengs ba med par mnyam par bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:2522: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor dbang phyug gis //
NK126(cho)001:2523: rnam rtog dgra bo rdul du rlog /
NK126(cho)001:2524: rat+na ko sha pa la a hoh ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:2526: do ha rdo rje'i dgongs pas mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te brgyad pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:2527: yang de'i dus de'i tshe na /
NK126(cho)001:2528: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa rnams kyi man ngag gi don thugs su lon nas /
NK126(cho)001:2529: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub thob tu cha ba la /
NK126(cho)001:2530: bram ze rgyal byed bya ba zhig gi mkhas pa
NK126(cho)001:2531: rnams la li ka ra'i zhal skyems re drangs nas
NK126(cho)001:2532: / rang byung ye shes chen po'i dgongs pa tshig
NK126(cho)001:2533: re re zhig thugs kyi dkyil nas phyungs la ma
NK126(cho)001:2534: rig mun nag bsal bar zhu 'tshal /
NK126(cho)001:2536: rgyal po d+ha he ta los dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2537: sems nyid ma bcos pa'i ye shes chen por yin par rig pas thag chod nas /
NK126(cho)001:2538: khams gsum sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2539: sras thu bo r+aa dza ha stis dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2540: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad rang gi byang chub kyi
NK126(cho)001:2541: sems ma bcos pa'i dbyings de nyid rang snang ste
NK126(cho)001:2542: / de ltar snang srid sangs rgyas pas 'bad rtsol med par thag chod de /
NK126(cho)001:2543: khams gsum sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2544: sras mo pa ra nis dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2545: rang gi kun gzhi byang chub sems ye thog ma
NK126(cho)001:2546: nas byed pa med pa'i ngang la sku dang ye
NK126(cho)001:2547: shes rang bzhin du gnas pa la blo'i rig pa
NK126(cho)001:2548: gzung 'dzin du ma zhen pa ni khams gsum sangs
NK126(cho)001:2550: klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2551: khams gsum gyi sems can gyi sems don gyi rnal
NK126(cho)001:2552: ma de bya ba med pa'i ngang du thag chod
NK126(cho)001:2553: na / khams gsum sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2554: gnod sbyin mo byang chub mos dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2555: kun gzhi ma bcos pa'i klong /
NK126(cho)001:2556: snying po lhun gyis rdzogs te 'khor 'das thams cad
NK126(cho)001:2557: kyi ngo bo skye 'gags med pa'i dbyings la bslad
NK126(cho)001:2559: khams gsum sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2560: smad tshong ma pa ra nis dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2561: kun gzhi byang chub sems ma bcos pa'i klong /
NK126(cho)001:2563: yid rang byung gi ye shes chen po mi 'gyur bar gnas pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:2564: khams gsum sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2565: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang gis dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2566: khams gsum gyi sems can ye gdod ma nas dag
NK126(cho)001:2567: pa'i dbyings kun tu bzang po'i bde bar chen po'i
NK126(cho)001:2568: ngang nyid ye shes chen po'i rang bzhin las 'khor
NK126(cho)001:2569: ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis su med
NK126(cho)001:2570: par rtogs na / khams gsum sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2571: rgyal po b+hud+d+ha sa mas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2572: sems can gyi sems la ma lus pa'i byang chub chen po thog mtha' med pa'i sku /
NK126(cho)001:2573: ma lus pa'i chos thams cad bde ba chen por
NK126(cho)001:2574: gsal bas khams gsum mya ngan las 'das pa rtogs
NK126(cho)001:2575: pas / dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2576: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku r+aa dzas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2577: snang srid kyi chos thams cad ma bcos pa'i ngang du rtogs nas ngang de la gnas pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:2578: bsgom pa'i don mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2579: u rgyan gyi mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dzas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2580: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK126(cho)001:2581: cad ye nas sangs rgyas par 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK126(cho)001:2582: sku spangs len med pa'i ngang du rtogs pa'i don
NK126(cho)001:2585: a tsar+ya a lo kes dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2586: kun gzhi ma bcos pa'i dbyings su snang srid sangs
NK126(cho)001:2587: rgyas pas 'khor ba nyid kun tu bzang por rtogs
NK126(cho)001:2588: pas / blo rig pa gzung 'dzin du ma zhen pa /
NK126(cho)001:2589: bsgom pa'i don mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2590: khyi'i mkhan po d+ha hu nas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2591: sems can gyi blo rtsol ba dang bral nas dus
NK126(cho)001:2592: gsum 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid la blo rig
NK126(cho)001:2593: pa / de bzhin du gnas pa bsgom pa'i mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2594: drang srong b+ha shi tas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2595: rang gi byang chub kyi sems ye ji bzhin pa nyid du yum gyi mkha' klong dag pa nas /
NK126(cho)001:2596: sras dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rig pa phyogs ris med par shar te /
NK126(cho)001:2597: gang la'ang bkag pa med pa'i ye shes ngang gi
NK126(cho)001:2598: shar bar gnas pa'i bsgom pa'i don mthar thug pa'o
NK126(cho)001:2599: // smad tshong ma bdag nyid las dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2600: rang gi kun gzhi ji bzhin pa'i klong kun tu bzang po'i rol par snang srid rgyas btab /
NK126(cho)001:2601: khams gsum sangs rgyas te de la ci'i ngo bo
NK126(cho)001:2602: yang mi dmigs par gnas pa ni bsgom pa'i don
NK126(cho)001:2603: mthar thug pa'o // na ga 'dzu nas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2604: kun gzhi 'dus ma byas pa'i snying po ma bcos
NK126(cho)001:2605: pa'i dbyings su ye nas dag pa de la rig
NK126(cho)001:2606: pa de bzhin gnas pa de la bsgom pa'i mthar
NK126(cho)001:2607: thug pa'o // 'jam dpal bzang gis dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2608: byang sems mtshon du med pa'i ngang la ye nas gnas pa /
NK126(cho)001:2609: thugs rje chen po'i klong du ye nas sangs rgyas te /
NK126(cho)001:2610: khams gsum mya ngan las 'das nas bsgom pa'i mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2611: sh+ri sing has dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2612: nyon mongs pa yang kun gzhi /
NK126(cho)001:2615: chos nyid dang sangs rgyas kyang kun gzhi /
NK126(cho)001:2616: 'khor 'das thams cad kun gzhi'i ngo bor lhun gyis rdzogs te /
NK126(cho)001:2617: re dogs med par gnas pa bsgom pa'i mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2618: kun dga' mos dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2619: snang srid sangs rgyas pa'i ngang la ma yengs par bsgom pa'i mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2621: bram ze rab tu dga' ste lus phul nas zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:2622: dgongs pa'i don brgyad cu rtsa gsum gnang /
NK126(cho)001:2623: bka'i zhal chems kun gyi sa gnang ste /
NK126(cho)001:2624: man ngag gi bcud btig nas gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:2625: bram ze rtogs pa phul ba /
NK126(cho)001:2626: e ma hoh mkhas pa'i man ngag bcud btig pas //
NK126(cho)001:2627: bram ze'i mun nag gtan nas bsal //
NK126(cho)001:2628: rtogs pa'i klong du su 'dris pa //
NK126(cho)001:2629: mi zhes bya ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:2630: mi rtog nyid du rtog pa'ang med //
NK126(cho)001:2631: mi gnas pa ru gnas pa'ang meng //
NK126(cho)001:2632: de phyir bsam gtan nyid las bsam du med //
NK126(cho)001:2633: bsgom pa nyid la bsgom du med //
NK126(cho)001:2634: mi rtog nyid du rtog pa'ang med //
NK126(cho)001:2635: mi gnas tshul du gnas pa'ang med //
NK126(cho)001:2636: bsam med tshul du bsam na g.yengs pa'ang med //
NK126(cho)001:2637: bsgom med tshul du bsgom na dmigs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2638: dmigs med tshul du dmigs na gza' gtad do //
NK126(cho)001:2639: de phyir ched du bya ba ci yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2641: de ltar 'du 'bral med pas ting 'dzin gcig /
NK126(cho)001:2642: ye nas gnas so ci la bsam //
NK126(cho)001:2643: e ma hoh chos sku nyid la rten mi bca' //
NK126(cho)001:2644: chos sku bya ba bsgom du med //
NK126(cho)001:2645: bsgom med nyid du bsgom ba'ang med //
NK126(cho)001:2646: de phyir thams cad rang rig pas //
NK126(cho)001:2647: spangs thob 'du 'bral bdag gzhan mi dmigs phyir //
NK126(cho)001:2648: mthong bas rkyen rnams bzod pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2649: gang dag der rig khams gsum lam //
NK126(cho)001:2650: mtha' las rtsod 'khrugs ye nas med //
NK126(cho)001:2651: de bas bya bral nyid du zhog /
NK126(cho)001:2652: ces pa'i rtogs pa'i don mgur du bzhengs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2653: bram ze rgyal byed nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin sangs rgyas so //
NK126(cho)001:2655: bram ze rgyal byed man ngag gi don khongs su chud de sangs rgyas pa'i skabs te dgu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:2657: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2658: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bshad pa 'di skad do //
NK126(cho)001:2659: rdo rje zhes pa dus gsum 'dus ma byas pa'i snying po la rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2660: de yang r+aa dza d+ha he na ta lo'i bzhed kyis rdo rje'i bshad pa 'di lta ste /
NK126(cho)001:2661: rdo rje zhes pa rang byung yang dag pa'i dbyings su 'khor ba nyid ye nas bcom te /
NK126(cho)001:2662: sku gsung thugs 'gyur ba med pa'i dbyings /
NK126(cho)001:2663: lhun gyis rdzogs pas 'khor ba'i ming yang med de /
NK126(cho)001:2664: khams gsum sangs rgyas pas dus gsum skye 'jig med do //
NK126(cho)001:2665: skye 'gag gi mtha' las 'das pas chos nyid 'pho 'gyur dang bral bas gting khung ring /
NK126(cho)001:2666: klong yongs rgya che ba dus gsum 'gyur ba med pas rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2667: de yang man ngag gi don mdor bsdus nas dgongs pa'i don la spyod pa /
NK126(cho)001:2668: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pa'i kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2669: smra bsam tshig las 'das pas ye nas spyad du med //
NK126(cho)001:2670: 'khor ba'i ming yang med pas rgyu drug gnas su dag /
NK126(cho)001:2671: stong pa'i ngo bos cis kyang bshig tu med pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2672: ma bcos rang bzhin bzhag pa bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2673: sras thu bo r+aa dza ha stis rdo rje bshad pas /
NK126(cho)001:2674: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi dbyings de mtshon du med /
NK126(cho)001:2675: mtshon pa las 'das pa dbyings mi 'gyur lhun gyis rdzogs te /
NK126(cho)001:2677: de yang man ngag gi don mdor bsdus nas dgongs pa'i don bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:2678: kun gzhi ma bcos chos nyid byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2679: rgyu rkyen gnyis dang bral bas gdod nas dag /'gyur ba med pas bde chen lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:2680: cis kyang bshig tu med pa'i rdo rje'i sems //
NK126(cho)001:2681: rang byung tshigs las 'das pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2682: sras mo pa ra nis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2687: gdod nas dag pa'i snying po /
NK126(cho)001:2688: byang chub kyi sems dgongs pa'i nges par ba stan pa la rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2689: de yang man ngag gi don mdor bsdus nas dgongs pa'i don la bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2690: gdags su med pa'i kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2691: dmigs dang bral bas yang dag nges pa'i lung //
NK126(cho)001:2692: gdod nas lhun grub byang chub snying po la //
NK126(cho)001:2693: cis kyang bshig tu med pas rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:2694: de nyid ma bcos dmigs su med pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:2695: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2696: klu yi rgyal po 'jog pos rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2697: rang byung gi dbyings 'gyur ba med pa'i sku /
NK126(cho)001:2699: ma brtsal ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che /
NK126(cho)001:2700: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems /
NK126(cho)001:2703: ma brtsal bar lhun gyis rdzogs pa la rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2704: de nyid mi 'gyur bar gnas pas sems pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2705: de yang man ngag gi don mdor bsdus nas dgongs pa'i don la bcad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2706: gdags su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2707: thogs ma med nas ye nas lhun gyis grub //
NK126(cho)001:2708: dmigs su med pas ya mtshan tshig las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:2709: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2710: ci yang dmigs su med pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2711: gnod sbyin mo byang chub kyis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2712: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems 'di /
NK126(cho)001:2713: gdod nas byang chub lhun gyis grub /
NK126(cho)001:2717: dus gsum gyi snying po zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2718: yang dag byang chub rgyu rkyen med pa'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:2719: rgyu rkyen bral nas skye 'jig gnas su dag /
NK126(cho)001:2720: ye sangs rgyas pas chos nyid klong du gyur //
NK126(cho)001:2721: dmigs med gdod nas dag pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2722: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang gis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2723: rdo rje ni kun gzhi byang chub sems /
NK126(cho)001:2724: rang byung gi dbyings 'gyur ba med pa'i sku /
NK126(cho)001:2726: de brtan g.yo rnam pa gnyis ni /
NK126(cho)001:2727: phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ye nas gnas su dag pas /
NK126(cho)001:2728: bde chen lhun gyis rdzogs te /
NK126(cho)001:2732: snod bcud byang chub sems dpa' de cir yang 'gyur ba med pas rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:2733: de nyid ma bcos par lhun gyis rdzogs pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2734: de yang kun gzhi ma bcos rang byung dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:2735: phyi nang snod bcud ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK126(cho)001:2736: rang byung rnam dag 'khor ba'i ming yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2737: gdod nas ma bcos snying po byang chub 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2738: dgongs pa lhun gyis rdzogs pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2739: yang dag don las mi 'gyur sems pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2740: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku r+aa dzas rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2741: rdo rje ni kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems /
NK126(cho)001:2742: de yang phyi snod kyi 'jig rten srid pa skye
NK126(cho)001:2743: ba'i rgyud bzhag kyang chos nyid bag la zhi ste
NK126(cho)001:2744: / mu mtha' med par khyab brdal bas /
NK126(cho)001:2745: chos nyid de dus gsum du 'gyur ba med pas kyang rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:2746: nang bcud kyi kun gzhi blo spangs te /
NK126(cho)001:2747: ye nas gnas su dag nas rgyu rkyen gyi mtha' las 'das pas yang rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2748: des na ma bcos pa'i rdo rje chos nyid de /
NK126(cho)001:2749: rang bzhin du gnas pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2750: de yang ma bcos gdod nas byang bas byang chub la //
NK126(cho)001:2751: rnam rtog lhun gyis rdzogs pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2752: rgyu rkyen tshig las 'das pas chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:2753: cis kyang bshig tu med pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2754: ma bcos gnas su dag pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2755: de nyid rang bzhin bzhag pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2756: smad tshong ma b+hud+d+ha ma tis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2757: rdo rje ni kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems 'gyur ba med pas rdo rje ste /
NK126(cho)001:2758: rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs las 'das te /
NK126(cho)001:2759: mi rtog pa'i ngo bo don gyi ma bcos pas rdo rje zhes bya ste /
NK126(cho)001:2760: des snod bcud gang la yang ma khyab pa med de /
NK126(cho)001:2761: khyab brdal bar gnas pa la sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2762: de yang kun gzhi ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2763: yang dag don la 'gyur med rdo rje la //
NK126(cho)001:2764: rnam par mi rtog ngo bo lhun rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:2765: kun gzhi ma bcos don gyi rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2766: 'khor ba ye sangs rgyas pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2767: de nyid tshig bral bzhag pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2768: smad tshong ma pa r+aa nis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2769: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems /
NK126(cho)001:2770: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin /
NK126(cho)001:2771: spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba mnyam
NK126(cho)001:2772: pa chen po'i ngang du ye nas brtsal du med
NK126(cho)001:2774: byang chub sems rang bzhin 'gyur ba med pa'i sku /
NK126(cho)001:2777: mtshan mar spyad du med pa byang chub sems la rdo rje zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:2778: de klong du gyur pas sems dpa' zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:2779: de yang ma bcos lhun gyis rdzogs pa gdod nas dag /
NK126(cho)001:2780: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pa don gyi mchog /
NK126(cho)001:2781: cis kyang bslad pa med pa rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2782: yang dag klong du gyur pa sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2783: ci yang dmigs su med pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2784: na ga 'dzu nas rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2785: phyi nang gi chos thams cad ye nas ngang gi
NK126(cho)001:2786: ma bcos pa ngang dwangs rang bzhin lhun gyis rdzogs
NK126(cho)001:2787: / ye nyid yang dag pa'i dbyings su lhun gyis rdzogs pas /
NK126(cho)001:2788: 'khor ba nyid byang chub pas khyab gdal chen po'i klong du mi 'byed cing /
NK126(cho)001:2789: mtha' dbus med pa'i thugs rjes zin pas chos nyid de klong du gyur pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2790: chos nyid 'du 'bral med pas rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2791: de yang kun gzhi ma bcos ngang dwangs rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:2792: snang srid 'khor ba ma lus byang chub pas //
NK126(cho)001:2793: 'khor ba nyid kyang mi 'gyur chos nyid de //
NK126(cho)001:2794: ma btsal klong du gyur pa'i rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2795: khams gsum bcos su med pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2796: 'jam dpal dpal bzang gis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2797: rdo rje ni bya btsal med de /
NK126(cho)001:2798: klong du gyur pa'i kun gzhi de /
NK126(cho)001:2799: rnam dag byang chub skye 'chi med /
NK126(cho)001:2800: 'khor ba gting phyungs nas bde ba'i don lhun gyis rdzogs pas /
NK126(cho)001:2801: phyi nang gi chos thams cad ma skyes pa'i sku /
NK126(cho)001:2805: yang dag pa'i chos nyid klong yangs gting khung ring
NK126(cho)001:2806: khyab gdal chen po'i rang bzhin du gnas pa la
NK126(cho)001:2808: de klong du gyur te mi phyed pa la sems dpa' zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:2809: de yang kun gzhi byang chub gnyis med chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:2810: rgyu rkyen gnyis bral ye nas gnyis su med //
NK126(cho)001:2811: sa las 'das pas sbyang zhing bsgrod du med //
NK126(cho)001:2812: 'gyur ba med pas yang dag don gyi bla //
NK126(cho)001:2813: tshig las 'das pas dgongs pa lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:2814: ma bcos ngang la gnas pa bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2815: khyi'i mkhan po d+ha h+au nis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2816: kun gzhi byang chub sems brtan g.yo rnam pa gnyis
NK126(cho)001:2817: phyi nang snod bcud kyi chos thams cad bya byed
NK126(cho)001:2818: kyi brtsol sgrub las 'das pas ma lus sangs rgyas
NK126(cho)001:2820: mya ngan rang bzhin gyi 'das khams gsum sangs rgyas te /
NK126(cho)001:2821: ma bcos pa don gyi ngo bo mi 'gyur ba la rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2822: ma bcos rtsol bsgrub las 'das pa'i klong du gyur pa la sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2823: de yang ma bcos gnas su dag pas 'khor ba mi yang med //
NK126(cho)001:2824: smra bsam yid las 'das pas tshig gis mtshon du med //
NK126(cho)001:2825: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pas kun gzhi chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:2826: rang byung lhun gyis rdzogs pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2827: dus gsum klong du gyur pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2828: sras mo b+ha shi tas rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2829: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems ye nas ma bcos
NK126(cho)001:2830: pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin yang dag pa'i
NK126(cho)001:2831: chos nyid de btsal du med de /
NK126(cho)001:2832: rtsol ba las 'das pa'i don byang sems kun tu bzang po de /
NK126(cho)001:2833: spyod pa dang bral ba la rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2834: ma bcos pa'i don las 'gyur ba med pas sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2835: de yang thog ma dus mtha' med pa nas //
NK126(cho)001:2836: tha ma dus mtha' med pa'i dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:2837: chos dang chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK126(cho)001:2838: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pas na //
NK126(cho)001:2840: klong du gyur pa sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2841: b+hud+d+ha kustasa rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2842: kun gzhi yang dag pa'i chos nyid dus gsum du 'dus ma byas pa'i rang bzhin /
NK126(cho)001:2843: spros pa med pa'i klong snying po 'dus ma byas
NK126(cho)001:2844: pa snang srid kun ka ba tsa ru lhun gyis
NK126(cho)001:2845: rdzogs pas / kun tu bzang po 'du 'bral med
NK126(cho)001:2846: pa'i chos nyid klong du gyur pa rdo rje bya'o
NK126(cho)001:2847: rdzogs pas / // dus gsum ma bcos rang bzhin dag pa'i klong de la sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2848: de yang chos nyid ma bcos dag pa'i rdo rje 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2849: rgyu rkyen gnyis bral gdod nas gnyis su med //
NK126(cho)001:2850: dngas snyigs mi 'byed chos nyid du gyur //
NK126(cho)001:2851: dus gsum 'dus ma byas pas snying po mchog /
NK126(cho)001:2852: yang dag lhun gyis rdzogs pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2853: smad tshong ma pa r+aa nis rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2854: kun gzhi dus gsum 'gyur ba med pas rdo rje zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:2855: ma bcos pas lhun gyis rdzogs pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2856: de yang snod bcud lhun gyis rdzogs pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2857: snod bcud lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:2858: mtshan mas bslad du med pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2859: chos nyid klong du gyur pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2860: de nyid ma bcos bzhag pa bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2861: u rgyan gyi mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dzas rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2862: badz+ra ni kun gzhi byang chub sems /
NK126(cho)001:2863: byed pa med pa'i chos nyid klong du gyur tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:2864: sems ye nas ma bcos par snang srid sangs rgyas /
NK126(cho)001:2865: ma lus lhun gyis rdzogs pas bde ba chen po 'od gsal khams gsum chos nyid du gyur ste /
NK126(cho)001:2867: spros med rang bzhin gyi gnas /
NK126(cho)001:2868: des na kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems /
NK126(cho)001:2869: bde ba chen por 'od gsal ba la /
NK126(cho)001:2870: cis kyang bslad pa med pas rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:2871: de'i don la gnas pas sems dpa' zhes kyang bya /
NK126(cho)001:2872: de yang 'khor 'das thams cad smra bsam tshig las 'das pas sems dapa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2873: sh+ri sing has rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2874: kun gzhi byang chub sems dus gsum du 'dus ma
NK126(cho)001:2875: byas pas skye 'jig med de rdo rje zhes bya'o
NK126(cho)001:2876: // de yang lhun rdzogs sku gsung thugs kyi rgya //
NK126(cho)001:2877: ma lus brdal ba chos nyid klong gi rgya //
NK126(cho)001:2878: gdal ba'i dkyil 'khor 'gyur ba med pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:2879: dngos po bslad pa med pa rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:2880: de nyid klong du gyur pa bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2881: de ba tsan tras rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2882: badz+ra ni kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems /
NK126(cho)001:2883: ma bcos pa phyin ci ma log pa la rdo rje zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:2884: lhun rdzogs khyab bdal gnas pa sems dpa' yin //
NK126(cho)001:2885: kun gzhi mi 'gyur chos sku chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:2886: bde chen lhun gyis rdzogs pas ye nas chos nyid dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:2887: des na dus gsum 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid de //
NK126(cho)001:2888: snang srid lhun gyis rdzogs pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2889: na ga dzu nas rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2890: mtshan ma dmigs su med pas kun gzhi byang chub sems /
NK126(cho)001:2891: dus gsum skye 'jig med pas rdo rje yin //
NK126(cho)001:2892: de nyid mngon du gyur pas sems dpa' yin //
NK126(cho)001:2893: gdod nas ma bcos chos nyid byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:2894: dus gsum 'gyur med klong du 'khor 'das lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:2895: sku gsum che ba'i yon tan nor bu'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:2896: bde chen dri ma med pas rdo rje ste //
NK126(cho)001:2897: gang yang rang bzhin med pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:2898: kun dga' mos rdo rje bshad pa /
NK126(cho)001:2899: dbyings mi 'gyur lhun gyis rdzogs pas kun gzhi dmigs su med de /
NK126(cho)001:2900: rtog pa'i dri ma dang bral /
NK126(cho)001:2901: rang byung dag pas rdo rje yin //
NK126(cho)001:2902: ma bcos dag pas sems dpa' zhes //
NK126(cho)001:2903: de yang ma bcos gdal bas chos nyid thig le la //
NK126(cho)001:2904: 'khor 'das chos rnams rang byung lhun rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:2905: snang srid ye sangs rgyas pas rdo rje'o //
NK126(cho)001:2906: de nyid bcos pa med pas bsgom pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:2908: de yan chad rgya gar gyi mkhan po nyi shu
NK126(cho)001:2909: rtsa gsum la dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK126(cho)001:2910: pa re re la brgyud do //
NK126(cho)001:2911: rtogs pas dngos grub thob ste /
NK126(cho)001:2912: dgongs pas sangs rgyas dang mnyams /
NK126(cho)001:2914: bya brtsal med pa'i lam chod /
NK126(cho)001:2915: bsam du med pa'i don la sangs rgyas so //
NK126(cho)001:2917: rdo rje sems dpa'i don rin po che'i phreng ba ltar brgyud pa'i skabs te bcu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:2919: u rgyan thor cog can gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling /
NK126(cho)001:2920: rnam dag chos kyi sprin du /
NK126(cho)001:2921: dge slong ma kun dga' mos man ngag gi chos
NK126(cho)001:2922: thams cad tshang dus kyi 'o ma bzhin du bcos
NK126(cho)001:2925: mi nad dang phyug nad dang /
NK126(cho)001:2927: dus ma yin pa'i rlung dang /
NK126(cho)001:2931: bkra mi shis pa sna tshogs byung /
NK126(cho)001:2932: bsgrub pa po kun gyis mtshan ltas kyang lo ste /
NK126(cho)001:2933: mkhas pa pan tri ta ku ku r+aa dza dang /
NK126(cho)001:2934: drang srong b+ha shi ta dang /
NK126(cho)001:2936: khyi'i mkhan po d+ha hu na dang /
NK126(cho)001:2946: man ngag gi chos bslad pas lan zer te /
NK126(cho)001:2947: des bslad pa dang nyams pa thams cad dor te /
NK126(cho)001:2948: rgyud sde kun la mna' sher bya /
NK126(cho)001:2950: byang sems rnam pa lnga dang /
NK126(cho)001:2951: nam mkha' rol pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK126(cho)001:2953: man ngag rgya mtsho klong la sogs pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:2954: sna tshang zhing dag pa tshan gcig rgyal blon dang
NK126(cho)001:2955: chos skyong ba'i lha 'dres yo dpang por bzhag te
NK126(cho)001:2956: / rdo rje gdan gyi 'og tu chos skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rgya dang /
NK126(cho)001:2957: pan tri ta'i rgyab sprod tu btab ste /
NK126(cho)001:2959: lhag ma yo zhugs la bzhen /
NK126(cho)001:2960: de'i dus de'i tshe dge slong ma kun dga' mo
NK126(cho)001:2961: la chos skyong ba'i lha srin rnams kyis mdo la
NK126(cho)001:2962: snying phyungs nas khrag gzags nas lus dor ro //
NK126(cho)001:2963: kun dga' mo nyid rtogs pa mthar phyin nas gsang sngags kyi che ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:2964: stobs chen phyag na rdo rje'i skur gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2965: de nas chos phag tshang dang lkog tshang bya thabs med /
NK126(cho)001:2966: snod dang skal bar ldan pa byung na /
NK126(cho)001:2967: kun grol byas nas sbyin par byas pas der yul phyogs bkra shis par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:2969: rgya gar gyi yul du ci ltar byung ba'i skabs bcu gcig pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:2970: da man ngag 'di bod kyi yul du ci ltar byung lugs ni /
NK126(cho)001:2971: sku rgyal bod kyi btsad po lha tho tho ri snyan shal gyi sku ring la /
NK126(cho)001:2972: bde bar gshegs pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK126(cho)001:2973: bod mun pa'i gang bar srin po'i yul 'di na /
NK126(cho)001:2974: rgya nag gi yul nas spang skongs phyag brgya pa
NK126(cho)001:2975: rnyed nas de bkur sti dang rim gro byas pas
NK126(cho)001:2976: / rje sku tshe ring ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:2978: chab srid mtho ba byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:2982: 'dre srin la rdzun gyis bstod de mchod pa byung /
NK126(cho)001:2983: mes srong btsan sgom po'i sku ring la dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar po dang /
NK126(cho)001:2985: mdo sde dkon mchog sprin dang /
NK126(cho)001:2986: de la sogs te chos dge ba bcu'i rgyun tsam byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:2987: dam pa chos kyi mgo brnyes /
NK126(cho)001:2988: de'i sras khri sde gtsug brten gyi sku ring la /
NK126(cho)001:2990: bal yul nas lha sh+aakya mu ne spyan drangs /
NK126(cho)001:2991: rgya nag ha shang ni le i shang pa'i ma h+aa ya na la sogs pa spyan drangs /
NK126(cho)001:2992: de'i sras khri srong lde'u btsan gyi sku ring la /
NK126(cho)001:2993: rgya gar nas slob dpon zhi ba mtsho /
NK126(cho)001:2995: de rnams spyan drangs nas dam pa chos kyi srol btod /
NK126(cho)001:2996: rgya gar nas mkhas btsun mang po pan tri ta mang du spyan drangs /
NK126(cho)001:2997: de'i dbon khri ral gyi lo ts+aa ba ka ba dpal brtsegs spyan drangs /
NK126(cho)001:2998: cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan la sogs te pan+di ta
NK126(cho)001:2999: brgyad la sogs slob ma rgan tshos skad bsgyur ba
NK126(cho)001:3000: la mos / gzhon tshos skad ma bsgyur ba la mos /
NK126(cho)001:3001: skad chos sbrag ma bslab par mos /
NK126(cho)001:3002: rgan tshos dbang chen ba thon mi sam b+ha tras
NK126(cho)001:3003: bod yig na ga ra'i yi ge las dpe blangs
NK126(cho)001:3004: te / bris nas lo bcu gcig bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3005: bod skad lha mi drangs bdun gyi kha bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:3006: chos skad sngags btsun sde gnyis kyis bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:3007: rgya bod kyi skad 'og dang po lo ts+aa bas bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:3008: 'dram po zhu yis ban+de ye shes sdes zhus te gtan la phab /
NK126(cho)001:3009: mdo sde dang sde snod gsum bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:3010: de nas glang dpal gyi seng ge /
NK126(cho)001:3011: gru gu u shi sha /'bri rgyal ba'i blo gros /
NK126(cho)001:3013: gnubs nam mkha'i snying po dang bod kyi dge slong
NK126(cho)001:3014: mi lngas rgya gar dang bal po ru dka' ba
NK126(cho)001:3015: spyad de / kri yog dang ma h+aa yo ga rnams kyang bod la bshad par bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3016: o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang /
NK126(cho)001:3017: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa b+ho ti sa t+wa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3018: bal po'i mkhas pa ka ru pa la sogs spyan drangs nas /
NK126(cho)001:3019: chos 'khor dpal gyi bsam yas la sogs pa gtsug lag khang brgya rtsa brgyad bzhengs /
NK126(cho)001:3020: dam pa'i chos nyi ma shar ba tsam dar zhing rgyas par mdzad do //
NK126(cho)001:3021: srid pa'i bon 'di 'jig rten pa'i lha srin gyi byas par 'khums nas lan gsum bsnubs so //
NK126(cho)001:3022: dus lan gcig sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'jig la /
NK126(cho)001:3023: tshe lo drug cu tham par mar mar la nub pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3024: man ngag gi chos bon du bsgyur nas /
NK126(cho)001:3025: bon chos la khyad par med do //
NK126(cho)001:3026: zhes bya ba'i sgra chen po sgrogs /
NK126(cho)001:3027: de'i dus su man ngag gi chos 'ga' tsam 'chad pa la yid ma ches te /
NK126(cho)001:3030: de'i dus su nad dang mtshon dang /
NK126(cho)001:3033: thog ser la sogs pa skyi gdong gi rgyun 'bab /
NK126(cho)001:3034: chos bon du bsgyur bas chos skyong gi lha srin 'khrugs /
NK126(cho)001:3035: rnam smin na rag gi rgyud 'phel lo //
NK126(cho)001:3036: de la dgongs nas bon lan gsum bsnubs so //
NK126(cho)001:3037: de nas mkhas pa mang po'i grwa ni btsug ste /
NK126(cho)001:3038: dam pa'i chos kyang mdo sde dang gsang sngags la sogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3039: rgyu 'bras dang lam gyi chos dar bar bzhugs pa las /
NK126(cho)001:3040: des kyang rgyal po thugs la ches te /
NK126(cho)001:3041: rgyal po nyid tshe snga ma rgya gar gyi yul du /
NK126(cho)001:3042: bram ze dpal ldan bya ba'i bu dge slong a
NK126(cho)001:3043: ba kha t+yu bya ba de bod du brtsad por
NK126(cho)001:3045: rgya gar gyi yul na man ngag gi chos yod par thugs la shar te /
NK126(cho)001:3046: bod kyi mkhas btsun yod tshad bsogs te /
NK126(cho)001:3048: rgyu 'bras kyi chos ni chog tsam bsgyur te /
NK126(cho)001:3049: rgyu 'bras gnyis la mi ltos pa'i chos shig dgongs par mthong /
NK126(cho)001:3050: rgya gar gyi yul 'dir sngon dang po ston pa sku 'khrungs /
NK126(cho)001:3051: bar du bstan pa rim gyi bsgrags /
NK126(cho)001:3052: tha mar sku der mya ngan las 'das pas /
NK126(cho)001:3053: des na rgyu 'bras gnyis la bzla ba'i chos shig yod nges pas /
NK126(cho)001:3054: tshol ba la gcig gi lam mi phyed pas zung gcig btang snyams pa na da 'gro su nus /
NK126(cho)001:3055: rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i chos shig bsgyur na /
NK126(cho)001:3056: de'i dge ba'i rtsa ba nam mkha' la'ang mi shong na /
NK126(cho)001:3057: nus pa yod dam ces bsgrags pas /
NK126(cho)001:3058: bod rang sa sgra chag go //
NK126(cho)001:3059: mi lus lan bdun brgyud nas skye ba barjesa pa /
NK126(cho)001:3060: dang po u rgyan gyi yul du /
NK126(cho)001:3061: rgyal po dpal la de ba zhes bya bar sku 'khrungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3062: de nas kha che'i khri steng du /
NK126(cho)001:3063: tsan+t+ra g+hirti zhes bya bar sku 'khrungs /
NK126(cho)001:3064: de nas sing ha yul gyi ma la ya ru /
NK126(cho)001:3065: dge slong legs pa'i blo gros sku 'khrungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3066: de nas mkhan po la brgal ba'i rnam smin gyis tsha ba rang gi phyugs rdzir sku 'khrungs pa /
