NK126(cho)001:3067: de nas rgya gar gyi yul du bram ze dpal
NK126(cho)001:3068: ldan bya ba'i bu dge slong a ba d+hu ti
NK126(cho)001:3070: de'i dus su mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan pho
NK126(cho)001:3071: bo dge slong a ba kha ru zhes bya bar
NK126(cho)001:3072: skyes so // de nas gtsang legs grub ni nu
NK126(cho)001:3073: bo dge slong d+ha tu r+aa zhes bya bar skyes
NK126(cho)001:3074: skyes so // so // de nas 'gyod nas sdom
NK126(cho)001:3075: pa blangs pas tsha ba rang gi dge slong pu
NK126(cho)001:3076: na zhes bya bar skyes so //
NK126(cho)001:3077: de nas bod yul du nyang chab gtsang chab 'dzom
NK126(cho)001:3078: po'i 'gram sa chen por skyes pa'i mi pe'u'i gan
NK126(cho)001:3079: jag rdo rje rgyal po zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:3080: ma brab shing za sgron skyid ces bya ba'i bu /
NK126(cho)001:3081: rgya mo tsha ba rang nas dge slong pu na
NK126(cho)001:3082: tshe 'phos pas pe'u'i gan jag thang zhes bya bar
NK126(cho)001:3083: sku 'khrungs te / lo bco lnga las ma lon pa la rab byung byas te /
NK126(cho)001:3084: dge slong gi khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu bsrung bsrung ba /
NK126(cho)001:3085: las 'phro dang bskal par ldan pa lo bzhi bcu zhe brgyad lon /
NK126(cho)001:3086: dmag khroms las mang ste rje'i bka' stsal cig la bdag 'gro la sogs zer te /
NK126(cho)001:3087: yang rgya gar gyi yul gyi khyim bdag dpal skyes
NK126(cho)001:3088: bya ba pha spad kyi btsun pa gsum mchod gnas
NK126(cho)001:3089: su btegs nas yod pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3090: khyim bdag dpal skyes pha spad yul sku da ra bya bar mgron la bos nas song bas /
NK126(cho)001:3091: btsun pa gsum la chos ston skyel ba med nas /
NK126(cho)001:3092: btsun pa gsum gyis chos ston 'phyis par dgos nas /
NK126(cho)001:3093: btsun pa b+ha hu ra bya bas chos ston len du phyin pas /
NK126(cho)001:3094: khyim bdag dpal gyi bu mo a ma le kha bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:3095: khyim mtsher khyim bdag drag shul can gyi 'khor mi
NK126(cho)001:3096: khye'u cig pho mo'i bya ba byed pa mthong bas
NK126(cho)001:3097: / khye'u de ngo tsha nas bros nas song /
NK126(cho)001:3099: b+ha hu ra ngo tsha bsres pas dga'/
NK126(cho)001:3100: nga la 'dod chags spyad cig zer /
NK126(cho)001:3101: b+ha hu ras ci ma tshangs dngos sdom pa bsrungs ba byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3102: nga la 'dod chags ma spyad na /
NK126(cho)001:3104: sdig b+ha hu ra khyod la bkal lo //
NK126(cho)001:3105: zer nas brang la gri btsug nas /
NK126(cho)001:3106: b+ha hu ra na re 'o na sgo srib cig khyod gar dgar bzhugs shig byas so //
NK126(cho)001:3107: b+ha hu ra'i bsam pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3108: ngas a ma le kha la 'dod chags spyad kyang sdoms pa nyams te na rag ltung /
NK126(cho)001:3109: ma spyad pas bu mo'i sdig pa bsgos te na rag tu ltung bar mthong ste /
NK126(cho)001:3110: mos sgo srib shul du rang la rang gis 'do mas ske bcad nas shi bas /
NK126(cho)001:3111: skye ba brgyud nas tshe 'phos pas /
NK126(cho)001:3112: rig pa dang ldan pa mos skyes pa'i sa la /
NK126(cho)001:3113: gtsang legs grub pha tshang shing len na len tra
NK126(cho)001:3114: zhes bya bar gtsang theg chen ces bya bar a
NK126(cho)001:3115: ma mkhar chen za lum ma zhes bya ba'i bu
NK126(cho)001:3117: gtsang legs grub ces bya ba de dmag khroms nas lang ste /
NK126(cho)001:3118: rjes bka' stsal ba dag btang na rog bagyi'o zer /
NK126(cho)001:3119: de nas rjes khab tu khrid nas rje'i bka' stsal
NK126(cho)001:3120: gyi sgo gnyis bdag cag gnyis kyis 'khums par mchis
NK126(cho)001:3121: 'tshal nas / de nas man ngag gi chos tshol bka' bsgo nas /
NK126(cho)001:3122: gser gyi pa tra zung cig mgo la sbas /
NK126(cho)001:3123: gser gyi thur ma gser gyi chags shing skur /
NK126(cho)001:3124: gser tshags lu gu rgyud byas nas dug po'i gseb tu bcug /
NK126(cho)001:3125: gser gyi phye ma ba man gyi r+aa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3126: pa tra brgyad rta mtshal bu bya gdong la bkal nas chas so //
NK126(cho)001:3127: de'i dus gtsang legs grub ni 'phral skad shes pa tsam yod do //
NK126(cho)001:3128: pe'u gan chags stang ni sgra tshad mdo sngags kun la mkhas pa /
NK126(cho)001:3129: grub pa phran tshag thob pa /
NK126(cho)001:3130: nag mo ri dang sgo bzhi dang /
NK126(cho)001:3131: nya ri phu'i brag so che'i brag phug tu nyi zer zhon nas /
NK126(cho)001:3132: phar 'gro tshur 'gro mdzad pa skad sum brgya drug bcur bsgyur shes pa /
NK126(cho)001:3133: sprul pa'i sku mkhas pa chen po yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:3134: de la rje yang shin tu yid ches so //
NK126(cho)001:3135: de'i dus su a khu sa gor he 'dod skad
NK126(cho)001:3136: pa des 'dun ma chen po bsogs nas rgyal po
NK126(cho)001:3137: spyan drangs ste / pe'u gan chags stong rgya gar
NK126(cho)001:3138: du 'gro ba la mi 'di btang pas mi 'ong
NK126(cho)001:3139: spyan drangs ste / byas te / rgyal po 'gro ba bcag par zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:3140: rgyal po'i zhal nas nga las gang byas kyang dad pa can btsun par 'jug pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3141: brtson 'grus can chos la 'gro ba mi gcog /
NK126(cho)001:3142: khyi ra ba dang nya gshar gyi kha srun mi phye /
NK126(cho)001:3143: rkun byi dang las ngan byed pa'i rgya brten dang dpung gnyen mi byed gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:3144: phyag rgyab tu bsgyur nas khab tu gshegs so //
NK126(cho)001:3145: pe'u gan chags he 'dod kyis tsha bo la khyod
NK126(cho)001:3146: la 'gro shi ste 'ong bas chung ma long nged
NK126(cho)001:3148: pe'u gan chags stang ma nyan no //
NK126(cho)001:3149: a khu he 'dod na re bu ma 'gro /
NK126(cho)001:3150: 'bru btab tshad skye ba'i zhing chu ma lung ring la yang chags sam /
NK126(cho)001:3151: bu skyes pa'i don pha mes kyi yul bsrungs byas pa /
NK126(cho)001:3152: lan du b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3153: a khu ci dang ci mi gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:3154: he 'dod ci dang ci ma gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:3156: bu tsha 'khor ba'i bshal thags yin //
NK126(cho)001:3157: pha tshan 'khor ba'i lag rdos la //
NK126(cho)001:3158: nor rdzas 'khor ba'i lcags sgrogs lags //
NK126(cho)001:3159: chab srid 'khor ba'i btson ra lags //
NK126(cho)001:3160: a khu 'di kun ci mi gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:3161: de la mos pa snying re rje //
NK126(cho)001:3163: a khu he 'dod kyis 'di skad lo //
NK126(cho)001:3164: bu ma zer nga'i gcan po pe'u gan chags rdo rje rgyal po dang /
NK126(cho)001:3165: pha rgan pe'u'i blon rje 'phags pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3166: sngon gyis pha men bzang pos kyang /
NK126(cho)001:3168: tsha zhang gi mgo rdzi bgyis /
NK126(cho)001:3169: da lta yang de'i bka'i rjes 'dzin /
NK126(cho)001:3170: da bu tsha khyed rang tsho yang pho barla ma btsong byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3171: yang de'i lan du b+aee ros mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3172: a khu ci dang ci mi gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:3173: snga ma 'das pa'i pha mes kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3174: skyes nas khyim dang mkhar brtsigs pa //
NK126(cho)001:3175: shi nas khyim ni mi dbang sgo ru bstan //
NK126(cho)001:3176: khyim mkhar brtsegs pa don re chung //
NK126(cho)001:3177: snga ma 'das pa'i pha mes kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3178: yul khams bsrungs phyir sdig spyad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3179: shi nas nyal sa barla gang las bsdad dbang med //
NK126(cho)001:3180: yul mkhar bsrungs kyang don re chung //
NK126(cho)001:3181: snga ma 'das pa'i pha mas kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3182: skyes nas zhing dang chus spyad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3183: shi ba'i ro khung rang shong tsam //
NK126(cho)001:3184: yul zhing sa bcad don re chung //
NK126(cho)001:3185: snga ma 'das pa'i pha mes kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3186: bu smad gso phyir sdig spyad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3187: rnam smin tshe 'das rang la smin //
NK126(cho)001:3188: nang na nye ba'i bu smad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3189: gshin la mi lta gson la lta //
NK126(cho)001:3190: bu smad gson pa don re chung //
NK126(cho)001:3191: snga ma 'das pa'i pha mes kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3192: skyes nas nor dang phyug bsogs kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3193: shi ba'i nang par gcer bur bton //
NK126(cho)001:3194: nor phyugs bsogs par don re chung //
NK126(cho)001:3195: snga ma 'das pa'i pha mes kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3196: skyes nas gnyen dang 'khor skyong yang //
NK126(cho)001:3197: shi bas bdag nyid gcig pur thon //
NK126(cho)001:3198: bag chags tsam zhig 'khor lags kyang //
NK126(cho)001:3199: rngan bsgrang brdung brtsog phyi thag med //
NK126(cho)001:3200: gnyen 'khor skyong ba don re chung //
NK126(cho)001:3201: a khu ma gsungs zhal dron che //
NK126(cho)001:3203: yang a khu he 'dod na re /
NK126(cho)001:3204: chos rang bden nges ci yod byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3205: yang b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3206: a khu gson dang he 'dod gson //
NK126(cho)001:3207: a khu bdag ni rjes su gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:3208: khyim thabs spongs na dge bcu spyod //
NK126(cho)001:3209: dge bcu spyod pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK126(cho)001:3210: mtho ris lha dang mi ru skye //
NK126(cho)001:3211: mi lus thobs pa'i yon tan ni //
NK126(cho)001:3212: smra bsam gnyis la rang dbang thobs //
NK126(cho)001:3213: de nas sems bskyed sdom blangs pas //
NK126(cho)001:3214: thob pa bsags pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK126(cho)001:3215: bsgom na bla med byang chub thob //
NK126(cho)001:3216: de yang 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal che //
NK126(cho)001:3217: de bas mtho ba lha yi yul //
NK126(cho)001:3218: 'dod pa khams kyi lha drug ni //
NK126(cho)001:3219: gzugs dang tshe tshad khyad par che //
NK126(cho)001:3220: longs spyod sna tshogs bsam mi khyab //
NK126(cho)001:3222: ma btab lo tog khrus kyi rdzing //
NK126(cho)001:3224: de na so nam khe spogs med //
NK126(cho)001:3225: de na tse ra jag rkun med //
NK126(cho)001:3226: 'du lnga nad kyis gnod pa med //
NK126(cho)001:3227: a khu mos pa mdzad na de la mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3228: lar nam yang 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i mi //
NK126(cho)001:3229: phyin ci log la dbang po gsal //
NK126(cho)001:3230: nyon mongs lnga la brtson 'grus che //
NK126(cho)001:3232: a khu lan gcig bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:3233: gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun la //
NK126(cho)001:3234: ting nge 'dzin gyis zas la spyod //
NK126(cho)001:3235: de na gnyis dang mi dge med //
NK126(cho)001:3237: 'dod yon lnga med 'du ba'i nad kyang med //
NK126(cho)001:3238: shi na ro med 'ja' tshon yal bar 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:3239: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3240: a khu lan gcig bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:3241: gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi la //
NK126(cho)001:3243: de na nga rgyal dregs spyod med //
NK126(cho)001:3244: de na re dogs 'dod sred med //
NK126(cho)001:3245: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3246: a khu dbang po tha ma ba //
NK126(cho)001:3247: mi dang lha yi theg pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:3248: a khu lan gcig bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:3249: rgyu 'bras gnyis la brtan pa'i theg pa brgyad //
NK126(cho)001:3250: ston pa shag thub gshegs shul ni //
NK126(cho)001:3251: dang po bden bzhi'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3252: 'du khrims gnyis brgya lnga bcu srung //
NK126(cho)001:3253: 'phags pa'i lam brgyad bsgrod pa'i mthar //
NK126(cho)001:3254: 'bras bu skyes bu zung bzhi dang //
NK126(cho)001:3255: gang zag ya brgyad thob par 'dod //
NK126(cho)001:3256: mos pa mdzad pa na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3257: a khu lan gcig bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:3258: 'phags pa rang rgyal gshegs shul ni //
NK126(cho)001:3259: rten 'brel bcu gnyis sgor zhugs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3260: slob dpon mi ltos rang gis rig pas rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:3261: smra sa bcad pa'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3262: 'bras bu bswe ru lta bu thob //
NK126(cho)001:3263: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3264: a khu lan gcig bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:3265: byang chub sems dpa'i gshegs shul ni //
NK126(cho)001:3266: bden pa gnyis kyi sgor zhugs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3267: lam lnga sa bcu bsgrod pa'i mthar //
NK126(cho)001:3268: kun tu 'od kyi sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:3269: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3270: a khu lan gcig bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:3271: gsang sngags rdo rje kri ya pa //
NK126(cho)001:3272: dag pa rnam gsum sgo zhugs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3273: rigs gsum dpon dang g.yog tu lta //
NK126(cho)001:3274: rdo rje 'dzin gyi sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:3275: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3276: gnyis ka spyod pa u pa ya //
NK126(cho)001:3277: kri ya spyod cing yo ga bsgrub //
NK126(cho)001:3278: nges pa med pa khe tshol 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:3279: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:3280: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3281: yo ga sems dpa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK126(cho)001:3282: 'jug sgo mngon par byang chub lnga //
NK126(cho)001:3283: rigs lnga ye shes lnga po la //
NK126(cho)001:3284: mnyam nyid grogs por blta zhing bsgrub //
NK126(cho)001:3285: stug po bkod pa'i sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:3286: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3287: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga ni //
NK126(cho)001:3288: ting 'dzin rnam gsum sgor zhugs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3289: sems kyi cho 'phrul ltar snang bas //
NK126(cho)001:3290: phyi nang gsang ba'i lam nas bsgrod //
NK126(cho)001:3291: pad+ma can gyi sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:3292: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3293: gsang sngags a nu yo ga ba //
NK126(cho)001:3294: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3295: grangs mdog ma nges sku gsung thugs //
NK126(cho)001:3296: sems ni ma brtsal sku gsung thugs su gsal //
NK126(cho)001:3297: kun bzang dbyer med sa yang non //
NK126(cho)001:3298: mos pa mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3299: gros 'debs mdzad na de ru mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3300: lar phyin ci log la dbang po gsal //
NK126(cho)001:3301: nyon mongs lnga la brtson 'grus che //
NK126(cho)001:3302: ngan song gnas su nam yang ltung //
NK126(cho)001:3303: de skad gsungs pas kho thag chod //
NK126(cho)001:3304: yid ches nas bu rang gar dga' mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:3307: man ngag gi chos tshol ba la skyes bu khyad
NK126(cho)001:3308: par can dgos par bstan pa'i skabs te bcu gnyis
NK126(cho)001:3309: pa'o //// yang de'i tshe de'i dus na b+aee ro tsa na dang /
NK126(cho)001:3310: gtsang legs grub gnyis kyi stag lo dpyid zla ra
NK126(cho)001:3311: ba'i lo gsar gyi tshes gsum la gza' zla ba
NK126(cho)001:3312: la brgyob gtad nas lho phyogs me'i thog tu phyin
NK126(cho)001:3313: te +aar+ya pa lo'i gling du dpag pas de ru
NK126(cho)001:3314: thugs rje chen po'i lung bstan thob pas /
NK126(cho)001:3317: de ru dgung gcig b+aee ro dang gtsang legs grub gnyis kyi gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:3318: b+aee ro tsa na la dgung gcig la rmi lam mi 'dra ba lnga byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:3319: srod la thun cig rnal ba'i rmi lam na /
NK126(cho)001:3320: bu mo gzhon nu ma lo brgyad lon pa zhig
NK126(cho)001:3321: gis ral gri 'od dang rang bcas pa 'bar ba
NK126(cho)001:3322: zhig gis b+aee ro tsa na'i gzugs kyi khang pa
NK126(cho)001:3323: nas dral nas / don snying phyung te bzhi gshags su gshags chu phyungs cu ser btsag par rmin /
NK126(cho)001:3324: nang gung la thun gcig rnal ba'i rmi lam na /
NK126(cho)001:3325: rgya gar skyes bu nyi shu rtsa gcig gi snying
NK126(cho)001:3326: phyungs te snying nyi shu rtsa gcig zos pa rmis
NK126(cho)001:3327: / nam phyed la thun gcig rnal ba'i rmi lam na /
NK126(cho)001:3328: rgya gar gyi mi ring skya bo zhig gi b+aee
NK126(cho)001:3329: ro tsa na'i spyi bo'i gtsug tu yi ge zhig
NK126(cho)001:3330: bzhag / a de 'od du zhu ste me ru gyur /
NK126(cho)001:3331: me'i b+aee ro'i gzugs phung bsreg cing rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3332: tho ras thun gcig nyal ba'i rmi lam na /
NK126(cho)001:3333: rgya gar yul gyi ston pa'i sku rten byang chub kyi shing bu de /
NK126(cho)001:3334: rtsa ba nas bcad nas bod du khyer nas 'ong ba rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3335: nam lang khar thun gcig rnal ba'i rmi lam na /
NK126(cho)001:3336: nam mkha'i dkyil nas nyi zla gnyis shar ba rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3337: zla ba nam mkha'i dkyil du rgas shing rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3338: nyi ma bsam yas has po ri la shar ba rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3339: yang theng gcig nyi ma nub nas rgas shing rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3340: yang theng gcig nyi ma bsam yas has po ri la shar bar rmis /
NK126(cho)001:3343: b+aee ros rmi lam bzlas pa /
NK126(cho)001:3344: grogs po byang chub sems dpa' snyan gson dang /
NK126(cho)001:3345: bdag srod la rmi ba sngon gyi bag chags rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3346: da lta rmi bas sngon gyi bag chags ngan pa byang ba'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3347: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:3348: nam gung la rmi ba sngon gyi las 'phro rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3349: sngon gyi las 'phro skal bar ldan pa yis //
NK126(cho)001:3350: rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag rgyu 'bras med pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:3351: b+aee ro bdag gi thob pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3352: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:3353: nam phyed thun gcig lon pa'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:3354: rgya gar skyes bu spyi gtsug yi ge a bzhag pas //
NK126(cho)001:3355: a ni mer gyur bdag gi gzugs phung bsreg par rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3356: a ni skye med chos sku dag pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:3357: skye med ye shes me dpung 'bar ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:3358: lus ngag yid gsum bag chags bsreg pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3359: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:3360: tho ras thun gcig rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:3361: rgya gar yul gyi ston pa'i sku rten byang chub shing bu de //
NK126(cho)001:3362: rtsad nas bcad de bod du khyer nas 'ong ba rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3363: rgya gar yul gyi man ngag bde chen rnams //
NK126(cho)001:3364: rtsad nas bcad de bdag gis thobs pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3365: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:3366: nam lang thun cig rnal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK126(cho)001:3367: nam mkha'i dkyil du nyi zla gnyis shar te //
NK126(cho)001:3368: zla ba nam mkha'i dkyil du rgas pa de //
NK126(cho)001:3369: legs grub gcan 'phrang dang pos bsad pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3370: nyi ma bsam yas has po ri la shar ba de //
NK126(cho)001:3371: rgyal po'i thugs la b+aee ros man ngag bshad pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3372: yang thang gcig nyi ma nub tu rgas shing rmi ba de //
NK126(cho)001:3373: b+aee ro tsha ba'i rang na lan gcig spyug pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3374: yang theng gcig nyi ma has po ri la shar ba de //
NK126(cho)001:3375: b+aee ro tsha ba rang na log nas rgyal po'i thugs la man ngag bshad pa'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3376: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:3378: de nas lo ts+aa ba gnyis po phar la phyin
NK126(cho)001:3379: pas zla ba gnyis kyis rgya gar gyi yul chu
NK126(cho)001:3382: gser phye phrog par byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3384: rin po che'i za ma tog gis nang du lcags
NK126(cho)001:3385: kyi spu gri zhig tu bardzusa nas 'dug pa la
NK126(cho)001:3386: / 'phrong bsrung gi dpon po ku ha ra da du bya ba de na re /
NK126(cho)001:3387: 'di ni ngo mtshar che'o zer nas /
NK126(cho)001:3388: cho 'phrul can 'di la zla bo 'di bsad la gser phye 'phrog byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3389: b+aee ro tsa nas grogs po legs grub bsad kyi
NK126(cho)001:3390: dogs nas matha'i mon pa spyi lum cig tu sprul
NK126(cho)001:3391: nas / 'phrang bsrung rnam la mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3392: skye 'chi gnyis med nam mkha' lta bu'i sems 'di la //
NK126(cho)001:3393: snang ba mun sel ci yang sprul pa'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:3394: 'dzam gling mun sel nyi ma ci bzhin du //
NK126(cho)001:3395: dam chos btsal la snyams snyams bya dgos pas //
NK126(cho)001:3396: gsal khyab nam mkha' lta bu'i sems 'di la //
NK126(cho)001:3397: bsad dang ma bsad shi dang ma shi med //
NK126(cho)001:3398: sgyu lus phung po'i srog 'di bcad na khyod la sdig par 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:3399: de bas sgyu ma gser gyi barngana pa 'di sbyin gyis //
NK126(cho)001:3400: rgya gar lam rgyus ci ltar yin de nga la bag tsam ston //
NK126(cho)001:3401: de skad byas pas khong tshos kyang ma bsad par /
NK126(cho)001:3402: byang lam dang po yar la bor /
NK126(cho)001:3403: tha ma mar la bor la /
NK126(cho)001:3404: bar pa nas zhugs la song zhig ces lam bstan te /
NK126(cho)001:3405: de nas rgya gar yul du sleb nas /
NK126(cho)001:3406: gser par skungs su sbas te /
NK126(cho)001:3407: man ngag gi chos su mkhas /
NK126(cho)001:3408: chos gra'i slob dpon su yin /
NK126(cho)001:3410: chos spyod pa ni su yin /
NK126(cho)001:3415: khang stong mgron po nyal ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:3421: mi mang po gang 'du bar mnyan pas /
NK126(cho)001:3422: chos pa mang ba spyod pa nyung na mi kha mthun par /
NK126(cho)001:3423: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha zhes bya ba pan tri
NK126(cho)001:3424: ta stong gi slob dpon du gyur pa mkhas pa
NK126(cho)001:3425: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i zhabs la gtugs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3426: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi zhal gzigs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3427: dgung lo lnga brgya lon pa zhig bzhugs zer /
NK126(cho)001:3428: khong gang na bzhugs dris pas /
NK126(cho)001:3429: d+ha na ko sha'i mdzod sing ldings bsil byed kyi tshal /
NK126(cho)001:3430: tsan+dana dri zhim gyi nags rin po che za ma tog spung pa'i khab na bzhugs so zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:3431: mthu d+ha na sam skri ta cho zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:3432: de'i dus su d+ha he na'i 'du khang du /
NK126(cho)001:3433: sems nyid thig le nyag gcig la /
NK126(cho)001:3434: rgyud lung man ngag gsum du phye ba la smad tshong ma bdag nyid ma dang /
NK126(cho)001:3435: dge slong ma kun dga' mo de gnyis brtsod pas /
NK126(cho)001:3436: kun gyis bltas shing rtsod pas /
NK126(cho)001:3438: bdag cag pan+di ta rnams mtshan bltas log /
NK126(cho)001:3439: khyed gnyis kyi man ngag gis chos la d+ha he
NK126(cho)001:3440: na'i 'du khang du brtsod pa byas te bsgrags pas
NK126(cho)001:3441: lan / dam chos phag tshang dang lkog tshang byed dbang med de /
NK126(cho)001:3442: sus byas pa la rgyal pos bka' chad gsol lo //
NK126(cho)001:3445: gtsang legs grub gnyis ngo nag ting nge thal lo //
NK126(cho)001:3446: bu gcig shi ba'i ma lta bu'i sdug bsngal yang byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3447: de'i dus de'i tshe sh+ri sing ha pra ba dang
NK126(cho)001:3448: bya ba des chos grwa'i slob dpon mdzad pa la
NK126(cho)001:3449: / man ngag gi chos la'ang mkhas te /
NK126(cho)001:3450: spyir na sgra la mnga' brnyes nas sgra bsgyur ba
NK126(cho)001:3451: la mkhas pa phul du phyin pa zhig lags skad
NK126(cho)001:3452: / yul d+ha he na ku sha'i 'du khang na byang chub shing drung na bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3453: de'i dus rgya gar gyi yul za kha b+hud+d+ha'i gling zhes bya ba na /
NK126(cho)001:3454: rgyal po ku ma sa du zhes bya ba cig bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3456: d+ha he na ku sha'i 'du khang gang na yod dris pas /
NK126(cho)001:3459: mdang sum bdag la rmi lam 'di ltar rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3460: bod kyi rgyal khams zer ba'i gangs bar nas //
NK126(cho)001:3461: mun nag smag tu gyur pa'i 'jig rten na //
NK126(cho)001:3462: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i rgyal po zhig /
NK126(cho)001:3463: rgya gar yul gyi bram ze dpal ldan bya ba'i bu //
NK126(cho)001:3464: dge slong a wa d+hu ti bya ba tshe 'phos nas //
NK126(cho)001:3465: bod kyi rgyal bur skyes pa nor bu lta bu ste //
NK126(cho)001:3466: gang bar mun nag sel zhing rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3467: ben d+he khyed gnyis rtsol med man ngag tshol du 'ong ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:3468: d+ha he na'i 'du khang mi ston zer ba la /
NK126(cho)001:3469: b+aee ro tsa nas len btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:3470: ye nas ma bcos chos nyid rang bzhin la //
NK126(cho)001:3471: 'du 'bral med par thams cad mnyam pa chen por gnas //
NK126(cho)001:3472: de phyir gnyis med byang chub sems su ye nas mnyam /
NK126(cho)001:3473: de phyir lung dang man ngag tshol du ma mchis te //
NK126(cho)001:3474: lho bal mon gyi rgyal khams ci lta bu //
NK126(cho)001:3475: bod kyi rgyal khams kun tu smras phyir dris pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:3477: rgyal po ku ma sa du na re yang 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:3478: khyed kyi bka' bden sems la 'chang ba'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK126(cho)001:3479: yul d+ha he na ku sha'i grong khyer 'di ltar lags /
NK126(cho)001:3480: zer nas ku sha'i 'du khang bstan te /
NK126(cho)001:3481: de na skyed tshangs chen po dgu yod de /
NK126(cho)001:3482: skyed tshongs chen po dgu po'i nang nas ston pa
NK126(cho)001:3483: dga' rab rdo rje zhes bya ba chos nyid skye
NK126(cho)001:3484: 'gags med pa'i dngos grub thob nas /
NK126(cho)001:3485: rig pa klong nas shar ba'i skyes bu de yi spyan snga na /
NK126(cho)001:3486: mkhas pa dgongs rgyud rnam par dag pa bcu drug bka'i lung nod cing bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3487: da bka'i lung rdzogs thob nas dgongs pa klong du
NK126(cho)001:3488: gyur nas smra ba'i tshig las 'das te gnas de
NK126(cho)001:3489: nyid du bzhugs / mkhas pa phyi ma bdun ni /
NK126(cho)001:3490: tshig phra mo las ma bzlog te da rung tshig la chags te /
NK126(cho)001:3491: skyed tshangs gnyis pa na bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)001:3492: skyed tshongs gnyis pa'i 'og gsum pa na slob dpon chen po bi ma la mi tra dang /
NK126(cho)001:3493: 'og khams pa ral la sogs pa grangs kyis bzhugs te /
NK126(cho)001:3494: mkhas pa de rnams kyi ston pa dga' rab rdo
NK126(cho)001:3495: rje'i zhal mthong zhing lung nod pa rnams yin no
NK126(cho)001:3496: // de'i gong ma mkhas pa bcu drug po lung
NK126(cho)001:3497: nod cing man ngag sgor khyud du bzhugs pa yin
NK126(cho)001:3498: // te / gnas de na bram ze rgan mo de dang mjal nas /
NK126(cho)001:3499: rgan mo de la skyed tshangs chen po dgu po gang yin /
NK126(cho)001:3500: man ngag gi chos la su mkhas /
NK126(cho)001:3501: mkhas pa sh+ri seng ha gang na bzhugs dris pas /
NK126(cho)001:3502: rgan mo de na tsan+dana gyi lo mas byad bkab
NK126(cho)001:3503: nas bod ban gnyis po ngas d+ha he na'i drung
NK126(cho)001:3504: na mnyan pas pan+di ta brgyad rmi lam zlos pa
NK126(cho)001:3505: thos pas sdug bsngal ma byed par nga la gser
NK126(cho)001:3507: an tsam cig blangs nas man ngag ngas bzla'i gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:3508: des mtsho kun tra'i 'gram du phyin te /
NK126(cho)001:3509: rgan mo de lus dra bar bzhugs /
NK126(cho)001:3511: kha ru u bi bcug ste /
NK126(cho)001:3512: u bi nas rgan mos rmi lam bzlas pa /
NK126(cho)001:3513: khyi'i mkhan po d+ha hu nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:3514: skye ba 'di la 'bras bu mngon du thob pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:3515: rgyu 'bras gnyis las 'das pa a ti'i yo ga chos //
NK126(cho)001:3516: las dang thugs rje 'brel pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK126(cho)001:3517: snod dang skal bar ldan pa ban+de gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:3518: ma 'ongs rgyal khams 'bras bu thob bya'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:3519: 'o skol rgyal khams 'di ru 'ong ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:3520: bud med bya ba'i rigs ngan rdol thabs smra //
NK126(cho)001:3521: rtsa ba dam tshig nyams shing gsang ma thub //
NK126(cho)001:3522: thang la smig rgyu chu la khyab yul du //
NK126(cho)001:3523: gsang sngags mtha' 'khob yul du khyer zhing rmi //
NK126(cho)001:3524: de skad zlos pas rgan mo bdag gi thos //
NK126(cho)001:3525: bod ban gnyis kyi don chen 'grub par nges //
NK126(cho)001:3526: smad tshong ma bdag nyid mas na re /
NK126(cho)001:3527: chos nyid rang bzhin mnyam pa chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:3528: chos pa shas che gsang tshig ma thub pas //
NK126(cho)001:3529: smon lam ma dag bud med lus blangs nas //
NK126(cho)001:3530: 'jig rten 'khor ba'i chos bzhin 'khrul ba'i rtags //
NK126(cho)001:3531: mnyams pa chen po gcig la gsum du phye ba'i rkyen //
NK126(cho)001:3532: nyon mongs dug lngas zas nor byed pa'i ma'i //
NK126(cho)001:3533: srin po gdong dmar dbyibs rgu sha nag ri pa'i mis //
NK126(cho)001:3534: skyes pa'i tha ma mi lus 'di bor nas //
NK126(cho)001:3535: byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa mi gnyis kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3536: gsang sngags theg pa mkhas pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK126(cho)001:3537: srin po gdong dmar rgyal po'i snyan rgyud de //
NK126(cho)001:3538: mnga' ris gsang sngags bod du bo zhing rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3539: bud med rigs la gsang tshig mi bstan ces //
NK126(cho)001:3540: dga' rab rdo rje'i zhal nas gsungs pa don re bden //
NK126(cho)001:3541: de skad gsungs pa rgan mo bdag gis thos //
NK126(cho)001:3542: bod ban gnyis kyi don chen 'grub par nges //
NK126(cho)001:3544: drang srong b+ha shi tas smras pa /
NK126(cho)001:3545: gcig las med pa'i chos nyid byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:3546: smra bsam tshig las 'das pa yin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:3547: rgyud lung man ngag gsum du phye ba'i skyon //
NK126(cho)001:3548: rtsod rgyu med par rtsod pa'i gzhir gyur pas //
NK126(cho)001:3549: bud med gsang ba'i bka' la mi gdags zhes //
NK126(cho)001:3550: ston pa'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i lung re bden //
NK126(cho)001:3551: de yi don gyis gsang ba bod du gyer //
NK126(cho)001:3552: gsang sngags rab tu 'chal zhing rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3553: de skad zlos pas rgan mo bdag gi thos //
NK126(cho)001:3554: bod ban gnyis kyi don chen 'grub par nges //
NK126(cho)001:3556: 'jam dpal dpal bzang gis gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3557: kun dga' ma dang bdag nyid ma //
NK126(cho)001:3558: bud med bya ba'i rig ngan khyed gnyis kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3559: chos rnams thams cad gcig las med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:3560: 'khrul pa'i sems kyis rgyud lung gsum du phye //
NK126(cho)001:3561: ci bzhin ma bcos rang bzhin med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:3562: dbang po rab 'bring tha ma gsum po de //
NK126(cho)001:3563: ji bzhin gcig la rgyud lung man ngag gsum //
NK126(cho)001:3564: 'khrul pas brtags na rgyud lung man ngag gsum du 'dod pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:3565: 'dod chags shas che rtogs pa'i klong gnas pa //
NK126(cho)001:3566: ma he bud med khyi la sogs //
NK126(cho)001:3567: 'khrul pa'i rgya mdud 'dzin pa'i mdud pa des //
NK126(cho)001:3568: lnga phung gzugs kyi phung po bsdom re legs //
NK126(cho)001:3569: rtog las 'das pas rang bzhin ngo ma shes //
NK126(cho)001:3570: nan brtags blo yis gnyis su phye ba 'di //
NK126(cho)001:3571: srin po gdong dmar bod kyi rgyal po la //
NK126(cho)001:3572: mkhas pa'i man ngag gsang ba'i ti ka rnams //
NK126(cho)001:3573: sa la gnas pa'i sprul pa byang chub sems dpa' yin //
NK126(cho)001:3574: spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa rgyal po la //
NK126(cho)001:3575: snyan khungs bzlas te 'chal pa phyar zhing rmi //
NK126(cho)001:3576: de skad gsungs pa rgan mo nga yis thos //
NK126(cho)001:3577: bod ban gnyis kyi don chen 'grub par nges //
NK126(cho)001:3579: khyi'i mkhan po phyi mas gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3580: rig pa 'gyur med rgyal ba'i dgongs pa de //
NK126(cho)001:3581: ya mtshan tshig las 'das pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:3582: tshig tu phye ba bud med rang bzhin te //
NK126(cho)001:3583: 'khor ba'i chos la sred pa ma spongs te //
NK126(cho)001:3584: ston pa'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i rgyud sde dang //
NK126(cho)001:3585: mkhas pas gsang ba'i man ngag ni //
NK126(cho)001:3586: ci bzhin ma bcos mkha' ltar dag pa'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:3587: ye nas dmigs med mnyam pa'i rgyal po de //
NK126(cho)001:3588: rgyud lung man ngag gsum du dbyer med la //
NK126(cho)001:3589: 'jig rten sgyu ma'i nor ltar sems 'khrul nas //
NK126(cho)001:3590: gcig la gsum du phye ba'i skyon yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:3591: ston pa'i thugs rje bri bkol mi mdzad de //
NK126(cho)001:3592: bod kyi rgyal khams thams cad du //
NK126(cho)001:3593: spyan ras gzigs kyi thugs rje'i nyi shar bas //
NK126(cho)001:3594: kun las 'das pa'i rgyal po gdong dmar gyis //
NK126(cho)001:3595: sa bcu sprul pa byang chub sems dpa' gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:3596: gser phye bardzongasa nas dka' ba'i yul 'di 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:3597: rgyal ba'i man ngag a ti ni //
NK126(cho)001:3598: phyags mas btab nas song zhing rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3599: de skad smra ba rgan mo nga yi thos //
NK126(cho)001:3600: bod bon gnyis kyi don chen 'grub par nges //
NK126(cho)001:3602: bud med bya ba'i g.yo sgyu ngo bzlog mkhan //
NK126(cho)001:3603: smra lce mang zhing khrel 'dzem yid ches dka' //
NK126(cho)001:3604: gsang tshig mi thub rtsod pa'i gzhir gyur pa //
NK126(cho)001:3605: de yi rkyen byas rmi lam 'di ltar byung //
NK126(cho)001:3606: rgya gar yul nas nyi zla gnyis shar bas //
NK126(cho)001:3607: skye ba phyi ma mi lan mi gnyis kyis //
NK126(cho)001:3608: nyi ma snam phrag bcug nas khyer ba rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3609: zla ba yul phyogs 'di ru lus pa rmis //
NK126(cho)001:3610: mkhas pa'i man ngag bod du khyer ba'i ltas //
NK126(cho)001:3611: de skad smra ba rgan mos bdag gi thos //
NK126(cho)001:3612: bod bon gnyis kyi don chen 'grub par nges //
NK126(cho)001:3614: b+aee ro tsa na yid ches sems sos so //
NK126(cho)001:3615: rgya gar gyi rmi lam dang mtshan ma bzlag pa dang po smras pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:3616: thams cad na re a ti mkhas pa'i lkog chos gsang ma thub ste /
NK126(cho)001:3617: bud med gnyis kyis rtsod pas nyes zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:3618: thams cad kun dga' mo la dgos pa skyes so //
NK126(cho)001:3620: gnas de na bram ze mo shel shes rab kyi
NK126(cho)001:3621: blo gros bya ba zhig rgyu 'dul byed cing chu
NK126(cho)001:3622: khur 'ong gi de la 'phrod cig byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3623: b+aee ro tsa na dang ban+de gnyis kyi skyed tshangs kyi sgo ru bsgug pas mjal te /
NK126(cho)001:3624: chun ma la thon bardzongasa pas /
NK126(cho)001:3625: brjed zer zhing zhag gsum du ma 'thon no //
NK126(cho)001:3626: der b+aee ro tsa nas mo'i chu'i bum pa la sgyu ma'i sbyor sngags dang chu sbyor btab te /
NK126(cho)001:3627: bum pa sa ma sbyar bas mo na re /
NK126(cho)001:3629: khyed kyis rdzu 'phrul de lta bu ston no //
NK126(cho)001:3630: bdag gi kyang chos 'phrul 'di lta bu ston zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:3631: mo rang gi mchan khungs g.yas pa nas gser gyi
NK126(cho)001:3632: zangs gri sor brgyad pa cig phyungs nas badz+ra b+han+d+ha
NK126(cho)001:3633: tra tha / ces brjod mo rang gi khog pa dral te bstan pas /
NK126(cho)001:3634: khog pa na yo ga dbyings kyi lha sum cu
NK126(cho)001:3635: rtsa bdun gyis dkyil 'khor bkra sa ler snang ste
NK126(cho)001:3636: / b+aee ro tsa na shin tu mos te /
NK126(cho)001:3641: sangs rgyas lags so skyabs kyi mgon /
NK126(cho)001:3642: dam chos lags so lam gyi gzhi /
NK126(cho)001:3643: dge 'dun lags so sa bcu non /
NK126(cho)001:3644: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:3645: gsung pa des sgrib pa lan gcig byang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3646: der bram ze rgan mo na re /
NK126(cho)001:3647: da skyed tshangs gnyis 'og gsum pa na /
NK126(cho)001:3648: mkhas pa bi ma mi tra la sogs pa grangs kyis bzhugs te /
NK126(cho)001:3649: des na skabs dang sbyor te nang du ci brtol gyis shig /
NK126(cho)001:3650: nang du brtol ba dang lha phyag gsum gyis shig /
NK126(cho)001:3651: de tsam na mkhas pa kun sba lcag lan gsum gsum sa la rdeb kyi 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3652: 'ong ngo bya ba lan bdun bdun dang /
NK126(cho)001:3653: kang kang lan cig gi brda mjal du 'ong gi /
NK126(cho)001:3654: des bka' mchid lo rgyus kyis zhus shig zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:3655: mo la gtsang legs grub kyis rna ltag g.yas pa nas gser zho brgyad bcad de byin no //
NK126(cho)001:3656: des skyed tshangs kyi sgor skabs btsal nas /
NK126(cho)001:3657: a tsa ra gcig phyir thon pa'i sgo dang nged
NK126(cho)001:3658: las pa las nang du rtol bas slob dpon rnams
NK126(cho)001:3659: ni gdan 'phar gsum gyis steng na /
NK126(cho)001:3660: snyan cha khrol le bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)001:3661: zhugs mar bya pho tsam btang nas bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3662: lha phyag lan gsum gsum byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3663: slob dpon rnams sba mkhar lan bdun bdun sa la
NK126(cho)001:3664: brdab pas bod kyi ban de gnyis kyis kang kang
NK126(cho)001:3667: slob dpon bi ma la'i zhal nas khyed cag 'dir ston pa ni su yin /
NK126(cho)001:3668: kong kong 'ong 'ong lan bdun byed du 'jug mi su yin /
NK126(cho)001:3669: don ci la 'ong ba yin gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:3670: b+aee ro tsa na dang gtsang legs grub gnyis kyis zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:3672: bdag cag ni bod yul dbus nas /
NK126(cho)001:3673: mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' khri srong lde'u btsan ces bya ba /
NK126(cho)001:3674: dkar po'i phyogs la mos pa /
NK126(cho)001:3675: rgyu'i chos ci rnyed spyad kyang /
NK126(cho)001:3676: 'bras bu bya rtsol med pa ma rnyed de /
NK126(cho)001:3677: 'bras bu rtsol sgrub bya rtsol dang bral ba cig
NK126(cho)001:3678: bzhed nas spyan sngar bardzangasa te mchis pa lags te
NK126(cho)001:3681: rtags ci dang ldan ces gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:3682: ban+d+he gnyis kyis khong rang gi dbu skra chan pas btab ste /
NK126(cho)001:3683: gser gyi pa tra gnyis mgo las zhwa bzhin phud nas phul bas /
NK126(cho)001:3684: slob dpon rnams zhal 'dzum pa mdzad nas /
NK126(cho)001:3685: zhal nas tshig shor ba yu ba thung mon nas /
NK126(cho)001:3686: zhal smad mdzad nas zhal rog ge bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)001:3688: nang par yang bram ze mo shel gyi blo gros
NK126(cho)001:3689: la brjed rdor zangs bum nang na rdo bcug ste
NK126(cho)001:3690: btang bas / de nas nang du chu zangs blug pas /
NK126(cho)001:3692: slob dpon sh+ri sing has gsan pas /
NK126(cho)001:3695: bod ban gnyis kyis brjed rdo lags /
NK126(cho)001:3696: khang pa nus pa phra mo 'dra ba yang ston cing gda'/
NK126(cho)001:3697: shog 'phrin 'di skur zhing gda' byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3699: ku ra na ma h+aa tsan /
NK126(cho)001:3700: b+hud+d+ha d+harma sang+ga na ma ya /
NK126(cho)001:3702: ku ru sa ma ya can dz+ny+aa na karma ku ru g+hu h+ya smin /
NK126(cho)001:3703: ces bya ba cig bardzangasa pas /
NK126(cho)001:3704: rje sh+ri sing has gzigs nas /
NK126(cho)001:3705: bod skad du bsgyur ba 'di skad du /
NK126(cho)001:3706: 'phags pa'i 'phags pa byang chub sems dpa' khyod /
NK126(cho)001:3707: 'gro ba rigs drug nang nas bsod nams mi lus sku //
NK126(cho)001:3708: nor bu rin chen 'bar ba sde snod gsum gyi dbyigs //
NK126(cho)001:3709: yid bzhin nor ldan thugs rje stobs mchog gi //
NK126(cho)001:3710: gsal khyab nyi ma lta bu thugs rje sku lus la //
NK126(cho)001:3711: skye ba brgyud nas mi lus thob pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:3712: bod kyi mi ngan dge bsnyen bdag dngos gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:3713: sgrib pa sbyong phyir dkon mchog rin chen la //
NK126(cho)001:3714: rtags par mchod cing rgyun du zhabs 'khor yang //
NK126(cho)001:3715: mun pa bsal nas bsod nams tshogs bskyed zhu //
NK126(cho)001:3716: thugs rjes ma smin smon lam ma dag pas //
NK126(cho)001:3717: 'phags pa'i bzhugs gnas sems can gnas su 'gyang //
NK126(cho)001:3719: thabs kyis 'od zer ston la thugs rje'i zhags pas zungs //
NK126(cho)001:3723: sa ma ya a pa ra mi ta dz+nya na bya ba cig bskur te /
NK126(cho)001:3724: b+aee ros sgra de bod skad du bsgyur ba /
NK126(cho)001:3725: dam tshig chen pos bdag bskul na //
NK126(cho)001:3726: mi 'phrad pa yi rang dbang med //
NK126(cho)001:3727: 'gro ba'i sems nyid de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs //
NK126(cho)001:3728: srin bu pad+ma yan chad sangs rgyas rigs //
NK126(cho)001:3729: 'gro ba rigs drug sangs rgyas nyid mnyam yang //
NK126(cho)001:3730: 'phags pa'i 'phags par mchod pa khyed gyis dang //
NK126(cho)001:3731: dkon mchog rin chen bla ma mchod gnas la //
NK126(cho)001:3732: dam par mthong ba'i tshogs rnams spyi ba'i rgyud //
NK126(cho)001:3733: sems kyi rus pas yan lag thang bcad nas //
NK126(cho)001:3734: dka' bas byon pa bdag cag dga' ba'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:3735: shes pa bdur ma zhad kyis 'phrad par bgyi //
NK126(cho)001:3737: bram ze ma shel gyi blo gros la tshes bzhi'i
NK126(cho)001:3738: zla ba nub tsam nam gung la 'phrad kyi gsungs
NK126(cho)001:3740: de nas nam gung la mjal nas /
NK126(cho)001:3744: mar me mdzad kyis brkyang phyag 'tshal nas bod kyi
NK126(cho)001:3745: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis bardzangasa pa'i glu
NK126(cho)001:3746: 'di gsungs zhes / b+aee ros mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:3747: bka' khri srong lde'u btsan gyis bdag dang //
NK126(cho)001:3749: bdag kyang dad pa'i snyan du mchod pa'i mi ma mchis //
NK126(cho)001:3750: bdag nyid drung du 'ong dus las kyi 'jil nyil mang //
NK126(cho)001:3751: re 'dod sems kyis phreng zhing bstod lags kyi //
NK126(cho)001:3752: rgyu 'bras gnyis las 'das pa'i chos shig gnang 'tshal thugs rjes zungs //
NK126(cho)001:3753: ces de skad rgyal pos gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:3754: de la sogs pa ston pas zhabs kyis bcag pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3755: rgya gar gyi yul du sngon ston pa sku 'khrungs /
NK126(cho)001:3757: tha ma sku mya ngan las der 'das pas /
NK126(cho)001:3758: des na rgyu 'bras gnyis las 'das pa'i chos shig
NK126(cho)001:3759: yod nges pas de bsgyur dgos gsungs nas nged gnyis
NK126(cho)001:3760: btang ba lags bya ba bram ze dpal ldan bu
NK126(cho)001:3761: ru skyes pa'i lo rgyus bsnyad pas yid ches /
NK126(cho)001:3765: slob dpon sh+ri sing ha'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:3766: dge slong ma kun 'ga' mos man ngag gi chos tshang dus kyi 'o ma bzhin bslad de spel /
NK126(cho)001:3767: tshig gi sgro 'dog mang pos bslad /
NK126(cho)001:3768: yang d+ha he na'i 'du khang du rgyud lung man
NK126(cho)001:3769: ngag gsum la smad tshong ma bdag nyid ma dang
NK126(cho)001:3770: / dge slong ma kun 'ga' mo kho gnyis kyi
NK126(cho)001:3771: rtsod pa byas pas pan tri ta thams cad mtshan
NK126(cho)001:3772: / ma log ste / pan tri ta thams cad tshogs nas gros byas nas /
NK126(cho)001:3773: mkhas pa brgyad kyis chos thams cad bsdus te /
NK126(cho)001:3774: legs su re bas bslad pa tsho bsreg /
NK126(cho)001:3775: rnal ma ma bslad pa rnams yo bsdeb te /
NK126(cho)001:3776: rdo rje gdan gyi 'og tu sbas te pan tri ta'i rgya dang /
NK126(cho)001:3777: rgya gar ba'i chos skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rgya gnyis phyag rgya ru sprod kyis btab nas yod /
NK126(cho)001:3779: dus da lta mtha' 'khob bod kyi yul du 'byung ba'i dus la bab nas gda'/
NK126(cho)001:3780: ngas do nub mnyam par bzhag la mtshan ma brtags gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:3781: nang par lo ts+aa gnyis po sh+ri sing has spyan sngar phyin pas mtshan ma bzang /
NK126(cho)001:3782: bod la phan thogs nyan 'dug gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:3783: g+hu ru sh+ri sing ha'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:3784: da yang bka' rgyas pa nas /
NK126(cho)001:3785: sgron ma dang mun pa'i bskal pa tshad med grangs
NK126(cho)001:3786: med pa spel mar dpag tu med pa 'das pa'i
NK126(cho)001:3787: skabs su / bskal pa dga' ba zhes bya ba la /
NK126(cho)001:3788: sangs rgyas stong phrag drug cu 'byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3789: tha ma'i sangs rgyas mngon rdzogs rgyas pos /
NK126(cho)001:3790: man ngag 'di rnams thugs kyi sras bdun la gtad do //
NK126(cho)001:3791: sangs rgyas blo gros bde byed dang /
NK126(cho)001:3799: de 'das nas mun pa'i bskal pa lnga brgyad 'byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3800: de nas bskal pa mngon par dga' ba zhes bya ba 'di la /
NK126(cho)001:3801: sangs rgyas stong rtsa gcig byung ba'i tha mar /
NK126(cho)001:3802: nga'i bstan pa tha ma la bstan pa lnga brgya phrag bcu dang sum brgya gnas pa las /
NK126(cho)001:3803: sum brgya yan chad du rgyu 'bras kyi chos gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:3805: lo gnyis stong brgyad brgya bdun cu rtsa bdun na /
NK126(cho)001:3806: rgya gar yul du dar ste /
NK126(cho)001:3807: u rgyan rgya phug d+ha na ko sha'i gling du 'dis 'khor ba lan gsum du stongs so //
NK126(cho)001:3808: de nas gsang ba dam pa 'di mtha' 'khob yul du rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3810: sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' zhig gis blangs nas /
NK126(cho)001:3811: mtha' 'khob rgyal po spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa la ston par 'gyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3813: de 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab ste /
NK126(cho)001:3814: de nas tsha ba'i yul du sa bdun pa'i byang
NK126(cho)001:3815: chub sems dpa' lkog ma na sme ba yod pa
NK126(cho)001:3816: cig dang / rang rgyal gyi sprul pa cig la ston par 'gyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3817: des yang sa bdun pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ston /
NK126(cho)001:3818: des sa lnga pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa la ston /
NK126(cho)001:3819: des sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ston /
NK126(cho)001:3820: des yang sa bdun pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ston /
NK126(cho)001:3821: des sa gsum pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ston /
NK126(cho)001:3822: des sa bdun pa dang brgyad pa nyi tshe ba
NK126(cho)001:3823: bdun la brgyud nas grub pa thob par 'gyur ro
NK126(cho)001:3824: // des sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' gcig
NK126(cho)001:3825: gi thun mong dang mang po'i tshogs pa la ston
NK126(cho)001:3826: // par 'gyur te / la las ni go /
NK126(cho)001:3830: bka' nyams glegs bam mang po bris te /
NK126(cho)001:3831: snod dang mi ldan pa'i lag 'grim ste /
NK126(cho)001:3832: de nas man ngag nyams te nub bo //
NK126(cho)001:3833: lha srin 'khrugs nas bskal pa phra mo 'jig go //
NK126(cho)001:3834: man ngag 'di dang 'phrad pa'i skyes bu 'ga' 'ag'i
NK126(cho)001:3835: bla ma sangs rgyas nyid du mthong bar byas te
NK126(cho)001:3836: / man ngag gsang ste spyad na mya ngan las 'das so //
NK126(cho)001:3837: des na phyis mun pa'i bskal pa lnga brgya 'byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3838: de nas mngon pa'i bskal pa 'byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:3839: de nas bskal pa bzang ldan ces bya ba la /
NK126(cho)001:3840: gsang ba'i snod ldan gang zag bzhi //
NK126(cho)001:3845: rdo rje rgyal mtshan bya ba dang bzhis grub pa
NK126(cho)001:3846: thob par gyur nas ston pa 'byung ba lags ste
NK126(cho)001:3847: / de la sogs pa dang sbyar nas dus la babs so //
NK126(cho)001:3848: des na khyod la bskur bar bya ste bskur thabs
NK126(cho)001:3849: ma legs na 'u cag gsum ka srog dang bral
NK126(cho)001:3850: bas / yul 'di ru yang gang dga' gar spyad du med /
NK126(cho)001:3851: gal te rgyal pos tshor na 'u cag gsum srog la lta ci smos /
NK126(cho)001:3852: man ngag rang yang rtsa ba nas med par byed pas /
NK126(cho)001:3853: khyed gnyis kyis pan tri ta brgyad la gser gang snang re phul la /
NK126(cho)001:3854: nyin mo bzhin du 'bras kyis chos nyon cig /
NK126(cho)001:3855: nam gyi gung man ngag gi chos bsgyur gyis gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:3856: des pan tri ta brgyad la gser srang re phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:3857: rgyu mtshan nyid dang 'bras bu'i theg pa phyi nang gi chos nyan no //
NK126(cho)001:3858: dus de tsam na pan tri ta phyi ma bdun tshang bar zhal bzhugs pas /
NK126(cho)001:3859: bdun kha la gsang sngags kyi chos nyan pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3860: lag len dang bcas pa lo gnyis bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3861: de nas lo gcig tu phyi nang gsang gsum gyis dbang rdzogs par mnos so //
NK126(cho)001:3862: de nas sh+ri sing ha man ngag gi chos mnyan te /
NK126(cho)001:3863: sh+ri sing has rang gi khang pa'i nang du rdo
NK126(cho)001:3864: chen po gsum gyi kha ru rdza ma zhig bzhag
NK126(cho)001:3865: ste / de'i nang du g+hu ru bzhugs /
NK126(cho)001:3867: rdza ma'i kha slang nga chus bkang ba cig gis bcad /
NK126(cho)001:3868: skya ga'i sgro gcig rkang pa'i 'og tu gtsug /
NK126(cho)001:3869: pho rog gi sgro cig mgo la btsug /
NK126(cho)001:3870: rdza ma la bug pa phug nas de'i nang bug
NK126(cho)001:3871: pa nas phar u 'bi ring pos gyang gi rta
NK126(cho)001:3873: b+aee ro tsa na dang ban de gnyis kyi phyi
NK126(cho)001:3874: rol nas sha ba'i sgyi bzhu ring po re gyon
NK126(cho)001:3875: khres po re khur mkhar ba re thogs nas nam
NK126(cho)001:3876: gung la mnyan / nyin nyi grib mtshams su dar
NK126(cho)001:3877: dkar la ra dkar mo'i 'o mas dpe bris so
NK126(cho)001:3878: gung la mnyan / // shing dur shing gi dud pas bdug /
NK126(cho)001:3879: phyis pan tri ta rnams na re /
NK126(cho)001:3880: dar ni ci yi ge mi 'dug ya mtshan re che /
NK126(cho)001:3882: de nas rgyud lung man ngag len pa la nam gyi gung la rdzu 'phrul bstan te /
NK126(cho)001:3883: shog gu la gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong gi gzugs byas te /
NK126(cho)001:3884: slob dpon sh+ri sing ha bzhugs /
NK126(cho)001:3885: b+aee ro tsa nas seng ge dam brtan gyi sbubs su bzhugs /
NK126(cho)001:3886: gtsang legs grub bya ngang pa'i sbubs su bzhugs /
NK126(cho)001:3887: lag tu slang nga re nya dang pir la sogs pas bkang nas lag par bzung ste /
NK126(cho)001:3888: rdo rje gdan yi 'og nas sh+ri sing ha dang b+aee ro tsa nas man ngag rkus so //
NK126(cho)001:3889: rgya rim pa bdun gyi btab pa bshig ste /
NK126(cho)001:3890: chos bam po lnga brgya lnga bcu rtsa bzhi blangs pas /
NK126(cho)001:3891: gtsang rigs kyi mgon po sum brgya drug bcu dang
NK126(cho)001:3892: sngags phyi nang gi bsrung ma rnams zhal mngon sum
NK126(cho)001:3893: du byon nas / sh+ri sing ha dang /
NK126(cho)001:3894: b+aee ro tsa na la g.yas phyogs nas g.yon su
NK126(cho)001:3895: bskor te phyag 'tshal nas bdag cag mi ma yin
NK126(cho)001:3896: chos skyong ba'i bsrungs ma rnams ni bka' 'di rnams
NK126(cho)001:3898: shin tu yang man ngag 'di rnams rjes su mchis so //
NK126(cho)001:3907: dad pa gding nas med pa /
NK126(cho)001:3908: zhen pa gting mi bzlog pa /
NK126(cho)001:3909: 'dzin chags gting nas mi grol ba /
NK126(cho)001:3910: des cha dang 'bul ba gnyis pham rgyal blta ba'i lag 'grim tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:3911: dam nyams lag tu song ba yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:3912: de tsam na bdag cag mi ma yin pa rnams ma dga'/
NK126(cho)001:3915: bdag cag mi ma yin pa rnams la la pha bsad pa snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:3916: la la ni ma bsad pa snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:3917: la la ni bu gcig stor ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:3918: la la ni dpral ba'i mig phyung ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:3919: la la ni khang gi snying phyung ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:3920: la la ni nor bu rin po che stor ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:3929: mi bde ba sna tshogs 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3930: na rag chen po dmyal ba la yang yongs su 'phel ba 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3931: slob dpon la'ang tshe thung la nad mang ba 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3932: slob ma rnams la'ang 'phongs pa sdug pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:3933: gri ru 'chi ba la sogs pa 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3934: chos la yang mthu chung ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:3938: srin po bdud du ldang dus 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3939: de nas la las ni man ngag 'di bsro /
NK126(cho)001:3943: de la bstan pa 'di 'chang ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:3945: 'di thugs la 'chang ba ni sangs rgyas ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK126(cho)001:3946: de la la las bskur pa 'debs /
NK126(cho)001:3949: de ltar byas pas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'jig par 'gyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:3950: de'i phyir shin tu gsang bar sbos shig /
NK126(cho)001:3952: gsang bar yid la gyis shig zer nas gtsang ris kyi mgon po sum brgya drug cu dang /
NK126(cho)001:3953: sngags phyi nang gi bsrungs ma rnams nam mkha' la gshegs nas song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:3957: res nam mkha'i dkyil nas bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3958: res rgya mtsho'i dbus su bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3959: de yang bod du man ngag 'byung ba'i rtags su rig pa'i khu byug bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3960: kun rdzogs pa'i rtags su rtsal chen bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3961: bsam gtan ston rtags su thig le drug pa bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3962: theg pa thams cad kyi lta spyod khang 'og tu 'dus pa'i rtags su khyung chen bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3963: theg pa thams cad las khyad du 'don pa'i rtags su mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3964: de nas g+hu ru'i rigs kyi bu magu'am byas pas rjes su yi rang /
NK126(cho)001:3965: de re yang re ste gda' yang gda'/
NK126(cho)001:3966: shin tu yang mos pa lags so //
NK126(cho)001:3968: yang thams cad 'dus pa'i rtags su yid bzhin nor bu bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3969: chos dang gang zag la che ba'i rtags su rje btsan dam pa bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3970: gong 'og gi skyon dang yon tan shes dgos pa'i rtags su /
NK126(cho)001:3972: shes rab gsum la brten dgos pa'i rtags su kun 'dus rin po che bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3974: shes pa thams cad gdams pa la rag las dgos pa'i rtags su bde 'byams bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3975: 'bras bu ka ba tsi la thug pa'i rtags su srog gi 'khor lo bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3976: dpe don rtags gsum la rag dgos pa'i rtags su tig dang nam mkha'i rgyal po bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3978: drangs don dang nges don gnyis kyis gzhan gyi don
NK126(cho)001:3979: byed dgos pa'i rtags su bde ba phra bkod bshad
NK126(cho)001:3980: / theg pa thams cad shan 'byed pa'i rtags su spyi bcings bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3981: rig pa dang mi 'gal par bya ba'i phyir rdo la gser zhun bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3982: spyod pa dang dam tshig rnal 'byor pa'i srog yin pa'i phyir rtse mo byung rgyal bshad /
NK126(cho)001:3983: de ni che ba'i phyogs bzhi'o //
NK126(cho)001:3984: chos 'chal ba dang mi 'chal ngo shes dgos pa'i phyir rmad du byung bar bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:3985: rmad byung yan chad thos pa tsam gyi bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi zhal mthong /
NK126(cho)001:3986: gsung thos dngos grub brnyes te ming yang b+aee ro tsa nar brtags so //
NK126(cho)001:3988: gtsang legs grub ni tshim zer nas lam du zhugs
NK126(cho)001:3989: nas song ba de gcan 'phrang dang po pas sku
NK126(cho)001:3990: tshe lo bzhi bcu zhe bzhi la bkum mo //
NK126(cho)001:3991: b+aee ro tsa nas ma tshim lags /
NK126(cho)001:3992: zer nas zhag gsum du kha sbub tu nyal te 'dug go //
NK126(cho)001:3994: khyod rog po song ba la ma dga' 'am byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:3995: b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:3996: mgron po gnas mthun rang rang gnas su gyes pa la /
NK126(cho)001:3997: de la mi dga' ci mchis smras pas /
NK126(cho)001:4000: b+aee ros na lags byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4001: khyod ci na gsungs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:4002: b+aee ro tsa nas nad glu ru blangs /
NK126(cho)001:4003: rje ma h+aa g+hu ru chen po lags //
NK126(cho)001:4004: bdag 'dra bod kyi b+aee ro tsa na la //
NK126(cho)001:4005: gzhan gyi nad lta ma mchis te //
NK126(cho)001:4006: mthong ste ma 'phrad bdag ni rang sems na //
NK126(cho)001:4007: thos te ma go rang sems na //
NK126(cho)001:4008: myong ste ma tshim rang sems na //
NK126(cho)001:4009: nad gzhi sems sde bco brgyad po //
NK126(cho)001:4010: gting ma rnyed pa 'dod pa rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:4011: mthar phyin gyi sman cig da bzod bzhu //
NK126(cho)001:4013: g+hu ru na re ngas ni /
NK126(cho)001:4014: kun bstan na khyod ci la sdug /
NK126(cho)001:4016: yang b+aee ro tsa nas lan du mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4017: lta ba phyogs ris med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:4018: las dang rtogs pa'i 'phrang la rdug /
NK126(cho)001:4019: spyod pa blangs dor med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:4021: lam la bsgrod du med pa de //
NK126(cho)001:4022: lung dang rig pa'i 'phrang la rdug /
NK126(cho)001:4023: rang byung ye shes chen po de //
NK126(cho)001:4025: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa de //
NK126(cho)001:4026: bying rgod gnyis kyi 'phrang la rdug /'bras bu sku gsum lhun grub de //
NK126(cho)001:4027: brda don sprad pa'i 'phrang la rdug /
NK126(cho)001:4028: rdzogs chen bya bral lhun grub de //
NK126(cho)001:4030: sangs rgyas spyod yul rang dbang la //
NK126(cho)001:4031: spyi blug tshangs pa'i dbang la rdug /
NK126(cho)001:4032: cha lags man ngag sems sde bco brgyad pos //
NK126(cho)001:4033: 'phrang brgyad skyel ma ma khogs so //
NK126(cho)001:4034: nga bdag b+aee ro tsa na yang //
NK126(cho)001:4035: yul du 'gro ba'i 'phrang la rdug /'phrang bsrungs gcan gzan rnams la rdug /
NK126(cho)001:4037: slob dpon sh+ri sing has bzhad de dgyes so //
NK126(cho)001:4039: man ngag bcel ba'i skabs te bcu gsum pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:4040: bar de rgya gar rmi lam bar pa logs ste /
NK126(cho)001:4041: mkhas pa pan+di ta la la na re /
NK126(cho)001:4042: chu thams cad bod du song zhing rmis zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:4043: mkhas pa la la na re /
NK126(cho)001:4044: rtsi shing me tog thams cad bod du khyer zhing rmis zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:4045: mkhas pa la la na re /
NK126(cho)001:4046: mkhas pa bod du spyan drangs kyi rmis zer /
NK126(cho)001:4047: mkhas pa la la na re /
NK126(cho)001:4048: snying phyungs shing bod du khyer zhing rmis zer /
NK126(cho)001:4049: mkhas pa la la na re /
NK126(cho)001:4050: nyi zla byang du rgas shing rmis zer /
NK126(cho)001:4051: dus der rgyud sde drug cu tham pa gnang /
NK126(cho)001:4052: dbang dang gdams ngag thams cad rdzogs par bstan /
NK126(cho)001:4053: khyad par man ngag rgya mtsho klong bstan nas dgyes so //
NK126(cho)001:4054: 'bad rtsol dang rtsol bsgrub kyis 'bras bu brtsal mi dgos te /
NK126(cho)001:4055: yin pa'i don la rtogs pa'i blos /
NK126(cho)001:4056: mnyam snyoms rang kha mar bzhag pas //
NK126(cho)001:4057: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i man ngag /
NK126(cho)001:4058: rgya mtsho klong bshad nas tshig lags so //
NK126(cho)001:4061: slob dpon sh+ri sing ha la bod du byon khar gser gyi pa tra gsum yon du phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:4062: sku gsum ston pa mchog gi sras //
NK126(cho)001:4063: thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag gi pha //
NK126(cho)001:4064: blo yi re dogs bcad pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4065: dbu bsnyungs bzhes pa'i chos shig zhu //
NK126(cho)001:4068: chos kyi dbyings la zad med kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4069: de bzhin nyid ni gcig shes na //
NK126(cho)001:4070: ma lus de la yongs su rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:4071: de las yod na sid+d+hi kan //
NK126(cho)001:4072: gsungs nas cang mi gsungs bar 'dug go //
NK126(cho)001:4073: de nas slob dpon la bstod pa phul bas /
NK126(cho)001:4074: ma skyes rdo rje bde ba'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:4075: grag stong 'gag med tshangs pa'i gsung //
NK126(cho)001:4076: gnyis med ye shes nam mkha' thugs //
NK126(cho)001:4077: sh+ri sing ha'i sku gsung thugs la bstod //
NK126(cho)001:4079: de la yid lhangs kyis ches /
NK126(cho)001:4081: 'khor 'das kyi chos snang srid zil gyis non /
NK126(cho)001:4083: der rje sh+ri sing ha'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4084: 'on kyang rgyal po mi bslu bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:4085: bod du bstan pa sgrogs shig gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:4086: yang rje sh+ri sing ha'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4087: slob dpon gyi brtsa bskur lugs la gsum yod de /
NK126(cho)001:4089: 'khor 'das thams cad gsal zhing mthong byed pa //
NK126(cho)001:4090: mig gi 'bras bu bzhin du brtsa bskur bar bya //
NK126(cho)001:4091: theg pa'i snying po kun gyi bcud yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:4092: snying gi khrag bzhin brtsa bskur bar bya //
NK126(cho)001:4093: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4094: srog rtsa chen po bzhin du brtsa bskur bar bya //
NK126(cho)001:4096: yang sbyin lugs rnam pa bzhi yod de /
NK126(cho)001:4097: yul du snying bzhin byed pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:4098: slob ma dad ldan 'jam ring la //
NK126(cho)001:4099: des 'grol ti ka sa gcod rnams //
NK126(cho)001:4100: grangs btab ti ka sdeb ste sbyin par bya //
NK126(cho)001:4101: dad ldan slob ma rgyud bzang zhing //
NK126(cho)001:4102: drung du yun ring sdod pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4103: sba gsang med par sbyin par bya //
NK126(cho)001:4104: rgyud bzang snod ldan yun ring la //
NK126(cho)001:4105: dad pa chung yang nan gyis sbyin //
NK126(cho)001:4106: pha la bskul zhing sbyin par bya //
NK126(cho)001:4107: dad pa gdung ste drung du 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:4108: shes rab rmongs pas ma go na //
NK126(cho)001:4109: yig snar byas nas sbyin par bya //
NK126(cho)001:4110: yang mi sbyin pa la bzhi yod de /
NK126(cho)001:4111: khong khro mtshur ngan dad med la //
NK126(cho)001:4112: tshig 'gal brid la bskrad la btang //
NK126(cho)001:4113: dad dang brtson 'grus shes rab chung //
NK126(cho)001:4114: don la mi slob bshad ring des 'grol 'dod pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4115: tshig 'gas brid la bskrad la btang //
NK126(cho)001:4117: bri lang med par gdams ngag 'dod //
NK126(cho)001:4118: 'jam pos brid la bskrad la btang //
NK126(cho)001:4119: dpe dang tshangs pa chos barje byed //
NK126(cho)001:4121: brtags nas ngal la 'dod pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4122: rgyal khams 'phya yang mkhon par bya //
NK126(cho)001:4123: yang spyod pa la yang bzhi yod de //
NK126(cho)001:4124: yang phur sman dang tshe bsgrub rnams //
NK126(cho)001:4125: dge slong dam nyams bud med yangs //
NK126(cho)001:4126: gzhung bzhin dang bsring drod rtags dbyung //
NK126(cho)001:4127: ngan sngags la sogs gsang sngags rnams //
NK126(cho)001:4128: gsang la dgos par mtshan rtags dbyung //
NK126(cho)001:4129: spyod mthong lugs kyi bdag nyid nyams //
NK126(cho)001:4130: gsang sngags thun mong ma yin 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4131: las ngan phag tu sba ma spyad //
NK126(cho)001:4132: bka' dang slob dpon man ngag kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4133: so sor rang re'i gzhung btsan pas //
NK126(cho)001:4134: bslad krug shes bcug ma byed par //
NK126(cho)001:4135: nyan bshad spyod pa de ltar spyod //
NK126(cho)001:4136: ces b+aee ro tsa na la nan tan byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4137: b+aee ros kyang g+hu rus gsungs pa bzhin bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:4140: sh+ri sing has b+aee ro tsa na la man ngag gtad pa'i skabs te bcu bzhi pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:4141: de nas b+aee ro tsa na rgya gar nas byon khar /
NK126(cho)001:4143: da khyod bod du 'gro ran no bya ba'i mgur bzhengs nas bskul ba /
NK126(cho)001:4144: gdug cig lon no khri gdugs nyi ma khyod //
NK126(cho)001:4145: gling khams gzhan du sgron me mdzad re ran //
NK126(cho)001:4146: dgung cig lon no bac+wo lnga'i nya chen khyod //
NK126(cho)001:4147: gling khams gzhan du snang ba 'char re ran //
NK126(cho)001:4148: dpag chen med pa'i gzhu 'dam khengs pa khyod //
NK126(cho)001:4149: dmigs pa'i 'ben la da ni 'degs re ran //
NK126(cho)001:4150: rgyud lung man ngag 'dzom pa'i b+aee ro tsa na khyod //
NK126(cho)001:4151: mnga' ris bod du bstan pa bsgrags re ran //
NK126(cho)001:4153: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas slob dpon sh+ri sing ha la mchid 'tshal ba /
NK126(cho)001:4154: dgung la shar ba'i khri gdugs rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:4155: gos med dbyar nas 'khyags kyi khri gdugs thugs rje mi chung 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4156: lhum ra'i nang nas skyes kyi nas 'bras 'ong mo che //
NK126(cho)001:4157: brgyag med ston nas ltogs kyi nas 'bras bu thugs rje mi chung 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4158: 'tsho byed sman gyi sgro ba rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:4159: 'du ba rnams bzhi'i gdungs gyi sman sgro thugs rje mi chung 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4160: 'bras chang ding mas gang ba'i rgya rdza rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:4161: tshad pas gdung bas kyang ni skam lags kyi //
NK126(cho)001:4162: rgya rdzas 'bras chang thugs rje mi chung 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4163: btsan po kha drags bskyes ma rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:4164: kha zhan khyim nas 'jigs kyi bskyel ma thugs rje mi chung 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4165: rgya gar sh+ri sing ha rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:4166: dad ldan 'khor bar 'khyam na snying re rje //
NK126(cho)001:4167: g+hu ru thugs rje mi chung 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4169: sh+ri sing has man ngag gi bcud phyungs pa b+aee
NK126(cho)001:4170: ro tsa na la man ngag mdzub tshugs su lhun
NK126(cho)001:4171: grub kyi sangs rgyas par byas so //
NK126(cho)001:4172: gsang ba dam pa'i mchog tu gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:4173: yang de'i dus su 'da' kha ma'i zhal chems rlung gi kyang thos su mi rung bar gdams pa /
NK126(cho)001:4174: sh+ri sing ha'i thugs kyi klong rdol nas /
NK126(cho)001:4175: b+aee ro tsa na'i sems la snying khung gdams pa /
NK126(cho)001:4176: las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pa cig dang 'phrad par shog /
NK126(cho)001:4177: rang sems ye shes rdo rje 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4178: yod med dbu ma tsam yang mi dmigs shing //
NK126(cho)001:4179: rtag chad mtha' la mi gnas te //
NK126(cho)001:4180: sgro skur med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:4181: blangs dor med pa'i blo bzhag ste //
NK126(cho)001:4183: de ni dgongs pa'i mthar thug go //
NK126(cho)001:4184: sems ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK126(cho)001:4185: sems zhes bya ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:4186: sems kyis sems la lta ba ni //
NK126(cho)001:4187: sems kyi skyon dang gol sa brtags //
NK126(cho)001:4188: de nas nyams dang drod tshad skye //
NK126(cho)001:4190: sems kyi kha dog cir mi dmigs //
NK126(cho)001:4191: dbyibs kyi rnam pa gang yang med //
NK126(cho)001:4192: sems ni rgyu las ma bskyed de //
NK126(cho)001:4193: rkyen gyis nyams pa 'jig pa med //
NK126(cho)001:4194: thog ma ma byung mthar mi stong //
NK126(cho)001:4195: dus gsum kun tu stang zhing dben //
NK126(cho)001:4197: dgag dang bzung dang gtang snyams dang //
NK126(cho)001:4198: skyes dang drug gi spyod yul min //
NK126(cho)001:4199: bying rmug gnyis po 'di la med //
NK126(cho)001:4200: ci bzhin pa yi ngang la bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:4201: yig 'bru phyag mtshan cir mi dmigs //
NK126(cho)001:4202: sgra dang tshig las 'das pa'i sgom //
NK126(cho)001:4203: sems kyi tshor ram spyod pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:4205: de dag kun la re dogs med //
NK126(cho)001:4206: ci yang ngo bor mi rtog go //
NK126(cho)001:4207: stong pa'i ngang las ma g.yos na //
NK126(cho)001:4208: dbug kyi rgyu ba mi tshor zhing //
NK126(cho)001:4209: phung po yod par mi mngon te //
NK126(cho)001:4210: nam mkha' stong pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK126(cho)001:4211: rig pa ye shes shar ba'i drangs //
NK126(cho)001:4214: de ltar cig tu go ba rdzogs pa'i lam //
NK126(cho)001:4215: thams cad stong pa'i rig pa'i rtsal //
NK126(cho)001:4216: mun pa sel ba nyi ma'i 'od //
NK126(cho)001:4217: mkhas pa sh+ri sing ha'i bka' //
NK126(cho)001:4218: b+aee ro tsa nas dka' ba spyad //
NK126(cho)001:4219: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i thugs la thims //
NK126(cho)001:4220: ces gsungs nas mgur du bzhengs so //
NK126(cho)001:4221: yang b+aee ro tsa nas mgur las drangs te slob dpon sh+ri sing ha la mchis 'tshal ba /
NK126(cho)001:4222: ma zho bus 'thung 'bral dang mi phod ste //
NK126(cho)001:4223: yar zho snyams pas yar bu kho thag chod //
NK126(cho)001:4224: bung ba me tog 'bral dang mi phod ste //
NK126(cho)001:4225: me tog rid do bung ba kho thag chod //
NK126(cho)001:4226: 'bras kyi tshang tshag 'bral dang mi phod ste //
NK126(cho)001:4227: tham bu gcur thag chod do chang ma kho thag chod //
NK126(cho)001:4228: slob dpon gdams ngag can dang 'bral ba mi phod ste //
NK126(cho)001:4229: rgyud lung man ngag rdzogs so kho thag chod //
NK126(cho)001:4231: der slob dpon sh+ri sing has /
NK126(cho)001:4232: b+aee ro tsa na snying rje bar dgongs nas /
NK126(cho)001:4233: slob ma 'chi'i dogs nas mgur gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4234: dper na rgyal po'i dkor mdzod dag tu sbas pa'i nor //
NK126(cho)001:4235: rkun ma dag gis khyer gyur na //
NK126(cho)001:4236: rjes bcad rnyed nas rin chen srog dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:4237: de bzhin rdo rje gdan du sbas pa'i man ngag a ti 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4238: phyag rgya ru sprod dag gis mnan yang ma btsan par //
NK126(cho)001:4239: nga yis blangs so b+aee ro tsa na khyod la bskur //
NK126(cho)001:4240: gal te rnyed na rin chen srog dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:4241: khyod kyi grogs kyang lam du gcan 'phrang dang pos bkum //
NK126(cho)001:4242: khyod kyang gsod du 'ong bas rkang mgyogs sgrubs la song //
NK126(cho)001:4244: gser phye slar b+aee ro tsa na la gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:4245: de nas yang slob dpon sh+ri sing ha la b+aee ros mgur du mchis 'tshal ba /
NK126(cho)001:4246: e ma hoh ngo mtshar che ba'i ya mtshan can //
NK126(cho)001:4247: zhal nas ci gsungs bdud rtsir 'dzag /'khor ba'i nad kyis gdung ba la //
NK126(cho)001:4248: thugs rje'i sman gyis phan re thog /
NK126(cho)001:4249: byang chub lag tu gtad pa'i rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:4250: skye ba phyi ma la yang mi 'bral 'grogs par smon //
NK126(cho)001:4251: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:4252: slob dpon sh+ri sing ha la phyi phyag byas smon lam btab /
NK126(cho)001:4253: de nas slob dpon sh+ri seng ha'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4254: khyod kyi grogs po legs grub kyang bod du song
NK126(cho)001:4255: ba la ma sleb par lam dkar gcan 'phrang dang
NK126(cho)001:4257: khyod kyang gcan 'phrang bas bsad du 'ong bas /
NK126(cho)001:4258: rkang mgyogs kyi dpon po ku ma ra bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:4259: ku ha ri bya ba gnyis yod kyi de gnyis
NK126(cho)001:4260: gang rung zhig la rog po gyis rkang mgyogs sgrubs
NK126(cho)001:4261: la song / de min na khyod bsad du 'ong
NK126(cho)001:4262: ngo gsungs nas b+aee ro tsa na la gser phye
NK126(cho)001:4263: la song / slar gnang ngo // de nas b+aee
NK126(cho)001:4264: ro tsa nas ku sha lcags kyi sdong po can
NK126(cho)001:4265: bya bar re ma ti lcags kyi dre'u rta rkang
NK126(cho)001:4266: gsum ma'i rkang mgyogs bsgrubs tu phyin pas /
NK126(cho)001:4267: ku sha lcags kyi sdong po can gyi yul mi kun na re /
NK126(cho)001:4270: b+aee ro tsa na la zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:4271: yang b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4272: bdag ni b+aee ro tsa na te //
NK126(cho)001:4273: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pa'i chos dbyings la //
NK126(cho)001:4274: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i klong chen pha //
NK126(cho)001:4275: ya mtshan rmad byung bdag ni lus 'di skyes //
NK126(cho)001:4276: mkha' klong rnam dag chos kyi dbyings nas 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:4277: 'jig rten 'di yi dgos pa'i gdam bgyis nas //
NK126(cho)001:4278: rig pa'i khang nas thugs rje'i nyi shar bas //
NK126(cho)001:4279: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa bdag nyid rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:4280: kun gzhi rnam dag bde chen lhun rdzogs a //
NK126(cho)001:4281: mkha' ltar dag pa'i byang chub sems ldan 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4282: skye med mi gnas yi ge a cig la //
NK126(cho)001:4283: dgongs pa'i don du bya ba de las med //
NK126(cho)001:4284: yi ge a ni dgongs pa'i byung khungs te //
NK126(cho)001:4285: de las byung ba'i don ni 'di ltar yin //
NK126(cho)001:4286: nor ni ma mchis mkhas pa'i man ngag 'chang //
NK126(cho)001:4287: slob dpon ma mchis dga' rab rdo rje lags //
NK126(cho)001:4288: 'khor ni ma mchis lha srin sde brgyad 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:4289: chung ma ma mchis kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' //
NK126(cho)001:4290: grogs ni ma mchis ma mo mkha' 'gro'i grogs //
NK126(cho)001:4291: bza' rgyu ma mchis sems nyid yid kyi bza' //
NK126(cho)001:4292: rta ni ma mchis tshogs drug yid kyi rta //
NK126(cho)001:4293: bu ni ma mchis rang rig sems kyi bu //
NK126(cho)001:4294: lha ni ma mchis rang rig sems kyis lha //
NK126(cho)001:4295: mthu ni ma mchis dug gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK126(cho)001:4296: brten pa ma mchis do nub brtag pa gcig zhu //
NK126(cho)001:4298: de nas yul mi thams cad dga' nas zhabs tog cher byas so //
NK126(cho)001:4299: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas /
NK126(cho)001:4300: rkang mgyogs kyi dpon po ku ha ra da du ma rnyed par /
NK126(cho)001:4301: rkang mgyogs kyi dpon po ku m+aa ra dang mjal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4302: gser gyi pa tra cig ku m+aa ra la phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:4306: phas bu la yang mi ster /
NK126(cho)001:4307: 'di nas bod du sleb tsam cig gter gyi gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:4308: ku m+aa ras b+aee ro tsa na la rkang mgyogs gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:4309: de yang rgya gar yul nas /
NK126(cho)001:4310: glag khra mo gzen la 'jug pa tsam yod ste /
NK126(cho)001:4311: b+aee ros kyang lo gcig rkang mgyogs bsgrub pas /
NK126(cho)001:4312: go bo ri rtsibs gcod pa tsam zhig 'grub bo //
NK126(cho)001:4313: de nas 'thon nas da gyi tsan+dana gyi gling zhes bya bar phyin nas /
NK126(cho)001:4314: der da kyi'i rgyal po ra hu la byi byi bya ba'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4315: bod kyi ban+desa skye ba med pa bya ba'i chos ci lta bu cig mchis /
NK126(cho)001:4316: bka' rtsol dang zhes zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:4317: rgyal pos ras kyi par kha ta cig b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la gsol nas /
NK126(cho)001:4318: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4319: bdag ni rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK126(cho)001:4320: 'gro ba rnam pa sna tshogs la //
NK126(cho)001:4321: snang khyab nyi ma bya dgongs nas //
NK126(cho)001:4322: dka' ba bcu drug dka' las bgyis //
NK126(cho)001:4323: sgyu ma'i phung po'i lus bshig ste //
NK126(cho)001:4324: ston pa'i thugs rje bdag la shar //
NK126(cho)001:4325: kun la snang bar mdzad pas na //
NK126(cho)001:4326: ming yang rnam par snang mdzad yin //
NK126(cho)001:4327: ming dang don du bdag mthun te //
NK126(cho)001:4328: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i gting rdzogs te //
NK126(cho)001:4329: sangs rgyas ngo bor ma gyur cig kyang med //
NK126(cho)001:4330: ston pa'i zhal skyin bdag gi bshad pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4331: rgyal pos sems la go bar bya yi bag tsam nyon //
NK126(cho)001:4332: dmigs su med pa byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:4333: gzung dang 'dzin pa gnyis las grol //
NK126(cho)001:4334: tha snyad tshig gi sgra spang nas //
NK126(cho)001:4335: de nyid gsal ba ma yengs na //
NK126(cho)001:4336: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid yin //
NK126(cho)001:4338: yang dgongs pa'i don du 'di bzhag go //
NK126(cho)001:4339: 'di nyid ma nor bsgom pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:4340: skye ba phyi mas lan pa des //
NK126(cho)001:4342: der da kyi'i rgyal pos nub mo bka' mchis smras pa /
NK126(cho)001:4343: sems can rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la ma chags te /
NK126(cho)001:4344: de nyid gnas su dag pas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku longs spyod dang 'dra'am mi 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:4346: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4347: 'dod pa'i yon tan ma spangs longs spyod rdzogs pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:4348: 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam lnga bde gshegs snying po'i dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:4349: spangs dang ma spong gnyis med don rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:4350: ci ltar spyod pa longs spyod dam pa'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:4352: yang rgyal po ra hu byi byis b+aee ro tsa na la zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:4353: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa chos kyi dbyings yin ces bgyi ba'i don ci lta bu lags /
NK126(cho)001:4355: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4356: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa rang gi blo yin te //
NK126(cho)001:4357: ma bcos blo las chos dbyings gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:4358: de phyir dbyings dang kun gzhi tha dad med pa'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:4359: gzhi rtsa bcad pas gnyis su med par 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:4360: gnyis med ma bcos a ti yo ga'i lung //
NK126(cho)001:4362: yang rgyal pos ma rig ye shes tha dad med //
NK126(cho)001:4363: ces bgyi ba'i don ci lta bu lags //
NK126(cho)001:4365: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4366: rig pa'i dus na ye shes dbyings su shar //
NK126(cho)001:4367: ma rig dus na ye shes 'khor bar snang //
NK126(cho)001:4368: rig dang ma rig khyad par che yis kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4369: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4371: ma rig dus na kun gzhi yin //
NK126(cho)001:4372: chos nyid dbyings las 'gyur ba med //
NK126(cho)001:4373: rig par gyur na bde chen chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:4376: gsang ba'i yang gsang rnal 'byor mchog 'di lta bas la bcad na ci ltar bcad //
NK126(cho)001:4378: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4379: theg mchog gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:4380: skye med rdo rje mngon du snang yang kun gyis mi rtogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:4381: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i don mtha' zhig /
NK126(cho)001:4382: su yis theg pa mtha' dag brtsal yang rnyed pa zur tsam med //
NK126(cho)001:4383: de phyir gsang sngags theg mchog 'di ni dam par gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:4389: a ti yo ga bzhi la don dam par khyad yod dam med zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:4390: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4391: rang byung mi dmigs chos dbyings kun gyi klong //
NK126(cho)001:4392: yo ga rnam bzhi lta spyod ma grub na //
NK126(cho)001:4393: mnyam nyid gsal ba'i gting mtha' mi rtogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:4394: lta spyod ya char gyur nas de nyid mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:4395: a ti theg chen byang chub snying po 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4396: lhun gyis rdzogs pas lta spyod gnyis dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:4397: gnyis su med pas ye nas mnyam par gnas //
NK126(cho)001:4398: bkag kyang ma bkag bde chen lhun rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:4399: lta dang spyod ces bya ba'i tha snyad med //
NK126(cho)001:4400: dbyings dang ye shes bya ba'i tshig las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:4403: ston can gnyis kyi lta ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:4404: a ti yo ga'i lta ba gang mtho zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:4405: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4406: lta phug thams cad chos kyi ro gcig kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4407: 'jug pa'i sgo nas mi mnyam ste //
NK126(cho)001:4408: ston tsam la sogs ston pa rnam gsum po //
NK126(cho)001:4409: 'gro ba thabs kyi 'dren pa'i stan gnas su //
NK126(cho)001:4410: da lta nyid du 'bras bu thob skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:4411: mthar thug ston par gsungs pa rgyu yi chos //
NK126(cho)001:4412: 'khor ba'i chos rnams thabs kyis spyod byed cing //
NK126(cho)001:4413: stong pa'i sgra yi sgribs pa gnyis spangs nas //
NK126(cho)001:4414: bskal par brgyud kyang byang chub don 'dod de //
NK126(cho)001:4415: theg pa chen por yid smon khas mches kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4416: rdzogs pa chen po'i gting mtha' ga la spog /
NK126(cho)001:4417: a ti rdzogs chen theg pa'i gtso //
NK126(cho)001:4418: rnam thar kun gyi mthar thug pa //
NK126(cho)001:4419: rang bzhin lhun rdzogs yid bzhin nor bu'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:4420: nam mkha' bzhin du yongs kyi gzhir gyur kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4421: mnyam la ma 'dres khyad par bsam 'das te //
NK126(cho)001:4422: ston tsan stong par khungs 'byin de nyid dang //
NK126(cho)001:4423: lta spyod la sogs khyad par kun spangs te //
NK126(cho)001:4424: lta ba'i stong zhes bya ba'i tshig las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:4425: spyod pa kun tu bzang po kun la gdal //
NK126(cho)001:4426: lta spyod gnyis kyang ma bcos lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:4429: ma h+aa yo ga bas lha rnal 'byor /
NK126(cho)001:4430: lta ba nyams su blangs na bsgom pa /
NK126(cho)001:4432: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4433: skye med dbyings las cho 'phrul sna tshogs 'byung //
NK126(cho)001:4434: snang srid lha yi sku ru gsal ba las //
NK126(cho)001:4435: lus kyi bskul bskyod phyag rgya'i skur snang zhing //
NK126(cho)001:4436: ngag gis ci smras chos sku'i gsung //
NK126(cho)001:4437: lag tu ci bzung dam tshig rgya //
NK126(cho)001:4438: snod bcud 'khor 'das snang srid thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:4439: phyag rgya chen po'i lha skur rtogs tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:4440: thams cad ma bcos rang bzhin dbyings su gsal //
NK126(cho)001:4441: de ni dgongs pa mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:4444: rje lags theg pa mtha' dag ni /
NK126(cho)001:4445: a ti yo gar rdzogs skad /
NK126(cho)001:4446: a ti yo ga ni ye nas tshig las 'das te sangs rgyas na /
NK126(cho)001:4447: ye nas khams gsum sangs rgyas par bsgom na ci ltar bsgom //
NK126(cho)001:4449: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4450: kun gzhi ma bcos ye nas lhun gyis grub //
NK126(cho)001:4451: 'gyur med kun gzhi brdal ba ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:4452: 'gro ba'i kun gzhi ye nas mi bden te //
NK126(cho)001:4453: ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs pas ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:4454: kun gzhi ma bcos chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:4455: ma bcos de nyid ci bzhin pa'i //
NK126(cho)001:4456: khams gsum ye sangs rgyas pas bsgom pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:4458: rgyal po ra hu la byi byi thugs mnyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:4459: rgyal po'i dregs pa chag nas brkyang phyag lan stong du mdzad do //
NK126(cho)001:4460: de bzhin du phyi rabs kyi gang zag kyang /
NK126(cho)001:4461: dregs pa mi chag na snod dang mi ldan pa yin pas rab tu yang gsang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:4463: b+aee ro tsa nas a ti don bstan pas /
NK126(cho)001:4464: rgyal po ra hu la byi byi dregs pa chag pa'i skabs te bco lnga pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:4465: yang rgyal pos b+aee ro tsa na la zhu ba phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:4466: dgung zhag gcig zhabs nas btegs so //
NK126(cho)001:4467: b+aee ro tsa nas rgyal po la 'di skad gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:4468: byang chub sems dpa' de nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:4469: gsang ba yid kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:4470: srid pa gsum nas ye nas dag pa'i zhing //
NK126(cho)001:4471: snyigs ma lnga nyid ye nas dben pa'i gnas //
NK126(cho)001:4472: snang srid 'khor 'das rang gi sems kyis sras //
NK126(cho)001:4473: snod bcud thams cad ye nas ngo bo dag /
NK126(cho)001:4474: srid gsum ye nas rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:4475: rgyal ba gzhan na med do byang chub sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:4476: srid gsum rnam dag dgongs pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4477: srid pa gsum na byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:4478: ngo bo'i rol pa sprin phung ste //
NK126(cho)001:4481: rje ma h+aa g+hu ru lags //
NK126(cho)001:4482: srid gsum dgongs pa ci ltar lags //
NK126(cho)001:4484: b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4485: nam mkha' klong yangs srid gsum gdal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:4486: snang srid klong yangs mi srid dgu srid la //
NK126(cho)001:4487: skye med klong yangs ye nas rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:4488: sna tshogs mtshan ma'i klong yangs ye nas rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:4489: sems nyid srid pa gsum du snang ba yang //
NK126(cho)001:4490: byang sems ngo bo nyid du rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:4491: de phyir phyogs bral bde ba chen po'i klong //
NK126(cho)001:4492: ye nas rnam dag sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:4494: de nas rgyal po ra hu la byi byi shin tu dgyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:4495: 'phags pa byams pa'i sku gser las byas pa cig
NK126(cho)001:4496: b+aee ro tsa na la phul nas 'di skad gsungs
NK126(cho)001:4497: / ston pa'i thugs la phyogs ris med kyis kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4498: sgrib gnyis byangs nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:4499: sku gsum mchog tu gyur pa'i rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK126(cho)001:4500: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gzugs skus byar med kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4501: rgyal po bdag gi sgrib pa byang ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4502: chos kyi sku la gzugs kyi sku gcig 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:4503: chos dbyings thugs rjes bdag la dgongs par mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:4504: ces gsungs nas 'phags pa byams pa'i gser sku de b+aee ro tsa na la phul lo //
NK126(cho)001:4505: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas u rgyan gyi d+ha na sam skri ta la ngan sngags zhus /
