NK126(cho)001:4506: kha che'i rgyal khams su nus pa ston /
NK126(cho)001:4507: be ta'i yul du mu stegs btul lo //
NK126(cho)001:4508: der de'i dus b+aee ro tsa na bod yul du chas pa la /
NK126(cho)001:4509: rgya gar gyi chos skyong ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK126(cho)001:4510: pan tri ta mkhas pa bdun la sogs pa kun rmi lam mi bzang ba sna tshogs bzlos shing /
NK126(cho)001:4511: grong khyer ser skya zhes bya bar dpal 'byung ba'i gnas sh+ri na lan+t+ri'i sgo ru tshogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:4512: kun mtshan ma log nas 'di ci yin sgrogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:4514: bod kyi ban+de des 'o cag gi chos ngag gi chos khyer bar yin zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:4515: rdo rje gdan gyi rgya bltas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4516: rgya btab pa de zhig nas 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:4517: der mkhas pa rnams tshogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:4519: dpe na ku la sher bas /
NK126(cho)001:4521: ri gsum gyi rtse la bsdad pa /
NK126(cho)001:4523: lus po mig gis khengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4525: spyi bo na mtsho yod pa /
NK126(cho)001:4526: mtsho'i nang na gangs yod pa /
NK126(cho)001:4527: rkang pa'i mthil nas yar la pho rog cig gi 'thog pa /
NK126(cho)001:4528: mgo nas mar skye ga cig gis 'thog pa /
NK126(cho)001:4529: mchu rings po zangs la byas pa gcig gi rdo
NK126(cho)001:4530: rje gdan du sbas pa'i man ngag blangs nas nang
NK126(cho)001:4531: nas bshad / spyi bo ring po cig /
NK126(cho)001:4532: gcan sing ge gcig bya ngang pa gcig gnyis kyis
NK126(cho)001:4533: khas dung 'bud cing khres po 'phra la ring ba
NK126(cho)001:4534: re khur ba der gnyis kyis phyi nas mnyan te
NK126(cho)001:4535: / rdo rje gdan na sbas pa'i man ngag bod du 'chor bar 'dug zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:4537: 'di lha ma yin gyi sprul pa yin nam /
NK126(cho)001:4538: ci yin ngo ma shes zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:4539: der pra se na'i sras kyang ngo ma zin /
NK126(cho)001:4541: kun brtags pas kyang ma zin nas /
NK126(cho)001:4542: rkang mgyogs btang la bsad par byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4543: rkang mgyogs kyi dpon po ku m+aa ras /
NK126(cho)001:4544: grogs po b+aee ro tsa na'i gan du rgyug ste /
NK126(cho)001:4545: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa bdun gyi rmi lam bzlas pa /
NK126(cho)001:4546: grogs po byang chub sems dpa' snyan gson dang //
NK126(cho)001:4547: ku ku r+aa dzas rmi lam 'di skad bzlas //
NK126(cho)001:4548: theg pa'i rgyal po man ngag bde chen 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4549: rdo rje yang theg man ngag don gyi rtsa //
NK126(cho)001:4550: tshe 'di 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag chos //
NK126(cho)001:4551: gab pa'i man ngag sems la sbas pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4552: dgongs pa'i nyams su bdag nyid 'di ltar rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4553: 'dzam gling kun la gsal ba'i nyi ma 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4554: sa brgyad byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa cig /
NK126(cho)001:4555: sgrib pa byang ba'i gnod sbyin mgo can gyis //
NK126(cho)001:4556: 'o skol rgya gar yul du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:4557: nyi ma snam phrag bcug nas khyer bar rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4558: pan+di ta yi rkang mgyogs la 'ur mthong //
NK126(cho)001:4559: de skad zer nas mchis pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:4560: dngos grub thob nas da ni gshegs pa rigs //
NK126(cho)001:4561: 'jam dpal dpal bzang gis 'di skad rmi lam bzlas pa /
NK126(cho)001:4562: yang dag byang chub bde chen lhun rdzogs 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4563: skal ldan rab kyi don du ston pas gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:4564: bdag cag mkhas pa bdun po phyi ma yang //
NK126(cho)001:4565: nyon mongs lnga nyid gnas su dag bya'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4566: tshe 'di 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag chos //
NK126(cho)001:4567: ma rig mun pa bsal phyir sems la gab //
NK126(cho)001:4568: ye nas lhun rdzogs bde ba chen po'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:4569: spyan ras gzigs dbang sku sprul rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:4570: sa la gnas pa'i bod kyi ban+de gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:4571: gser phye bskur nas 'di ni mchis pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4572: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs rje'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK126(cho)001:4573: yang dag thugs rje'i nyi ma de shar te //
NK126(cho)001:4574: kun la dgos pa'i yid bzhin nor bu de //
NK126(cho)001:4575: snam phrag bcug cing bod du khyer ba rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4576: pan+di ta yi rkang mgyogs la 'ur thong //
NK126(cho)001:4577: de skad zer nas spyan sngar mchis pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:4578: dngos grub thob nas de nas gshegs par rigs //
NK126(cho)001:4579: bdag nyid mas rmi lam 'di skad bzlas //
NK126(cho)001:4580: kun gzhi ma bcos snang srid sangs rgyas la //
NK126(cho)001:4581: chos nyid ma bcos de bzhin rnal ma de //
NK126(cho)001:4582: rang byung lhun grub gsang sngags theg chen chos //
NK126(cho)001:4583: rdo rje gdan du lnga brgya sbas pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4584: rigs gsum sprul pa bod kyi rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:4585: yang dag sprul pa byang chub 'bras bu'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:4586: rgyu 'bras don la mkhas pa'i pan+di ta yin //
NK126(cho)001:4587: dbang po dang pa'i mig gcig yod pa de //
NK126(cho)001:4588: rtsad nas phyungs nas bod du khyer bar rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4589: pan+di ta yis rkang mgyogs la 'ur thong //
NK126(cho)001:4590: de skad zer nas spyan sngar mchis pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:4591: dngos grub thob nas da ni gshegs par rigs //
NK126(cho)001:4592: sh+ri sing has rmi lam 'di skad bzlas //
NK126(cho)001:4593: dbang po rab mchog skal ldan don ched du //
NK126(cho)001:4594: rang bzhin ma bcos theg pa'i rgyal po 'di //
NK126(cho)001:4595: skal ldan phyi ma rnams kyi don ched du //
NK126(cho)001:4596: rdo rje gdan du lnga brgya sbas pa de //
NK126(cho)001:4597: rigs gsum sprul pa khri srong lde'u btsan gyi //
NK126(cho)001:4598: tshe 'di 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag chos //
NK126(cho)001:4599: 'gro ba skal ldan smin cing grol gdod nas //
NK126(cho)001:4600: bod kyi ban+de gnod sbyin mgo can gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:4601: gser phye bskur nas 'dir nas mchis ba las //
NK126(cho)001:4602: rtag par mi bzod sgyu ma'i phung po la //
NK126(cho)001:4603: dngas ma'i mig cig yod pa phyung nas bod du khyer bar rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4604: pan+di ta yi rkang mgyogs la 'ur thong //
NK126(cho)001:4605: de skad zer nas spyan sngar mchis pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:4606: dngos grub thob nas da ni gshegs par rigs //
NK126(cho)001:4607: kun dga' mo'i rmi lam 'di skad rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4608: yang dag chos nyid ma nor bde ba'i lam //
NK126(cho)001:4609: rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag bde chen lam //
NK126(cho)001:4610: byams sems bde ba'i klong du sbas pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4611: skye ba 'di yi snga ma la //
NK126(cho)001:4612: rgya gar yul gyi bram ze dpal ldan bu //
NK126(cho)001:4613: dge slong a ba kha 'du tshe 'phos pas //
NK126(cho)001:4614: bod kyi rgyal po spu rgyal lus blangs te //
NK126(cho)001:4615: bod kyi rgyal khams kha lo des bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:4616: de nyid byang chub sems dpa'i sku'i sprul pa //
NK126(cho)001:4617: yang dag bde chen bod du dar bya'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4618: shes rab lus la rdzogs pa'i ban+de gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:4619: gser phye bskur nas 'dir ni mchis pa las //
NK126(cho)001:4620: rdo rje gdan gyi sku rten byang chub shing bu de //
NK126(cho)001:4621: bod kyis tshubs nag shin tu 'jigs su rung ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:4622: ston pa'i sku rten byang chub shing bu rtsad nas gcod cing rmis //
NK126(cho)001:4623: pan+di ta yis rkang mgyogs la 'ur thong //
NK126(cho)001:4624: de skad zer nas spyan sngar mchis pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:4625: dngos grub thob nas da ni gshegs par rigs //
NK126(cho)001:4626: ces ku m+aa ras b+aee ro tsa na la bzlas te //
NK126(cho)001:4627: phyag nas 'jus nas snying gdung ste bshums so //
NK126(cho)001:4628: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4629: e ma grogs po khyed nyid ni //
NK126(cho)001:4630: mi ru skyes pas skye ba gzhan las 'phags //
NK126(cho)001:4631: smon lam dag pas rgya gar yul du skyes //
NK126(cho)001:4632: dngos grub thob pas rdzul 'phrul rkang mgyogs thob //
NK126(cho)001:4633: bla ma mched legs cho rigs btsun par skyes //
NK126(cho)001:4634: dam tshig bsrungs bas 'di ru bsam dgu 'grub //
NK126(cho)001:4635: sgrib pa byang bas 'phags pa'i bka' grogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:4636: gzhung lugs bzang bas kun gyis brten par gyur //
NK126(cho)001:4637: dgos dgu lus la tshang bas bdag gis grogs su 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4638: lus po pha mas bskyed kyang srog srid grogs pos 'don //
NK126(cho)001:4639: khyod dang grogs po byas pas yang dag byang chub rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:4640: bod kyi rgyal khams ma rig mun pa sel //
NK126(cho)001:4641: 'gro ba smin cing ci ltar grol ba kun //
NK126(cho)001:4642: ku m+aa ra la dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo //
NK126(cho)001:4643: bskal par bgrangs kyang byang chub don dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:4644: rkang mgyogs 'grub pas da ni bdag kyang 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:4645: snying gtam bya yi bal yul mthil tsam skyol //
NK126(cho)001:4646: byas nas ku m+aa ra la gser gyis pa tra gcig byin no //
NK126(cho)001:4647: de nas da kyi'i rgyal po ra hu byi byis
NK126(cho)001:4648: phul ba'i gser gyi byams pa de khyer nas grogs
NK126(cho)001:4649: po ku m+aa ra dang sgrag nas gcan 'phrang dang
NK126(cho)001:4650: por phyin no // de nas 'phrang bsrung gi dpon
NK126(cho)001:4651: po ku ha rang dang grogs po byas nas gser
NK126(cho)001:4652: phye bag tsam gcig byin te /
NK126(cho)001:4653: b+aee ro'i mgo la sha ba'i skyi bzhu ring mo zhig gyon /
NK126(cho)001:4654: rkang pa la zon lham phyin ci log cig gyon /
NK126(cho)001:4655: bla mkhar skya bo'i zhabs la wa lags cig btags /
NK126(cho)001:4656: ka ba rgyab tu bsnol nas byin no //
NK126(cho)001:4657: de nas ku m+aa ras 'phrang bsrung gi dpon po
NK126(cho)001:4658: ku ha ra da du la gser phye zhig byin
NK126(cho)001:4659: nas / de nub ngo rkang mgyogs pa tsho 'di ru 'ong ba la /
NK126(cho)001:4660: de tsa na bod kyi ban+de de mthong ngam bya yi /
NK126(cho)001:4661: khyod kyi bod kyi ban+de de ni ma mthong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:4662: mgo la sha ba'i skyi bzhu ring mo mnab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4663: rkang pa la zon lham phyin log tu gon pa /
NK126(cho)001:4664: bla mkhar skya mo'i zhabs la wa lag btags pa /
NK126(cho)001:4665: ka ba rgyab tu bsnol ba cig gi /
NK126(cho)001:4666: da song na bod yul mthil du sleb cig gsungs
NK126(cho)001:4667: nas 'phrang bsrung gi dpon po ku ha ra da
NK126(cho)001:4668: du la ku m+aa ras mna' ngag bcug go //
NK126(cho)001:4669: de nas ku m+aa ras grong khyer ser skya'i sgor song nas rkang mgyogs zla bo kun sbran te /
NK126(cho)001:4670: b+aee ro tsa na 'di nas mar la song zer bas brdas la bsad do byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4671: rgya gar chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK126(cho)001:4672: mkhas pa kun gyis zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4673: ded la bod kyi ban+de b+aee ro tsa na sod la shog cig gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:4674: de nas rkang mgyogs pa rnams kyis gcan 'phrang dang por phyin nas /
NK126(cho)001:4675: 'phrang bsrung la bod kyi ban+de ma byung ngam byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4677: bod kyi ban+de 'dra ba ni ma byung /
NK126(cho)001:4678: mgo la sha ba'i skyi bzhu ring mo gon pa /
NK126(cho)001:4679: rkang la zon lham phyin ci log tu gon pa /
NK126(cho)001:4680: bla mkhar skya ba'o zhabs la wa lag btags pa /
NK126(cho)001:4681: ka ba rgyab tu bsnol ba /
NK126(cho)001:4682: khres po phra la ring ba khur ba /
NK126(cho)001:4686: gang yin cha med pa gcig gi deng song bod yul mthil du sleb 'phrang bsrung bas byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4687: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas bal yul du ma sleb nas /
NK126(cho)001:4688: dag sha ka ra bya ba'i yul du gzim pas /
NK126(cho)001:4689: pan+di ta pradz+ny+aa pi ti bya ba mjal nas /
NK126(cho)001:4690: pan+di ta pradz+ny+aa pi tis b+aee ro tsa na la rtogs tshad ci 'dra 'dug dris pas /
NK126(cho)001:4691: bod kyi ban+de rang sems ci ltar rtogs na rtogs pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:4692: theg pa gang la mkhas na 'bras bu thob //
NK126(cho)001:4693: mchod pa gang gi mchod na 'phags pa brnyed //
NK126(cho)001:4695: b+aee ro tsa nas dang po rang sems ci ltar rtogs na rtogs zhes pa lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4696: sems kyi mtshan nyid gdod nas rang bzhin med //
NK126(cho)001:4697: rgyu las ma byung dpes kyang mtshon du med //
NK126(cho)001:4698: rang bzhin 'od gsal dmigs med dag pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4699: rgyal ba rnams kyi mtshon du med par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:4700: gnyis pa theg pa gang la mkhas pa'i len btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4701: don dam chos nyid lta phug gcig pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4702: dbang po rab 'bring rim pa gsum gsum phye //
NK126(cho)001:4703: dam chos theg pa zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' //
NK126(cho)001:4704: gang ltar rtogs kyang 'bras bu thob bam dgongs //
NK126(cho)001:4705: gsum pa mchod pa gang gis mchod kyi lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4706: ye nas dag pa'i klong chen mi dmigs na //
NK126(cho)001:4707: ye nas 'od gsal spros med sangs rgyas sku //
NK126(cho)001:4708: sems la chags med 'khor yul zang zing gi //
NK126(cho)001:4709: ser sna ma zhugs kun la mnyam snyam na //
NK126(cho)001:4710: de ni mchod pa'i nang nas dam pa ste //
NK126(cho)001:4711: 'phags pa rnams kyang de la mnyes sam dgongs //
NK126(cho)001:4714: dgung zla gcig mchod gnas byas so //
NK126(cho)001:4715: de nas b+aee ro tsa na rgya dang bal po'i
NK126(cho)001:4716: kha la la kha tu bod kyi 'tshong pa dang
NK126(cho)001:4717: 'phrad de / de'i gseb na blon po ma ra dag rje bya ba 'dug ste /
NK126(cho)001:4718: bzlog ste b+aee ro tsa nas /
NK126(cho)001:4719: rje khri srong lde'u btsan la shog 'phrin bskur ba /
NK126(cho)001:4721: rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK126(cho)001:4722: yang dag bde chen gyi don ni ma rtogs cing //
NK126(cho)001:4723: kun rdzob 'khor ba'i chos la thugs ches pas //
NK126(cho)001:4724: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po'i spyan sngar ru //
NK126(cho)001:4725: b+aee ro tsa na bdag gis 'jal phyag 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:4726: dgung lo dgu ru zhal g.yar ma 'jal bas //
NK126(cho)001:4727: rin chen 'bar ba sku yi phung po la //
NK126(cho)001:4728: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pas ma bser ram //
NK126(cho)001:4729: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs kyis ma spyod par //
NK126(cho)001:4730: kha la la kha'i kha ru bdag gis 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:4731: kun la dgos pa'i spyi yi khrims chen kyang //
NK126(cho)001:4732: dbus nas ma g.yos mtha' nas ma zag par //
NK126(cho)001:4733: kha la la kha'i kha ru bdag gis 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:4734: phying bar stag rtse bkra shis dang rtse na //
NK126(cho)001:4735: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po'i sku khams bde //
NK126(cho)001:4736: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa na yis //
NK126(cho)001:4737: zla ba drug gi dmyal dbyang lam bcad pas //
NK126(cho)001:4738: mtha' yi phyogs bzhir kha bzhi bstan bstan nas //
NK126(cho)001:4739: ma myong dgu myong shi ba ma myong ba'i //
NK126(cho)001:4740: b+aee ro tsa nas rje la bzhes phyag 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:4741: de skad bya ba'i shog 'phrin nang 'khor ba cig la bardzangasa pas /
NK126(cho)001:4742: nang 'khor ba rje'i spyan sngar mchis ma thag tu phyag byas te /
NK126(cho)001:4743: b+aee ro tsa na'i 'phrin yig gtad pas /
NK126(cho)001:4744: rje khri srong lde'u btsan dgyes te /
NK126(cho)001:4745: yang rje yig dag rje bzlog ste /
NK126(cho)001:4746: b+aee ro tsa na'i shog 'phrin lan bardzongasa pa //
NK126(cho)001:4747: phying bar stag rtse bkra shis dang rtse na //
NK126(cho)001:4748: 'khor ba'i chu 'dzin 'dra ba'i kha dpon bdag /
NK126(cho)001:4749: phung po ma g.yos khams chen bco brgyad bde //
NK126(cho)001:4750: bka' yi phung po lnga dang khams chen bco brgyad bde //
NK126(cho)001:4751: lan gcig 'jig pa bdag gis mi bzod na //
NK126(cho)001:4752: phung po khams chen 'jig pa'i sman chen po //
NK126(cho)001:4753: phyi nang mtshan nyid man ngag bde ba'i lam //
NK126(cho)001:4754: man ngag rgyal po du zhig lon nas byon //
NK126(cho)001:4755: ma nor yang dag bde ba'i chos chen po //
NK126(cho)001:4756: bsnams nas byon nam zhal mjal spyi bor khur //
NK126(cho)001:4757: dgung lo dgu ru mtha' yi kha brgyud nas //
NK126(cho)001:4758: gnod sbyin gtum dang 'phrang bsrung mi bzad pa //
NK126(cho)001:4759: gcan gzan dam dred spyang ku sbrul rnams kyis //
NK126(cho)001:4760: bka' yi yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i phung po la //
NK126(cho)001:4761: bskyod par ma nus byin brlabs thugs rje che //
NK126(cho)001:4762: dgung lo grongs kyis ma mjal bar skabs su //
NK126(cho)001:4763: sku la nongs pa ma byung glo ba dga' //
NK126(cho)001:4764: yang dag ma nor bde ba'i chos bdog na //
NK126(cho)001:4765: bod kyis rgyal pos mdun bsu 'phrad par smon //
NK126(cho)001:4766: ces bya ba'i shog 'phrin cig bris nas /
NK126(cho)001:4767: sa khor po bya ba gcig gi tshang pa la
NK126(cho)001:4768: bskur nas b+aee ro tsa na'i sa ru btang ngo
NK126(cho)001:4769: // de nas b+aee ro tsa na bal yul d+ha he na'i yul du byon te /
NK126(cho)001:4770: kha bal gyi rgyal po d+ha he na bya ba'i
NK126(cho)001:4771: rgyal phran gcig la b+aee ro tsa na bab nas
NK126(cho)001:4772: / rkang mgyogs kyi nus pa yar 'grib ste /
NK126(cho)001:4773: b+aee ro tsa nas bal skad du mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4774: grong khyer 'di yi mi rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:4775: ban rgan 'di la brten sa cig /
NK126(cho)001:4776: g.yar 'tshal cig ni zhus pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:4778: yang kho bal gyi rgyal po d+ha he nas b+aee ro tsa na la /
NK126(cho)001:4781: don ched ci bsgrub gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:4782: b+aee ro tsa nas bal skad du mgur du bzhengs te len btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4784: sems la skye 'gag med pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4785: gdod nas ma skyes nam mkha' dang pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4786: nam mkha'i dbyings nas nam mkha'i cho 'phrul shar //
NK126(cho)001:4787: sprin dang khu rlang nyi zla gza' skar byung //
NK126(cho)001:4788: nam mkha'i dbyings nas nam mkha' byung tshor byung //
NK126(cho)001:4789: ci ltar byung yang nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:4790: de la gdod nas skye bar ngas ma mthong //
NK126(cho)001:4791: sems nyid ma skyes ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK126(cho)001:4792: ston pa'i byung tshul sems nyid dbyings nas byung //
NK126(cho)001:4793: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya 'dod yon rnam lnga po //
NK126(cho)001:4794: rang byung rang zhir bzhag na chos nyid dbyings kyi ngang //
NK126(cho)001:4795: de la gdod nas skye ba med par rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:4796: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pa'i chos dbyings la //
NK126(cho)001:4797: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i klong chen pha //
NK126(cho)001:4798: ya mtshan rmad 'byung bdag gi lus 'di skyes //
NK126(cho)001:4799: mkha' klong rnam dag chos kyi dbyings nas 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:4800: 'jig rten 'di yi dgos pa'i gtam bgyis der //
NK126(cho)001:4801: rigs pa'i klong nas thugs rje'i nyi shar bas //
NK126(cho)001:4802: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa bdag gis rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:4803: kun gzhi rnam dag bde chen lhun rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:4804: mkha' ltar dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid ni //
NK126(cho)001:4805: skye med ya mtshan yi ge a cig la //
NK126(cho)001:4806: yi ge a ni dgongs pa'i byung khung te //
NK126(cho)001:4807: dgongs pa'i don du bya ba de las med //
NK126(cho)001:4808: de las byung ba'i nor ni 'di rnams yin //
NK126(cho)001:4809: nor ni ma mchis bla ma'i man ngag 'chang //
NK126(cho)001:4810: slob dpon ma mchis sh+ri sing ha las //
NK126(cho)001:4811: 'khor ni ma mchis lha srin sde brgyad 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:4812: chung ma ma mchis kun tu bzang mo lags //
NK126(cho)001:4813: grogs ni ma mchis ma mo mkha' 'gro'i grogs //
NK126(cho)001:4814: rta ni ma mchis tshogs drug yid kyi rta //
NK126(cho)001:4815: bu ni ma mchis rang rig yid kyi bu //
NK126(cho)001:4816: mthu ni ma mchis dug gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK126(cho)001:4817: brgyag phye ma mchis ting 'dzin zas su za //
NK126(cho)001:4818: de 'dra nga la yod pa tshol du phyin //
NK126(cho)001:4819: brten sa ma mchis do nub brten sa cig zhus pas //
NK126(cho)001:4820: bal yul d+ha he na'i yul mi kun dga' nas phyag byas dgung zhag cig zhabs nas btegs so //
NK126(cho)001:4821: de nas b+aee ro tsa na li yul lcang ra smug por byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:4822: rkang mgyogs kyi nus pa yang yal te /
NK126(cho)001:4823: btsun ma li tsha tshul khrims sgron ma bya ba la /
NK126(cho)001:4826: 'di la bzhugs pa'i yon bdag mo //
NK126(cho)001:4827: ban rgan 'di la brten sa g.yar //
NK126(cho)001:4828: bza' rgyu ma mchis yon cig zhu gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:4829: btsun mo li tsha tshul khrims sgron mas /
NK126(cho)001:4830: b+aee ro tsa na la lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:4831: brten sa ma mchis bdag rang mi go 'drim //
NK126(cho)001:4832: sku yon sbyin du bdag rang mi zas za //
NK126(cho)001:4833: slob dpon yang sku yon cang bzhed dam //
NK126(cho)001:4835: yang slob dpon gyis mgur 'di bzhengs so //
NK126(cho)001:4836: 'gro sas sdug pa'i ban rgan la //
NK126(cho)001:4837: skyid na sgo rgyab yin kyang chog /
NK126(cho)001:4838: dro na phyar hrul yin kyang chog /'grang na zas lhag yin kyang chog /
NK126(cho)001:4839: cis kyang gzhan du 'gro re skan //
NK126(cho)001:4841: li tsha tshul khrims sgron ma'i sems la mkhas pa
NK126(cho)001:4842: b+aee ro tsa na bya ba zhig byon kyin 'dug
NK126(cho)001:4844: de yin na nga'i mo ring ma'i khyim ngo tsha snyams pa las /
NK126(cho)001:4845: shin tu 'o brgyal la nyams thag par 'dug snyam nas dgung zhag gcig zhabs tog cher byas so //
NK126(cho)001:4846: de nas b+aee ro tsa na yin par shes nas /
NK126(cho)001:4847: ma h+aa g+hu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:4848: sems nyid ci ltar rtogs na rtogs par 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:4850: b+aee ro tsa nas lan gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4851: sems nyid nam mkha' dbyings dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4852: nam mkha'i dbyings la mtha' dbus med //
NK126(cho)001:4853: nam mkha'i dbyings la gzhi rtsa med //
NK126(cho)001:4855: nam mkha' dbyings la skye shi med //
NK126(cho)001:4856: sems kyi dpe ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4857: byang chub sems la gzhi rtsa med //
NK126(cho)001:4858: byang chub sems la mtha' dbus med //
NK126(cho)001:4859: byang chub sems la mtshan ma med //
NK126(cho)001:4860: byang chub sems la skye shi med //
NK126(cho)001:4861: dgongs pa mtha' dbus med par rtogs pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:4862: gzhi rtsa med par rtogs pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:4864: skye shi med par rtogs pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4865: ma yengs ma bcos gnas pa na //
NK126(cho)001:4866: bsgom pa ming du btags pa de las med //
NK126(cho)001:4868: gzhan yang man ngag mang po gnang /
NK126(cho)001:4869: li tsha tshul khrims sgron ma yid ches /
NK126(cho)001:4871: li tsha tshul khrims sgron mas b+aee ro tsa na
NK126(cho)001:4872: la rta ngang pa gser mdog bya ba gcig phul
NK126(cho)001:4873: bas / b+aee ro tsa nas rta ngang pa gser mdog bcibs nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:4874: nam mkha' che yi sa gzhi la //
NK126(cho)001:4875: rmad du byung ba'i rta pho phyo //
NK126(cho)001:4876: rdo la gser zhun sga cig bstad //
NK126(cho)001:4877: bde ba'i 'phra bkod yob chen btags //
NK126(cho)001:4878: yid bzhin nor bu'i glo srab bsdom //
NK126(cho)001:4879: rje btsun dam pa'i mi cig zhon //
NK126(cho)001:4880: spyi bcings rgyal po'i rmog cig gon //
NK126(cho)001:4881: rtse mo byung rgyal 'phru gcig gtsug /
NK126(cho)001:4882: thog med drug gi khrab gcig gyon //
NK126(cho)001:4883: srog gi 'khor lo'i phub chung khur //
NK126(cho)001:4884: rtsal chen sprug pa'i gzhu cig brdungs //
NK126(cho)001:4885: drangs pa'i sems kyi mda' gcig la //
NK126(cho)001:4886: kun 'dus rigs pa'i made'u cig btsug /
NK126(cho)001:4887: spyi gcod rnon po'i ral dri btags //
NK126(cho)001:4888: rig pa khu byugs lcag gi brab //
NK126(cho)001:4889: kun byed rgyal po'i stag dong du //
NK126(cho)001:4890: rgyud sde drug cu'i mda' mo blug /
NK126(cho)001:4891: rgyud sde'i bstan bsrungs kun gyi dong rgyan byas //
NK126(cho)001:4892: khyung chen lding ba'i nga rgyal bskyed //
NK126(cho)001:4893: bde byams sdug med lam las byung //
NK126(cho)001:4897: de nas bal yul du byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:4898: rgya gar gyi brten ma re ma tis lam khar kha ba btang bas /
NK126(cho)001:4899: rje b+aee ro tsa nas bka' bden nam mi bden brtags nas /
NK126(cho)001:4900: dus gsum sangs rgyas rang gis sems yin no //
NK126(cho)001:4901: skye 'chi med pas dus gsum sangs rgyas so //
NK126(cho)001:4902: yang rab skal ldan blo dang ldan pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4903: sems kyi nyi ma gsal bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4904: bsam pa bzang po gser dang 'dra ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:4905: bod kyi yul nas rgya gar lam bar la //
NK126(cho)001:4906: dka' ba bcu drug bsdos pa'i man ngag la //
NK126(cho)001:4907: bka' ba cig gis lam du ma gcod par //
NK126(cho)001:4908: kha ba 'di yis bar du gcod la khad //
NK126(cho)001:4909: bka' 'di bden na kha ba 'di ka chod //
NK126(cho)001:4910: gsungs pas rgya gar gyi brtan ma re ma ti
NK126(cho)001:4911: lha mo dmar mo sprin gyi gseb nas sku bstan
NK126(cho)001:4912: nas / b+aee ro tsa na la phyag 'tshal lus
NK126(cho)001:4913: bran du khas blangs pas dus der kha ba chod
NK126(cho)001:4914: nas / do // gdug rab tu gsal lo //
NK126(cho)001:4915: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas kho bal gyi rgyal
NK126(cho)001:4916: po d+ha he nas phul ba'i 'phags pa byams pa'i
NK126(cho)001:4917: gser sku de bal yul 'phags pa shing kun la
NK126(cho)001:4919: sgrib rkyen mi mnga' dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:4920: thugs rje dbang btsan dzam gling nyi ma 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4921: ston pa'i sku la phyogs ris mi mnga' yang //
NK126(cho)001:4922: 'khor ba'i las yin zad med nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4923: thugs rjes 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho bskoms pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:4924: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku la bzod par gsol //
NK126(cho)001:4926: de nas rje b+aee ro tsa nas bsam yas su byon pas /
NK126(cho)001:4927: sa gor som ting ba dang 'phrad nas rgyal po khang pa dgu rim na bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:4928: nang 'khor ba cig la shog 'phrin bardzangasa pa /
NK126(cho)001:4929: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po lags //
NK126(cho)001:4930: 'jig rten 'khor ba'i chos la thugs dbyung nas //
NK126(cho)001:4931: ma nor yang dag bden pa'i chos 'dod nas //
NK126(cho)001:4932: gser phye bardzangasa nas bdag cag tshol du btang //
NK126(cho)001:4933: dmyal sbyang lam bcad mtha' yi kha bskor te //
NK126(cho)001:4934: bde chen lhun rdzogs rnyed pa dgung lo brgyad //
NK126(cho)001:4935: 'jig rten 'khor ba'i nad chen gso ba la //
NK126(cho)001:4936: sman dang sman par bcas pa ma nor bden pa'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:4937: bod kyi ban rgan lus la mchis lags te //
NK126(cho)001:4938: b+aee ro tsa na ha cang bod la glo ba ches shing rmar rgyu med //
NK126(cho)001:4939: rgyal po nad ka che bas yar le sham po 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4940: blon po gdug pa che ste btsan dug khol ma 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4941: btsun mo khong gyong che ste gyang kha'i khyi 'phyo 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4942: stag shar sgrin la mnag chung pho rog khra ded 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4943: chab srid dar la yun thung phug chu blug pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4944: bstan bcos klog bshad bya byed byis pa'i klog mkhan 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4945: sngags pa grong gnyer byed de gyer bon rnga thogs 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4946: dam nyams tshogs dpon byas pa khrag gis khrag 'khrugs 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4947: skad 'gyur rang mthong che ba sngags bshad brag cha 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4948: rgyal po khyed nyid bzhugs pa yang //
NK126(cho)001:4949: ma nyes snyan khung chung chung 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:4950: 'dra ba mang po'i gseb na b+aee ro tsa na mchis //
NK126(cho)001:4951: kye ma ma nor bden pa'i chos mchis te //
NK126(cho)001:4952: b+aee ro tsa na gar 'gro gtol ma mchis //
NK126(cho)001:4953: khyod nyid ri bo lta bur mi 'gyur brtan pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:4954: rgyal mtsho'i gting ltar mi bskyod dal bar mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:4955: bod la dgos rgu ban rgan lus la mchis lags te //
NK126(cho)001:4956: zhal g.yar mjal nas bka' mchid snyan du gsol //
NK126(cho)001:4957: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po'i zhal mjal zhe sa 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:4958: zhes rje'i spyan sngar shog 'phrin byung ma thag tshig gcig kyang yong long med par spyan drangs so //
NK126(cho)001:4959: b+aee ro tsa na dang zhal mjal zhe sa ma phul bar du /
NK126(cho)001:4960: b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:4961: rje yi bka' rtsal gnyer ni bdag gis 'khums nas mchis //
NK126(cho)001:4962: legs grub gzhi ni snga la song bas gcan 'phrang bas bsad //
NK126(cho)001:4963: rgya gar phrag dog che bas snyan phra la dga' //
NK126(cho)001:4964: snyan phra byung nas gsan du mi rung lags so byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:4965: rje yis b+aee ro tsa na la srog la mi bab pa'i bka' rtags srog tshig nos so //
NK126(cho)001:4966: rje'i zhal nas de mi gsungs 'tshal dgyes par bgyi gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:4967: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas jo mo dmar rgyan la shog 'phrin bardzongasa pa /
NK126(cho)001:4968: ma bcos chos dbyings ma rtogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:4969: snang srid 'khor ba'i chos la yid ches pas //
NK126(cho)001:4970: mnga' thang rtse ru chibs pa'i rje mo dmar rgyan ma //
NK126(cho)001:4971: b+aee ro tsa nas sku la bzhes phyag 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:4972: dgung lo brgyad nas lha zhal ma 'khums pa'i //
NK126(cho)001:4973: nor bu rin chen btsun mo dam pa la //
NK126(cho)001:4974: stong phrag brgyad cu bgegs kyi tshogs rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:4975: 'byung ba lnga yi nad kyi thang lhag ma mchis par //
NK126(cho)001:4976: de ring yin snyan 'khor du bka' mchis 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:4977: kun la dgos pa'i spyi khrims chen po yang //
NK126(cho)001:4978: dbus nas ma g.yos mtha' nas ma 'gram snyad //
NK126(cho)001:4979: gces pa'i sku las 'khrungs pa'i rgyal bu mched gsum ni //
NK126(cho)001:4980: bgegs kyi ma bskyed 'khrungs par lags pa yang //
NK126(cho)001:4981: kha la la kha'i kha ru bka' mchis 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:4982: 'phying par sta rtse bkra shis dang rtse na //
NK126(cho)001:4983: bod kyi mnga' bdag nyid dang mjal ba'i sku gsung thugs ni bde //
NK126(cho)001:4984: zla ba drug gis phar lam bcad bcad pas //
NK126(cho)001:4985: ku sha'i 'du khang rdo rje gdan du sleb //
NK126(cho)001:4986: dbus kyi bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa na //
NK126(cho)001:4987: rdo rje gdan du ma bsdad dgung zla drug /
NK126(cho)001:4988: ku sha'i 'du khang tshun chad zla ba bdun //
NK126(cho)001:4989: phar la dgur zla bdun gyi lam bar la //
NK126(cho)001:4990: de'u shi de'u chad lnga bcu rtsa bdun myong //
NK126(cho)001:4991: ma myong dgu myong shi ba ma myong ba'i //
NK126(cho)001:4992: b+aee ro tsa na 'khyam po bdag /
NK126(cho)001:4993: rje mo dmar rgyal sku la bzhes phyag 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:4994: thugs rje reg na nang 'khor cig la shog 'phrin bardzangasa //
NK126(cho)001:4995: lha rgyal chen mo bdag dngos zhal mthong 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:4997: der lha rgyal yab yum dang mjal /
NK126(cho)001:5000: b+aee ro tsa na dgung lo lnga bcu rtsa bdun
NK126(cho)001:5001: la rgya gar nas bod du byon pa'i skabs bcu
NK126(cho)001:5002: drug pa'o //// de nas rje'i dbu skra lcang lo theg pa'i kha la bkrom nas /
NK126(cho)001:5003: de'i steng nas yar la b+aee ro tsa na byon
NK126(cho)001:5004: du bcug nas zhabs spyi bo'i thog tu bzhag nas
NK126(cho)001:5005: / b+aee ro'i zhabs kyi 'go nas rde'u cig phyungs nas rje'i dbu thog tu bzhag nas /
NK126(cho)001:5006: sngags btsun sde dbu'i mchod gnas su bkur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5007: mtshan yang man ngag bdag po lha rje bla mar btags so //
NK126(cho)001:5008: des dus de nas ser chags dbu'i mchod gnas su khur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5009: phyis kyang slob dpon dbu yi mchod gnas su mi
NK126(cho)001:5010: khur bar chos 'go bru nas zhus nas chos rku
NK126(cho)001:5012: de ni dam tshig nyams pa'i las yin te de 'dra byar mi rung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:5013: ston pa sh+aaka thub bka' nas tshig gsum smra ba slob dpon yin //
NK126(cho)001:5014: yid kyis blangs la spyi bor khur //
NK126(cho)001:5016: de nas khri srong lde'u btsan gyis b+aee ro tsa
NK126(cho)001:5017: na la man ngag a ti rdzogs pa chen po
NK126(cho)001:5019: spyir yang slob dpon chen po b+aee ro tsa nas
NK126(cho)001:5020: rgya gar gyis yul nas rgyu 'bras kyi chos mang
NK126(cho)001:5021: po bsgyur te / shes rab kyi pha rol du
NK126(cho)001:5022: phyin pa stong phrag brgya pa la sogs pa 'bum
NK126(cho)001:5024: shes rab pha rol du phyin pas stong phrag brgya pa las byams pas zhus pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:5027: bam po lngas kha ma long ngo //
NK126(cho)001:5028: lang kar gshegs pa la bam po bco lnga pa bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:5030: dkon mchog brtsegs pa la bam po so lngas kha ma sos so //
NK126(cho)001:5031: sangs rgyas phal po che la bam po brgya dang brgyad la 'gyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5032: mya ngan las 'das pa la nyis brgya bcu gnyis ma 'gyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5033: lung gi rgyud la gshin rje'i rgyud rnams /
NK126(cho)001:5035: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud dang gsum bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5036: man ngag ni nam mkha' che la sogs pa rtsa ba brgyad /
NK126(cho)001:5037: rgyud rmad du byung ba dang drug /
NK126(cho)001:5039: spyi sems smad bcu dgu bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5040: zhi ba bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i rgyud /
NK126(cho)001:5041: khro bo sun+da ri ka'i rgyud la sogs pa ma h+aa tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5043: gzhi ma rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga /
NK126(cho)001:5044: bsgrub pa lag len gyi rgyud lnga /
NK126(cho)001:5045: spyi 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga ste bco lnga /
NK126(cho)001:5046: rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po dang bcu drug /
NK126(cho)001:5047: ma tshang ba kha bskangs ba rngam bzlog gi rgyud dang bcu bdun /
NK126(cho)001:5048: don gyi mjug sdud pa rdzu 'phrul thabs zhags rgyud dang bco brgyad do //
NK126(cho)001:5049: de la rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga ni /
NK126(cho)001:5050: sku'i rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK126(cho)001:5051: gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le /
NK126(cho)001:5052: thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK126(cho)001:5053: yon tan gyi rgyud bdud rtsi rol pa /
NK126(cho)001:5054: phrin las kyi rgyud karma ma le'o //
NK126(cho)001:5055: lag len gyi rgyud lnga ni /
NK126(cho)001:5056: sku'i bsgrub pa he ru ka gal po /
NK126(cho)001:5057: gsung gi bsgrub pa rta mchog rol pa /
NK126(cho)001:5058: thugs kyi bsgrub pa thugs rje rol pa /
NK126(cho)001:5059: yon tan gyi bsgrub pa bdud rtsi rol pa /
NK126(cho)001:5060: phrin las kyi bsgrub pa ki la ya bcu gcig gi tan+t+ra'o //
NK126(cho)001:5062: lta ba'i rgyud ri bo brtsegs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5063: spyod pa'i rgyud glang chen chur 'jug /
NK126(cho)001:5064: ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyud rtse gcig bsdus pa /
NK126(cho)001:5065: dam tshig sa ma ya bkod pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:5066: 'bras bu'i rgyud gangs pa lung ston no //
NK126(cho)001:5067: de ltar bco lnga'i steng du rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po dang bcu drug /
NK126(cho)001:5068: ma tshang ba kha bskangs ba'i rgyud rngam glog rgyud dang bcu bdun /
NK126(cho)001:5069: don thams cad kyi 'jug bsdud pa sgyu 'phrul thabs zhags kyi rgyud tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5070: bee ro tsa na nyid kyis mdzad pa'i man ngag kyang bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)001:5071: nyin mo rgyu 'bras kyi chos bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:5072: mtshan mo gsang sngags kyi rgyud a ti rdzogs pa chen po bsgyur ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:5073: de yang de'i dus de'i tshe na rgya gar gyi pan+di ta rnams dang /
NK126(cho)001:5074: rgya gar chos kyi rgyal po rnams la cig la gcig thugs ma ches yid mkhon te /
NK126(cho)001:5075: pan+di ta rnams kyi thugs la rgya ru sprod chos skyong ba'i rgyal pos bshig nas /
NK126(cho)001:5076: bod kyi rgyal po a ti bskur ram bsam /
NK126(cho)001:5077: rgyal po'i thugs la rgya ru sprod pan+di tas bshig nas bod kyi ban+de la bskur bas /
NK126(cho)001:5078: de man ngag gi rgyal po a ti ni bod du shor bas /
NK126(cho)001:5079: des phyi mo chu srin gyi khar rin po che
NK126(cho)001:5080: shor ba ltar bskal pa'i bar du gter du 'khums
NK126(cho)001:5081: gsungs nas rdo rje gdan du gter sbas pa yang
NK126(cho)001:5082: zer / a su ra'i brag la gter du sbas sam yang zer /
NK126(cho)001:5083: bya rgod phung po'i ri la gter du sbas sam yang zer /
NK126(cho)001:5084: rgyal pos man ngag gi chos a ti rdzogs pa chen po gar song cha med par byas so //
NK126(cho)001:5085: pan+di ta rnams la chab gsol ba yang glengs /
NK126(cho)001:5086: de'i dus de'i tshe na bod la ngan sgrogs su btang ste /
NK126(cho)001:5087: bod kyi btsan po rje 'bangs la bod kyi ban+desa
NK126(cho)001:5088: rgyal pos tshol du btang ba'i man ngag gi chos
NK126(cho)001:5089: ni ma rnyed / rgya gar gyi ngan sngags dang khro chu phra man ma la sogs te /
NK126(cho)001:5090: bod kyi phugs cha sna tshogs khyer bas bod kyi
NK126(cho)001:5091: bka' khrims chen po dang sbyor cig par bsgrags so
NK126(cho)001:5092: // der blon po kun tshogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5094: ban+de 'dis rje'i tshol du btang ba'i man ngag ma rnyed /
NK126(cho)001:5095: bod phung bar byed pa'i ngan sngags nyi tshe khyer bar mchis pas /
NK126(cho)001:5096: ban+de 'di ma bsad na bod kyi rgyal khams phung bar 'gro bas /
NK126(cho)001:5097: ban+de 'di bsad dgos byas nas rgyal po la zhus nas /
NK126(cho)001:5098: der btsad po'i zhal nas de gtsug min b+aee ro
NK126(cho)001:5099: tsa na 'di sprul pa'i sku yin gsungs nas ma
NK126(cho)001:5100: gnang ngo // blon po rnams kyi nang nas re re bzhin zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:5101: b+aee ros sprul pa'i mi cig byas /
NK126(cho)001:5102: de nas rgyal pos b+aee ro tsa na'i gos lham gyi sbubs su bcug nas /
NK126(cho)001:5103: zangs chen po gnyis kha sbyar nas de'i nang du b+aee ro tsa na bzhugs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5104: kha la lcags gzer btab nas yar gtsang skyi gtsang 'dus pa'i chu la bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:5105: rgyal pos b+aee ro tsa na la chab gsol lo //
NK126(cho)001:5109: ngo log mchi ma dbyung ba'i tshul byas so //
NK126(cho)001:5110: de nas rje rang gi gdan khri'i 'og nas mal sa rkos pas /
NK126(cho)001:5111: sa phug gcig de'i nang nas mar me bya pho tsam zhig btang nas slob dpon sbas na /
NK126(cho)001:5112: nam gyi gung la chos gsan cing zhus pa las /
NK126(cho)001:5113: nub gcig nang 'khor ba glo ba nye ba gcig
NK126(cho)001:5114: gis rje'i pho brang nas yar la phyin pas rje
NK126(cho)001:5115: pho brang nang na mi bzhugs par 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:5116: bzhugs khri la ltas pas gdan khri'i 'og nas sa rgya nyams nas 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:5117: der gdan bsal nas bltas pas bzhugs khri 'og nas mar las stegs khrig ge 'dug nas /
NK126(cho)001:5118: de nas mar la phyin pas sa phug gi nang na me dmar bya pho tsam zhig btang 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:5119: slob dpon khri kha na chos gsungs gis 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:5120: rjes phrug ras ang ga ra gcig gsol nas bkru bshal mdzad gin 'dug go //
NK126(cho)001:5123: nang 'khor de dang gsum ka sngangs shing bred do //
NK126(cho)001:5125: ngas gdugs khang cig dbub gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5126: ka ba sbom po zhig mdzad nas /
NK126(cho)001:5127: ka ba khang stong du brus nas bsam le bcug
NK126(cho)001:5128: nas ka ba'i nang du b+aee ro tsa na sbas
NK126(cho)001:5130: nam gyi gung la 'bangs bshan thogs pa yan chad nyal ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:5131: rje'i ka ba'i bsam le phyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:5132: chos gsan cing zhus pa la /
NK126(cho)001:5133: nub gcig rtsa na btsun mo tshe spang ma dmar rgyal gyi 'khums nas /
NK126(cho)001:5134: dmar rgyal gyi blon po ngam stag ra klu gang
NK126(cho)001:5135: la nam gyi gung la rje la gleng rog pa
NK126(cho)001:5136: cig 'dug b+aee ro tsa na min nam byas pas
NK126(cho)001:5137: / yang blon po rnams kyi rje la zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:5138: rje'i zhal snga nas nang pa'i bka' lnga /
NK126(cho)001:5139: yab mes kyis kyi lha khang mdzad gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5140: gser dngul rnams 'dag sa la bskus /
NK126(cho)001:5141: 'phan gdugs mdzad gsungs nas dar zab rnams phrag bsil te nor /
NK126(cho)001:5142: de dang 'dra bar rjes yang chos byed gsung nas
NK126(cho)001:5143: ban+de sprang po ci ma nyes pa bzung nas chab
NK126(cho)001:5144: la bskur te / rje la thugs rje mi mnga' ste nor /
NK126(cho)001:5145: de lta yang gdugs khang sbub gsungs nas bod phung
NK126(cho)001:5146: bar byed pa'i ban+de ngan sngags mkhan ka ba'i nang
NK126(cho)001:5148: da rgyal khrims 'jig gda' zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:5150: rta kha srab du song ste /
NK126(cho)001:5151: der yang rje'i zhal nas sngon yang de 'dra 'dra nas da lta yang de 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:5152: 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang mi mthong ba yin /
NK126(cho)001:5153: da nga'i mkhas pa chen po 'di la chab gsol mi phod kyi /
NK126(cho)001:5154: da khyod tshos la bcad nas bkum pa bas spyugs par gyis shig par bka' stsal pa la /
NK126(cho)001:5155: blon po ngam stag ra klu gong na re /
NK126(cho)001:5156: b+aee ro tsa na byang du spyugs na tsh+wa dang bal 'gags /
NK126(cho)001:5157: shar du spyugs na dar zab 'gags /
NK126(cho)001:5160: rgya nag por spyugs la thang byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:5162: cis kyang nga spyugs na rgya nag por ma spyugs /
NK126(cho)001:5163: nga skye ba snga ma'ang rgyal mo tsha ba rong nas tshe 'phos pa yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:5164: da yang man ngag gi chos 'di rgyal mo tsha ba rong du dar ba 'dra ba yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:5165: nga rgyal mo tsha ba rong du spyugs gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5166: rgya nag por gshegs su ma bzhed de /
NK126(cho)001:5167: b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs par byas so //
NK126(cho)001:5168: der rgyal po ni mya ngan gyis zin /
NK126(cho)001:5169: slob dpon b+aee ro tsa nas dus der bka' ba bcu drug gi mgur bzhengs te /
NK126(cho)001:5170: 'bru sna lnga 'khrungs gtsang po 'gram gyis yul //
NK126(cho)001:5171: mig ltar gces par byed pa'i lus bskyed pha ma dang //
NK126(cho)001:5172: gson shi dur gyis 'brel pa'i gnyen gzhi dang //
NK126(cho)001:5173: rtse gcig las kyi bsdus pa'i phur mi gnyen 'dun dang //
NK126(cho)001:5174: 'khor g.yog drung pos 'brel pa'i de rnams dang //
NK126(cho)001:5175: skad cig tsam yang 'bral ngo sus kyang ma chog par //
NK126(cho)001:5176: rje blon 'bangs gsum gang nas thugs tshod skyed //
NK126(cho)001:5178: rje blon 'bangs gsum snyan gson dang //
NK126(cho)001:5179: bco lnga lon nas lnga bcu rtsa bdun du //
NK126(cho)001:5180: rje yi zhabs nas gtegs pa ci tsam pa //
NK126(cho)001:5181: khri srong lde'u btsan thugs la mnga' ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5182: las dang skal bar ldan pa'i khri srong lde'u btsan gyis //
NK126(cho)001:5183: dang po man ngag tshol bar bsgos pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)001:5184: btsal yang mi rnyed tshol bar 'gro bar dka' bas dka' ba gcig /
NK126(cho)001:5185: de nas b+aee ro tsa na lam du zhug tsa na //
NK126(cho)001:5186: mtshon pa'i sa mkhan bdag la ma mchis par //
NK126(cho)001:5187: 'gro ba dka' ste dka' ba gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:5188: kha la la khar kha ba bab pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)001:5189: gom gang 'khrul nas 'chi bar phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5190: de 'dra'i kha bar thar ba dka' ste dka' ba gsum //
NK126(cho)001:5191: po bo rang gi gnod sbyin gtum pa'i sar //
NK126(cho)001:5192: mi 'dug dbang med mtshan cig 'dug pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5193: gnod sbyin mi sha rlon par za ba de la thar bar dka' ste dka' ba bzhi //
NK126(cho)001:5194: brag ra smug por rkang phran tshogs nas su //
NK126(cho)001:5195: rkang phran tshogs kyi za bas dka' ste dka' ba lnga //
NK126(cho)001:5196: 'gro bar dka' ba'i bal yul dka' ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5197: lce spyang lag gnyis btsug nas phyin te dka' ba drug /
NK126(cho)001:5198: bzur sa med pa'i rgya gar 'phrang la phyin //
NK126(cho)001:5199: khrims kyis 'phrang bsrung gis ni gsod par nges pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5200: de las thar bar dka' ste dka' ba bdun //
NK126(cho)001:5201: 'og min ral gri gdug pa'i thabs //
NK126(cho)001:5202: mgo bo pa tras gril nas phyin //
NK126(cho)001:5203: ston par dka' ba'i rdzu 'phrul stobs kyis phyin te dka' ba brgyad //
NK126(cho)001:5204: chu 'phrang shing 'phrang 'jig skrag skye bung par //
NK126(cho)001:5205: mtshal bu bya gdong shi nas sa la gser sbas te dka' ba dgu //
NK126(cho)001:5206: brda 'phrad dka' ba'i mon pa 'phrang bsrungs kyis //
NK126(cho)001:5207: 'tsho bar dka' ba'i nywa sul bkrol nas dka' ba bcu //
NK126(cho)001:5208: a gang da sha'i gling du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5209: matha'i sa yul rtogs byed byung zer nas //
NK126(cho)001:5210: sbal sbrul dong du bskyur te de las thar bar dka' ste dka' ba bcu gcig go //
NK126(cho)001:5211: rgya gar pra te su ta'i gling du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5212: stag dang sbrul dang dam la sogs pa 'jigs pa mang pos srog 'di gcod par nges //
NK126(cho)001:5213: de las thar bar dka' ste dka' ba bcu gnyis so //
NK126(cho)001:5214: rgya gar la ta'i gling du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5215: brgal bar dka' ba'i dug gi rgya mtsho la //
NK126(cho)001:5216: ras la khrus lding byas te dka' ba bcu gsum mo //
NK126(cho)001:5217: rgya gar a ba bdud 'dul phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5218: mtha' yi mon pa 'jigs su rung ba yis //
NK126(cho)001:5219: kho rang ma chad bar du dbyug pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:5220: char gyis brdungs te dka' ba bcu bzhi'o //
NK126(cho)001:5221: rgya gar ar+ya pa lo'i gling du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5223: bltas pa tsam gyis thar bar dka' ste dka' ba bco lnga'o //
NK126(cho)001:5224: rgya gar yul gyis kha zas mang po la //
NK126(cho)001:5225: zas su zos pa dug tu 'gyur nges mang //
NK126(cho)001:5226: lo dgu bar du dug las thar bar dka' ste dka' ba bcu drug go //
NK126(cho)001:5227: brid par dka' ba'i bram ze rgan mo brid //
NK126(cho)001:5228: bram ze rgan mos nyams dang rmi lam bzlas te dka' ba bcu bdun pa //
NK126(cho)001:5229: phyi ma bdun gyis man ngag rtsad nas gcod //
NK126(cho)001:5230: byang chub sems kyis bskul ma de'i btab ste dka' ba bco brgyad pa //
NK126(cho)001:5231: de 'dra'i dka' ba bco brgyad spyad nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5232: rje yi spyan sngar yus te mchi ma shor bas //
NK126(cho)001:5233: b+aee ro tsa na sdug rgyu min te skad //
NK126(cho)001:5235: rje blon rnams dbu smad mdzad nas /
NK126(cho)001:5237: yang mi spyugs pa la phan nam dgongs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5238: b+aee ro tsa nas mgur 'di bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5239: kyeeh rje blon 'bangs gsum bdag la gson //
NK126(cho)001:5240: 'bru sna lnga 'khrungs gtsang pos rib ma byas //
NK126(cho)001:5241: de 'dra'i dbu rgyal bod yul nas //
NK126(cho)001:5242: mig ltar gces pa'i lus bskyes pha ma dang //
NK126(cho)001:5243: gson gshin dur gyis 'brel pa'i gnyen 'dun dang //
NK126(cho)001:5244: rtse gcig las kyis 'brel pa'i phur khyim la //
NK126(cho)001:5245: 'khor yul drung pos 'brel pa 'di rnams dang //
NK126(cho)001:5246: skad cig tsam yang 'bral ngo sus kyang ma chog na //
NK126(cho)001:5247: rje blon 'bangs dang bcas pa gang nas thugs tshod che //
NK126(cho)001:5248: bco lnga lon nas lnga bcu rtsa bdun du //
NK126(cho)001:5249: rje yi zhal nas btegs pa ci tsam pa //
NK126(cho)001:5250: khri srong lde'u btsan thugs la mnga' bas las //
NK126(cho)001:5251: dgung lo gsum du gsol kha bgyis pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:5252: gsol kha snyoms par bgyis pas spyugs su med //
NK126(cho)001:5253: nang blon kha blon 'phrin blon gsum bgyis pas //
NK126(cho)001:5254: rje yi zhal nas btegs pa spyugs su med //
NK126(cho)001:5255: rje yi 'bangs rnams bsogs nas bka' stsal man ngag 'tshol bar 'tshol ba'i tshe //
NK126(cho)001:5256: b+aee ro tsa nas rje yi dka' yi bcag par
NK126(cho)001:5257: dka' ba spyad nas man ngag tshol du phyin pas
NK126(cho)001:5258: spyugs su med // bod kyi rgyal khams smin par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:5259: dang po kun tshogs bka' gros bstun nas man ngag tshol du btang //
NK126(cho)001:5260: bod nas rgya gar yul gyi lam bar la //
NK126(cho)001:5261: de'u shi de'u chad lnga bcu rtsa bdun byas //
NK126(cho)001:5262: dang po dbus nas bdag nyid chas pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5263: tshe mi mgon po'i rta yi brdab byas te //
NK126(cho)001:5264: zhag gcig kha dbugs chad de de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5265: sum pa mgon no de ru zhags sa la //
NK126(cho)001:5266: kha gdong khyis bzung phog ci de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5267: shes chung smon mos de ru zhags sa la //
NK126(cho)001:5268: skom tsa'i 'og tu nyal nyal nas //
NK126(cho)001:5269: tho rang gdung chag lus po 'go ru song //
NK126(cho)001:5270: phyung ba'i kha dbugs chad de de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5271: sna nam rgyal bu'i de ru zhags sa las /
NK126(cho)001:5272: chen chun 'thab pa'i bar du 'gro 'gro nas //
NK126(cho)001:5273: lag la gri zug nywa sol rnag tu song //
NK126(cho)001:5274: zla ba phyed du de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5275: rdza ma'i rdza mkhan rtsa ru zhag sa la //
NK126(cho)001:5276: bsad brdungs rtsib ma bcag nas me btsas gdug /
NK126(cho)001:5277: dmyal sbyangs kha dbugs chad nas de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5278: lang 'gro a re'i rtsa ru 'dug pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5279: rtsi shing mes tshe de ru de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5280: gnyen pa gru mkhan gnas su phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5281: grur zhugs phar kar 'gro bar 'dod pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5282: gru log skya shar chu'i khyer ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5283: gru pa gzhan gyis bzung bas de'i shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5284: sug mkhan mgar ba'i rtsa ru zhag sa las //
NK126(cho)001:5285: khang pa rdib nas de'u shi yang cig byas //
NK126(cho)001:5286: so legs yon tan de ru zhag sa las //
NK126(cho)001:5287: khang pa chus khyer bdag kyang khyer nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5288: rgya mkhan gzhan gyis bzung bas de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5289: 'or ma sna ma'i gad phug nyal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5290: gad pa rdib nas de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5291: lhen gyis khang skyar bdag ni phyin nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5292: rnyang ngag dpal le de ru zhag sa la //
NK126(cho)001:5293: mtshal bu bya gdong dag gi lus brjid te //
NK126(cho)001:5294: khong pa rnyog nas de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5295: nyang jo phyam mtshal ne chung mchis pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5296: skyes bus mda' 'phang rtse ba'i mda' cig gis //
NK126(cho)001:5297: ro stod gos la thal phyungs sha la ma theg ste //
NK126(cho)001:5298: gshin grir de'u bsad de da ru de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5299: tsha mo rong ru bdag nyid phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5300: shing bu'i mo lo'i nang du nyal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5301: sdong gog chad nas de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5302: khri spang khri lung khang par nyal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5303: mdzo nag 'thab pa'i 'og tu tshud nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5304: nyal ba'i 'og tu skad kyang ma phyin lus po rnyogs //
NK126(cho)001:5305: mgo chags rkang drum de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5306: spang mo spang dkar gling du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5307: spang dkar spyang ku bdun gyis rgol ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5308: phyin pa lag phug lus la khrag phyungs te //
NK126(cho)001:5309: kha dbugs chad de de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5310: lci ba lung ma tshal du nyal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5311: g.yag gis brang du brdungs te lag pa bcag /
NK126(cho)001:5312: zla ba phyed du de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5313: tsha ba'i rong du bdag nyid mchis pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5314: tshang pa tsa ra ba cig dgra rnams kyis //
NK126(cho)001:5315: rgyal mo blang ba'i ming po 'thu ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:5316: 'phrad de rta 'phras bdag la de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5317: de nas grang po thang du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5318: bye ma'i gad 'phrang chad de de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5319: de ri'i mu gnyan mkhar du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5320: lus la srin bus 'gong ste khar phyungs nas //
NK126(cho)001:5321: srin bu snar song sna sub khrag phyungs nas //
NK126(cho)001:5322: kha dbugs chad de de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5323: kha la kha ba lung du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5324: nyin mtshan drug tu kha ba byung ba las //
NK126(cho)001:5325: kha ma'i 'og tu mi phyugs zhag gsum chud //
NK126(cho)001:5326: de'u shi de'u chad kha bas zhag gsum byas //
NK126(cho)001:5327: rna la kha tshe lung du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5328: 'phar ba dmar pos khang rar bcug nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5329: 'phar ba dmar pos de'u shi de'u bsad par byas //
NK126(cho)001:5330: bdud yul bra ma lung du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5331: nam phyed nam gyi gung la ni //
NK126(cho)001:5332: dmu rdo zlum po ltag pa'i khungs su brgyab //
NK126(cho)001:5333: thang cig brgyal te de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5334: ra rnal kha tsha'i khang du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5335: than thag su phung long gi lus la thal //
NK126(cho)001:5336: mgo lus med par bsreg te de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5337: dkar la la thog kha ba byung ba las //
NK126(cho)001:5338: gom gar 'khrus pas 'chi bar phyin pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:5339: kha ba byung bas 'og sa kha thal te //
NK126(cho)001:5340: kha dbyugs chad de de'u 'chi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5341: dpal mo dpal 'bar dpal mtshor phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5342: shing gis lho mas srog la brgal ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:5343: nyin mtshan gsum du de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5344: bal yul ni bal mkhar du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5345: bswe yi lha mos srog la brgal nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5346: mngon du gtam byas gser phye byin nas btang //
NK126(cho)001:5347: nyin mtshan bzhi ru de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5348: khang dmar khang sngon sgang du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5349: phyugs dred 'jigs pas mi sha za ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:5350: lce spyang mang pos sbubs su bcug nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5351: srog kyang de'u chad rdul du de'u btang byas //
NK126(cho)001:5352: tsha ba rang gshog gnod sbyin gtum po'i sar //
NK126(cho)001:5353: mi 'dug dbang med nub cig 'dug pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5354: gnod sbyin sha rjen rlon par za ba yis //
NK126(cho)001:5355: srog 'di de'u bcad de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5356: shing 'phrang chu 'phrang 'jigs skrag skyi bung sar //
NK126(cho)001:5357: mtshal bu bya gdong sha nas gser phye ras la shi //
NK126(cho)001:5358: rkang phran mang po'i tshogs 'dus mchu ring gis //
NK126(cho)001:5359: srog 'di bcad de de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5360: bdud 'phrang mi mi rgyur ni phye ma la //
NK126(cho)001:5361: lam bdud sngon po rta pa rkya drug la //
NK126(cho)001:5362: blu ba'i barngana pa chu gtor sna tshogs btang //
NK126(cho)001:5363: lam bdud chen pos srog 'di de'u bcad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5364: rnga mang tshul bsdong bgegs 'phrang chen po der //
NK126(cho)001:5365: mi rgod 'phrang bsrungs dka' brda mi 'jal bas //
NK126(cho)001:5366: 'og mi'i ral gri'i lus po kun btsab nas //
NK126(cho)001:5367: mgo bo pa tras gril la brdungs te de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5368: ma ga ta yi lcags 'phrang chen po der //
NK126(cho)001:5369: mi 'gro dbang med bzur sa med phyir nas //
NK126(cho)001:5370: brda sprad dka' bas 'phrang bsrungs mi rnams gyis //
NK126(cho)001:5371: btsag bu'i nywa sog bkrol te de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5372: e sha ke sha'i yul du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5373: brda sprad dka' ba'i mod pa mang po yis //
NK126(cho)001:5374: zas la dug btab zas nyid dug sbyar te //
NK126(cho)001:5375: kha zas bzang po dug gi de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5376: kri ka kri shi'i yul du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5377: mtha' yi rtogs mi byung zhes zer nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5378: mon bu'i dbyugs pa'i char gyi de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5379: b+hi b+hi ri'i tshal du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5380: rgyal po'i chad pas zhag drug dong du bcug /
NK126(cho)001:5381: kha zas bral te sna zhom de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5382: mu ze'i rgyal mtsho brgal bar dka' ba la //
NK126(cho)001:5383: gzhan ni sgrol med ras la gru byas pas //
NK126(cho)001:5384: 'chi bar nges pa'i mu za'i rgya mtsho las //
NK126(cho)001:5385: nyi zhag gsum du thar te de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5386: mar tsa'i lcags 'phrang chen por thar dka' der //
NK126(cho)001:5387: mi 'gro dbang med bdag gis der phyin pas //
NK126(cho)001:5388: brda 'phrad dka' ba'i 'phrang bsrungs mang po yis //
NK126(cho)001:5389: sbal dong bcug nas de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5390: ar+ya pa lo'i gling du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5391: bswe 'bag lcags 'bag 'jigs su rung ba yis //
NK126(cho)001:5392: thang cig brgyal bar byas te de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5393: 'bur 'ob 'ub tu thang la phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5394: bye ma mkhar lding sa la bab pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)001:5395: 'og tu tshud de de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5396: kir gling kri sna'i yul du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5397: gser sbrul gdug pas brdas te de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5398: be ra ha yi yul du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5399: g.yu sbrul sngon pos lag pa bzung ste de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5400: ke ke'u sham dkar phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5401: sgyu ma'i sbyor sngags mkhan gyis sngags btab ste //
NK126(cho)001:5402: nyin mtshan gsum du mi la phag pa byas //
NK126(cho)001:5403: su sha su ma'i gling du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5404: phag rgod stag 'dra 'jigs su rung ba yis //
NK126(cho)001:5405: lus kyi gos gshags de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5406: sur le sur me deb sha 'bar ba las //
NK126(cho)001:5407: nag khung dam dregs 'jigs 'jigs lta ba yis //
NK126(cho)001:5408: skrag cing dngangs par ded de de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5409: khung bu mtsho 'dra lta mi phod pa'i sar //
NK126(cho)001:5410: mgo bcug ltas pas de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5411: bdud 'dul sngags pa'i gling du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5412: 'jam dpal sku sprul bud med lo brgyad pas //
NK126(cho)001:5413: bum pa'i chu skur ces pas spyod byas te //
NK126(cho)001:5414: bum pa'i sngags sbyor drag pos de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5415: sh+ri sing ha pra bar ta dang mjal ba las //
NK126(cho)001:5416: ngan sngags sbyor sngags drag pos de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5417: rdo rje gdan gyi 'og nas man ngag nyi shu rnyed pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5418: gnod sbyin gsang ba rgyal gyi 'gram pa la //
NK126(cho)001:5419: lag pas thal lcags brgyab nas brgyal bar byas //
NK126(cho)001:5420: de tshe kha dbugs chad de 'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5421: sa la lung bstan man ngag der rnyed nas //
NK126(cho)001:5422: bod kyi yul du yang bar gzas pa 'das //
NK126(cho)001:5423: rkang mgyogs tsakra ke ru la sogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:5424: lus po rdul du de'u btang de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5425: ba ta hor gyi yul du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5426: ta la'i lo mar bris pa'i byang sems lnga //
NK126(cho)001:5427: rgyal khams phung ba'i ngan sngags yin zer ba'i //
NK126(cho)001:5428: 'phrog ste 'od tshal brgyab nas de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5429: hor dge b+ha cha'i yul du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5430: ho dge rgyal po b+ha ta ku ti yis //
NK126(cho)001:5431: rgya gar yul gyi dam sri man ngag ston zer nas //
NK126(cho)001:5432: shig gis dong du zhag gsum de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5433: bal yul yang le shod du 'ong ba las //
NK126(cho)001:5434: srin bu pad+mas lus kyi khrag 'jib nas //
NK126(cho)001:5435: sha lpags bye nas de'u shi de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5436: bal yul ku ka ta ru phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)001:5437: tshad pa'i rgyal po zla ba phyed zin nas //
NK126(cho)001:5438: ga pur ka ras lus gsos de'u shi byas //
NK126(cho)001:5439: chu bar shing kun tras gdang brgyad cu la //
NK126(cho)001:5440: thar pa'i dus med zhag gsum bar du sbyong //
NK126(cho)001:5441: kha ru phyin pas kha dbugs de'u chad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5442: ba la'i rnag khung nang nas 'ong ba las //
NK126(cho)001:5443: dam dregs stag sogs gdug pa mang po yis //
NK126(cho)001:5444: brang gnyer lus bsgrib mche brdar de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5445: dpal thang 'gram du bswe mos gtses nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:5446: ser ba drag po phog nas de'u bsad byas //
NK126(cho)001:5447: de tshe bstan pa bsrungs bar mos kyang khas blangs te //
NK126(cho)001:5448: shi las de'u thang lnga bcu rtsa bdun byas //
NK126(cho)001:5449: rin chen sdong pos man ngag tshol bar dka' ba de tsam byas //
NK126(cho)001:5450: tsha ba'i yul du spyugs pas sdig re che //
NK126(cho)001:5452: blon po ngam ta ra klu gang na re /
NK126(cho)001:5453: nga la sdig mi sdig med kyis zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:5454: rgyal blon gzhan rnams ngo smad mdzad nas lan ma byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:5455: yang b+aee ro tsa nas rje 'bangs la skyeng cig 'ong bar re nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5457: b+aee ro tsa na'i lus la dgos dgu tshang lags na //
NK126(cho)001:5458: mi zan rta tshas tshol ba'i tshe spun po b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5459: 'du ba'i nad kyis mi tshug 'tsho byed sman dpyad b+aee ro bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5460: bkres skom lto brgyab gnyis kyis mi 'jigs nor rgyun
NK126(cho)001:5461: 'tsho ba zas mod b+aee ro tsa na bdag la
NK126(cho)001:5462: mchis // dug lnga dug gsum spangs ba'i nyan thos 'dul khrims b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5463: lam lnga sa bcu bsgrod pa'i dbu ma sems tsam b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5464: phyir rgol mu stegs sun 'byin sgra tshad rnam gnyis b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5465: 'gal ba cham la pheb pa'i ma gshin phur gsum b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5466: nus pa bskyed cing sgrib sbyangs tshogs rdzogs bsgrub pa rnam gsum b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5467: mchog dang thun mong gnyis kyi bsgrub pa zhi khro rnam gnyis b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5468: sangs rgyas lag tu gtod pa'i rdzogs pa chen po b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5469: dgos dgu lus la tshang ba'i b+aee ro tsa na spyugs rgyu min //
NK126(cho)001:5470: rog la gzhung ngan gnyen la mna' chung rje la snying ring byed pa gsum ni spyugs rgyu yin //
NK126(cho)001:5471: ces gsungs pa skyed ma byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:5472: yang b+aee ro tsa nas blon po rnams la skyeng
NK126(cho)001:5473: yang bar re nas rgyal po dam brdar ba'i tshul
NK126(cho)001:5476: dam pa dgu yi glu cig len //
NK126(cho)001:5477: pha yi dam pa rdo rje slob dpon yin //
NK126(cho)001:5478: pha gzhan 'khor ba'i rgyab non lags pas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5479: ma yi dam pa shes rab gsal ba lags //
NK126(cho)001:5480: ma gzhan phal pa 'khrul pa'i lam sna lags pas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5481: bu yi dam pa snod ldan slob bu la //
NK126(cho)001:5482: rnam rtog bu tsha 'khrul snang lags pas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5483: bsgom pa'i dam pa cir yang dmigs su med pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:5484: mtshan bcas kyi bsgom pa rtog par gda' ba mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5485: lta ba'i dam pa phyogs med rang shar yin //
NK126(cho)001:5486: phyogs 'dzin gyi lta ba 'di 'khor ba'i sa bon lags pas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5487: lta ba'i dam pa sems nyid rtogs pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:5488: zhi khro'i sangs rgyas yid smon du gda' bas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5489: mthu yi dam pa ma gshin phur gsum lags //
NK126(cho)001:5490: ngan sngags kyi mthu 'di srog mkhan sdig pa'i rgyu //
NK126(cho)001:5491: dmyal bar 'gro bas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5492: nor gyi dam pa 'phags pa'i nor bdun lags //
NK126(cho)001:5493: zang zing sgyu ma'i nor 'di bslu brid du gda' bas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5494: rgyan gyi dam pa mkhas pa'i yon tan lags //
NK126(cho)001:5495: lus sgog gi rgyan 'di rdzun dang 'dra bas mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5496: 'dul zhing gi dam pa chos nyid dbyings nyid lags //
NK126(cho)001:5497: 'gro drug gi 'dul zhing 'khor ba'i dra ba lags par mkhyen lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:5498: zhes pas mgur bzhengs pa yang skyed ma byung /
NK126(cho)001:5499: yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgyal po la mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5501: rje blon 'bangs gsum tshul gson dang //
NK126(cho)001:5502: rje yi bka' lung khri gdugs lta bu mi nyan par //
NK126(cho)001:5503: tshed med mtha' ma'i gtam la dam par 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:5505: nges don ma nor ston pa'i b+aee ro tsa na mtha' ru spyugs //
NK126(cho)001:5506: lus sems bsregs pa'i blon po phug tu bzhag /'o skol rje 'bangs 'di rnams ni ngan 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:5507: 'di phyir gnyis kar phan pa'i dam chos spangs //
NK126(cho)001:5508: bdag gzhan gnyis ka phung ba'i mtha' mis dbyen la 'dud //
NK126(cho)001:5511: yang tshe spangs ma dmar brgyal ma la b+aee ro tsa nas 'khang ba'i mgur 'di bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5512: skye ba phyi ma mi len ba'i b+aee ro tsa na bdag /
NK126(cho)001:5513: bod kyi rgyal khams smin par bya dgongs nas //
NK126(cho)001:5514: 'bru sna lnga 'khrungs gtsang pos rib ma byas //
NK126(cho)001:5515: dgos dgu rang las byung ba'i bod yul dang //
NK126(cho)001:5516: btsal bas mi rnyed drin chen pha ma dang //
NK126(cho)001:5517: sha rus drung pos 'brel pa'i gnyen bzhi dang //
NK126(cho)001:5518: rtse cig las kyi 'brel pa'i phur khyim gnyen 'dun rnams //
NK126(cho)001:5519: bco lnga lon nas lnga bcu rtsa bdun bar //
NK126(cho)001:5520: bod khams smin par bya phyir dka' las ci tsam byas //
NK126(cho)001:5521: jo mo yab yum thugs la mnga' lags ste //
NK126(cho)001:5522: sku tshe ring thung 'bras bu thob pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:5523: gtsug lags smin par bgyid pa'i b+aee ro tsa na bdag la mchis lags te //
NK126(cho)001:5524: bod la ngan pa'i blon po klu gang gis //
NK126(cho)001:5525: bka' mchid ram 'degs bgyid pa jo mo nyid la 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:5526: byams pa snying ring gang zhig byed pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:5527: dkon mchog khur zhing gnyen par mi byed par //
NK126(cho)001:5528: ngan song gsum las gzhan du 'gro mi 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:5529: skad 'gyur mkhas pas bsgyur ba'i bka' dag gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:5530: thar bar dka' ba'i brag ri'i ra bar chud //
NK126(cho)001:5531: thabs la mkhas pa'i spre'u mi phyungs nas //
NK126(cho)001:5532: byams la snying ring byas pa jo mos gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:5533: lo brgya 'dug kyang skyo ngal mi bya zhing //
NK126(cho)001:5534: 'di dang phyi ma gnyis su 'grogs dgos nas //
NK126(cho)001:5535: tshig gi bkrir gtub bud med rang bzhin yang //
NK126(cho)001:5536: sngar bshad chos kyi nyes dmigs mi gnas jo mo nyid la 'khong //
NK126(cho)001:5537: cho rigs che zhing gang ma rnams la ni //
NK126(cho)001:5538: bsnyen bkur rim gro kun la che //
NK126(cho)001:5539: las su bya ba rnam pa bzhi zhig yod //
NK126(cho)001:5540: mi chos gzhung bzang chad la btsan pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:5541: lam la ma rmongs dam tshig bsrung ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:5542: dkon mchog gnas shing ru la bkur sti che ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:5543: gnyer gtad dam du byed pa'i gzhung lugs ni //
NK126(cho)001:5544: che btsan gung ma rnams kyang gdung zhing brtsigs lags te //
NK126(cho)001:5545: gang yang sten du ma pheb jo mo nyid la 'khong //
NK126(cho)001:5546: dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes mig ci tsam pa //
NK126(cho)001:5547: zhal nas gsungs pa'i nges don mtha' dag gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:5548: glang po rab 'bog rgyud dag dang //
NK126(cho)001:5549: mdo sde 'dul ba dag las ni //
NK126(cho)001:5550: stong gsum sems can dus gcig bsad pa bas //
NK126(cho)001:5551: rtsa ba brgyad kyi dam tshig las //
NK126(cho)001:5552: yan lag dam tshig gcig nyams pa //
NK126(cho)001:5553: de ni sdig sgrib shin tu che //
NK126(cho)001:5554: rig pa bsgrang zhing dpag las 'das //
NK126(cho)001:5555: dam tshig nyams pa'i rnam smin ni //
NK126(cho)001:5556: mdze dang shu ba long ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:5557: 'bras dang phol mig sna tshogs dang //
NK126(cho)001:5558: yang na ma yis bu bsad bu yis ma bsad la sogs mtshon grir shi ba 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:5559: de yang lo 'dab tsam chag 'di la smin pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:5560: rtsa ba sdong po tsam cig phyi ma dag la smin //
NK126(cho)001:5561: dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes dmig ci tsam pa //
NK126(cho)001:5562: glang po rab 'bog rgyud dag dang //
NK126(cho)001:5563: 'dul ba rnam dag rgyud nas gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:5565: tshe spangs za dmar rgyal gyis b+aee ro tsa na la lan btab pa /
NK126(cho)001:5566: rje cig jo mo bdag gi mchid 'di gsol //
NK126(cho)001:5567: bco lnga lon nas nyi shu rtsa gcig bar //
NK126(cho)001:5568: pha ma rnyed par dka' sla ci tsam pas //
NK126(cho)001:5569: nung bung chung chun chad g.yar tshod che //
NK126(cho)001:5570: dka' las grangs las 'das pa de lags kyang //
NK126(cho)001:5571: bod kyi rgyal khams phung du tho ba yi //
NK126(cho)001:5572: mtha' yi mon tsha khri srong lde'u btsan dang //
NK126(cho)001:5573: 'bangs kyi yang gang dam ra klu gang dang //
NK126(cho)001:5574: bod kyi nyi ma spyugs pa snying re rje //
NK126(cho)001:5575: zhes dmar rgyan gyi bshums pas /
NK126(cho)001:5576: yang b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:5577: jo mos bka' gros gang du mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:5579: jo mo dmar rgyan mas na re /
NK126(cho)001:5580: mkhas pa chen pos ci mi gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:5581: pha dang mnyam pa'i bu gsum la //
NK126(cho)001:5583: bud med rang bzhin chags pa che //
NK126(cho)001:5584: 'di la brjed pa'i dus ma mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5586: b+aee ro tsa nas rgyal po'i snyan du thos par bya ba'i phyir mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5587: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa na la //
NK126(cho)001:5589: bsad pas sdig tu yang ma mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5590: chos nyid rgya mtsho lta bu'i gting rtogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:5591: sgyu ma'i nor gyi ci bgyis mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5592: snang srid thams cad gzhal yas las //
NK126(cho)001:5593: bdag 'dzin yul gyi ci bgyir mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5594: dkon mchog gsum gyi pha yod pas //
NK126(cho)001:5595: bdag 'dzin 'khrul pa'i pha mas ci bgyir mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5596: 'byung ba lnga yi gnyen yod pas //
NK126(cho)001:5597: bdag 'dzin 'khrul pa'i gnyen gyi ci bgyir mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5598: bstan pa bsrung ba'i sngags yod pas //
NK126(cho)001:5599: dgra dang bgegs kyi ci bgyir mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5601: rgyal mo tsha ba rong du gshegs pa'i grab la chas te /
NK126(cho)001:5602: der b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs pa'i gros byed dus su /
NK126(cho)001:5603: sna bo che bya ba'i rgyal po cig byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:5604: b+aee ro tsa na gar gshegs byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:5605: blon po ngam ta ra klu gang gis b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i rong du spyugs byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:5606: sna bo che yi rgyal pos rje khri srong lde'u btsan la zhes phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:5608: snyun dam pa rje lha cig khyed /
NK126(cho)001:5609: b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs na bod kyi nyi ma ma nub lags gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5611: rje khri srong lde'u btsan gyis blon po rnams la mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5612: bka' rtse cig las kyi 'brel pa'i phyi blon nang blon rnams //
NK126(cho)001:5613: mtha' mi skad rig mi cig pa dang 'phrad na yang //
NK126(cho)001:5614: b+aee ro spyugs na bod kyi nyi ma nub par sgrogs pa na //
NK126(cho)001:5615: dgos dgu phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag po 'di //
NK126(cho)001:5616: bod kyi yul du mchis pa mchis grogs gsol //
NK126(cho)001:5617: zhes gsungs nas spyan chab phyungs nas bshums pas /
NK126(cho)001:5618: blon po rnams kyis gros nas /
NK126(cho)001:5619: b+aee ro tsa na ma spyugs na mthu dang ngan
NK126(cho)001:5620: sngags 'phel gyi dogs nas mi bzhag par b+aee ro
NK126(cho)001:5621: tsa na rgyal mo tsha ba rong du spyugs par
NK126(cho)001:5623: de blon ngam ta ra klu gang gi rje'i len du 'bangs kyi mchid glu blangs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5625: rje 'bangs kun la dgos pa'i srid kyi mkhar //
NK126(cho)001:5626: rje'i mnga' thang bskyed pa blon po yin //
NK126(cho)001:5627: 'bangs kyis mchid glings rje yis gsan par ring //
NK126(cho)001:5628: mi gsan zer na yon mchod gnyis ka 'gum //
NK126(cho)001:5630: rje kha blon la chibs kha srab du sang nas
NK126(cho)001:5631: b+aee ro tsa na cis kyang rgyal mo tsha ba'i
NK126(cho)001:5632: rong du spyugs par byas so //
NK126(cho)001:5633: de nas yang b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5634: kyee rje blon rim gyi gsan lags dang //
NK126(cho)001:5635: b+aee ro tsa na gsang sngags chos la mkhas //
NK126(cho)001:5636: gsang sngags rang bzhin ur mo'i btsa'/
NK126(cho)001:5639: 'di nas ma dpe la chad snyam /
NK126(cho)001:5640: des na b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i rang du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5641: bod la dka' las che bas brtson 'grus can //
NK126(cho)001:5642: tsha ba'i yul mi chos la 'dzud du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5643: bod la lus ngag btsun pa'i b+aee ro tsa na bdag /
NK126(cho)001:5644: tsha ba'i yul du 'dul khrims bsrungs su mchis //
NK126(cho)001:5645: mthong dgu lag gis shes pa'i b+aee ro tsa na bdag /
NK126(cho)001:5646: tsha ba'i yul du bzod sna slob du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5647: mtha' yi skad bslab skad 'gyur sum brgya drug cu shes //
NK126(cho)001:5648: tsha ba'i yul du skad 'gyur slob du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5649: man ngag bstan pa tsam gyi sangs rgyas lag 'chang ba //
NK126(cho)001:5650: tsha ba'i yul du man ngag ston du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5651: 'gal ba 'cham la phab pa'i bstan bsrung ni //
NK126(cho)001:5652: tsha ba'i yul du bstan pa bsrung du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5653: sde snod bstan bcos drangs don mtha' dag shes //
NK126(cho)001:5654: tsha ba'i yul du mi nag 'dren du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5655: steng na gnas pa'i lha dang lha ma yin //
NK126(cho)001:5656: b+aee ro tsa na bdag dang zhal yang mjal //
NK126(cho)001:5657: 'og na gnas pa'i lha klu rnams //
NK126(cho)001:5658: b+aee ro tsa na bdag dang zhal yang mjal //
NK126(cho)001:5660: lha la sogs pa lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi /
NK126(cho)001:5661: b+aee ro tsa na la sku dngos bstan nas bskor ba dang phyag byas te /
NK126(cho)001:5662: b+aee ro tsa na'i bka' nyan par dam bcas so //
NK126(cho)001:5663: de nas b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul du gshegs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:5664: btsad pos ga pur bre re bsil sman du bardzongasa
NK126(cho)001:5665: nas bza' yang drangs te slob dpon tsha ba'i yul
NK126(cho)001:5666: du gshegs par zhu phul bas /
NK126(cho)001:5667: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:5668: bdag ni tshe snga ma yang rgyal mo tsha ba
NK126(cho)001:5669: rong gi dge slong pur+na bya ba tshe 'phos pa
NK126(cho)001:5670: yin pas / da yang man ngag gi chos 'di
NK126(cho)001:5671: rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du dus la bab pa
NK126(cho)001:5672: kho na 'dra yi gsungs nas tsha ba'i yul du
NK126(cho)001:5674: der rgyal po rje 'bangs bdun dang /
NK126(cho)001:5675: dge 'dun sde gnyis kyi rgya dang bod kyi sa
NK126(cho)001:5676: mtshams ma la la khar bskyal nas phyag dang bskor
NK126(cho)001:5677: ba byas so // de nas b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5678: b+aee ro tsa na gser gyi khye'u chung 'di //
NK126(cho)001:5679: 'chi bar nges pa'i tsha ba rong du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:5680: klu gang nyi shu rtsa gcig nas 'das te //
NK126(cho)001:5681: ban rgan spyugs pas nyes de gcig /
NK126(cho)001:5682: rgyal po lo skor gcig nas 'das te //
NK126(cho)001:5683: ban rgan spyugs pas nyes de gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:5684: blon po klu gang drin gyis bod khams sil bur 'gro ste //
NK126(cho)001:5685: ban rgan spyugs pas nyes te gsum //
NK126(cho)001:5687: khab tshe ya za dmar rgyan ma //
NK126(cho)001:5688: rgyal po gnyis la 'kheng rgyal du smras pa /
NK126(cho)001:5689: b+aee ro tsa na la mos pa'i tshul bstan /
NK126(cho)001:5690: wa bod la mi med blon po klu gang byed //
NK126(cho)001:5691: bod khams phung du tho bas btsad po snyan khungs srab //
NK126(cho)001:5692: dam tshig nyams bsnyo ba'i dmar rgyan wa bdag 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5693: bod kyi mkhas pa b+aee ro tsa na bzhugs su gsol //
NK126(cho)001:5695: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas mgur 'di skad bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5696: rgyal po na ka che ste yar le shom po 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5697: blon po gdug pa che ste btsan dug khol ma 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5698: btsun mo gyong khengs che ste gyang khang khyi mtshong 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5699: stag shar sgrin la mnog chung pho rog khras ded 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5700: chab srid dar la yun thung dbyar gyi phug chu blug pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5701: bstan bcos klog bshad byas pa byis pa'i klog 'khon 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5702: sngags pa grong bsnyen byas pa gyer bon rnga thog 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5703: dam nyams tshogs dpon byas pa khrag gi khrag bkru 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5704: lo tsh+aa rang mthang skyes pa sngags bshad brag cha 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5705: 'dra ba mang po'i gseb tu b+aee ro tsa na sdod re kan //
NK126(cho)001:5706: de nas btsad po thugs ma ches pas zhabs spyi gtsug tu bzhag nas phyag 'tshal te /
NK126(cho)001:5708: da yang jug bya gsung te bshums pas /
NK126(cho)001:5710: chos nyid bsam du med pa'i don la longs spyod kyang //
NK126(cho)001:5711: 'dus byas kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba rgyun ma bcad par mdzod ces gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:5712: de nas b+aee ro tsa na btsad po rje 'bangs
NK126(cho)001:5713: dang dge 'dun sde gnyis kyis rgya dang bod kyis
NK126(cho)001:5714: mtshams sma la la khar bskyal bas /
NK126(cho)001:5716: bod yul na yar la gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:5717: sa cha bsil la nyams dga' ba /
NK126(cho)001:5718: ri thams cad bya rgod spungs pa 'dra ba /
NK126(cho)001:5719: tha ma gangs kyis bskor ba mi rje lhas mdzad pa /
NK126(cho)001:5720: shin tu sa cha bsil la nyams dga' bar 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:5721: tsha ba rong du mar la gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:5722: tsha ba'i lung pa de rtsub pa /
NK126(cho)001:5724: 'dam khol ma lta bu nag ting nge 'dug par gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:5725: dgongs pa sangs rgyas dang mnyam yang /
NK126(cho)001:5726: sku sems can du bzhugs pas /
NK126(cho)001:5728: dge 'dun sde gnyis la bshums shing mgur 'di gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5729: ri mtho gangs gtsangs spu rgyal bod kyi yul //
NK126(cho)001:5730: brda sprad skad snyan sku rgyal gyi mi //
NK126(cho)001:5731: mi rje lhas mdzad dpag bsam ljon shing 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:5732: dgos dgu yid bzhin nor bu kun tshang ba //
NK126(cho)001:5733: de 'dra'i rin chen mtsho yi rang khyu nas //
NK126(cho)001:5734: ngang mo gcig cig yar ba glo ba dbyar lag cag /
NK126(cho)001:5735: de skad gsungs nas spyan chab phyung bas /
NK126(cho)001:5736: rgyal po rje 'bangs dge 'dun sde gnyis kyang bshums so //
NK126(cho)001:5737: yang thugs bsnyung ba de bsang bar bya ba'i phyir du mgur 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:5738: yul la nges pa med pas spyugs kyang nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:5739: sems la skye shi med pas bsad kyang nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:5740: gnyen la dang ma chags pas dgra la zhe mi sdang //
NK126(cho)001:5741: dgra la zhe mi sdong bas gnyan la dang mi chags //
NK126(cho)001:5742: yon tan sgyu mar 'dug pas skyon la dngos gzhi med //
NK126(cho)001:5743: ma bshums lus la gnad lags de bas bstan chos 'di gson /
NK126(cho)001:5745: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas rgya'i ri bo rtse lnga la zhal gzigs te /
NK126(cho)001:5746: spyan nam mkha' la gzigs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5747: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:5749: lar 'o skol khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad la /
NK126(cho)001:5750: thar med 'khor ba'i btsan rar dmar po ni zhugs /
NK126(cho)001:5751: bdag tu lta ba'i mdud pa dam pos ni bcings /
NK126(cho)001:5752: log rtog gzung 'dzin gyi brag gis lcags su ni bsdom /
NK126(cho)001:5753: g.yang sa ngan song gsum gyi dong ni ltung /
NK126(cho)001:5754: skye rgas na 'chi'i chu bo chen po bzhi'i 'obs su ni tshud /
NK126(cho)001:5755: ye shes sgron ma 'bar ba'i mthong ka ni bka'/
NK126(cho)001:5756: thar pa byang chub kyi lam skas ni chad /
NK126(cho)001:5757: 'dren mdzad thugs rje'i zhags pa'i spyang thag ni chad nas gda' ba gzigs sam /
NK126(cho)001:5758: lar 'o skol khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad la /
NK126(cho)001:5759: gti mug gi dug phag nag po ni phug nas mkhun /
NK126(cho)001:5760: zhe sdang gi dug sbrul sngon po ni rked la 'khril /
NK126(cho)001:5761: 'dod chags kyi srin bu mchu dmar ni sngon nas rgod /
NK126(cho)001:5762: nga rgyal gyi glang bu rog po ni phug nas rwa brdar /
NK126(cho)001:5763: phrag dog gi khyi rgan rgya bo ni rang la rang za bar gda' ba 'di gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5764: lar 'o skol skye ba'i sgo ni bdud kyi stobs
NK126(cho)001:5765: kyis kyang mi kheg /'chi ba'i lam bde bar gshegs
NK126(cho)001:5766: pa'i thugs rje kyang mi ldog /
NK126(cho)001:5767: las kyi rnam par smin pa'i nad ni 'tsho byed gzhon nus kyang mi sos /
NK126(cho)001:5768: rgas par gyur pa ni lcags kyi gtod phur la gnan yang mi thub /
NK126(cho)001:5769: dgra sdong ba dang 'phrad dog pa ni bye'u chung khras nyan pa dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5770: gnyan byams pa dang bral gyi dog pa'i sdug bsngal ni rnga mang bu stor ba dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5771: med pa btsal gyi mi rnyed pa'i sdug bsngal ni yi dwags kha skom pa dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5772: yod pa brtsa'i mi thub pa'i sdang gi mi mched /
NK126(cho)001:5773: mo mtshar ba la bsam pa ni 'dod chags kyi chu blugs /
NK126(cho)001:5774: rang gi yon tan la bsam pa ni nga rgyal gyi ra skyes /
NK126(cho)001:5775: gzhan gyi yon tan la bsam pa ni phrag dog gi rlung 'tshub /
NK126(cho)001:5776: rang la longs spyod la bsam pa ni ser sna'i rtsa ba dam /
NK126(cho)001:5777: gzhan gyi longs spyod la bsam pa ni gnod sems
NK126(cho)001:5778: kyi lag g.yab yin par gda' ba gzigs lags sam
NK126(cho)001:5779: / lar 'o skol dregs pa can lha yi bu'i bdud kyis zil gyis mnan /
NK126(cho)001:5780: nyams nga ba sdug bsngal gyi phung po'i bdud kyis gzir te nyon mongs /
NK126(cho)001:5781: 'chi bdag mi rtag pa'i bdud srog gcod de tshe thung /
NK126(cho)001:5782: ma rig pa nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyis don bsgrib ste lam gol nas gda' ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5783: zhe sdang gi rgyu las bsad bcad kyi rkyen gyis
NK126(cho)001:5784: smin pa'i sems can dmyal ba ni tsha grang gi
NK126(cho)001:5785: sdug bsngal / ser sna yi rgyu las rku phrog
NK126(cho)001:5786: gi rgyu rkyen gyis smin pa'i sems can yi dwags
