NK126(cho)001:5787: sdug bsngal / kyi bkres skom / gti mug gi
NK126(cho)001:5788: rgyu la bkol spyod kyi rkyen gyis smin pa'i byol
NK126(cho)001:5789: song gi gnas 'pho yin sdug bsngal /
NK126(cho)001:5790: nga rgyal gyis rgyu las 'thab rtsod kyis rkyen gyis smin pa'i lha ma yin 'thab cing rtsod /
NK126(cho)001:5791: dge sems kyi rgyu las smon lam gyi rkyen gyis
NK126(cho)001:5792: smin pa'i lha dang mi ni rang yang sdug bsngal
NK126(cho)001:5793: gyi gda' ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5796: dge 'dun gsum ni ltag skra bzhin du rgyab tu bor /
NK126(cho)001:5797: bdud dang mu stegs bon po gsum ni gces phrug bzhin du dpang du blangs /
NK126(cho)001:5798: sdom pa dang dam tshig 'dul khrims gsum ni rdo bzhin blangs nas 'phen /
NK126(cho)001:5799: 'dod chags dang zhe sdang gti mug gsum ni bsrung ba'i sman bzhin lus la bcangs /
NK126(cho)001:5800: pha dang ma dang bla ma gsum ni khyi rgan bzhin du sgo ru bton /
NK126(cho)001:5801: rgas pa dang na ba 'chi ba gsum ni grib so bzhin du shul nas rnyog /
NK126(cho)001:5802: dmyal ba dang yi dwags byol song gsum ni bsgug
NK126(cho)001:5803: pa bzhin du sngun nas sdod kyin gda' ba gzigs
NK126(cho)001:5804: lags sam / lar 'o skol gyis gzugs kyi phung po ni lam ka'i bye'u tshangs dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5805: tshe srog gi zug rngu ni bye'u phrug sha rje dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5806: 'chi bdag gi bdud ni bye'u khra hor pa dang 'dra bar gda' ba mkhyen lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5807: lar 'o skol gyi gzugs kyi phung po ni rgya mtsho skam pa dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5808: tshe srog gi zug rngu ni sbrul gyi phung dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5809: 'chi bdag gi bdud nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po dang 'dra ba ma gzigs sam /
NK126(cho)001:5810: lar 'o skol gyi gzugs kyi phung po ni da ra kha yod pa dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5811: tshe srog gi zug rngu ni lu gu tshe ru dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5812: tshe bdag gi bdud ni lcags kyi spyang ku sngon po dang 'dra ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5813: lar 'o skol sangs rgyas la ma brten par skyabs su la brten /
NK126(cho)001:5814: bla ma mi khur bar gang na rten ci yod /
NK126(cho)001:5815: chos la mi spyod par blo gang gi bde /
NK126(cho)001:5816: dge 'dun mi mchod par su la ltos /
NK126(cho)001:5817: mched grogs dang mi 'grogs par su dang lab /
NK126(cho)001:5818: sdom pa mi bsrung bar su la re /
NK126(cho)001:5819: sbyin pa mi btang bar su la spyol /
NK126(cho)001:5820: 'khor ba la mi skyo bar ngang re ring /
NK126(cho)001:5821: bdud kyi mi 'jigs pa tshen re che /
NK126(cho)001:5822: shi yi mi dogs par blo re bde /
NK126(cho)001:5823: rgas pa mi tsher bar gzu re btul /
NK126(cho)001:5824: 'chi nad rjed pa yi re nge /
NK126(cho)001:5825: sdig spyod dam tshig nyams pa blo re nyes gda' ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5826: lar 'o skol sbyin pa'i gter ni ser sna'i rkun pos brkus /
NK126(cho)001:5827: tshul khrims kyi zam pa ni 'chal ba'i chus khyer /
NK126(cho)001:5828: bzod pa'i gos ni khong khro'i mes bsreg /
NK126(cho)001:5829: brtson 'grus kyi rta ni le lo'i sgrogs su bcug /
NK126(cho)001:5830: bsam gtan gyi zas ni g.yengs ba'i khyi rgan gyis barlama /
NK126(cho)001:5831: shes rab kyi ral gri ni rmongs pa'i tho bas bsnyal nas gda' ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5832: lar 'o skol byams pa tshad med pa ma lta bu ni spangs /
NK126(cho)001:5833: snying rje tshad med pa sring mo lta bu ni stor /
NK126(cho)001:5834: dga' ba tshad med pa bshes mo lta bu ni bor /
NK126(cho)001:5835: btang snyoms tshad med pa kun la snyoms pa rgyal
NK126(cho)001:5836: po lta bu bshol nas dga' ba gzigs lags sam
NK126(cho)001:5837: / lar 'o skol chos kyi sku cig ma thob na /
NK126(cho)001:5838: gzugs kyi phung po 'di chu bur dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5839: tshang pa'i gsungs cig ma thob na /
NK126(cho)001:5840: ngag gi sgra 'di brag cha dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5841: ye shes kyi thugs cig ma thob na /
NK126(cho)001:5842: rtogs pa'i yid 'di dug sbrul dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5843: theg chen gyi mkhar cig ma brtsegs na /
NK126(cho)001:5844: brtsegs pa'i mkhar 'di dri za'i grong khyer dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:5845: sangs rgyas kyi yul cig ma mthong na /
NK126(cho)001:5846: mtshan pa'i yul rmi lam dang 'dra ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5847: lar 'o skol srog gcod pa la ni spyang ku bas dga'/
NK126(cho)001:5848: mi gtsang spyod pa la ni bong bu bas kyang rem /
NK126(cho)001:5849: ma byin pa len pa la ni byi ba bas kyang gus /
NK126(cho)001:5850: rdzun du smra ba la ni wa bshor bas kyang gzod //
NK126(cho)001:5851: nyon mongs pa skyes pa'i cha mas ni rgyal 'gong bas kyang btul bar gda' ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5852: lar 'o skol chos pa kha cig gi chos ni dga' phyi'i zhal mtshan tsam /
NK126(cho)001:5853: chos pa kha cig gi chos 'di bu tsa'i skam stib tsam /
NK126(cho)001:5854: chos pa kha cig gi chos 'di 'phral gyi rkyen bzlog tsam /
NK126(cho)001:5855: chos pa kha gcig gi chos 'di khe drag tsam du gda' ba gzigs lags sam /
NK126(cho)001:5857: mos pa bdog na smon lam cig thob /
NK126(cho)001:5859: btsas pos bral ma phod de /
NK126(cho)001:5860: btsas pos bshums shing slob dpon gyi mthu ba la bzung zhing /
NK126(cho)001:5862: rgyal khrims rang zhig na'ang zhig /
NK126(cho)001:5863: bod khams sil bur song na'ang song gi /
NK126(cho)001:5864: slob dpon bod yul du slar ldog par 'tshal byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:5865: b+aee ro tsa nas mgur 'di skad bzhengs so //
NK126(cho)001:5866: ri gzar kha nas drag po'i sbab 'drel bas //
NK126(cho)001:5867: skyes pa stobs chen cig gi cang ldog gam //
NK126(cho)001:5868: 'a mo shi ba'i ste ri sngon chen 'di //
NK126(cho)001:5869: ba yar 'o mas cang sos sam //
NK126(cho)001:5870: rgya mtsho skom pa'i nya chen g.yor mo 'di //
NK126(cho)001:5871: sbrang char zam zim cig gi cang sos sam //
NK126(cho)001:5872: bod khams gting nas log pa'i b+aee ro tsa na 'di //
NK126(cho)001:5873: btsad po gang zag cig gi dad pas cung ldog gam //
NK126(cho)001:5875: phyi mig kyang mi lta bar bzhud do //
NK126(cho)001:5876: bod rong pa dang stengs lha /
NK126(cho)001:5878: bar lha srin kun gyis mchi ma shor /
NK126(cho)001:5879: kun gyi gdod pa dag dag tu ngus so //
NK126(cho)001:5880: der b+aee ro tsa nas brgyag phye ja khur du byas te mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:5881: dgos dgu lus la tshang ba'i b+aee ro tsa na bdag /'gro ni tsha ba'i rong du 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:5882: nub ni bod kyi nyi ma nub //
NK126(cho)001:5883: bod na gza' dang skar ma tsam yang med //
NK126(cho)001:5884: bod yul mun pa'i gling du gyur pa snying re tshim //
NK126(cho)001:5885: bstan pa tsha ba rong du shar //
NK126(cho)001:5886: tsha ba'i rong dang rgyal mo'i yul //
NK126(cho)001:5887: stong khams rang gi mi rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:5888: khri gdugs shar ro bkur sti dang //
NK126(cho)001:5889: rim gro ma chung zhig gsungs te se gol lan gsum brdab te /
NK126(cho)001:5890: bya lhag nam mkha' la 'phur ba ltar tsha ba'i rong du gshegs so //
NK126(cho)001:5892: bod na man ngag gi snod med nas b+aee ro
NK126(cho)001:5893: tsa na dgung lo drug cu rtsa gcig la tsha
NK126(cho)001:5894: ba'i rong du spyugs pa'i skabs te bcu bdun po'o
NK126(cho)001:5895: //// de nas de'i tshe de'i dus tsha ba'i rang
NK126(cho)001:5896: du lhen gyis bab b+aee ros ma phod de ri
NK126(cho)001:5898: der tsha ba rangs pa'i mis mthong nas /
NK126(cho)001:5899: rgyal mo dpal bzhes kyi sna drangs mi mang po
NK126(cho)001:5900: sbran nas bod kyi rtog chen po yin byas nas
NK126(cho)001:5902: dar b+aee ros nga rtog chen pa min /
NK126(cho)001:5903: bod kyi rgyal khams na rgyal po rgyu 'bras kyi chos la thugs ma ches nas /
NK126(cho)001:5904: khri srong lde'u btsan bya ba'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:5905: rgya gar yul na dang po ston pa sku 'khrungs /
NK126(cho)001:5907: tha ma sku mya ngan las de ru 'das pa yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:5908: de nas rgyu 'bras gnyis las 'das pa'i chos shig mi bzhugs mi srid gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5909: zung cig btang nas 'gro nus pa yod dam gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:5910: der nga dang gtsang legs grub bya ba gnyis kyis phyin nas /
NK126(cho)001:5911: legs grub gcan 'phrang dong po bas bsad /
NK126(cho)001:5912: bdag gi man ngag gi chos mang po slob dpon sh+ri sing ha bya ba la zhus nas /
NK126(cho)001:5914: rgya gar gyi chos skyong ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK126(cho)001:5915: pan+di tas phrag dog byas te /
NK126(cho)001:5916: bod du rgyal blon rnams la dbyen rnams phra ma skyel ba'i mi btang bas /
NK126(cho)001:5917: bod kyi ban+de 'dis rgyal pos chos tshol du btang ba'i man ngag gi chos ma rnyed /
NK126(cho)001:5918: rgya gar gyi khro chu phra men ma dang /
NK126(cho)001:5919: man ngag nyi tshe khyer nas song bas /
NK126(cho)001:5920: bod kyi rgyal blon rnams kyis bka' khrims chen po dang sbyor cig par bsgrags pas /
NK126(cho)001:5921: der blon po ngam ta ra klu gang bya bas
NK126(cho)001:5922: bod kyi ban+de 'dis man ngag gi chos tshol du
NK126(cho)001:5923: btang ba'i man ngag gi chos ni ma rnyed par
NK126(cho)001:5924: / ngan sngags nyi tshe ba khyer nas mchis pas /
NK126(cho)001:5925: 'di bas 'tshal rgyal po la yang yang zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:5926: rgyal po de tsug min b+aee ro tsa na sprul pa'i sku yin gsungs nas ma lo bar /
NK126(cho)001:5927: da spyugs pa yin byas nas lo rgyus bsnyad pas
NK126(cho)001:5928: ma lo bkyig te sbas pa'i don du bcug pas
NK126(cho)001:5929: / sdug bsngal de zhag gsum 'o dod chen po bos /
NK126(cho)001:5931: yul phyogs 'di ni bzhugs pa che btsun rnams //
NK126(cho)001:5932: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa na yi //
NK126(cho)001:5933: bco lnga lon nas lnga bcu rtsa bdun bar //
NK126(cho)001:5934: bod kyi rgya khams dkar por yang bsgyur phyir //
NK126(cho)001:5935: theg pa'i kha gcong 'bras bu sangs rgyas chos //
NK126(cho)001:5936: rgya gar mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gsum gyi //
NK126(cho)001:5937: bstan pa'i man ngag bod du mchis lags te //
NK126(cho)001:5938: rgyal khams phung du tho ba'i blon po klu gang dang //
NK126(cho)001:5939: dam tshig nyams las bsnyos pa'i tshe spangs dmar rgyal dang //
NK126(cho)001:5940: bod khams sil bur 'gro rtags btsad po bcos sla bas //
NK126(cho)001:5941: rgya gar sdug pa'i phra ma ngan pas snyan //
NK126(cho)001:5942: bod kyi nyi ma mkhas pa bdag spyugs te //
NK126(cho)001:5943: tshe 'dir 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag dang //
NK126(cho)001:5944: ma rig mun pa sel ba'i bsnyen bsgrub 'di //
NK126(cho)001:5945: rin chen phung po bstan 'chol sgyu ma dang //
NK126(cho)001:5946: 'tsho bar byed pa'i rin chen sman dpyad dang //
NK126(cho)001:5947: bod kyi ban chung lus la 'chis lags te //
NK126(cho)001:5948: 'jigs skrag sbal pa'i dong nas sbyangs su gsol //
NK126(cho)001:5949: g.yu sgra'i yab rin po che'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)001:5950: bod kyi mnga' bdag spu rgyal tshan chung des //
NK126(cho)001:5951: tshan de chung la las su bya ba mang //
NK126(cho)001:5952: chung ma len na go kha'i bran mo mkhan //
NK126(cho)001:5953: slon po byed na nyon mongs che dgus byed //
NK126(cho)001:5954: zas su za na sha chen sna dgu za //
NK126(cho)001:5955: gos su gyon na mtha' yi mon gos gyon //
NK126(cho)001:5956: nor du byed na rdo la nor du byed //
NK126(cho)001:5957: las su byed na rku dang dmag dpon byed //
NK126(cho)001:5958: lha ru mchod na gnod sbyin srin po mchod //
NK126(cho)001:5959: grogs po tshol na klu las gdug pa che ba med par tshol //
NK126(cho)001:5960: tho phyi'i mig la rkyang du mi ltos pas //
NK126(cho)001:5961: srin po gdong dmar rgyal po 'dod pa can //
NK126(cho)001:5962: glo ba ches rgyu ma mchis ban+de khyod lta bu //
NK126(cho)001:5963: blon po che btsun kun kyang ka bgyis pas //
NK126(cho)001:5965: sdig spyod rgyal po 'di la blo ba ches rgyu ma mchis te //
NK126(cho)001:5966: sbal pa'i dong nas thon nas shig gi dong du skyur //
NK126(cho)001:5967: dgu bdun bar du bod kyi dmag dpung ma byung na //
NK126(cho)001:5968: khyod kyis bka' stsal gtso bor bgyis la spyi bor bkur zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:5969: shig dong du bskur ba'i don du sbal dong nas thon nas b+aee ro tsa na bton pas /
NK126(cho)001:5970: lus la sbal pas mig man chod du 'jus nas byung bas /
NK126(cho)001:5971: b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad bshags pa byas te /
NK126(cho)001:5972: bdag ni b+aee ro tsa na ste //
NK126(cho)001:5973: skye ba 'di'i gang de yi snga ma la //
NK126(cho)001:5974: yul phyogs 'di yi 'dab chag ne'u ler skyes //
NK126(cho)001:5975: sbrul dang sbal pa zas su zos //
NK126(cho)001:5976: de yi rnam smin da lta byung //
NK126(cho)001:5977: lan chags de yi khengs gyur cig /
NK126(cho)001:5979: sbal pa thams cad lus las bog 'brul te /
NK126(cho)001:5980: so sor bros te song bas /
NK126(cho)001:5981: yang yang shig dong du bskyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:5982: der slob dpon gyi thugs la zhag gsum nas shig
NK126(cho)001:5983: dong nas 'don gyi zer bas de la dgongs nas
NK126(cho)001:5985: zhag bdun nas rgyal mo tsha ba'i yul pa kun tshogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:5986: da thon zer nas shig dong nas bton pas /
NK126(cho)001:5987: lus mgo zhabs la go mtshams med par shig gi 'jus nas byung bas /
NK126(cho)001:5988: yang b+aee ros shig la bshags pa byas te /
NK126(cho)001:5989: bdag ni b+aee ro tsa na ste //
NK126(cho)001:5990: skye ba 'di yi yang snga na //
NK126(cho)001:5992: dge slong pur+na bya bar skyes //
NK126(cho)001:5993: de tshe chos gos shig tshang byar thur bcug /
NK126(cho)001:5994: de yi rnam smin da lta byung //
NK126(cho)001:5997: shig rang sa so sor brul nas song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:5998: der dge slong pur+na'i bu dge slong gru bya bas /
NK126(cho)001:5999: sngon tsa na yab dge slong lha btsun p+aur+na bya ba de yin par ngo shes nas /
NK126(cho)001:6002: bu tsa rnams kyis kyang smras /
NK126(cho)001:6003: bdag cag gi yab mes brlag par gda' bas //
NK126(cho)001:6004: yab mes sprul pa'i sku ru byon pa la //
NK126(cho)001:6005: 'di lta bu'i sdug bsngal byas pa gsungs te ngus so //
NK126(cho)001:6006: yul ma'i tshogs chen po yang mchi ma shor ro //
NK126(cho)001:6007: der rgyal mo tsha ba'i yul pa rje 'bangs kun
NK126(cho)001:6008: kyang 'gyod pa skyes te bshags pa phul ba 'di
NK126(cho)001:6009: skad do // bod la mi med rgyal po 'dod pa can //
NK126(cho)001:6010: skye ba snga phyi shes pa'i byang chub sems dpa' khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6011: 'gro don khyad par 'phags pa bod yul mdzad dgongs nas //
NK126(cho)001:6012: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab tsha ba'i yul 'di gshegs //
NK126(cho)001:6013: sa bcu byang chub sems dpa' 'gro don mdzad pa khyed la 'dud //
NK126(cho)001:6014: spyo ba drag po byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK126(cho)001:6015: bzod par bzhes te thugs rje chen po khyed la mthol zhing bshags //
NK126(cho)001:6016: byams mgon ston pa khyed la bzod par phul //
NK126(cho)001:6018: de nas dris pas skyes bu khyed lta bu la spyugs pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:6019: sdug bsngal 'di lta bu myong ba rgyu rkyen gang lags byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6020: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:6021: skye ba bzhi pa sdom pa blang ba ste /
NK126(cho)001:6022: sdom pa ma thub nyams pa bya ne'u ler skyes /
NK126(cho)001:6023: sdom pa blang ba'i stobs kyi ne'u le ma smin chu la shi //
NK126(cho)001:6024: sdom pa las 'phro bzang bas mi ru skyes //
NK126(cho)001:6025: cho rigs btsun par skyes pas dge ba mang po spyod //
NK126(cho)001:6026: dge ba mang por bskyed pas rnams smin mi ru skyes //
NK126(cho)001:6027: de yi dus su 'dul khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu bsrungs //
NK126(cho)001:6028: nyis brgya lnga bcu thub par bsrungs bas mi ru skyes //
NK126(cho)001:6029: rdo rje sems dpa' dga' rab 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi //
NK126(cho)001:6030: yang dag ye shes thugs kyi gsang ba rdol //
NK126(cho)001:6031: tshe 'di nyid la skye med don rtogs te //
NK126(cho)001:6032: shes bya'i sgrib pa cha 'ga' ma dag pas //
NK126(cho)001:6033: de yi rkyen gyis tsha ba'i yul spyugs sdug bsngal byung ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:6034: skye med su rtogs da lta ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:6035: de la byis pa rnams ni sgro dang bskur pas btab //
NK126(cho)001:6037: yang mi nag yul mi kun la mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:6038: dpyid nyi ring po la gro gsum drang gsum 'ong /
NK126(cho)001:6039: nam zla ring po la 'grong gsum ltog gsum 'ong /
NK126(cho)001:6040: lam thag ring po la dkar gsum 'tsher gsum gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:6042: mi nag byis pa kun na re /
NK126(cho)001:6043: da rung gsungs dang zer ro //
NK126(cho)001:6044: yang gsungs pa ri po mtho gdugs kyi rgyal /
NK126(cho)001:6045: gdugs kyi rgyal te chabs kyi phab /
NK126(cho)001:6046: de la skyid sdug phyed mar gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:6047: btsan phyugs brtan po dang 'dra ste res mos su gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:6048: rong khung dog mor chab kyis rgyal /
NK126(cho)001:6049: chab kyi rgyal te gdugs kyi pham /
NK126(cho)001:6050: mi tshe kun gyi skyid sdug phyed mar gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:6051: btsan phyugs kun rmi lam dang 'dra'o //
NK126(cho)001:6052: bden nges de lha chos su gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:6054: yul gyi mi nag kun gyis lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:6056: kun gyis b+aee ro tsa na'i zhabs spyi bor blangs so //
NK126(cho)001:6058: a a tra tha ka pa le na ga /
NK126(cho)001:6060: rgyal mo yul gyi mi kun na re /
NK126(cho)001:6064: skye med byang sems bde chen man ngag 'di /
NK126(cho)001:6065: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po'i snyan gsan du /
NK126(cho)001:6066: bstan cing bsnyad pas ma go bdag spyugs te /
NK126(cho)001:6067: bdag gi mnga' bdag rgyal po dgung zla gsum nas 'das te /
NK126(cho)001:6068: de la bdag ni ma dga' rgyal blon khyed kyang de ltar ma mdzad cig /
NK126(cho)001:6069: bya ba yin gsungs te mchi ma shor bas /
NK126(cho)001:6070: rgyal blon kun kyang bshums so //
NK126(cho)001:6071: de nas gdan dgu brtsegs te bzhugs su gsol /
NK126(cho)001:6072: rgyal blon kun gyis sna drangs te gser dang dngul gyi dang tse phul te 'di skad zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:6073: rigs drug don mdzad byang chub sems dpa'i sku /
NK126(cho)001:6074: yid bzhin nor bu dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i thugs /
NK126(cho)001:6075: mi dmigs rgyal ba'i dgongs pa 'phro ba thugs /
NK126(cho)001:6076: sde snod gsum gyi yab men theg pa'i rtse //
NK126(cho)001:6077: dus gsum sangs rgyas sku gsum lhun rdzogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:6078: mi gnyis mnyam sbyor 'gro ba'i mgon po la //
NK126(cho)001:6079: dngul gyis man+dala gser gyi me tog phul //
NK126(cho)001:6080: thugs rjes dgongs la srid pa'i mtsho bsgral 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:6081: ye shes thugs rje'i zhags pas bzung du gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6082: zhes smras te me tog dor bas /
NK126(cho)001:6084: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po ma gus te /
NK126(cho)001:6085: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos b+aee ro tsa na la nyams sad pa'i phyir brtags pa mdzad do //
NK126(cho)001:6086: de la bu gcig shi ba'i pha ma btang ste /
NK126(cho)001:6088: chos zhu 'tshal chos byas na bu dang 'phrad dam mi 'phrad /
NK126(cho)001:6089: 'phrad thabs 'dra bdog gam zhu zhus pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6092: skye ba'i dbang gis 'chi bar nges //
NK126(cho)001:6094: da ring song 'chi sus kyang mi shes te //
NK126(cho)001:6095: snga gro phyi gro yin pa wa le yod //
NK126(cho)001:6096: 'chi ba'i grogs su dam chos bzang //
NK126(cho)001:6097: dam chos skye shi med par brten //
NK126(cho)001:6098: skye shi med pas sdug bsngal med //
NK126(cho)001:6099: sdug bsngal med pa sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:6101: 'byor zhing dar ba'i dbang gis rgud par nges //
NK126(cho)001:6102: rgud pa'i grogs su sbyin pa bzang //
NK126(cho)001:6103: sbyin pa snga btang sngon du 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:6106: 'bral ba'i grogs su smon lam bzang //
NK126(cho)001:6107: mi 'bral grogs pa'i smon lam thob //
NK126(cho)001:6108: smon lam btab na gnas shig nges par 'phrad //
NK126(cho)001:6109: 'phrad kyang ngo shes shin tu dka' //
NK126(cho)001:6110: de bas rang sems chos sku la //
NK126(cho)001:6111: cer gyis ltos la phyad kyis thong //
NK126(cho)001:6112: ma bcos rtsol med thig le bde //
NK126(cho)001:6113: ces rgan mo mdzub tshugs su bstan no //
NK126(cho)001:6115: rgan rgon 'chi ru cha ba tshan gcig btang nas /
NK126(cho)001:6116: rgan rgon gyi chos shig zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6118: 'o cag rgan rgon kun kyang ni //
NK126(cho)001:6119: dang po sha bkra bod tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6120: rgyan dang rtsed mo ma gtogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:6121: dam pa'i chos dang smos ci dgos //
NK126(cho)001:6122: 'phral gyi lto yang brjed du cha //
NK126(cho)001:6123: bar du khyim thabs byas tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6124: bu dang nor lam ma gtogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:6125: dam pa'i chos dang smos ci dgos //
NK126(cho)001:6126: lto dang rgyab kyang brjod du cha //
NK126(cho)001:6127: de nas rgas shing rgud tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6128: bza' dang btung ba ma yin pa //
NK126(cho)001:6129: dam pa'i chos la smos ci dgos //
NK126(cho)001:6130: byams pa'i gnyen yang brjed du 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6131: tha ma 'chi bar thug tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6132: kha chu sna chu mig chu gsum //
NK126(cho)001:6133: chu gsum ka kha'i gdong la blugs //
NK126(cho)001:6134: lus ni mi thegs ri bas lci //
NK126(cho)001:6136: ngag ni digs pa bas kyang lkugs //
NK126(cho)001:6137: smra rgyu yod kyang smra mi nus //
NK126(cho)001:6138: sems ni mar me bas kyang gsal //
NK126(cho)001:6139: yul mkhar gser g.yu bres gcal phog pa'i bu tsha yang //
NK126(cho)001:6140: rgan rgon shi rung zer zhing rgol tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6141: 'chi bar nges pa tshor nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:6142: dus der dam pa'i chos dran te //
NK126(cho)001:6143: bstan yang mi go ci ltar bgyi //
NK126(cho)001:6145: 'chi nges shes pas ma cha ma zhan cig /
NK126(cho)001:6146: zhan cing chags pa sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK126(cho)001:6147: byang sems ma bcos rtsol med dang //
NK126(cho)001:6148: ma chags ma zhen bde ba'i mchog /
NK126(cho)001:6149: ces 'da' kha ma'i man ngag gsungs nas dus 'dir bstan thabs de las med gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:6150: yang rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos /
NK126(cho)001:6151: yul gyi shar po shar mo rgyan dang chas te chos zhu ru btang nas /
NK126(cho)001:6153: dga' bde 'di las lhag pa rang /
NK126(cho)001:6154: sangs rgyas rang la yang yod dam zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:6155: b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:6156: nyon cig gson cig gzhon pa kun //
NK126(cho)001:6157: khyod kyang 'og rta bzang po de //
NK126(cho)001:6158: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6159: rgan pa'i dbang gis swo shed bral //
NK126(cho)001:6160: swo shed gnyis dang bral tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6161: rtsa chu mi 'chib khang phyi bskor //
NK126(cho)001:6162: tha ma rta mgo chab la 'phyo //
NK126(cho)001:6163: rmig bzhi gog po ngan khung bsgyur //
NK126(cho)001:6164: rta lpags rtsigs pa'i log la bkram //
NK126(cho)001:6165: de la rtag pa ci zhig gda' //
NK126(cho)001:6166: khyod kyi gos rnams legs mo de //
NK126(cho)001:6167: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6168: rgas pa'i dbang gis dug por 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6169: snal ma nyal nyil mal pa bsrungs //
NK126(cho)001:6170: tha ma khal rta'i stan du 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6171: de la rtag pa ci zhig gda' //
NK126(cho)001:6172: khyod kyi sha bkra legs mo de //
NK126(cho)001:6173: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6174: rgas pa'i dbang gi sha zad nyer mar 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6175: de la rtag pa ci zhig yod //
NK126(cho)001:6176: khyod kyi skra lo legs mo de //
NK126(cho)001:6177: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6178: rgas pa'i dbang gis dkar por 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6179: de la rtag pa ci zhig yod //
NK126(cho)001:6180: khyod kyi yan lag 'jam po de //
NK126(cho)001:6181: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6182: gyong po dregs pa'i dbang du 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6183: khyod kyi tshigs bzhi legs mo 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6184: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6185: rgas pa'i dbang gis rus mgo gyong por 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:6186: khyod kyi bzhin sar legs mo 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6187: lo gcig lo gnyis lon tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:6188: lpags pa rgas te hel dge tshig pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:6189: mig chus byad las bsren mar btang //
NK126(cho)001:6190: sna chu kha yi nang du blugs //
NK126(cho)001:6191: kha chu brang gi log la babs //
NK126(cho)001:6192: de la rtag pa ci zhig yod //
NK126(cho)001:6193: de la mno sa la lha chos mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:6194: ces shes pa drangs tshugs su bstan no //
NK126(cho)001:6195: de nas kun gyi chos dang ldan pa mthong /
NK126(cho)001:6196: chos yod par yid ches nas /
NK126(cho)001:6198: rin po che las byas pa'i me tog gtor nas /
NK126(cho)001:6200: nyin mo dkon mchog brtsegs pa la sogs pa 'bum sde lnga bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:6201: mtshan nyid sde gsum dang 'gro ba dad pa bskyed pa'i bsgrub pa rnam gsum bshad /
NK126(cho)001:6202: mtshan mo ni byang chub kyi sems phyogs bshad /
NK126(cho)001:6203: nam gyi gung la gsang sngags bsgyur /
NK126(cho)001:6204: de nas rgyal mo gru las sogs pas ni legs pa mkhyen /
NK126(cho)001:6205: de nas rgyal po g.yu sgra snying pos 'og rta la sga srab bstad /
NK126(cho)001:6206: mthur mda' dar yug gi byas nas zhus pas gnang ste /
NK126(cho)001:6208: lta ba'i rgyal po nam mkha' che //
NK126(cho)001:6210: dud 'gro'i rgyal por rtar btsong na //
NK126(cho)001:6211: dus gsum rgyal ba'i lung dang 'gal //
NK126(cho)001:6213: yang gser phye bre gang dang /
NK126(cho)001:6215: da man ngag sbyin dgos byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6216: yang b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:6217: gser gyi ri la g.yu yi chu blugs kyang //
NK126(cho)001:6218: nor gyi dam pa bla ma'i gdams ngag bzang //
NK126(cho)001:6220: yang tsha ba rong gi dbang por khri gdugs la chab la sku bsil du gshegs zer te /
NK126(cho)001:6221: g.yu sgras sba dkyil du b+aee ro tsa na bor bas /
NK126(cho)001:6223: yon dang dad pa gnyis med pas //
NK126(cho)001:6224: chos la nan btsir byas pa cang 'khums sam //
NK126(cho)001:6225: shi yang gnyis ka shi ba las //
NK126(cho)001:6227: khyod shi ngan song gnas su 'khyams //
NK126(cho)001:6228: khyod kyis phod na nga yi phod //
NK126(cho)001:6229: gsungs te g.yu sgra'i ltag khung nas bzung nas chab la kha rngogs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6232: ku re byas pa lags gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6233: yang dar dkar la bris pa'i dpe cha'i sgro ba'i zhabs phug ste kun byed rkus nas /
NK126(cho)001:6234: da nga la yang rgyud sde de yod byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6235: yang b+aee ro tsa nas mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:6236: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa brtags dka' 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6237: drang don ma yin nges don yin //
NK126(cho)001:6238: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs la ma shar na //
NK126(cho)001:6239: yig nag klog pas byang chub lam mi rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:6240: der g.yu sgra snying po ngo nag ting nge song nas /
NK126(cho)001:6241: mig nas mchi ma gsha' zer byung nas /
NK126(cho)001:6243: mkhas pa'i rab mchog man ngag gi sdong po /
NK126(cho)001:6244: kho'i snying lta bu dang 'phrad nas /
NK126(cho)001:6246: a ti brtsal med gang ltar zhus kyang ma gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6248: der slob dpon gyi 'di dad med tshod lta byed pa ru mi 'dug pa thugs la dgongs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6249: de nas g.yu sgra la rgyu 'bras kyi chos mang du bshad pas /
NK126(cho)001:6250: g.yu sgra yid ma ches pas /
NK126(cho)001:6251: yang mchi ma mang po bton nas /
NK126(cho)001:6252: rje ma h+aa g+hu ru chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:6253: tshe 'di nyid la 'khor bar mi sdod par sangs rgyas pa'i chos shig zhu byas te /
NK126(cho)001:6254: brkyang phyag lan stong du g.yu sgras btsal bas /
NK126(cho)001:6256: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:6257: stsol med bde chen sangs rgyas thob par 'dod na /
NK126(cho)001:6258: khyod kyi nga la sbyangs pa dgu dang /
NK126(cho)001:6259: phod pa bcu gsum byed nus sam gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6260: de ci ste mi bya gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:6261: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po na re /
NK126(cho)001:6262: ma h+aa gu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:6263: ci ltar gsungs pa bzhin du nyan par bgyis //
NK126(cho)001:6264: zhal nas bdud rtsi'i thig pa gnang bar zhu //
NK126(cho)001:6266: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:6267: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor rgyud drug 'khor ba'i gnas
NK126(cho)001:6268: las thar bar 'dod pas sbyangs pa dgu po 'di
NK126(cho)001:6269: ltar gyis shig / sku'i sbyangs pa gsum la /
NK126(cho)001:6270: bla ma'i zhing yul bzhugs gnas la so nam las khur lus sems khol du bgyis /
NK126(cho)001:6271: des skal bar bsags pa'i sdig pa dag /
NK126(cho)001:6272: bla ma smod cing 'jom pa'i sku dgra la //
NK126(cho)001:6273: lus dang srog la mi 'phong bar //
NK126(cho)001:6274: dgra bcom dmag dang bsad bcad kyis //
NK126(cho)001:6275: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib par byang //
NK126(cho)001:6276: bla ma'i zhabs tog tu gyur na //
NK126(cho)001:6277: rang gi sha rus lpags pas yang brnyes par bya //
NK126(cho)001:6278: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6279: gsung gi sbyangs pa gsum ni /
NK126(cho)001:6280: bla ma'i sku dgrar gyur pa la //
NK126(cho)001:6281: srog dang ser ba la sogs pa'i //
NK126(cho)001:6282: drag sngags bzlas brjod sna tshogs byed //
NK126(cho)001:6283: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6284: bla ma'i sku dgrar gyur pa la //
NK126(cho)001:6285: brdzun dang barlanga tshig zhe gcod smra //
NK126(cho)001:6286: drag po'i shag chen sna tshogs gdab //
NK126(cho)001:6287: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6288: ru yi skyon rnams mi brjod par //
NK126(cho)001:6289: yon tan sna tshogs brjod par bya //
NK126(cho)001:6290: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6291: thugs kyi sbyangs pa gsum la /
NK126(cho)001:6292: rtag tu 'gro dang 'chags dang nyal yang rung //
NK126(cho)001:6293: bla ma spyi bo'i gtsug tu khur //
NK126(cho)001:6294: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6295: rtag tu rtog tshogs yi dam lha bsgom yang //
NK126(cho)001:6296: spyi bo'i gtsug tu bla ma bsgom //
NK126(cho)001:6297: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6298: rtag tu mi brjed gdung sems gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6299: bla ma khong gi snying bzhin khur //
NK126(cho)001:6300: bla ma'i don du 'gyur ba na //
NK126(cho)001:6301: bu dang chung ma nor dang 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:6302: rgyal srid dang ni nor gyis dbyig /
NK126(cho)001:6303: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad phul //
NK126(cho)001:6305: des bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa byang //
NK126(cho)001:6306: mi phod pa gsum pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:6307: mdo zlas sngags tshig ji snyed pas //
NK126(cho)001:6308: bla ma'i sku dgrar gyur pa la //
NK126(cho)001:6309: zhe bcad barlangasa po'i tshig gcig dga' //
NK126(cho)001:6310: brgya phrag du ma'i char yang mi phod do //
NK126(cho)001:6311: stong gsum 'jig rten tha dag tu //
NK126(cho)001:6312: rin chen gser g.yu la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:6313: rgyal ba'i sku gsum sna tshogs byas //
NK126(cho)001:6314: de la ji snyed bskor dang phyag 'tshal bas //
NK126(cho)001:6315: bla ma brnyes pa'i 'gro don theg 'phrin skad cig dga' //
NK126(cho)001:6316: brgya phrag du ma'i char yang mi phod de //
NK126(cho)001:6317: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten tha dag gi //
NK126(cho)001:6318: nyan thos rang rgyal dge tshogs bcas //
NK126(cho)001:6319: byang chub sems dpa' tha dag la //
NK126(cho)001:6320: ji snyed mnyes pa byas pa bas //
NK126(cho)001:6321: bla ma dar tsam mnyes pas dga' //
NK126(cho)001:6322: brgya phrag du ma'i char yang mi phod do //
NK126(cho)001:6324: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas bas //
NK126(cho)001:6325: bla ma mnyes par shes par byed //
NK126(cho)001:6327: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:6328: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK126(cho)001:6329: dkon mchog gsum gyi rtsa ba ste //
NK126(cho)001:6330: rje btsun bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:6331: de ltar sbyangs pa dgu sbyangs shig /
NK126(cho)001:6332: rtsol med rdzogs pa chen po'i bka' lung man ngag rnyed par 'gyur /
NK126(cho)001:6333: ces rje b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6334: yang rgyal bu g.yu sgra snying pos /
NK126(cho)001:6335: brkyang phyag lan stong du 'tshal nas 'di zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:6336: bla ma bshes gnyen dam pa khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6337: bdag cag rnams kyi pha lags so //
NK126(cho)001:6338: bla ma bshes gnyen dam pa khyed //
NK126(cho)001:6339: bdag cag rnams kyi ma lags so //
NK126(cho)001:6340: bla ma bshes gnyen dam la khyed //
NK126(cho)001:6341: bdag cag rnams kyi mgon lags so //
NK126(cho)001:6342: bla ma bshes gnyen dam pa khyed //
NK126(cho)001:6343: mun pa sel ba'i sgron ma lags //
NK126(cho)001:6344: bla ma bshes gnyen dag pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:6346: thugs rje chen po'i spyang thag lags //
NK126(cho)001:6347: bla mas ci ltar gsung ba ltar du bgyi lags na //
NK126(cho)001:6348: bla ma'i thugs rjes 'khor ba'i 'dam nas drong du gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6349: ces bla ma la gsol ba btab pas yab rje b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:6350: nga la nyon dang g.yu sgra snying po khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6351: 'gro drug 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho zhe re 'jigs //
NK126(cho)001:6352: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal zhe re 'tsher //
NK126(cho)001:6353: dmyal khams bco brgyad sdug bsngal sha re g.ya' //
NK126(cho)001:6354: bskal pa grangs med tshe tshad skyi sha bun //
NK126(cho)001:6355: de la thar bar 'dod pa'i g.yu sgra khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6356: phod pa bcu gsum phod mi phod //
NK126(cho)001:6357: phod pa bcu gsum mi phod na //
NK126(cho)001:6358: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar bar dka' ste mchis //
NK126(cho)001:6360: rgyal bu g.yu sgra snying pos 'di skad zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:6361: skal med ngan song sdug bsngal las //
NK126(cho)001:6362: mi tshe gcig po 'di la cis kyang phod lags na //
NK126(cho)001:6363: bla mas cis gsungs nges par nyan //
NK126(cho)001:6365: yang b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:6366: 'o na nga la nyon cig g.yu sgra snying po khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6367: dad dang mos gus yon gyi man ngag a ti mi zhu bar //
NK126(cho)001:6368: g.yo dang thabs kyis 'go brus byas pas byang chub gding chen ci la thob //
NK126(cho)001:6369: snga ma 'dra na nga yi snod med khyod la man ngag sbyin du dus gsum bka' rgya yod //
NK126(cho)001:6370: lha srin sde brgyad chad pa 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:6371: phod pa bcu gsum phod pa na //
NK126(cho)001:6372: gser phye bre do khyer la lho nub u rgyan yul du song //
NK126(cho)001:6373: kun bzang gdung tshabs rgyal ba nyid dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:6374: dga' rab rdo rje nyid la gser phye bre do phul //
NK126(cho)001:6375: dga' rab rdo rje'i brnag pa nga'i khyod la sbyin //
NK126(cho)001:6376: rgya gar mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gsum la //
NK126(cho)001:6377: gser phye bre gang phul la brgya phyag stong stong 'tshol //
NK126(cho)001:6378: rgya gar mkhas pa'i 'dra 'bags chen po nga yis khyod la sbyin //
NK126(cho)001:6379: rdo rje gdan gyi khrom seng la //
NK126(cho)001:6380: gser phye bre phyed phul la brkyang phyag stong stong 'tshol //
NK126(cho)001:6381: rgyud sde drug cu rtsa bzhi khyod la sbyin //
NK126(cho)001:6382: deng song bod yul dbus kyis bsam yas na //
NK126(cho)001:6383: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6384: rgya gar mkhas pa bi ma mi tra spyan drangs nas //
NK126(cho)001:6385: chos grwa'i slob dpon de yis mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:6386: mkhas pa mang po grwa ni btsugs //
NK126(cho)001:6387: bskur pa chen po b+aee ro tsa nas nga la 'debs //
NK126(cho)001:6388: theg dman a nu man chad brgyad kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK126(cho)001:6389: g.yu sgra snying po der song la //
NK126(cho)001:6390: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dag bsdur gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6391: mkhas pa'i sgra bsgyur de ru bsgyur //
NK126(cho)001:6392: dregs pa sun 'byung de ru dbyung //
NK126(cho)001:6393: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul de ru ston //
NK126(cho)001:6394: b+aee ro tsa na nga la ngan pa sgrogs pa yod //
NK126(cho)001:6395: g.yu sgra snying po de ru song //
NK126(cho)001:6396: phyi nang gsang gsum dbang man ngag /
NK126(cho)001:6398: bu dang chung ma khabs su zhog /
NK126(cho)001:6399: lo dgu nga yis g.yog po gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6400: dbu skra gser g.yu'i lcang lo rtsad nas chod //
NK126(cho)001:6401: gser g.yu sor gdub rgyan cha phog /
NK126(cho)001:6402: chu rtsas btsos pa'i ther ma gon //
NK126(cho)001:6403: lo thug phye thug chan thug 'thung //
NK126(cho)001:6404: rtag tu khe grags nga rgyal shol //
NK126(cho)001:6405: rgyal srid yul mkhar ltag tu bor //
NK126(cho)001:6406: de tsho phod na man ngag bde chen rtsol med nga yis khyod la sbyin //
NK126(cho)001:6407: da lta bla ma mnyes par ma byas shig /
NK126(cho)001:6408: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK126(cho)001:6409: nyan pa la sogs bsgrub pa brtsams pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6411: bla ma mnyes par ma byas pas //
NK126(cho)001:6412: man ngag dang du len pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:6413: kha brag lam du zhugs pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:6414: ces rje b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:6415: der g.yu sgra snying pos slob dpon la mes mi tshig pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:6417: gcan gzan gyis mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:6419: rdzu 'phrul mang po bslab nas chibs rta ser po
NK126(cho)001:6420: seng ge'i gshogs can la gser phye bre do rin
NK126(cho)001:6421: po che mang po bkal nas lam du zhugs te
NK126(cho)001:6422: / u rgyan dang rgya gar yul du gshegs par chas pa las /
NK126(cho)001:6423: g.yu sgra'i yab rgyal po rin po che dang /
NK126(cho)001:6426: yab yum rje blon dang bcas pas slob dpon la
NK126(cho)001:6427: nongs sor shor ba la 'gyod bshags su phul nas
NK126(cho)001:6428: / g.yu sgra snying po la 'di skad ces smras so //
NK126(cho)001:6429: g.yu sgra snying po bya ba'i khe drag nga rgyal can //
NK126(cho)001:6430: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho bskom pa'i khri gdugs nyi ma ni //
NK126(cho)001:6431: b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul du byon pa la //
NK126(cho)001:6432: mos shing gus pa'i sems kyi zhabs nas spyi bos mi 'degs shing //
NK126(cho)001:6433: ku re thug thub byas pa g.yu sgra khyod kyi nongs //
NK126(cho)001:6434: nang 'gal mchis la bla ma nyid la bzod par gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6435: dga' rab rdo rje sangs rgyas kun gyi rje //
NK126(cho)001:6436: btsal bas rnyed par mi 'gyur gyi //
NK126(cho)001:6437: bla ma sangs rgyas nyid la bzod par phul //
NK126(cho)001:6438: de dang mnyam pa'i 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sogs //
NK126(cho)001:6439: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gsum la //
NK126(cho)001:6440: bshags pa phul nas bskal pa'i sgrib pa byang lags te //
NK126(cho)001:6441: btsal bas mi rnyed bla ma nyid la bzod par gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6442: sh+ri sing ha dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyis rje //
NK126(cho)001:6443: de la bzod par gsol na mun nag sbyang bar ltar ci smon //
NK126(cho)001:6444: de bas bla ma nyid la bzod par gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6445: g.yu sgra khyod la bshol yang 'debs //
NK126(cho)001:6446: bla ma nyid la bzod par gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6447: g.yu sgra 'khyams shing gang du phyin na yang //
NK126(cho)001:6448: rtsol med sangs rgyas mi rnyed tshe zed brgyag chad 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:6450: g.yu sgra snying po'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:6451: bla ma'i bka' bcag tu mi rung /
NK126(cho)001:6452: rgya gar du 'gro dgos zer nas ma nyan no //
NK126(cho)001:6453: de nas b+aee ro tsa na g.yu sgra'i gan du phyin nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:6454: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa na yis //
NK126(cho)001:6455: 'di nas rgya gar yul gyi lam bar la //
NK126(cho)001:6456: de'u shi de'u chad lnga bcu rtsa bdun byas //
NK126(cho)001:6457: bka' ba bcu drug spyad pa'i man ngag la //
NK126(cho)001:6458: mos shing gdung bas mi zhu bar //
NK126(cho)001:6459: man ngag thob tu re ba snying re rje //
NK126(cho)001:6460: da yang g.yu sgra snying po khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6461: rgya gar yul du ma 'gro bar //
NK126(cho)001:6462: ci ltar phod pa'i bshags pa khyod kyi nga la gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6464: de nas g.yu sgra snying po rgya gar du gshegs pa bshol nas /
NK126(cho)001:6465: yab rgyal po rin po che dang /
NK126(cho)001:6468: yab yum blon 'bangs 'khor dang bcas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6469: rje b+aee ro tsa na la ber gyi gdan 'phar ba dgu rtsegs ni bting /
NK126(cho)001:6470: na bza' ber chen dgu rtsegs ni sku la gsol /
NK126(cho)001:6471: steng nas rma bya sbab zer gsum gyi gdugs phub /
NK126(cho)001:6472: dar zab kyi bla re sprin ltar du gtib /
NK126(cho)001:6473: gser gyi rta la g.yu yi sga srab can dang /
NK126(cho)001:6474: g.yu yi rta la gser gyi sga srab can dang /
NK126(cho)001:6477: rnga mang la nor sna tshogs kyi khal bkal ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:6478: gser gyi dang tse g.yu'i bkang ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:6479: g.yu'i dang rtse gser gyi bkang ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:6480: gzi mchong gi ga'u mu tig gis bkang ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:6481: bcud dang ldan pa'i bza' skyems mang po drangs /
NK126(cho)001:6482: bla ma'i thugs nong pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6483: gser gyi rdo rje g.yu'i 'phras brgyan pa /
NK126(cho)001:6484: rtse gru gang phyag tu phul /
NK126(cho)001:6485: sku chab tu gshegs pa la rgyal po'i bla g.yu 'od can mgul du btags /
NK126(cho)001:6490: sgra snyan sna tshogs phyag tu phul /
NK126(cho)001:6491: gser gyi man+dala la g.yu'i me tog dang /
NK126(cho)001:6492: gling bzhi nyi zla gza' skar dang bcas pa bkod nas rje b+aee ro tsa na la phul lo //
NK126(cho)001:6493: g.yu sgra snying pos 'di skad gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6494: rje yi rje ni sa bdag rgyal po lags //
NK126(cho)001:6495: sa bdag rgyal po rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:6496: lha rgyal rin po che'i rje ni b+aee ro tsa na lags //
NK126(cho)001:6497: dkon mchog bla med yon tan rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:6498: dad mos rnams kyi yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK126(cho)001:6499: b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la bzod par gsol //
NK126(cho)001:6500: ces g.yu sgra snying pos gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6501: brkyang phyag lan stong du mdzad do //
NK126(cho)001:6502: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6503: snga ma nongs pa shor ba sems can 'khrul pa'i blo //
NK126(cho)001:6504: phyis nas sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum dang /
NK126(cho)001:6505: 'gyod bshags phul ba bdag kyang glo ba dga' //
NK126(cho)001:6507: g.yu sgra snying po'i spyi gtsug tu b+aee ro tsa nas zhabs dbang bskur ro //
NK126(cho)001:6508: de nas g.yu sgra snying pos dbu skra g.yu'i lcong lo breg /'gul brgyan dang /
NK126(cho)001:6510: phyag sor gyi brgyan rnams phud /
NK126(cho)001:6516: 'khor dang g.yog thams cad bla ma la phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:6517: de nas phyi nang gsang gsum gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK126(cho)001:6518: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang bskur nas man ngag 'phrul gyi lung dgu byin /
NK126(cho)001:6519: thig le chen po'i dbang bskur nas sems nyid 'gyur med kyi man ngag byin /
NK126(cho)001:6520: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i dbang bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:6521: spyod lam lhug pa'i man ngag byin /
NK126(cho)001:6522: rdo rje lung gi dbang bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:6523: ye shes ngos bzung gi man ngag byin /
NK126(cho)001:6524: lhun grub gnyis kyi dbang bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:6525: sku gsum thug 'phrad man ngag byin /
NK126(cho)001:6526: gnyis med 'brel ba'i dbang bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:6527: phyag rgya chen po'i man ngag sbyin /
NK126(cho)001:6528: rdo rje lung gi dbang bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:6529: rgyal tshabs bskor ba'i man ngag byin /
NK126(cho)001:6530: dbang dang 'brel ba'i man ngag bdun byin /
NK126(cho)001:6531: rgyud sde drug cu tham pa gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:6532: man ngag thams cad rtsad nas gcod par g.yu sgra la gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:6533: g.yu sgras kyang phyir mi ldog pa'i don rnyed de /
NK126(cho)001:6535: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos sbyangs pa dgu dang
NK126(cho)001:6536: phod pa bcu gsum byas pa'i skabs te bco brgyad
NK126(cho)001:6537: pa'o //// de nas rje b+aee ro tsa nas g.yu
NK126(cho)001:6538: sgra snying po la man ngag mtshor rdzir gtad pa'i
NK126(cho)001:6540: g.yu sgra snying po 'dus pa'i sems //
NK126(cho)001:6541: bdag gi smras pa'i sems 'di las //
NK126(cho)001:6542: dus gsum dus med rtogs par zhog /
NK126(cho)001:6543: bdag gi dka' las ci tsam pa //
NK126(cho)001:6544: snga gong sems brlan pa bas //
NK126(cho)001:6546: rgya gar yul du phyin pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)001:6547: de'u shi de'u chad lnga bcu rtsa bdun byas //
NK126(cho)001:6548: g.yu sgra snying po rin chen gter //
NK126(cho)001:6549: dad mos gnyis su ldan pa'i slob ma khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6550: man ngag 'di la bca' lugs rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK126(cho)001:6551: man ngag rin chen dam pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6552: thams cad mthong zhing gsal byed pa //
NK126(cho)001:6553: mig gi 'bras bu lta bur btsa' //
NK126(cho)001:6554: theg pa kun gyi snying po lung yin pa //
NK126(cho)001:6555: srog rtsa snying gi tshul du btsa' //
NK126(cho)001:6556: chos nyid nam mkha'i snying yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:6557: yan lag bzhi yi gtsug tu khur //
NK126(cho)001:6559: sbyin lugs rnam pa bzhi yod de //
NK126(cho)001:6560: yun du snying bzhin byed pa'i dad ldan mdzad ring dang //
NK126(cho)001:6561: bla ma'i bka' la zur tsam rdul tsam yang //
NK126(cho)001:6562: skad gcig tsam yang mi gcog na //
NK126(cho)001:6563: des 'brel ti ka sa gcod dang //
NK126(cho)001:6564: man ngag dbang dang ngo sprod sbrel la byin //
NK126(cho)001:6565: khong khro mtshur ngas dad med la //
NK126(cho)001:6566: tshig 'ga' brid la skrad la btang //
NK126(cho)001:6567: dad pa chung la bshad pa ring //
NK126(cho)001:6569: rgyud dang bstan bcos yug pa kyang ma gtad //
NK126(cho)001:6570: dad pa chung yang spu bzang snying nye dang //
NK126(cho)001:6571: bsgo ba nyan cing drung du 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:6572: de la blo dang sbyar la bshad //
NK126(cho)001:6573: spus bzang slob ma yun ring snod ldan la //
NK126(cho)001:6574: dad pa chung yang nan gyis sbyin //
NK126(cho)001:6575: phar la bskul cig sbyin par bya //
NK126(cho)001:6576: dad pa gdung ste drung du 'khor //
NK126(cho)001:6577: shes rab rmongs pas ma go na //
NK126(cho)001:6578: yig snar byas la sbyin par bya //
NK126(cho)001:6579: 'ong long med par bri bar ring //
NK126(cho)001:6580: bri long med par gdams ngag 'dod //
NK126(cho)001:6581: 'jom pos brid la bskrad la btang //
NK126(cho)001:6582: spus ngan tshongs pa chos rjes byed //
NK126(cho)001:6585: rgyal khams phya yang 'khon par bya //
NK126(cho)001:6588: bsgrub pa lung gi spyad lugs ni //
NK126(cho)001:6589: phur pa ma bu bsgrub pa yang //
NK126(cho)001:6590: gang zhig rnag pa byed 'dod na //
NK126(cho)001:6591: las su bya ba rgyun du bsring //
NK126(cho)001:6592: bal gyi lcag rdo ci bzhin du //
NK126(cho)001:6593: de yi dgra bgegs brlag par 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:6594: drag sngags gsang sngags gsang thig rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6595: mis ma tshor bar spyod par bya //
NK126(cho)001:6596: spyod mthong tsam gyi nyams par 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:6597: tshe dang bdud rtsi'i bsgrub pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6598: dge slong dam nyams bud med dag la mi bstan par //
NK126(cho)001:6599: gzhung bzhin bsgrub na drod rtags 'byung //
NK126(cho)001:6600: yang dag bsgrub kyang de ltar spyod //
NK126(cho)001:6601: slob dpon rang gi chos lugs dang //
NK126(cho)001:6602: rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag yang //
NK126(cho)001:6603: so sor rang rang gzhung btsan pas //
NK126(cho)001:6604: bslad cing dkrug par mi byed cig /
NK126(cho)001:6605: g.yu sgra snying po khyod la ni //
NK126(cho)001:6606: 'khyam po b+aee ro bdag gis man ngag bstan //
NK126(cho)001:6607: snod med rnams la ma bstan te //
NK126(cho)001:6608: ces gsungs nas gtad rgyar gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:6610: b+aee ro tsa nas tsha ba rong du bstan pa bsgrags pa'i skabs te bcu dgu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:6611: de nas b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i rong du spyugs nas lo skor gcig lon tsa /
NK126(cho)001:6612: rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po bi ma mi
NK126(cho)001:6613: tra bod yul dbus kyi bsam yas su byon nas
NK126(cho)001:6614: / chos gsungs zhing bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6615: bod du byon pa la lugs gnyis yod pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6616: lugs gcig ni spyugs nas bi ma la mi tra bod du byon pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:6617: lugs gcig rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis spyan
NK126(cho)001:6618: drangs nas bod du byon pa'i lugs gnyis bdog pa
NK126(cho)001:6619: la / dang po ni spyugs nas bi ma la bod du byon pa'i lugs 'byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:6620: de yang rgya gar gyi chos skyong ba'i rgyal po
NK126(cho)001:6621: gcig phyi'i rgya mtsho la sku skyo ba 'chags su
NK126(cho)001:6622: gshegs pa'i sku'i bar chad bsrungs ba'i sngags mkhan du
NK126(cho)001:6623: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra khrid nas /
NK126(cho)001:6624: rdzing bcas te mtsho la btang ste mthun pa'i rlung dang sbyar te byon tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:6625: rgya mtsho'i sum cha tsam du phyin tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:6626: rgya mtsho'i nang nas chu srin chen po zhig byung
NK126(cho)001:6627: nas chu srin la slob dpon bi ma la mi
NK126(cho)001:6628: tras gdangs mig tu spyan gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6629: chu srin gyi bi ma la mi tras spyan 'bru
NK126(cho)001:6630: tshugs su gzigs pas gzi brjid ma bzod chu srin
NK126(cho)001:6632: rdzing nam mkha' la gling gling byung bas /
NK126(cho)001:6634: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra la /
NK126(cho)001:6638: slob dpon bi ma la mi tras mnyam bzhags la bzhugs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6639: chu srin yang lhan gyi song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:6640: chu srin lhan gyi song nas rgya mtsho yang lhan gyis song /
NK126(cho)001:6641: rgyal po bred de bi ma la mi tra la slob dpon phyir la log 'dong gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6643: rgyal po sku 'chags su gshegs gsungs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6645: cis kyang log la gshegs zer nas /
NK126(cho)001:6646: rgyal po dang bi ma mi tra la sogs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6648: rje la gnod pa ci mnga'/
NK126(cho)001:6649: sku skyo ba mi 'chags par ldog pa cug lags pas /
NK126(cho)001:6651: nga la mi srid pa'i cho 'phrul chen po zhig byung bas log pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:6653: phan btags de man na nga shi gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6654: blon po rnams na re ban+de kho rang gi cho
NK126(cho)001:6655: 'phrul yin pas de nas gang yang min pa zer
NK126(cho)001:6656: nas / blon po rnams na re /
NK126(cho)001:6657: ban+de 'di bsad dgos rgyal po la zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:6660: blon po rnams ma lo bar rgyal po la yang yang zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:6661: rgyal po'i zhal nas ban+de 'di bsad pas mi 'ong bas /
NK126(cho)001:6662: bsad pa bas spyugs pa gnang gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6663: bsams yas su spyugs nas byon pa yin no //
NK126(cho)001:6664: spyan drangs nas bod du byon pa'i lugs ni /
NK126(cho)001:6665: rje b+aee ro tsa na ni tsha ba'i yul du spyugs /
NK126(cho)001:6666: chos grwa'i slob dpon med par rgyal po khri srong
NK126(cho)001:6667: lde'u btsan gyis mkhon klu'i dbang po bya ba mi
NK126(cho)001:6668: gsum gser phye bre gsum bskur nas /
NK126(cho)001:6669: shog 'phrin du rgya gar ba nga'i zhang po yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:6670: rgya gar gyi rgyal po la gser phye 'di phul
NK126(cho)001:6671: la bla'i mchod gnas pan+di ta lnga brgya'i nang nas
NK126(cho)001:6672: mkhyen rgya gang che ba zhig bardzangasa 'tshal lo zhes
NK126(cho)001:6673: springs pas / rgya gar gyi rgyal po la gser phye phul nas shin tu mnyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:6674: pan+di ta rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK126(cho)001:6675: khyed rnams kyi nang nas mkhyen rgya gang che ba cig bod yul du gshegs 'tshal zhus pa las /
NK126(cho)001:6676: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra la pan+di ta rnams kyi spyan gzigs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6677: bi ma la mi tra khong bod yul du gshegs 'tshal dgongs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6678: bi ma la mi tra'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:6679: g+hu ya a ka sha ya zhes lan gsum gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6680: bod yul du byon pa rje b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul du gsan nas /
NK126(cho)001:6681: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:6682: g.yu sgra snying po la khyod bod yul du song
NK126(cho)001:6683: la rgya gar gyi slob dpon bi ma la mi
NK126(cho)001:6684: tra ni pan+di ta lnga brgya'i nang nas /
NK126(cho)001:6685: mkhas btsun shin tu man ngag gi a ti la mkhas pa chen po yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:6686: nga'i chos ni gsang sngags su 'dug gam /
NK126(cho)001:6687: man ngag a ti rdzogs chen du 'dug gam bi
NK126(cho)001:6688: ma la dang gnyis dgongs pa sdur cig gsungs nas
NK126(cho)001:6689: rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong gi yul de ba has
NK126(cho)001:6690: bya bar zla ba brgyad du sems phyogs kun gzigs
NK126(cho)001:6691: nas / lcags 'grel la sogs pa 'grel pa dgu rtsam nas /
NK126(cho)001:6692: de nas g.yu sgra snying po la sgra 'gyur gyi skad mi 'dra ba bcu gsum bslab nas /
NK126(cho)001:6693: bi ma la dang g.yu sgra gnyis chos su mkhas 'gron cig gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:6694: de nas g.yu sgra snying pos bod yul bsam yas su byon pas /
NK126(cho)001:6695: slob dpon bi ma la dbu rtse'i nang na nyan
NK126(cho)001:6696: thos kyi chos pra ka ra na sde brgyad bya
NK126(cho)001:6697: ba 'chad pa'i chos thun la bab pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6698: g.yu sgra snying pos slob dpon bi ma la mi tra la /
NK126(cho)001:6699: rgyal mo tsha rong ba mjal dgos byas te /
NK126(cho)001:6701: bi ma la mi tras bag tsam bzhugs cig /
NK126(cho)001:6702: chos thun la bab nas yod kyi byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6703: g.yu sgra bzhugs su ma bzhed nas dbu rtse'i sgo phul nas nang du thol gyi byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:6704: mkhas pa bi ma la mi tra g.yu sgras spyan cer gyi gzigs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6707: ka kha pa ri gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6708: bi ma la mi tras d+ha thim d+ha thim /
NK126(cho)001:6709: d+ha thim gsungs nas dbu smad mdzad nas bzhugs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6710: g.yu sgras btsad po la spyan cer gyi gzigs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6711: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po bka' 'khor rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6712: man ngag bde chen btsal du med pa'i chos //
NK126(cho)001:6713: skye med lhun rdzogs tshig cig don gyi 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa //
NK126(cho)001:6714: man ngag snying po tsha ba'i yul du spyugs //
NK126(cho)001:6715: a kha ra mi tha the dza li /
NK126(cho)001:6717: lce lco shan dza man dza go ces gsung zhing phyir log te gshegs so //
NK126(cho)001:6718: btsad po rje 'bangs kyi mkhas pa bi ma mi tra la /
NK126(cho)001:6720: mtha' mi de 'dra ba zhig dbu rtse'i nang du 'ong nas de 'dra'i skad smra nas /
NK126(cho)001:6722: bi ma la mi tra'i zhal /
NK126(cho)001:6723: g.yu sgra'i ka kha pa ri /
NK126(cho)001:6725: wa spre'u dag gi sgra grags kyang //
NK126(cho)001:6726: seng ge'i gdangs su cong 'gyur ram //
NK126(cho)001:6727: pha rol dag gi 'gros bsgrod kyang //
NK126(cho)001:6728: khams gsum sa gzhir 'khor ba cang 'gyur ram //
NK126(cho)001:6729: nyan thos byis pa'i chos bshad pas //
NK126(cho)001:6730: rtsol med 'bras bu cang thob bya ba lags //
NK126(cho)001:6731: bdag rang gi d+ha thim bya ba gsum po de /
NK126(cho)001:6732: chos thams cad mnyams pa nyid la 'dra mod bya ba lags //
NK126(cho)001:6733: g.yu sgra snying pos a kar ra pa ra mi tha th+aed dza li bya ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:6734: ma rig nyon mongs 'tshal ba'i rje blon snying re rje bya ba lags /
NK126(cho)001:6735: lce lco shan tsa man tsa go bya ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:6736: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhes bya lags gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:6737: de nas g.yu sgra snying pos nyo chang ma la chang gang na yod dris nas /
NK126(cho)001:6738: nyo chang nyo yin bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6739: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras nyo chang ma la
NK126(cho)001:6740: chang nyo rgyu bskyal nas chang 'di sleb tsam na
NK126(cho)001:6742: nga rang yang bya ra byed kyi byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6743: chang gis slebs te nyo chang mas g.yu sgra snying po la sbran te /
NK126(cho)001:6744: rnyag dz+ny+aa nas phra yol zung cig snam phrag tu bcug nas /
NK126(cho)001:6745: chang ma'i sa ru phyin pas /
NK126(cho)001:6746: chang mas phra yol cig bzung ste chang gi bkang nas g.yu sgra la g.yas nas drangs /
NK126(cho)001:6747: rnyag dz+ny+aa nas 'phra yol cig bzung ste phyag g.yon par phul /
NK126(cho)001:6748: lus las gos phud de g.yu sgra'i sku la gsol te /
NK126(cho)001:6749: man ngag chos shig zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6751: khyed la slob dpon bi ma la mi tra 'dug pa des chog mod gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6752: rnyag dz+ny+aa nas pan+di ta gnyis ka la chos zhu byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:6753: g.yu sgra snying po'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:6754: nged dang bi ma la mi tra gnyis mthun yang /
NK126(cho)001:6755: sna la phyag dka' la yang mi mthun gsungs yang gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:6756: rnyag dz+ny+aa nas bi ma la mi tra la /
NK126(cho)001:6757: g.yu sgras sngon la phyag mdzad dam zhus pa las /
NK126(cho)001:6758: nga lo nga brgya lon pa zhig gis rgyal mo'i
NK126(cho)001:6759: phru gu byis pa la phyag cang byed dam gsungs
NK126(cho)001:6760: pas / bi ma la mi tras g.yu sgra la phyag mdzad du ma bzhed do //
NK126(cho)001:6761: der rdzu 'phrul gang che ba cig la phyag bya bar chad de /
NK126(cho)001:6763: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos gser gyis bye'u chung zhig tu sprul nas /
NK126(cho)001:6764: lcang ma'i khar spur te 'phur nas song bas /
NK126(cho)001:6765: bi ma la mi tras khra hor pa cig tu bardzusa nas nam mkhar nas song bas /
NK126(cho)001:6766: gser gyi byi'u chung de sa la bab nas gser
NK126(cho)001:6767: gyi rdo dum bu cig tu byas nas sa la
NK126(cho)001:6769: der rdzu 'phrul mnyams par 'dug pas gnyis kas phyag 'tshal ba med par byas so //
NK126(cho)001:6770: der 'phan yul 'phan gyi brag khung bu gsum sbrel te /
NK126(cho)001:6772: cig tu bi ma la mi tra bzhugs /
NK126(cho)001:6773: cig tu g.yu sgra snying po bzhugs te /
NK126(cho)001:6774: bar du rnyag dz+ny+aa na lo tsa ba bzhugs te /
NK126(cho)001:6775: g.yu sgras g.yas nas snga 'gyur lnga bshad /
NK126(cho)001:6776: bi ma las g.yon nas phyi 'gyur bcu gsum bshad /
NK126(cho)001:6777: khra ma bu sdeb pa bzhin du tshag par gcig kyang ma 'grus par khrig khrig byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:6778: der rnyag dz+ny+aa nas bsgro gleng mdzad par zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:6779: mkhas pa bi ma la mi tras g.yu sgra snying po ma thub nas /
NK126(cho)001:6780: g.yu sgras bi ma la mi tra la bzhugs shigs byas nas /
NK126(cho)001:6781: g.yu sgras snga 'gyur lnga bshad pa 'di ltar ro //
NK126(cho)001:6782: kun la 'jug gis lta bsgom phye //
NK126(cho)001:6783: nam mkha' che yi theg sgo gsal //
NK126(cho)001:6784: byams pa bsgom pas mnyams pa'i ngang la zhog /
NK126(cho)001:6785: rig pa'i khu byug theg dman zil gyi mnan //
NK126(cho)001:6786: rtsal chen sprug pas 'khor ba bag la bsad //
NK126(cho)001:6789: mi nub rgyal mtshan nam mkha' dngas pa bzhin du gom sgrib so sor gsal /
NK126(cho)001:6790: khyung chen lding ba bzhin du gshogs rdzogs mkha' la lta ba rlabs kyi gcod /
NK126(cho)001:6791: sems bsgom drug pas klong chen dril ba bzhin du thams cad la ni gcig tu zlo /
NK126(cho)001:6792: rtsal chen sprul pas seng ge gnam du 'chang ba
NK126(cho)001:6793: bzhin du sems kyi rtsal ni chos nyid nam mkha'i
NK126(cho)001:6795: rig pa'i khu byug bya rje khu byug bzhin du rtsol bsgrub zil gyis gnon /
NK126(cho)001:6796: rnam lnga sems phyogs drag sngags dz+ny+aa na khyod la gtad do shor la re /
NK126(cho)001:6798: rgyal mo g.yu sgras rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra la dbang bskur /
NK126(cho)001:6799: rgyal po'i gzhung du dbang bskur gsang mtshan rdo rje grub pa gter du btags so //
NK126(cho)001:6800: b+ai ma las bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur gsang mtshan dri med zla shar du btags so //
NK126(cho)001:6801: de'i g.yu sgras sngon la bshad pa tsho la snga 'gyur lnga zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:6802: b+ai ma las rting nas phyi 'gyur bcu gsum zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:6803: de'i tshe de'i dus na bod kyi rje blon rnams gyis /
NK126(cho)001:6804: b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul du spyugs pa la 'gyod pa skyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:6806: la la ni mchi ma phyungs te /
NK126(cho)001:6808: dkon mchog rin chen bla med mchod gnas pa //
NK126(cho)001:6809: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:6810: thugs rje byams pa'i gsungs ni dbyangs su sgrogs //
NK126(cho)001:6811: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i gsungs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:6812: sna tshogs skye med phyogs med klong du bton //
NK126(cho)001:6813: kun bzang nyid du bzhugs pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:6814: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:6816: de nas rje b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul du spyugs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:6817: bod kyi rje blon 'bangs rnams 'gyod pa skyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:6818: btsad po dang bi ma la mi tra dang /
NK126(cho)001:6820: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK126(cho)001:6821: bod kyi chos byed mkhas btsun grangs mang po 'tshogs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6822: a tsa ra b+aee ro tsa na'i yon tan bsgrang ba /
NK126(cho)001:6823: bod kyi mkhas pa a tsa ra b+aee ro tsa na 'di /
NK126(cho)001:6824: skye ba snga phyi shes pa'i byang chub sems dpa' yin yang dag /
NK126(cho)001:6825: man ngag gi chos btsal gyi mi rnyed pa ma
NK126(cho)001:6826: lus pa gting 'byin par rnyed pa'i sprul pa'i sku
NK126(cho)001:6827: yin yang dag / dgung lo bco lnga las ma
NK126(cho)001:6828: lon par bod nas rgya gar gyis yul du lam
NK126(cho)001:6830: lha'i spyan dang ldan pa yin yang dag /'di nas rgya gar gyi lam bar la mi rgod dang /
NK126(cho)001:6832: gcan gzan gdug pa rnams kyi 'phrang la phyin pas
NK126(cho)001:6833: bar chad gang gis kyang ma tshugs par 'khor bar
NK126(cho)001:6834: mi ldog pa yin yang dag /
NK126(cho)001:6835: rgya gar yul nas bod yul la zla ba drug gis lam bar la /
NK126(cho)001:6836: nyin lam bdun gyi brtol bas lcags kyi dre'u rta
NK126(cho)001:6837: rkang gsum ma'i rkang mgyogs kyi dngos grub thob pa
NK126(cho)001:6838: yin yang dag / sbal dong dang shig dong du
NK126(cho)001:6839: bcug kyang 'jigs shing skrag pa med pas bzod pa
NK126(cho)001:6841: man ngag 'di'i chos rnams thos pa tsam gyis go
NK126(cho)001:6842: zhing rtogs par 'gyur bas don dam pa'i bden pa
NK126(cho)001:6844: matha'i kha brgyud nas sgra 'gyur kun la bslab pas
NK126(cho)001:6845: gang la yang ma rmongs pa logs pa sgrib gnyis
NK126(cho)001:6847: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa kun gyi man ngag ni
NK126(cho)001:6848: gang la yang gces dgu thob pas sangs rgyas kyi
NK126(cho)001:6850: sangs rgyas kyi mtshan rtags nas theg pa gang la'ang
NK126(cho)001:6851: ma rmongs par mkhyen pas ston pa'i zhal skyin yin
NK126(cho)001:6852: yang dag / rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs bcu dang ldan
NK126(cho)001:6853: pas sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' yin yang
NK126(cho)001:6854: yang dag / dag / ces pas b+aee ro tsa
NK126(cho)001:6855: na la yang dag bcu gcig gi yon tan bsgrang
NK126(cho)001:6857: rje blon 'bangs dang mkhas pa mang pas /
NK126(cho)001:6858: tsha ba'i rong gi yul phyogs na mar la lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam btsal lo //
NK126(cho)001:6859: de nas g.yu sgra tsha ba'i rang du slar byon
NK126(cho)001:6860: nas mkhas pa b+aee ro tsa na la yang dag
NK126(cho)001:6861: bcu gcig gi bstod pa la sogs pa'i bka' mchid
NK126(cho)001:6862: gleng mo zhib tu brjod pas /
NK126(cho)001:6863: b+aee ro tsa na shin tu dgyes nas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:6864: bdag 'dra 'khyam po b+aee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6865: yang dag bcu gcig don dang ye nas ldan //
NK126(cho)001:6866: shes bya'i sgrib pa bag tsam ma byang bas //
NK126(cho)001:6867: bod yul mun pa'i gling du skyes //
NK126(cho)001:6868: rgya gar yul nas man ngag mthar thug btsal //
NK126(cho)001:6869: bod yul rgyal dang blon po rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6870: rgya gar phra ma gdug pa snyan du gsan //
NK126(cho)001:6871: rgyal dang blon po kun logs nas //
NK126(cho)001:6872: mchis pa tsha ba'i yul du b+aee ro tsa na spyugs //
NK126(cho)001:6873: tsha ba'i rgyal khams dkar por bsgyur //
NK126(cho)001:6874: tshe gzhugs slar log bod du mchis //
NK126(cho)001:6875: sgyu ma'i phung po der bsnyil nas //
NK126(cho)001:6876: skye med nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:6879: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos bod yul gyi grags ngan pa bcag pas /
NK126(cho)001:6880: slar b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul du spyugs
NK126(cho)001:6881: pa la 'gyod pa skyes nas yang dag bcu gcig
NK126(cho)001:6882: gi bstod pa'i skabs te nyi shu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:6883: de'i dus de'i tshe rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos /
NK126(cho)001:6884: rje b+aee ro tsa na la gser bya mo'i sgong nga tsam dgu /
NK126(cho)001:6885: rin chen phra men gyi bya skyog mdas kyang mi sleb pa cig /
NK126(cho)001:6886: rgun skyems ding ba dang bcas te phyag tu phul /
NK126(cho)001:6887: spyi bos slob dpon gyi zhabs la gtug ste /
NK126(cho)001:6889: rje ma h+aa gu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:6890: lung dang man ngag gi chos ni /
NK126(cho)001:6891: slob dpon chen pos mkhyen tshad thos /
NK126(cho)001:6893: man ngag chos la dgongs pa 'ub chub cig tu rtogs shing /
NK126(cho)001:6894: mkhyen par bgyi na ci ltar bgyi //
NK126(cho)001:6895: dgongs pa mthar thug tu bzhag na ci ltar bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:6897: rje b+aee ro tsa nas man ngag mdzub tshugs su bstan pas /
NK126(cho)001:6898: bod kyi mi la snod med gsang mi thub /
NK126(cho)001:6899: skal ba dang ldan nyung bas ma bstan /
NK126(cho)001:6900: nga g.yu sgra snying po khyod la mkhas pa nyi
NK126(cho)001:6901: shu rtsa gsum gyi bshad lugs ni rting phyin par
NK126(cho)001:6902: bshad ni / g.yu sgras zhus pa'i don la /
NK126(cho)001:6903: snga ma tshos khyod yid ma ches pa dgongs nas /
NK126(cho)001:6904: man ngag gi chos yo dgongs pa bslang ste /
NK126(cho)001:6905: rtsad bcas pa'i mdo don cig bsdus nas dgongs pa'i
NK126(cho)001:6906: zhe phug bka' gsal mgur du bzhengs pa 'di gsungs
NK126(cho)001:6907: so // h+aumh sngon sbyangs las 'phro ldan pa'i g.yu sgra khyod //
NK126(cho)001:6908: sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum bag chags sbyangs //
NK126(cho)001:6909: phod pa bcu gsum byas pas man ngag snod du gyur //
NK126(cho)001:6910: sems nyid klong du gyur pa'i b+aee ro tsa na bdag /
NK126(cho)001:6911: bod khams 'bras bu'i chos kyi rgyas par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:6912: dka' ba bcu drug spyad nas rgya gar yul du phyin //
NK126(cho)001:6913: rdo rje sems dpa' dga' rab rdo rje 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang //
NK126(cho)001:6914: rdo rje gdan gyi man ngag lung bstan te //
NK126(cho)001:6915: nyi shu rtsa gsum mkhas pa'i man ngag rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6916: nga yi go ba bzhin du khyod la sbyin pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:6917: de yis yid ma ches na bag chags ma sbyang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:6918: man ngag byang chub sems phyogs nyi shu bzhi //
NK126(cho)001:6919: rgyud sde ma bu drug cu rtsa brgyad la //
NK126(cho)001:6920: mdo don man ngag gda' tshang rtsad nas bcad //
NK126(cho)001:6921: rtsa ba 'dus pa'i man ngag 'di las med //
NK126(cho)001:6922: gus pas rna bar nyon la yid la zungs //
NK126(cho)001:6923: rtsol sgrub bya brtsal med pa'i man ngag sems phyogs 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6924: snang srid phyi bshig nang grol rtsad bcad pas //
NK126(cho)001:6925: chos thams cad thams cad ngo bo chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:6927: kun gzhi ma bcos ye nas gnas //
NK126(cho)001:6928: rgyu las ma byung rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NK126(cho)001:6929: rkyen dang ma 'brel gnyen pos bshig tu med //
NK126(cho)001:6930: dngos po med pas 'bras bu'i 'dod pa bral //
NK126(cho)001:6931: gzhi lam gnyis dang bral nas ye nas chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:6932: dbyibs dang kha dog bral bas dpe yi mtshon du med //
NK126(cho)001:6933: 'khor 'das skye shi med pas rtags pa chen po'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:6934: rtag chad gnyis su med pas mtha' gnyis rkyen dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:6935: mtho dman med pas theg pa kun gyi rtse //
NK126(cho)001:6936: che chung med pas dmigs pa kun dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:6937: yangs dogs med pas kun tu bzang po'i mkha' //
NK126(cho)001:6938: mtha' dbus med par kun la khyab pas brdal //
NK126(cho)001:6939: phyi nang med par ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:6940: mtshon du med pa sku yi tshad dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:6941: snang med mtshon bral byang chub chos nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6942: ye nas ma bcos ngang gi gnas pa la //
NK126(cho)001:6943: rtsol bsgrub cis kyang btsal du med par rtogs par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6944: g.yu sgra snying pos sems la go bar gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6945: dgongs pa nyams su blang bar bya ba ni //
NK126(cho)001:6946: ye nas ma bcos kun gzhi dag pa'i klong //
NK126(cho)001:6947: 'bras bu chos nyid bya ba de nyid yin //
NK126(cho)001:6948: ma bcos kun gzhi'i klong nas rang byung bde chen 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6949: ma bcos rang bzhin bzhag pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:6950: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di yin te //
NK126(cho)001:6951: de las lhag pa bsgom du ci yang med //
NK126(cho)001:6952: bsgom du med pa'i chos dbyings chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:6953: bsam du med pa rig pa ma yengs zhog /
NK126(cho)001:6954: lta bsgom man ngag bya ba de las med //
NK126(cho)001:6955: b+aee ro tsa na bdag nyid kyis //
NK126(cho)001:6956: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs phyungs bas //
NK126(cho)001:6957: man ngag gter chen zab mo 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6958: dga' rab 'jam dpal thugs rje bshad //
NK126(cho)001:6959: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gsum gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6960: man ngag gter chen sbas pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6961: b+aee ro tsa na'i thugs kyi bcud //
NK126(cho)001:6962: g.yu sgra snying po bu la gtad //
NK126(cho)001:6963: yang nas yang du sems la lhon //
NK126(cho)001:6964: khyod kyi zhus pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6965: sems la snying bzhin brtse ba las //
NK126(cho)001:6966: khe drag nor ngor btang ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:6967: kha 'jam brid ngor ston pa na //
NK126(cho)001:6968: mgo bo gas shing lus yang 'jig /
NK126(cho)001:6969: mthar yang 'bras bu brlag par gdon mi za //
NK126(cho)001:6972: yang rab blo ldan re dang 'phrad par shog /
NK126(cho)001:6973: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa na yis //
NK126(cho)001:6974: mkhas pa'i man ngag ta ki rnams //
NK126(cho)001:6975: bka' ba las dang bsdos nas btsal ba 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6976: bshad lugs grangs med mang po yang //
NK126(cho)001:6977: sa bcad rang lugs drangs tshig dka' //
NK126(cho)001:6978: rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6980: gzhan la med par yid ches gyis //
NK126(cho)001:6981: g.yu sgra snying po'i thugs la stims //
NK126(cho)001:6982: b+aee ro tsa na'i bka' med par //
NK126(cho)001:6983: khe drag nor 'dod mkhan po yi //
NK126(cho)001:6984: rdzun gyi sha bcug zang du byas //
NK126(cho)001:6985: tshig gi sgro 'dogs mang pos bslad //
NK126(cho)001:6986: med pa'i rgyu 'bras khur du khur //
NK126(cho)001:6987: man ngag ti ka gsang chen 'di //
NK126(cho)001:6988: gzhan la yod re na ra kan //
NK126(cho)001:6989: ces b+aee ro tsa nas dbu bsnyung bzhes nas /
NK126(cho)001:6990: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la man ngag gi bcud gtig cing gnang ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:6991: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po'i yab rgyal po rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:6993: sku tshe lo brgya nyi shu lon nas grangs so //
NK126(cho)001:6994: yul tsha ba rong ba yin /
NK126(cho)001:6996: b+aee ro tsa nas g.yu sgra snying po la man
NK126(cho)001:6997: ngag gi bcud btig cing bro bar po'i skabs te
NK126(cho)001:6998: nyer gcig pa'o //// de nas b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul nas rgya nag por byon te /
NK126(cho)001:6999: bdag 'dra 'khyams po b+aee ro tsa na yis //
NK126(cho)001:7000: sngon gyi las dbang rngag pas tsha ba'i yul du mchis //
NK126(cho)001:7001: tsha ba'i rgyal khams dam pa'i chos la bsgyur nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:7002: rgya nag mkhas pa kun dang dgongs pa bsdur du mchi //
NK126(cho)001:7004: rgya nag po'i ku su lu b+hi ti g+har+b+hasa 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:7005: de kho nyid don skor lnga gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7006: ye shes spyi blugs su 'char ba nyi ma lta bu /
NK126(cho)001:7007: chos nyid thugs 'phrad du 'char ba rgyal po mthong ba lta bu /
NK126(cho)001:7008: rnam rtog ye shes su 'char ba /
NK126(cho)001:7009: nags la me shor ba lta bu /
NK126(cho)001:7010: mtshan ma rang sar grol ba /
NK126(cho)001:7012: ting nge 'dzin 'byung 'jug med pas gser gling du phyin pa lta bu /
NK126(cho)001:7013: de ltar don skor lngas bstan pa la /
NK126(cho)001:7015: dus thams cad du gsal 'grib med par gnas pa bzhin du /
NK126(cho)001:7016: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:7017: dran tshad snang tshad bzang ngan dang /
NK126(cho)001:7018: blang dor gyi mtshan ma med de rig pa rang shar chen po /
NK126(cho)001:7019: ye shes spyi blugs su shar ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:7021: rgyal po mthong bas gnyen po'i sems thugs 'phrad du 'char ba bzhin /
NK126(cho)001:7022: rnal 'byor pas kyang dbang po rnam lnga /
NK126(cho)001:7025: snang tshad sems nyid rang snang /
NK126(cho)001:7026: rang shar yin pas chos nyid thug 'phrad du rang shar rang snang ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:7031: che ba dang chung ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:7034: rdo la sogs pa thams cad me'i grogs su 'char ba bzhin du /
NK126(cho)001:7035: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems nyid du shes pas /
NK126(cho)001:7051: chos nyid rang shar ba min pa med do //
NK126(cho)001:7068: nag po kun rang shar rang byung /
NK126(cho)001:7070: rang grol nam mkha' nyid las rdul tsam las med /
NK126(cho)001:7071: de bzhin du byang chub sems nyid ni /
NK126(cho)001:7075: rigs drug kun byang chub sems su skye ba med /
NK126(cho)001:7076: 'khor 'das nyon mongs bde sdug kun byang chub sems yin ye nas grol /
NK126(cho)001:7088: thams cad du yang gser gyi ngo bor yod pa bzhin /
NK126(cho)001:7089: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems rang byung gi
NK126(cho)001:7090: ye shes bcos bslad kyi rgyu rkyen dang bral nas
NK126(cho)001:7091: 'dug / sems las gzhan pa'i chos med pas /
NK126(cho)001:7092: ting nge 'dzin nyams su blang bya dang /
NK126(cho)001:7094: dgongs pa de lta bu dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK126(cho)001:7095: ye shes spyi blugs su 'char bas gol sgrib med pas thag chad do //
NK126(cho)001:7096: chos sku thug 'phrad du shar bas spang len med par thag chad do //
NK126(cho)001:7097: rnam rtog ye shes su shar bas skyon yon la spang len med par thag chod do //
NK126(cho)001:7098: mtshan ma rang grol du 'dug pas /
NK126(cho)001:7099: blos yi dam gyi lha bsgom mi dgos par thag chod do //
NK126(cho)001:7101: 'bad rtsol bya mi dgos par thag chod do //
NK126(cho)001:7103: rgya nag ku su lu b+hi ti g+har+b+ha nyid dang
NK126(cho)001:7104: zhal thug gi mjal yang dgos pa 'di las dpag
NK126(cho)001:7106: dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la /
NK126(cho)001:7107: gdams pa kun gyis go ba ma yin /
NK126(cho)001:7108: sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7111: 1 yang dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la /
NK126(cho)001:7112: rgya nag po'i mkhas pa ku su lu d+har+m+aa b+ho d+his /
NK126(cho)001:7113: rtsol bsgrub la bzlas te de kho na nyid rdo rje'i tshig gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7114: lta ba'i la zlo na mun pa'i smag la rug /
NK126(cho)001:7115: bsgom pa la chod na rang srog chod de //
NK126(cho)001:7116: spyod pa la zlo na gtad med phyal pa bu chung 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:7117: skye shi la la zlo na sems can gyi rang srog chod //
NK126(cho)001:7118: 'bras bu'i la zla na re dogs kyi sems thag pa chod //
NK126(cho)001:7119: rgyu rkyen phyag mas btab pas ye shes kyi la zlos //
NK126(cho)001:7120: ces b+aee ro tsa na la gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7121: rgya nag d+har+m+aa b+ho d+hi nyid dang zhal mjal yang //
NK126(cho)001:7122: dgongs pa de las dpag tu med pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:7123: sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7126: 2 yang dge slong b+aee ro tsa nas /
NK126(cho)001:7127: rgya nag po'i mkhas pa ku su lu badz+ra su ke de ba la gdams pa zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:7128: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i gdams pa 'di gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:7132: sgo lnga'i yul du sems kyi dran rtog gang byung yang /
NK126(cho)001:7133: sprul pa'i sku nyid shar ba yin /
NK126(cho)001:7134: gang shar cig ltar snang yang rang bzhin med de /
NK126(cho)001:7136: zad pa dang shar ba dbyer med de /
NK126(cho)001:7137: longs skur ye nas gnas pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:7138: rang shar rang zad rang snang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:7140: skye med 'dus ma byas su 'dug pas bsgom pa'i blo dang bral /
NK126(cho)001:7141: ci shar sku gsum lcog bzhengs su 'dug pas spyod pa'i blo dang bral /
NK126(cho)001:7142: sku gsum lhun grub tu ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK126(cho)001:7144: ces dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7145: badz+ra pu ka de ba nyid dang mjal yang de las dpag tu med pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:7146: kun gyi go ma yin pas sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7148: 3 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7149: pa ku su lu pan ti bar ma la gdams
NK126(cho)001:7150: pa zhus pas / rig pa cer zin gyi man ngag gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7151: rang gi sems la ltos dang /
NK126(cho)001:7152: rgyu rkyen kha dog dngos po gda' lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:7153: skye 'jig bral bas ma mthong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:7154: nam mkha' lta bu'i don la gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:7155: phyi'i yul la phar ltas pas //
NK126(cho)001:7156: snang tshad rang gi sems su 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:7157: nang du ltas pas nga dang bdag la rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:7158: nyams su blangs bya'ang mi gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:7159: cir snang rang shar de la dgag bsgrub med //
NK126(cho)001:7160: thob bya thob byed med pas 'bras bu'o //
NK126(cho)001:7161: gza' gtad phyogs ris med pas lta ba'i la chod yin //
NK126(cho)001:7162: zher 'dzin dmigs gtad med pas bsgom pa'i la chod yin //
NK126(cho)001:7163: cir yang chos skur shes na spyod pa'i la chod yin //
NK126(cho)001:7164: 'khor 'das rgyu 'bras re dogs bral tsam na //
NK126(cho)001:7165: 'bras bu'i la chod de ru chod //
NK126(cho)001:7166: ces dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7167: pan ti bar ma nyid dang mjal /
NK126(cho)001:7168: yang dgongs pa de las dpag tu med pa yin no //
NK126(cho)001:7169: kun gyi mi go sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7173: 4 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7174: pa tsan+d+ha ri khrod pa la gdams pa zhus pas
NK126(cho)001:7175: / ri khrod pas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:7176: rtogs pa klong du chud par bya /
NK126(cho)001:7177: snang ba dbang du 'dus par bya /
NK126(cho)001:7182: dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7183: tsan+d+hi ri khrod pa dang mjal yang dgongs pa de las dpag tu med pa yin no //
NK126(cho)001:7184: kun gyi mi go bas sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7186: 5 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7187: pa ku su lu ma h+aa be de la gdams
NK126(cho)001:7189: 'gyu ba dang sangs kyi gdams pa gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7197: sangs pa dang dus mnyams so //
NK126(cho)001:7199: 'gyu ba ni nyol tshor byung ba'i dus /
NK126(cho)001:7201: rig pa rang shar khyug gis shar ba'i dus /
NK126(cho)001:7202: bltas pas skye med zang thal /
NK126(cho)001:7203: de la bzhag pas 'dzin med du dngas /
NK126(cho)001:7207: grol ba ma skyes zang thal lo //
NK126(cho)001:7208: de ltar thams cad ngo bo nyid du grol te /
NK126(cho)001:7209: chos sku blo yul du dbyer med de /
NK126(cho)001:7211: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7212: rgya nag po'i mkhas pa ma h+aa b+ae de nyid
NK126(cho)001:7213: dang mjal yang dgongs pa de las dpag tu med
NK126(cho)001:7214: do // kun gyi mi go sa ma ya rgya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7216: 6 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7217: pa ku su lu sh+ri la ni la gdams pa
NK126(cho)001:7218: zhus pa la / rlung gsum rang sar dang ba'i gdams pa gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7227: des na dgongs pa bla ma yid yul 'das pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7228: de ltar ma shes te nang nas phyi'i rlung 'tshub pas /
NK126(cho)001:7232: rang rlung dngas su ma shes na /
NK126(cho)001:7234: ces dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7235: mkhas pa sh+ri la ni nyid dang mjal yang dgongs
NK126(cho)001:7236: pa 'di las dpag tu med pa kun gyi go
NK126(cho)001:7238: sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7239: 7 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7240: pa ku su lu ha shang b+hi ti la gdams
NK126(cho)001:7241: pa zhus pa / thag chod pa rdo rje'i tshig drug pa 'di gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7242: snang srid thams cad nam mkha'i klong du 'dus pas /
NK126(cho)001:7243: dngos po rang mtshan med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7244: 'khor 'das kyi snying po sems su 'dus pas /
NK126(cho)001:7245: sangs rgyas gzhan du med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7246: bde ba sgyu mar snang bas /
NK126(cho)001:7247: sdug bsngal la rang bzhin med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7248: stong pa'i 'od la bsam du med pas /
NK126(cho)001:7249: sems rang byung du 'bar ba thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7250: ye shes la skye 'gags med pas /
NK126(cho)001:7253: skye ba mi len par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7254: ces dge slob b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7256: 8 yang b+aee ro tsa na rgya nag po'i mkhas pa ku su lu d+har+m+aa b+ho d+hi'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:7257: dge slong nam mkha' la ltos dang /
NK126(cho)001:7262: de ring gi sprin de kha sang gi sprin de men /
NK126(cho)001:7263: nang par gyi sprin ni di ring mi 'ong /
NK126(cho)001:7264: dge slong rang gi sems la ltos dang /
NK126(cho)001:7267: de ring gis dran rtog ni kha sang gi dran rtog min /
NK126(cho)001:7268: de ring gi dran rtog nang par mi sdod /
NK126(cho)001:7269: nang par gyi dran rtog de ring mi 'ong /
NK126(cho)001:7270: dran rtog rang byung rang dngas su 'dug pas /
NK126(cho)001:7272: nyon mongs ye shes rang byung rang dngas yin /
NK126(cho)001:7273: nam mkha' stong pa la ri mo bri ba'i sa med /
NK126(cho)001:7274: rig pa stong pa la sdig pa bsogs pa'i gnas med /
NK126(cho)001:7275: chu bran chu bo ci snyed kun //
