NK126(cho)001:7276: rgya mtsho nyid du ro cig bye brag med //
NK126(cho)001:7277: ces dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7278: sa ma ya snod med la na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7279: 9 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7280: pa ku su lu sur+ya g+hirti la gdams pa zhus
NK126(cho)001:7284: rig pa gcig gcod man ngag bzhi dang ldan par byas /
NK126(cho)001:7285: thug 'phrad rgyal po lta bus dran rtog ye shes ngos bzung /
NK126(cho)001:7286: cog bzhag bya lta bus rnam rtog ye shes ngos bzung /
NK126(cho)001:7287: rang rdol ko mo'i rig pa rang rdol /
NK126(cho)001:7288: rig pa chu lta bus 'khor 'das kyi bde sdug
NK126(cho)001:7289: mnyam par rtogs nas rang grol dgongs pa rnyed par
NK126(cho)001:7290: yin / gcig chod lo ngar btub pa lta bus chos thams cad ngo bo cig tu rtogs so //
NK126(cho)001:7291: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7293: 10 yang b+aee ro tsa na la rgya nag po'i
NK126(cho)001:7294: mkhas pa ku su lu shan+ta a tis dngos po'i
NK126(cho)001:7295: 'dug lugs de kho nyid gdams pa /
NK126(cho)001:7296: thams cad sangs rgyas nyag gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7299: phyi nang med pa'i zang thal chen po /
NK126(cho)001:7300: thams cad ye shes gcig tu rtogs pas zang thal chen po /
NK126(cho)001:7301: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7304: 11 yang b+aee ro tsa na la rgya nag po'i
NK126(cho)001:7305: ku su lu yo gi ni dur khrod pas gdams
NK126(cho)001:7306: pa / snying po byang chub kyi sems /
NK126(cho)001:7307: ci bzhin pa de rtogs par bya /
NK126(cho)001:7309: rtogs snyams pa de yid kyi rtogs pa yid kyi yid chos kyi gdings ma rnyed na /
NK126(cho)001:7310: re dogs kyi thag pa chod dgos /
NK126(cho)001:7311: de tsa na gnyis med brjod 'das bsam med brjod du med /
NK126(cho)001:7312: ngos bzung dang bral ba'i chos nyid blo yul du ma gyur pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7313: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams pa /
NK126(cho)001:7316: 12 yang b+aee ro tsa na la rgya nag po'i ku su lu pa tri ni pas /
NK126(cho)001:7317: de kho na nyid kyi rtsad gcod gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:7318: dang po sems kyi byung sa tshol /
NK126(cho)001:7319: bar du sems kyi gnas sa tshol /
NK126(cho)001:7320: tha ma sems kyi 'gro sa tshol /
NK126(cho)001:7321: dang po sems kyi byung sa med pa rgyu med pa gcig yin /
NK126(cho)001:7322: bar du sems kyi gnas sa med pas lam med pa gcig yin /
NK126(cho)001:7323: tha ma sems la 'gro sa med pas 'bras bu la bsgrub med cig yin /
NK126(cho)001:7324: de ltar rtogs pa lta ba /
NK126(cho)001:7325: de la yid ches pa bsgom pa /
NK126(cho)001:7326: de la yid ches pa spyod pa /
NK126(cho)001:7327: de la thob bya thob byed med pa 'bras bu'o //
NK126(cho)001:7328: de nas ye dag chen po /
NK126(cho)001:7333: gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:7334: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7336: blo chung la na ra kan /
NK126(cho)001:7339: 13 yang dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la rgya
NK126(cho)001:7340: nag po'i ku su lu yo gi bar mas 'di
NK126(cho)001:7341: skad gsungs so // lta ba yin pa med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7342: de la bsgom du cir yang med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7343: spyod pa spang len med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7344: 'bras bu la thob bya thob rgyu med par thag chod /
NK126(cho)001:7345: rnal 'byor rab kyi dgongs pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:7347: 14 yang yo gi bar mas blo gsar bu la gdams pa /
NK126(cho)001:7348: skyes bu lta byed la brten nas lta mkhan ngos bzung /
NK126(cho)001:7350: bsgom bya bsgom byed la brten nas /
NK126(cho)001:7352: bsgom snang la brten nas bsgom pa ma mthong gi dngos po'i 'dug tshul ltos dang /
NK126(cho)001:7354: spyod bya la brten nas spyod mkhan ngos bzung dang bral nas gada'o //
NK126(cho)001:7355: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7361: 15 yang dge slong b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag
NK126(cho)001:7362: gi mkhas pa ku su lu he yo gi grong
NK126(cho)001:7363: khyer ba la gdams pa zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:7364: 'jug sgo gsum gyi man ngag gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7368: snang ba rang snang du shes pas phyi'i 'jug sgo gtan la pheb /
NK126(cho)001:7369: shar ba rang shar du shes pas nang gi 'jug sgo gtan la pheb /
NK126(cho)001:7370: yin lugs ma skyes skye med du shes pas gsang ba'i 'jug sgo gtan la pheb ste /
NK126(cho)001:7371: lus rang rig btsal du med pas /
NK126(cho)001:7372: lus sems gnyis sbrel mkhan med de /
NK126(cho)001:7373: 'gro sa sangs rgyas las med pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:7374: snang ba rang snang du shes pas rkyen las byung ba'i ma rig pa sangs /
NK126(cho)001:7375: shar ba rang shar du shes pas rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma rigs pa sangs /
NK126(cho)001:7376: rlung rang rtsal du gnon pas /
NK126(cho)001:7377: gnyis can las byung ba'i ma rig pa sangs /
NK126(cho)001:7378: lus sems gnyis kyi 'brel pa thag chod pas /
NK126(cho)001:7379: des sgrib pa gsum las grol te /
NK126(cho)001:7381: zhes dge slob b+aee ro tsa na la gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:7383: 16 b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas pa
NK126(cho)001:7384: ku su lu he seng ngu la gdams pa zhus
NK126(cho)001:7385: pa / skye 'gags gnyis med kyi man ngag gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7386: 'gags pa med pa'i stag mgo dgu pa de'i pha rol tu ltos shig /
NK126(cho)001:7387: skye med du thag chod nas gda'/
NK126(cho)001:7388: de gnyis kyi bar du ltos dang /
NK126(cho)001:7389: de la brjod du gda' yeng /
NK126(cho)001:7396: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7398: 17 yang b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas
NK126(cho)001:7399: pa ku su lu yo gi ni ri khrod pa
NK126(cho)001:7400: la gdams pa zhus pa 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7401: sangs rgyas par 'dod na rtsol ba zhog /
NK126(cho)001:7402: sems blta bar 'dod na rang gi dbugs la ltos /
NK126(cho)001:7403: ye shes 'dod na dran pa rtag tu ltos /
NK126(cho)001:7404: bde ba 'dod na dug lnga'i ngo bo rnyed dam ltos /
NK126(cho)001:7405: sangs rgyas par 'dod na phung ba yin /
NK126(cho)001:7406: zhes dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la mkha' 'gro mas gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7409: 18 b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas pa
NK126(cho)001:7410: ku su lu pradz+ny+aa g+hirti la gdams pa zhus pa
NK126(cho)001:7421: shes bcu ldan na grol bar gda' gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7422: dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7425: 19 b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i rnal 'byor
NK126(cho)001:7426: ma la nges pa'i don ci ltar lags dris pas
NK126(cho)001:7427: / ri khrod ma chung ngus 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7428: mkha' ltar dag pa rtogs pa na //
NK126(cho)001:7429: dge sdig gnyis ka tha snyad tsam //
NK126(cho)001:7430: bdud dang 'khor ba gdod nas med //
NK126(cho)001:7431: skye med chos la rtsol ba med //
NK126(cho)001:7432: rnal grol med de rnam par bcing ba med //
NK126(cho)001:7433: byang chub snying po bya ba gdod nas med //
NK126(cho)001:7434: gang zhig byis pas de ltar ma rig ste //
NK126(cho)001:7435: don med sgra phyir 'brang ba rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7436: dge ba'i chos ni rnams spang nas //
NK126(cho)001:7437: 'khor ba'i chos la chags shing 'dzin pa che //
NK126(cho)001:7439: ces dge slong b+aee ro tsa na la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7440: 20lcam pa rje rgyal b+aee ro tsa na la /
NK126(cho)001:7441: rgya nag po'i mkhas pa rnams dang /
NK126(cho)001:7456: 'di tshe zad sgrib pa zad pa rnams dang 'phrad par smon /
NK126(cho)001:7458: nyang chab gtsang chab 'dab pa'i rtsa //
NK126(cho)001:7459: po'u'i gan jag b+aee ro tsa na bdag /
NK126(cho)001:7460: skad rigs mi 'dra sum brgya drug cu dang //
NK126(cho)001:7461: yig rigs mi cig sum brgya drug cu shes //
NK126(cho)001:7462: dkar nag rgya dang u rgyan yul //
NK126(cho)001:7463: mkhas pa rnams kyi thugs mdzod brdol //
NK126(cho)001:7464: 'di ni rgya nag yul gyi rgyal khams na //
NK126(cho)001:7465: ha shang gar pa la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:7466: ri brag shing drung dur khrod nas //
NK126(cho)001:7467: rnal 'byor rnams kyi la zla re //
NK126(cho)001:7468: b+aee ro tsa na bdag la gnang //
NK126(cho)001:7469: skal ldan mos pa 'ga' bdog pas //
NK126(cho)001:7470: 'di dag rtogs par shin tu dka' //
NK126(cho)001:7471: rgyal ba'i yig 'bru dang po la //
NK126(cho)001:7472: ka zhing kha bar gsungs nas gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7473: ka kha ces pa gsungs pas mngon //
NK126(cho)001:7474: rang gi blo yi ma rtogs rtogs ldan rnams la sgro skur 'debs //
NK126(cho)001:7475: des sgrib gol bas dmyal bar 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:7476: bskal pa 'bum du mi thar te //
NK126(cho)001:7477: na rag chen por nges par ltung //
NK126(cho)001:7478: de phyir rdzogs chen man ngag rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7479: shin tu gsang ngo thub par sbos //
NK126(cho)001:7480: g.yu sgra snying po khyod la gtad //
NK126(cho)001:7481: sa ma ya ni dam tshig rgya //
NK126(cho)001:7482: dam tshig rgya yi mnan la sba //
NK126(cho)001:7486: las rab skal bar ldan pa ma rnyed na //
NK126(cho)001:7487: srog la bab kyang sba bar bya //
NK126(cho)001:7489: thabs kyi dpe kun thob la re //
NK126(cho)001:7490: mos pas mi zhu thabs kyi 'bru //
NK126(cho)001:7491: bla ma spyi gtsug mi khur phyag dang zhe sa med //
NK126(cho)001:7492: gces pa'i nor mchog mi phod par //
NK126(cho)001:7493: chags zhen ser snas bcings pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:7494: lag tu thob na gzhog ngom byed //
NK126(cho)001:7495: zong du tshong gin kha tshig bshad //
NK126(cho)001:7496: de 'dra'i lag tu shor srid na //
NK126(cho)001:7497: bdag gzhan gnyis ka brlag par 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:7499: lo nyes sad ser la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:7500: bskal pa phra mo glo bur 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:7501: nad rims dpe ngan dar bar 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:7502: des na a tig rdzogs chen man ngag shin tu sba //
NK126(cho)001:7503: mthu dang ngan sngags shin tu sba //
NK126(cho)001:7504: ngan thabs gdug pa'i las 'di shin tu sba //
NK126(cho)001:7506: dam nyams rnams kyi bsgrub pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:7508: mu stegs la logs bsgrub pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:7509: snod ngan lag tu song na ni //
NK126(cho)001:7510: smyon pa'i lag tu mtshon cha bskur 'dra ste //
NK126(cho)001:7512: des na man ngag sba bar bya //
NK126(cho)001:7513: g.yu sgra snying po bu gces rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du /
NK126(cho)001:7514: g.yu sgra snying po la rgya nag gi mkhas pa
NK126(cho)001:7515: rnams kyi dgongs pa rje b+aee ro tsa nas zhus
NK126(cho)001:7517: g.yu sgra snying pos bod yul du rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7518: des sogs po lha dpal gyi ye shes la gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:7519: des gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:7521: b+aee ro tsa nas rgya nag po'i mkhas pa ku su lu rnams dang /
NK126(cho)001:7522: dgongs pa bsdur ba'i skabs te nyer gnyis pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:7523: de'i dus de'i tshe khri srong lde'u btsan grongs nas /
NK126(cho)001:7525: sras mu ne btsad po chung bar yod nas /
NK126(cho)001:7526: sras mu ne btsad po dang /
NK126(cho)001:7527: bod kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams /
NK126(cho)001:7528: rje chos kyi bsdur ba dga'/
NK126(cho)001:7529: blon po rje bon gyis bsdur ba dga' ba las /
NK126(cho)001:7530: sras mu ne btsad po dang /
NK126(cho)001:7531: bod kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams dbang che ste /
NK126(cho)001:7532: rje b+aee ro tsa na rgya nag po nas byon
NK126(cho)001:7533: nas rgyal mo tsha ba rong na bzhugs zer pa
NK126(cho)001:7534: sras mu ni btsad po gsan nas /
NK126(cho)001:7536: zhu sna ba sba ba can gnyis rje chos kyi
NK126(cho)001:7537: bsdur ba la slob dpon b+aee ro tsa na rgyal
NK126(cho)001:7538: mo tsha ba'i rong du bzhugs pa spyan 'dren du
NK126(cho)001:7539: btang ba la / rje b+aee ro tsa na tsha
NK126(cho)001:7540: ba'i rong nas bod du gshegs par byas pa la
NK126(cho)001:7541: btang ba la / / rgyal mo tsha ba rong pa ma dga' ste /
NK126(cho)001:7542: lha rje bla ma mkhas pa chen po //
NK126(cho)001:7543: bsgres kha sa phyogs ngan par gda' bas bod yul du mi gshegs par zhu byas te /
NK126(cho)001:7545: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7546: 'khor 'das chos nyid klong nas shar ba la //
NK126(cho)001:7547: phyogs dang ris su 'dzin pa snying re rje //
NK126(cho)001:7548: gzung 'dzin gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK126(cho)001:7549: nga ni gdul bya'i sems can smon lam btab nas yod pas 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:7550: khyed rnams chags zhen med par gdams pa'i steng na zhog /
NK126(cho)001:7552: mkhas pa'i mkhas pa man ngag bcu dang ldan //
NK126(cho)001:7553: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi bla na gnyen //
NK126(cho)001:7554: rje ma h+aa g+hu ru rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:7555: b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:7556: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal ngo dngos bstan pa dang 'dra ba'i /
NK126(cho)001:7557: 'dra 'bags chen mo zhes bya ba'i lta ba'i rgyal po'o //
NK126(cho)001:7560: zla ba ni khra yi zla ba'i nya la /
NK126(cho)001:7562: zhu sna ba sba ba can gnyis kyi b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba rong nas spyan drangs te /
NK126(cho)001:7563: dpal dbus kyi bsam yas su byon pas /
NK126(cho)001:7564: mi rnams kun gyi la las ni dar phyar /
NK126(cho)001:7566: la las ni cha lang brdab /
NK126(cho)001:7567: la las ni dril bu bkrol /
NK126(cho)001:7569: la las ni bdug spos khol /
NK126(cho)001:7576: la las ni dga' ches ngus /
NK126(cho)001:7577: la las ni rin chen sna tshogs phul /
NK126(cho)001:7578: rje mnga' bdag gi rje'i bla g.yu dkar po seng ge nyal ba phul lo //
NK126(cho)001:7579: kun gyis lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam brtsal lo //
NK126(cho)001:7580: de nas rje blon 'bangs gsum khrom rnams kyis /
NK126(cho)001:7581: zhabs g.yas pa'i pus mo lha nga sa la btsug ste /
NK126(cho)001:7582: rje ma h+aa gu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:7583: sku ni mi nub rgyal mtshan rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:7584: dkar nag rgya dang u rgyan bal yul mon dang bod //
NK126(cho)001:7585: gdug pa'i sgra yis ma tshugs rdo rje 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:7586: b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la bdag cag 'dud //
NK126(cho)001:7587: gsung ni tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi bka' rgyud kyi //
NK126(cho)001:7588: man ngag gsum ni dus kyi sbrang char lta bur sgrogs //
NK126(cho)001:7589: b+aee ro tsa na'i gsung la bdag cag 'dud //
NK126(cho)001:7590: thugs ni nyi ma'i snying po lta bur gsal sgrib med //
NK126(cho)001:7591: b+aee ro tsa na'i thugs la bdag cag 'dud //
NK126(cho)001:7592: yon tan ma lus rdzogs pa yis //
NK126(cho)001:7593: lha rdzas rin chen lta bus dgos 'dod sna tshogs 'byung //
NK126(cho)001:7594: b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK126(cho)001:7595: phrin las thabs kyi sems can don du mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:7596: b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK126(cho)001:7598: rje b+aee ro tsa nas lan gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:7601: rje yi bka' stsal bdud pas gnyan /
NK126(cho)001:7602: b+aee ro tsa na bdag la bsdad pa'i dbang med stong khams khyab par 'khyam /
NK126(cho)001:7603: na tsha shi chad mi gda' snyam par gda'/
NK126(cho)001:7604: dbu mdzad zhal g.yar ma mchis bar du sku gsung thugs la bse ra ma mchis sam /
NK126(cho)001:7606: de nas b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba'i yul nas
NK126(cho)001:7607: bod du byon pa'i zhabs tog la g.yu sgra snying
NK126(cho)001:7609: rgyal po grongs pa'i shing khra bo byed pa'i khrom mang po 'tshogs pa'i gseb du gral med nas /
NK126(cho)001:7610: b+aee ro tsa na cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyi rgyab tu bzhugs pas /
NK126(cho)001:7611: cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyi rgyab nas phar gzigs pas /
NK126(cho)001:7613: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:7615: der cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyi kag gi long
NK126(cho)001:7616: nas b+aee ro tsa na dang g.yu sgra la phyag
NK126(cho)001:7617: byas te / der cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyi gdan la /
NK126(cho)001:7618: pa gor b+aee ro tsa na la bzhugs su bcol nas /
NK126(cho)001:7619: de nas rje b+aee ro tsa nas dgongs pa mdzad de /
NK126(cho)001:7620: g.yu sgra snying po'i cho ga mkhan po mdzad pas /
NK126(cho)001:7621: bon po dang sngags pa gral mgo ma 'cham pa la /
NK126(cho)001:7622: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i gral mgo bzung pas h+aum zhes gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:7623: b+aee ro tsa na'i lus po khro chu du byin gyis brlabs te sprul pas /
NK126(cho)001:7624: bon po rnams bred de gral mgo nas 'thon no //
NK126(cho)001:7625: der rje bsdur ba'i dus su gshen po khri srong lde'u btsan du sprul nas /
NK126(cho)001:7626: la thod ye re byung bas /
NK126(cho)001:7628: rje nyid kyi byin brlabs kyi khug nas byon pa yin zer ba la /
NK126(cho)001:7629: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas rje min /
NK126(cho)001:7630: gshen po rje ru sprul nas 'ong ba yin byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:7632: gshen po min rje nyid kyi mthus khug pa yin zer ba la /
NK126(cho)001:7633: rje yin nam gshen po yin nga'i lta'o gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:7634: b+aee ros mig bsgrang te bsdigs mdzub phyar te /
NK126(cho)001:7635: h+aum zhes gsungs te bon pos khug pa'i rje de gshed por song ste /
NK126(cho)001:7636: skad ngan dang bcas te gar song cha med par bros so //
NK126(cho)001:7637: der bon po rnams kyang ngo log ste 'khros so //
NK126(cho)001:7638: blon po rnams kyang rje chos kyi bsdur ba la ma dga' ste dbang med do //
NK126(cho)001:7639: rje khri srong lde'u btsan yang chos kyi bsdur ro //
NK126(cho)001:7640: sngags pa de nas gnyen par byas so //
NK126(cho)001:7641: bon thams cad kyis sngags pa spyi bor khur bar byas so //
NK126(cho)001:7642: de nas rje b+aee ro tsa nas chos thang dkar gyi yang thog tu bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)001:7644: gser srang sum cu tham pa phul nas rmad du byung ba bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:7646: b+aee ro tsa na dgung lo bdun cu rtsa gsum
NK126(cho)001:7647: la tsha ba rong nas bod du byon pa'i skabs
NK126(cho)001:7648: te nyi shu rtsa gsum pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:7649: de nas kun gyis bza' skyems mang po drangs nas
NK126(cho)001:7650: bdag cag 'khor rnams dam pa'i chos la ci ltar
NK126(cho)001:7651: 'jug par bgyi / chos la ci ltar spyad nas legs pa lags /
NK126(cho)001:7653: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7654: thos bsam mang po byas nas slob ma 'du //
NK126(cho)001:7655: dam tshig ma nyams par srung na dam can 'du /
NK126(cho)001:7656: dam can 'du na byin brlabs che ste longs spyod 'du /
NK126(cho)001:7657: mi chos mkhas na mi kha byams te 'khor dang longs spyod 'du /
NK126(cho)001:7658: chos pa byed na kha na ma tho ba ma gsungs mdzod /
NK126(cho)001:7659: kha gtam smras pas gzhan gyi snying la phog pas kha song snying song du ma smra mdzod /
NK126(cho)001:7660: spyir yang kha ni bdud kyi sgo mo lags kyi smra ba ma mang mdzod /
NK126(cho)001:7661: da ni cha yod dam lnga yod de /
NK126(cho)001:7662: sos kos byed byed 'chi kos brjed pa cha yod dam /
NK126(cho)001:7663: rang sems ma rtogs pa la byas tshad rnam smin sogs pa cha yod dam /
NK126(cho)001:7664: chos nyid ma rtogs par brjod tshad 'khrul gtam yin pa cha yod dam /
NK126(cho)001:7665: mi gros byed byed nas rang tshe zad pa cha yod dam /
NK126(cho)001:7666: tshogs sogs byed zer nas med pa la phral nas mi dgos pa la 'bul ba cha yod dam /
NK126(cho)001:7667: da mi 'tsheng pa bzhi yod de /
NK126(cho)001:7668: tshogs bsags pa'i mis slang yang mi ster ba'i dge rtsa des kyang ma 'tshengs so //
NK126(cho)001:7669: yang dge rtsa byed zer nas mi bla 'dres khyer
NK126(cho)001:7670: nas mi sha phyugs la len pa'i dge rtsa des
NK126(cho)001:7672: dad pa can yin zer nas 'chi ba mi dran pa'i chos nyan des kyang ma 'tshengs so //
NK126(cho)001:7673: chos pa yin zer nas gos ring po gon nas
NK126(cho)001:7674: lto bza' yang mi khom par rgyug 'dram byed pa'i
NK126(cho)001:7675: chos pa des kyang ma 'tshengs so //
NK126(cho)001:7676: da ni rtsing po bzhi yod do //
NK126(cho)001:7677: ngag gi spyod lam rtsing nas don med par dgra sdang /
NK126(cho)001:7678: lus kyi spyod lam rtsing nas don med pa'i na tsha 'ong /
NK126(cho)001:7679: sems kyi spyod lam rtsing nas don med pa'i sdug bsngal byed /
NK126(cho)001:7680: za 'thung gi spyod lam rtsing nas don med pa'i 'thab mo 'ong /
NK126(cho)001:7681: da ni rgod bro ba bzhi yod de /
NK126(cho)001:7682: rgyud ngan 'grogs zla ma rnyed pa'i cig gtam sprang po de yang rgod re bro /
NK126(cho)001:7683: grod po che'i ltog med de yang rgod re bro /
NK126(cho)001:7684: ma thub pa'i bzod pa bsgom pa de yang rgod re bro /
NK126(cho)001:7685: ma rnyed pa'i chags med de yang rgod re bro /
NK126(cho)001:7686: da ni rung ba bzhi yod do //
NK126(cho)001:7687: gnam stong srung ba bas stong nyid srung na rung /
NK126(cho)001:7688: bco lnga bsrungs ba bas dug lnga srung na rung /
NK126(cho)001:7689: tshes brgya bsrung ba bas drag pa'i chos brgyad bsrung na rung /
NK126(cho)001:7690: spyir sdom pa srung ba bas sdig bcu bsrung na rung /
NK126(cho)001:7691: de la kril gyi slob ma bzhi yod de /
NK126(cho)001:7692: sbyin pa'i lam du zhugs tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:7693: ser sna'i mdud pa kril gyis slob /
NK126(cho)001:7694: bzod pa'i lam du zhug tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:7695: khang khro cig gi kril gyi slob /
NK126(cho)001:7696: brtson 'grus lam du zhugs tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:7697: le lo cig gi kril gyi slob /
NK126(cho)001:7699: dgung dang nyi zla gling bzhi bskor ba bas //
NK126(cho)001:7700: 'o skol tshe zad mgyogs par gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7701: rgya mtshor pha wong bskyur ba bas //
NK126(cho)001:7702: 'o skol tshe zad mgyogs par gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7703: skyes pa'i dpag chen mda' bas ni //
NK126(cho)001:7704: 'o skol tshe zad mgyogs pa gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7705: mi tshe mi sdod 'gro yin gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7706: 'o skol 'chi ba mi dran stor shing gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7707: lus kyi sdug bsngal chu chad nya dang 'dra ste ya re cha //
NK126(cho)001:7708: ngag gi sdug bsngal rnga mang gi bu stor ba 'dra ste ya re cha //
NK126(cho)001:7709: sems kyi sdug bsngal mgron po bsgug rar tshud pa 'dra ste ya re cha //
NK126(cho)001:7710: nga bdag sdug bsngal gyi ri dwags rgya la tshud pa dang 'dra ste ya re cha //
NK126(cho)001:7711: mi lus cig gi sdug bsngal 'di 'dra na //
NK126(cho)001:7712: bskal pa grangs med ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal ci ltar byed //
NK126(cho)001:7713: da ltar lo zla zhag grangs cig gi sdug bsngal mi tshug na //
NK126(cho)001:7714: bskal par bgrang ba'i sdug bsngal bzod lags sam //
NK126(cho)001:7716: gson dang sems la dal ba thob na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7717: rtogs tshad khang du shar na nam kyang legs //
NK126(cho)001:7718: lus sems bskyed pa'i pha ma khur na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7719: rdo rje slob dpon khur na nam kyang legs //
NK126(cho)001:7720: dam pa'i chos sgor zhugs na nam kyang legs //
NK126(cho)001:7721: bka' rgyud man ngag rnyed na nam kyang legs //
NK126(cho)001:7722: spyir yang dam pa'i lha chos spyod na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7723: bu tsha chung nas yig rtsis bslab na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7724: rtag tu thos bsam byas na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7725: thos pa sems thog pheb na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7726: rtag tu 'chi ba dran na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7727: zas nor zhan pa chung na legs //
NK126(cho)001:7728: 'du 'dzi la chags pa ma che mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:7729: chags pa che na sna la 'dre ru skye //
NK126(cho)001:7730: des nas na rag gnas su ltung //
NK126(cho)001:7731: na rag gnas su ltung tsa na //
NK126(cho)001:7732: thar pa med pa bka' rgyud kun la gzigs //
NK126(cho)001:7733: zhe sdang che la khrag dang sha la dad na na rag gnas su skyes //
NK126(cho)001:7734: 'dod chags che na ma byin rku 'phrog byas na yi dwags gnas su skye //
NK126(cho)001:7735: chos la mi dad lan mo zla //
NK126(cho)001:7736: byol song spel zhing bkol spyod nyo tshang byas pas byol song gnas su skye //
NK126(cho)001:7737: mi dge bcu la spyod cing las su sdig pa spyod //
NK126(cho)001:7738: de yi lan du dge ba spyod pa bstan //
NK126(cho)001:7739: de ni mi yi gnas su skye //
NK126(cho)001:7740: dge bcu spyod cing nya stong dus brgyad bsrungs //
NK126(cho)001:7741: blo la gzung 'dzin zhen chags che //
NK126(cho)001:7742: 'di ni sa bdag gnas su skye //
NK126(cho)001:7743: dge bcu spyod cing sdom pa bsrungs //
NK126(cho)001:7744: rigs gsum bsgrub cing zhen chags che //
NK126(cho)001:7745: sngags dang ting 'dzin dam par byed //
NK126(cho)001:7746: 'di ni sa bdag gnyer du skye //
NK126(cho)001:7747: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spangs //
NK126(cho)001:7748: rigs gsum rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul //
NK126(cho)001:7749: gtsang ba'i mchod pas phyi la mchod //
NK126(cho)001:7750: gzung 'dzin zhen pa ma khrol bas //
NK126(cho)001:7751: 'di ni klu yi rigs su skye //
NK126(cho)001:7752: lta ba bdag med ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK126(cho)001:7754: yi dam lha la dam par 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:7755: 'di ni klu chen rigs lngar skye //
NK126(cho)001:7756: ting 'dzin rnam gsum sgor zhugs pas //
NK126(cho)001:7757: lta ba thabs dang shes rab sbyor //
NK126(cho)001:7758: longs spyod rdzogs sku thob 'dod pas //
NK126(cho)001:7759: ma h+aa yo ga'i bsgom bsgrub 'di //
NK126(cho)001:7760: mthu stobs rdzul 'phrul ldan pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:7761: lha min gnas su nges par skye //
NK126(cho)001:7762: pha rol phyin bcu stong nyid bsgom pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:7763: rab tu ma dmigs dbu ma la //
NK126(cho)001:7764: gsal la zhen med bsgom pa a ma na se ba //
NK126(cho)001:7765: dran dang dran med blo 'das chen po bsgom pa'i phyag rgya ba //
NK126(cho)001:7766: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs pa'i //
NK126(cho)001:7768: dbyer med bde ba chen po bsgom //
NK126(cho)001:7769: 'di rnams mtha' bral yan chad nas //
NK126(cho)001:7770: skye mched mu bzhi man chad skye //
NK126(cho)001:7771: rang sems skye med phyogs su med par rtogs pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:7772: de ni rtsol med chen po kun tu bzang //
NK126(cho)001:7773: ces gsungs pas khrom thams cad yid ches so //
NK126(cho)001:7775: rje mnga' bdag gi thang khang gi yang thog tu spyan drangs nas /
NK126(cho)001:7776: gdan 'phar ba dgu brtsegs ni bting /
NK126(cho)001:7779: bza' skyems mang po ni drangs /
NK126(cho)001:7780: rje blon mang pos lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam du byas te /
NK126(cho)001:7782: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal na 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:7783: lta spyod kun rig bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:7784: bya bral dri med nam mkha' lta bu'i don rtogs kyang //
NK126(cho)001:7785: mdzad spyod 'di ltar byas na legs par 'khums //
NK126(cho)001:7787: don rtogs rnal 'byor kun kyang dgongs mdzod dang //
NK126(cho)001:7788: yang dag nges pa'i don ston bla ma spyi bor khur //
NK126(cho)001:7789: des bstan man ngag snying la rtag tu 'chang //
NK126(cho)001:7790: rnal 'byor rta khams ma chung spyod pa khams ma che //
NK126(cho)001:7791: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa rtogs kyang mdzad spyod mi dang bstun //
NK126(cho)001:7792: dge sbyor tshogs lam mi dgag drangs don kun dang bstun //
NK126(cho)001:7793: rtogs pa shugs las 'char gyis gtong phod snying rje bskyed //
NK126(cho)001:7794: theg dgu rang sar bden gyi theg pa'i kha ma 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:7795: don dam lta phug cig gis chos sde phyogs ris skyung //
NK126(cho)001:7796: rang rgyud thos pas grol gyi thob pas ngam ma skyen //
NK126(cho)001:7797: mi 'thad don dang 'gal na rgyal ba'i bka' yang zhog /
NK126(cho)001:7798: bden cing don dang mthun na legs bshad byis pa'i chos kyang longs //
NK126(cho)001:7799: yid chos gding chen rang la yod kyang kun la dri tshul ston //
NK126(cho)001:7800: rang nyams rmu cor ma smra shin tu gsang //
NK126(cho)001:7801: bdag gi gzhan skyon ma rtogs rang skyon rtogs la thong //
NK126(cho)001:7802: sems can mos pa tha dad yid kyi gang la yang bskur ma btab //
NK126(cho)001:7803: mkhas pa phul du phyin yang nga rgyal dregs pa skyungs //
NK126(cho)001:7804: rang che mthong bar 'dod na gzhan skyon zur za spangs //
NK126(cho)001:7805: don med nyon mongs skye yi the tshom rtsod pa shol //
NK126(cho)001:7806: lha chos bshad par 'dod na bdag rang chos bzhin mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:7807: bshad pas gang zag mi thul rang la nang du shod //
NK126(cho)001:7808: nges shes nang du skye yi rnal 'byor rgyud la bcol //
NK126(cho)001:7809: legs nyes tshe 'dir yang gi dam tshig shin tu 'dzem //
NK126(cho)001:7810: rtse cig bsgom par 'dod na cig pur dben sar sdod //
NK126(cho)001:7811: rtogs na gar yang bde yi mched grogs gar bde gyis //
NK126(cho)001:7812: chos dang rgyab bsnol 'gro yi mi chos bya ba mthong //
NK126(cho)001:7813: khro gtum kha smra ma 'jug cig pur gar dgar sdod //
NK126(cho)001:7814: chags sdang ngang gi chung gi rang yul bor yin thong //
NK126(cho)001:7815: chags sdang gzung 'dzin chung na gang na bsdad kyang bde //
NK126(cho)001:7816: chos pa'i 'gal rkyen lags kyi 'du 'dzi g.yeng ba spangs //
NK126(cho)001:7817: gang yang chos sku shes na cir yang spang rgyu med //
NK126(cho)001:7818: chos gzhan spyad pas 'tsho'i rnal 'byor log 'tsho ma tshol cig /
NK126(cho)001:7819: lta dgongs kha ru ma 'don smras na kun dang 'gal ba'i rgyu //
NK126(cho)001:7820: spyod pa bcos ma mi bya byas na bskur pa'i gzhi //
NK126(cho)001:7821: che bzhed nga rgyal byas nas rnal 'byor rang kha sbub //
NK126(cho)001:7822: mkhas bzhed rtsod pa byas na don med nyon mongs skye //
NK126(cho)001:7823: zol zog mi la byas na rnam smin sngun sdod rang la 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:7824: g.yo sgyu sems la byas na yi dam mkha' 'gros khrel //
NK126(cho)001:7825: tshig mkhas don la med na rnal 'byor grogs kyis khrel //
NK126(cho)001:7826: ma rtogs rtogs tshul byas na rang rdzun rang la byas //
NK126(cho)001:7827: mi shes shes tshod byas na ston pa mkhas pa'i tshogs na khrel //
NK126(cho)001:7828: rnal 'byor 'dod gdung che na rang lkogs grogs kyis khrel //
NK126(cho)001:7829: snyan grags bsod nams che na rnal 'byor bdud kyi bslu //
NK126(cho)001:7830: gzung 'dzin zhen chags che na rtag tu 'khor bar 'khyam //
NK126(cho)001:7831: chos rnams rtsa ba lags kyi rang sems gtan la phob //
NK126(cho)001:7832: rnam rtog rtsa ba lags kyi nga bdag chung ngu mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:7833: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba lags kyi gzung 'dzin zhen chag skyur //
NK126(cho)001:7834: myang 'das rtsa ba lags kyi rang sems gtan la phob //
NK126(cho)001:7835: chos nyid gzhan nas ma tshol rnam rtog nyid la ltos //
NK126(cho)001:7836: rnam rtog chos nyid mthong rgyu med na de ka yin //
NK126(cho)001:7837: dpe na bde ba dang du ma lan sdug bsngal spang du med //
NK126(cho)001:7838: sdug bsngal sems su bde ba brtsal du med //
NK126(cho)001:7839: tshig gi rtsa ba ma bcad don gyi rtsa ba chod //
NK126(cho)001:7840: tshig gi rtsa ba brtsad na nam mkha' mtha' dang mnyams //
NK126(cho)001:7841: don gyi rtsa ba bcad na tshig mtha' de las med //
NK126(cho)001:7842: chos kyi rtsa ba ma bcad sems kyi rtsa ba chod //
NK126(cho)001:7843: sems kyi rtsa ba chod na chos nyid rtsa ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:7844: sangs rgyas med kyi ma tshol sems kyi rtsa ba tshol //
NK126(cho)001:7845: sems kyi rtsa ba ma rnyed sangs rgyas rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:7846: sems kyi gzhi rtsa shes nas sangs rgyas yin //
NK126(cho)001:7847: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba chos kyi sku ru bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:7848: mtshon pa'i thabs mchog bla ma mkhas pa brten //
NK126(cho)001:7849: man ngag tha ram lde mig 'dra ba bla ma de la zhus //
NK126(cho)001:7850: yin nam min pa'i rtogs dpyod sems la thang //
NK126(cho)001:7851: the tshom za na bka' rgyud man ngag ltos //
NK126(cho)001:7852: yid ches thag chod byung na 'bras bu thob ches bya //
NK126(cho)001:7853: tshe la nges pa med pas yid ches gdeng ldan mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:7854: rtogs na bya brtsal med kyi gang dga' stabs bder mdzod //
NK126(cho)001:7856: gson dang rtogs par 'tshal ba'i gang zag rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7857: ring par mdzod la dal bar sdod //
NK126(cho)001:7858: mang du nyon la nyung ngu dril //
NK126(cho)001:7860: rtsing por go yang zhib mor spyod //
NK126(cho)001:7861: yang sar mthong yang dgos par srungs //
NK126(cho)001:7862: mnyam par rtogs kyang sdig pa 'dzem //
NK126(cho)001:7863: gnyid dang 'dod chags sha chang rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7864: 'di la bag tsam rtsis thang chung na bzang //
NK126(cho)001:7865: yul ngan grogs ngan slob dpon ngan //
NK126(cho)001:7866: 'di gsum chos kyi gegs rkyen lags //
NK126(cho)001:7867: spangs du 'dod na thabs kyi spangs //
NK126(cho)001:7868: snyan grags bsod nams 'khor g.yog rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7869: 'di yang bdud kyi zhags pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:7870: thabs kyi bde ba'i sa ru bros //
NK126(cho)001:7871: rang yul gnyen dang nor rdzas gsum //
NK126(cho)001:7872: mi nag skyo ba'i sman yin te //
NK126(cho)001:7873: chos pa rnams kyi dug yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:7874: 'di la ha cang zhen ma che //
NK126(cho)001:7875: chos rnams kun dang mthun par mdzad pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7876: khro gtum phyi yi dgra rkun cham //
NK126(cho)001:7877: g.yo zog nang gi khang skran thon //
NK126(cho)001:7878: sdug bsngal rkyen la bsran ma chung //
NK126(cho)001:7879: 'khor ba'i gnas su ngang ma ring //
NK126(cho)001:7880: mi chos nang du rang pham long //
NK126(cho)001:7881: mi yi nor la kha ma che //
NK126(cho)001:7882: bzhu rgyu med pa'i zas nor dug dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:7883: chos khral nang du zog ma 'jug /
NK126(cho)001:7884: mched grogs nang du spyang ma 'tshang //
NK126(cho)001:7885: nyon mongs gtam la zur ma rno //
NK126(cho)001:7886: rgyal ba'i bka' la 'dzin ma chung //
NK126(cho)001:7887: 'khrul pa'i chos la blo ma gsal //
NK126(cho)001:7888: rang don chos la gal ma chung //
NK126(cho)001:7889: 'jig rten chos la gal ma che //
NK126(cho)001:7890: 'khrul pa'i chos la zhen ma che //
NK126(cho)001:7891: skye shi gnyis la ring par bros //
NK126(cho)001:7892: b+aee ro tsa na nga'i gros la ma nyan na //
NK126(cho)001:7893: ngan song gsum du gdon mi za //
NK126(cho)001:7894: lha chos mdzad pa mang lags te //
NK126(cho)001:7895: skye shis 'jigs pa nyung bar gda' //
NK126(cho)001:7896: dad pa gting nas ma skyes shing //
NK126(cho)001:7897: ngan song gsum gyis mi 'jigs cing //
NK126(cho)001:7898: skye shi gnyis la nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:7899: bslab tshul ston kyang bsod nams 'dod //
NK126(cho)001:7900: bsgrub par rem yang rkyen bzlog brtsams //
NK126(cho)001:7901: dge sbyor rem yang kha drag brtsams //
NK126(cho)001:7902: chos bshad mkhas kyang kha tshig yin //
NK126(cho)001:7903: chos gos bzhag nas bsgom thags bcug pa tshul chos yin //
NK126(cho)001:7904: chos pa rnams la dad pa gces pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:7905: bdud kyis bslus pa'i chos pa kha cig gi //
NK126(cho)001:7906: snyan grags bsod nams chen po 'dod //
NK126(cho)001:7907: mi nag 'gong po bsdus nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:7908: lus ngag chos spyod 'bad nas spyad //
NK126(cho)001:7909: khog pa g.yo sgyu zog gi bkang //
NK126(cho)001:7910: dug lnga nyon mongs mi nag bas kyang che //
NK126(cho)001:7911: de 'dra'i gang zag chos pa ci la tshud //
NK126(cho)001:7912: skal ldan las 'phro sad pa'i skyes bu dag /
NK126(cho)001:7913: kun la 'phags pa'i rtogs pa khyad par can //
NK126(cho)001:7914: kun dang mthun pa'i spyod pa byed //
NK126(cho)001:7915: phyi nang phyogs ris med par zhen pa chung //
NK126(cho)001:7917: thad kar 'khri ba rnam rtog chod //
NK126(cho)001:7918: dam tshig phyi nang med par srung //
NK126(cho)001:7919: sems can lus la rgyal ba'i thugs //
NK126(cho)001:7920: de 'dra'i skyes bu shin tu dkon //
NK126(cho)001:7921: lta ba mtha' phyin zhe blo bde //
NK126(cho)001:7922: bsgom pa brtan pa khang blo bde //
NK126(cho)001:7923: spyod pa yangs pas gar yang bde //
NK126(cho)001:7924: 'bras bu mthar phyin shi yang bde //
NK126(cho)001:7925: de 'dra'i skyes bu dam pa shin tu dkon //
NK126(cho)001:7926: de ltar mdzod cig rje blon rnams //
NK126(cho)001:7927: bdag 'dra 'khyam po b+aee ro tsa na yin //
NK126(cho)001:7928: mched lcam chos ngo ma shes pa rnams la //
NK126(cho)001:7929: zhal chems mdo tsam smras pa lags //
NK126(cho)001:7930: phyi rabs rnal 'byor kun kyang ni //
NK126(cho)001:7931: de la gson cig thugs la zhog /
NK126(cho)001:7934: b+aee ro tsa nas rje blon rnams la zhal chems bzhag pa'i skabs te nyer bzhi pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:7935: de nas rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK126(cho)001:7936: mchims shakya pra b+ha wa dang /
NK126(cho)001:7937: ru skyong dar ma ra tsa dang /
NK126(cho)001:7938: gru gu e pe sha dang /
NK126(cho)001:7939: sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms dang /
NK126(cho)001:7940: de rnams kyi kha g.yu kha gser deng bcas /
NK126(cho)001:7941: lags pas dar zab thegs tshad phyag tu phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:7942: dbu rtse yang thog tu chos 'di rnams zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:7943: rdzogs pa chen po rgyud la tha ma'i klong dgu bal po nyi khri las bsdus pa las /
NK126(cho)001:7944: rgyud kyi dbye ba lnga ni /
NK126(cho)001:7945: byang chub kyi sems rmad du byung ba'i rgyud dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7946: nam mkha' che rgyas pa'i rgyud dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:7947: rdo rje sems dpa' mkha' mnyam klong gi rgyud sde dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:7948: khu byung kun bzang rig pa klong gi rgyud sde dang bzhi /
NK126(cho)001:7949: byang sems nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud sde dang lnga las /
NK126(cho)001:7950: rmad 'byung rang la rtsa ba'i rgyud sde le'u lnga pa /
NK126(cho)001:7951: bshad pa'i rgyud le'u bcu gcig pa dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:7952: nyi shu rtsa lnga pa dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:7954: nam mkha' che rang la yang nam mkha' che rgyas pa'i rgyud dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7955: nam mkha' che rgyas pa gsang ba'i rgyud dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:7956: nam mkha' che nag po kha gdangs pa'i rgyud dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:7957: nam mkha' che skye ba med pa'i rgyud dang bzhi /
NK126(cho)001:7958: yi ge med pa'i rgyud dang lnga /
NK126(cho)001:7959: gdams ngag dang bcas nas bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:7960: yang rdo rje sems dpa' mkha' mnyam klong gi rgyud sde las /
NK126(cho)001:7961: nam mkha' dri ma med pa dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7962: gsang ba sgo mang gi rgyud dang gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:7963: mkha' ltar dag pa'i rgyud dang gsum bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:7964: khu byug kun bzang rig pa klong gi rgyud sde las /
NK126(cho)001:7965: rgyud ma bu gsum bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:7966: sems smad rtsa ba bco brgyad las rgyud re re bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:7967: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam pa'i rgyud sde gnyis te /
NK126(cho)001:7968: nam mkha' ltar mtha' dbus med pa'i ston pa'i rgyud dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7969: rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud dang gnyis so //
NK126(cho)001:7970: lta ba nam mkha' ltar mtha' dbus med pa'i rgyud la /
NK126(cho)001:7971: rtsa ba'i rgyud kun byed rgyal po /
NK126(cho)001:7972: mdo le'u lnga bcu rtsa bdun pa dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7973: rgyud phyi ma le'u bcu gnyis pa dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:7974: rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma le'u bco lnga pa dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:7975: gsum ka bsdom pas le'u brgyad cu rtsa bzhi bshad /
NK126(cho)001:7977: mdo bcu dang rgyud ma bu bzhi bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:7978: de rnams spyir bshad pa'i rgyud la /
NK126(cho)001:7979: lta ba nam mkha' ltar mtha' dbus med par bstan pa'i rgyud le'u bcu bzhi pa dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7980: sgom pa rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa rnyog pa med pa'i rgyud le'u brgyad pa dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:7981: spyod pa nyi zla dang mnyam pa gsal 'grib med
NK126(cho)001:7982: par ston pa'i rgyud le'u bcu gnyis pa dang gsum
NK126(cho)001:7983: / 'bras bu rin po che dang mnyam pa skye
NK126(cho)001:7984: ba med pa'i rgyud le'u bco lnga pa dang bzhi
NK126(cho)001:7985: / / de rnams kyi rgyud phyi ma gsang ba
NK126(cho)001:7986: mtha' dang mnyam pa byang chub kyi shes bya mtha'
NK126(cho)001:7987: gcod le'u nyer bzhi dang ma bu dgu bshad do
NK126(cho)001:7988: / / // yang rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde dang /
NK126(cho)001:7989: man ngag rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:7990: bshad pa'i rgyud badz+ra kha sa tan+t+ra nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:7991: man ngag bsgom pa'i tan+t+ra ye shes rdzogs pa dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:7992: man ngag gi rig pa klong rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang bzhi /
NK126(cho)001:7993: bsam gtan gyi rnyog ma sel ba a ra li rnyog ma sel ba'i rgyud dang lnga /
NK126(cho)001:7994: bsgom chen gyi nyams bskyed pa nya mo bag la nyal 'khor lo'i rgyud dang drug /
NK126(cho)001:7995: phyi ru 'gro ba rin po che'i 'khor lo'i rgyud dang bdun /
NK126(cho)001:7996: ye shes rdzogs pa klong dgu'i rgyud dang brgyad /
NK126(cho)001:7998: de rnams bshad pas rgyud pa tha mar grags so //
NK126(cho)001:8000: rgyud pa tha ma bshad pa'i skabs te nyer lnga pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:8001: de nas b+aee ro tsa nas theg dman zil gyis
NK126(cho)001:8002: gnon pa'i lta ba'i gyad tshig mgur du bzhengs pa
NK126(cho)001:8004: snang srid thams cad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin la //
NK126(cho)001:8005: la las dug tu mthong nas spang gi gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8006: la las sman du mthong nas len gyis gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8007: la las 'dren par mthong nas 'byed kyi gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8008: la las dri mar mthong nas 'khrud kyi gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8009: la las rtogs par mthong nas thub kyi gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8010: nga yis 'ub kyi bsdus nas khyur mid byas //
NK126(cho)001:8011: so sor mthong ba nga la med //
NK126(cho)001:8013: khams gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK126(cho)001:8014: rang gi dri mas rang la bsgrib //
NK126(cho)001:8015: de la 'jigs shing skrag pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:8016: bsam pas sel bar mi 'gyur bros pas thar ba med //
NK126(cho)001:8017: spang bas mi spang bzhag pas mi lus te //
NK126(cho)001:8018: nga yi mun pa'i gling du nyal bas grib ma bya ba nga la med //
NK126(cho)001:8020: rgya mtsho chen po'i chu bo la //
NK126(cho)001:8021: de la 'thung bas mang bar gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8022: ngas kyang hub kyi 'thung bas nga ma ngam //
NK126(cho)001:8023: rgya mtsho khrog gi 'thung bas kha ngam tsam //
NK126(cho)001:8024: da 'thung yang mi 'thung ngam nas gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8026: nga ni nyal ba'i mal sa tshol //
NK126(cho)001:8027: 'jig rten khams kyi sa bsgrod pas //
NK126(cho)001:8028: nga yis nyal ba'i sa ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:8029: dma' ste dmyal ba'i sa la rkang cig bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:8030: rkang cig srid pa'i rtse nas mnan //
NK126(cho)001:8031: srid gsum gam pa gang du byas //
NK126(cho)001:8032: de nga'i bsdad sa lus ngag rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:8033: da sdod sa tshol yang mi tshol nyal nas sdod //
NK126(cho)001:8035: nga yi gos cig gon bsam pas //
NK126(cho)001:8036: brtsem sdug gos kyi nga ma gro //
NK126(cho)001:8037: nam mkha' rgyab tu gon pas rgyab gro tsam //
NK126(cho)001:8038: da gon yang mi gon bzhag nas btang //
NK126(cho)001:8040: nga ni lto cig bza' dgos pas //
NK126(cho)001:8041: khams kyi zas kyis nga mi 'grang //
NK126(cho)001:8042: snang srid khyud mid byas pas lto bde tsam //
NK126(cho)001:8043: da za yang mi za chog par gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8045: nga 'jig rten khams na grangs tshad 'jal //
NK126(cho)001:8046: rdul phran bsgrang pas yid ma ches //
NK126(cho)001:8047: snang srid thams cad gcig tu bsgrangs //
NK126(cho)001:8048: des ni nga yi grangs rtsis yin //
NK126(cho)001:8049: da bsgrang yang mi bsgrang bzhag pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:8051: nga ni rgya mtsho gdan du bting bas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8052: seng ge rta ru zhon pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8053: nam mkha' gos su gon pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8054: 'khor lo lag tu thogs pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8055: nyi zla khyur mid byas pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8056: sangs rgyas rgyab tu sbas pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8057: dam chos rgya mtshor pho bas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8058: sems can thams cad bsad pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8059: 'khor 'das gnyis ni nga las med pas bde //
NK126(cho)001:8060: nga ni sus kyang ma mthong mthong nas las rnams zin //
NK126(cho)001:8062: dar rje dpal gyi drag pa na re /
NK126(cho)001:8063: slob dpon gyi mgur dbyangs tshig sbam song yor che byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:8064: slob dpon gyis yang mgur 'di bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:8065: sems nyid thig le nyag cig 'di //
NK126(cho)001:8066: brgyad khri bzhi stong theg pa'i nang nas sbom //
NK126(cho)001:8067: de las sbom pa ngas ma mthong //
NK126(cho)001:8068: drangs don 'khrul chos thog nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:8069: rdzogs chen a ti som yor che //
NK126(cho)001:8070: a ti yo ga blta ba'i som yor yin //
NK126(cho)001:8071: ri rgyal lhun po ri yi som yor ni //
NK126(cho)001:8072: rgya mtsho chen po chu yi som yor yin //
NK126(cho)001:8073: khri gdugs nyi ma gdugs kyi som yor yin //
NK126(cho)001:8074: rang rig sems nyid sangs rgyas som yor yin //
NK126(cho)001:8076: sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms na re /
NK126(cho)001:8077: slob dpon chen pos mgur bzhengs pa de go ba ma mchis /
NK126(cho)001:8079: da rung man ngag dril ba cig gnong byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:8081: h+aumh theg pa dman la zhugs pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8082: ngang gi blo dpang dma' ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:8083: thos pa nyung ba'i blo sbom dang //
NK126(cho)001:8084: don med bslad pa'i tshig 'chal dang //
NK126(cho)001:8085: khur zhen dad pa chung ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:8086: pho dregs che la rang mthong che //
NK126(cho)001:8087: bcad kyang khrag med ser snas 'ching //
NK126(cho)001:8088: de la a ti'i don mi bshad //
NK126(cho)001:8089: bshad kyang sems rgyud mi khrol bas //
NK126(cho)001:8090: slad la phya zhing sgro bskur 'debs //
NK126(cho)001:8091: des na man ngag a ti shin tu gsang //
NK126(cho)001:8093: de nas rje mnga' bdag na re /
NK126(cho)001:8094: ma h+aa gu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:8095: gu rus gsungs pa'i man ngag rnams /
NK126(cho)001:8096: tshig don can cig yin par mchis lags te /
NK126(cho)001:8097: dbyar du 'khums par ma mchis na /
NK126(cho)001:8098: dbyar du 'khums pa'i man ngag cig gnang bar zhu smras pas /
NK126(cho)001:8099: slob dpon zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8100: gangs kyi seng ge gdangs phyungs na //
NK126(cho)001:8101: sder chags phal dang gdangs mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8102: gdangs skad 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8103: rgya mtsho chen po'i brlab mthong na //
NK126(cho)001:8104: chu phran phal dang rlab mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8105: rlab mchog 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8106: ri rgyal lhun po'i rtser phyin na //
NK126(cho)001:8107: ri phran phal dang yang mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8108: rtse rgyal 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8109: mkha' gsal nyi ma'i 'od mthong na //
NK126(cho)001:8110: gza' skar phal dang 'od mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8112: khyung chen gnam 'phang gcod mthong nas //
NK126(cho)001:8113: 'dab chags phal dang shugs mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8114: rtsal shugs 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8115: a ti rdzogs chen don mthong nas //
NK126(cho)001:8116: theg dman rnams dang don mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8117: don mchog 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8118: rdo rje theg pa'i gting mthong nas //
NK126(cho)001:8119: theg dman phal dang gting mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8120: gting dpag 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8121: shes rgyud sbyor ba'i mkhas pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8122: thos pa chung ba'i blo bram gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:8123: 'gro ba'i don la don mi mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:8124: don mchog 'di yang thun mong min //
NK126(cho)001:8126: kun gyis lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam btsal to //
NK126(cho)001:8127: de nas zhu ba kun gyis ma spobs so //
NK126(cho)001:8129: b+aee ro tsa nas theg dman sgrin tshig can zil
NK126(cho)001:8130: gyis gnon pa'i gyad tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad gsungs
NK126(cho)001:8131: pa'i skabs te nyer drug pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:8132: de nas ru gyang dar ma ra tsa na re /
NK126(cho)001:8133: rje ma h+aa gu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:8134: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la /
NK126(cho)001:8135: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba la gal che'am mi che lags zhus pa la /
NK126(cho)001:8137: bstan pa bsrung ba la shin tu yang gal che gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:8138: ru gyang dar ma ra dza na re /
NK126(cho)001:8140: bstan pa bsrung ba la gang zag ci lta bu 'tshal /
NK126(cho)001:8141: thabs ci ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:8142: slob dpon gyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8143: nyon cig bstan pa bsrung ba'i skyes bu rnams /
NK126(cho)001:8144: dug lnga rnam rtog chung la rig pa rtsal dang ldan pa yi /
NK126(cho)001:8145: byin brlabs bka' yi zam pa ma chad pa'i bla ma la /
NK126(cho)001:8146: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi zhabs tog mnyes byas la /
NK126(cho)001:8147: bsre dbang rdzogs par thob par bya /
NK126(cho)001:8148: de nas thos bsam shes rgyud khrol bar bya /
NK126(cho)001:8149: de nas bde pa'i gnas su 'dug nas ni /
NK126(cho)001:8150: lha bsnyen chu bo'i gzhung bzhin bsgrang /
NK126(cho)001:8151: rtsa ba yan lag kun nas dam tshig bka' gzhung bzhin bsrung ba shin tu gces /
NK126(cho)001:8152: dam tshig nyams na bskal par bsgrub kyang mthu rtsal 'ong re kan /
NK126(cho)001:8153: dam tshig bsrung na dam can 'du bar rgyal bas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8154: de nas gsang sngags dam tshig gces /
NK126(cho)001:8155: de nas rnal 'byor pa des dam rdzas rnams ni 'tshogs pa bsogs /
NK126(cho)001:8160: 'dus byas dge sbyor grub tshad bya /
NK126(cho)001:8161: de nas mdos chen gang 'grub dgra phyogs bskyal /
NK126(cho)001:8162: thabs dang shes rab dbyings dang ye shes sam /
NK126(cho)001:8163: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dbyer med dam /
NK126(cho)001:8164: thams cad chos nyid rig pa rang gi rtsal du
NK126(cho)001:8165: shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyi rang gzhung gang ltar yin
NK126(cho)001:8167: de nas 'jig rten 'das dang ma 'das par dpang po bzhag /
NK126(cho)001:8168: bden rdzun 'gug gzhug shag rnams gdab /
NK126(cho)001:8169: de nas dam can rgya mtsho lha srin sde brgyad bos la /
NK126(cho)001:8170: gdung ba'i mchi ma bton la snying rje chen po
NK126(cho)001:8171: thugs rje yis lha phral gnas nas 'gug gzhug byed
NK126(cho)001:8172: du bcug / gzugs la bstim zhing gang yin lugs kyis brab /
NK126(cho)001:8173: rtags byung nas ni las mtha' btul /
NK126(cho)001:8174: phung po las mkhan tshogs la gtor mar 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:8175: rnam shes rgyal ba'i tshogs la dbyings su bstim //
NK126(cho)001:8176: srog ni rang la bstim la dbyer med chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:8177: des bsgom mkhan yang ltung bar mi 'gyur te //
NK126(cho)001:8178: mtho ris gnas su smon ci dgos //
NK126(cho)001:8179: de ni gnas mchog chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:8180: ces b+aee ro tsa na bdag gis bshad //
NK126(cho)001:8181: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kyi brnags pa +thii //
NK126(cho)001:8183: ru gyang dar ma ra tsa la bstan pa bsrungs shig par bstan pa'i skabs te nyer bdun pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:8184: de nas glang dpal gyi seng ges na re /
NK126(cho)001:8186: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa zhes gang la bgyi /
NK126(cho)001:8187: bsrung na ci ltar srung ba lags /
NK126(cho)001:8190: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8191: nyon cig phyi rabs rnal 'byor kun //
NK126(cho)001:8192: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba ni rang rig pa'i ngo bo 'di /
NK126(cho)001:8193: ci yang bzung du mi btub pa de la sangs rgyas zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:8197: de la mos shing 'dun pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8198: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:8199: de yang spyir yang chos sku'i bstan pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8200: phyi snod 'byung ba lnga las bsdus pa /
NK126(cho)001:8202: thams cad chos sku'i bstan pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8203: ston pa dpal kun tu bzang po'o //
NK126(cho)001:8204: bstan pa'i snying po zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka'/
NK126(cho)001:8205: a ti a nu ma h+aa dang gsum mo //
NK126(cho)001:8206: de bzhin longs sku'i sprul sku'i ston pa bstan pa zhing khams la sogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:8207: des yi ge'i 'brel pa dang pos 'dus /
NK126(cho)001:8208: des bstan pa ji snyed gsungs pa yang /
NK126(cho)001:8209: theg pa rim dgur 'dus pa la /
NK126(cho)001:8210: de la mos dang slob dang bshad dang nyan pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8211: bsgom dang bsgrub cing spyod pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:8212: 'di rnams sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:8213: de la dam chos smod cing 'joms pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8214: bsad bcad brdeg btsog rku phrog byed //
NK126(cho)001:8215: dben gnas bshig dang bka' rgyud bsreg /
NK126(cho)001:8217: dug dang gdug pas las rnams 'byed //
NK126(cho)001:8218: gzhan yang ma nyes thabs la gcod pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8219: kha drag zang du 'tshang ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:8220: rmong po theb la gnon pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8221: mi chags bu lon ded pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8222: man ngag gus par mi zhu thabs kyi bru //
NK126(cho)001:8223: gsang sngags dam las log pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8224: slob dpon smad cing mched grogs 'joms //
NK126(cho)001:8225: 'di rnams bstan pa'i dgra yin pas //
NK126(cho)001:8226: 'di rnams bsrungs ba'i thabs la brtson par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:8228: yang glang dpal gyi seng ges zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:8229: rje ma h+aa gu ru chen po lags /
NK126(cho)001:8230: bstan pa bsrung ba'i thabs gang che lags /
NK126(cho)001:8233: b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)001:8234: bstan pa bsrung ba'i thabs ni /
NK126(cho)001:8235: theg pa gang mthong ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8236: lta ba gang mthong ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8239: theg chung blo dman dgongs pa'i gding med rnams kyi bya ba min /
NK126(cho)001:8241: rang phung byang chub brlag pa gdon mi za /
NK126(cho)001:8242: des na gang du bstan pa bzhin shes par bya /
NK126(cho)001:8243: bstan pa bsrung ba'i man ngag ni /
NK126(cho)001:8244: phyi nang gnyis su shes par bya //
NK126(cho)001:8245: phyi ni mu stegs ngan sngags rnams la bya //
NK126(cho)001:8246: rno ste bzlog pa slan tshan chung //
NK126(cho)001:8247: dgra yang phung ste rang yang phung //
NK126(cho)001:8248: bdag gzhan gnyis ka na rag gnas su ltung //
NK126(cho)001:8249: nang pa sangs rgyas bstan bsrung ni //
NK126(cho)001:8250: 'jig rten pa dang 'das pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NK126(cho)001:8251: 'jig rten pa yi bstan bsrung ni //
NK126(cho)001:8253: bsnyen dang bsgrub dang 'bod pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8254: rbad pa dang ni bsad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8255: rtogs pa'i gting dang mi ldan na //
NK126(cho)001:8256: bskal par bsgrub kyang mi 'grub cing //
NK126(cho)001:8257: yi chad sgyid lugs chos la bskur pa 'debs //
NK126(cho)001:8258: sngags la bzlog dkrug shi pa bstan na dgra yang 'chi //
NK126(cho)001:8259: gting la rang yang srog skyin 'bebs te rang yang 'chi //
NK126(cho)001:8260: phyi nas dregs pa can bsgrub cing bstan pa med gyur na //
NK126(cho)001:8261: phung shing brlag par gdon mi za //
NK126(cho)001:8263: ma gshin phur gsum dag la bya //
NK126(cho)001:8264: 'di ni gol sa shin tu che //
NK126(cho)001:8265: lta dgongs tshad du ma phyin na //
NK126(cho)001:8266: bsgrub par dka' la 'khu ldog che //
NK126(cho)001:8267: phyi ma bdud dang ru tra srin por skye //
NK126(cho)001:8268: lta dgongs tshad du phyin pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8269: ma gshin bran bzhin las rnams byed //
NK126(cho)001:8270: 'jig rten dregs pa lta ci smon //
NK126(cho)001:8271: dgra bo mtho ris gnas su 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:8272: rnal 'byor gzugs sku rnam gnyis thob //
NK126(cho)001:8274: ru gyang dar ma ra tsas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8275: rje ma h+aa gu ru lags /
NK126(cho)001:8276: mthu che ba la man ngag zab pa la che ba las /
NK126(cho)001:8277: chos mi mkhas kyang mi rung lags sam zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:8278: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:8279: srid gsum 'gran zla med pa rgyal ba'i mthu //
NK126(cho)001:8281: mthu yi rang bzhin mkhas shing rtogs las byung //
NK126(cho)001:8282: gal te byang chub sems dang ma ldan na //
NK126(cho)001:8283: gnod sbyin srin po las la mi chud ste //
NK126(cho)001:8284: gnyis phung rang la 'ong ba shin tu mang //
NK126(cho)001:8287: glang dpal gyi seng ge dang ru gyang dar ma
NK126(cho)001:8288: ra tsa bstan pa bsrung ba la che bar bstan
NK126(cho)001:8289: pa'i skabs te nyer brgyad pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:8291: slob ma rnams la byang chub kyi sems gang yin bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:8293: byang chub sems ni kun tu bzang po yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8294: rdo rje sems dpa' yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8295: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kyang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8296: rigs kyi yum lnga'ang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8297: byang chub sems ni sems dpa' dang sems ma'ang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8298: byang chub sems ni sku yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8301: byang sems ni 'byung ba lnga yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8302: byang chub sems ni rgyu yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8307: chos kyi dbyings kyang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8309: byang chub sems ni dka' ba yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8311: byang chub sems ni nyon mongs pa yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8314: mya ngan las 'das pa yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8315: gnyis su med pa yang yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8319: kun kyang the tshom skyes so //
NK126(cho)001:8320: yang b+aee ro tsa nas 'di gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8321: khyung chen gshog rdzogs mkha' la lding ba la //
NK126(cho)001:8322: rgya mtsho ngam 'grogs g.yang sa nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:8323: rtsa gsum rdzogs pa'i seng ge gangs gong 'grim pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8324: spyi bser lhag pas nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:8325: rig pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK126(cho)001:8326: khams gsum 'khor ba'i g.yang la nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:8327: shel gyi 'khor lo nyi ma'i snying po la //
NK126(cho)001:8328: grib ma mun pa'i tshogs kyi nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:8329: ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK126(cho)001:8330: tha snyad tshig gi sgro 'dogs nyams mi nga //
NK126(cho)001:8332: de nas rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras /
NK126(cho)001:8334: g.yu sbram bcug lag tu dar zab mang po thogs /
NK126(cho)001:8335: bskor ba mang po ni byas /
NK126(cho)001:8336: lha phyag mang po btsal nas /
NK126(cho)001:8337: rje ma h+aa gu ru lags /
NK126(cho)001:8338: bka' rgyud lung gi bsdus don /
NK126(cho)001:8339: man ngag gi bcud rtogs dgongs pa 'ub chub par
NK126(cho)001:8340: bsdu ba'i man ngag cig gnang 'tshal zhes zhus pas
NK126(cho)001:8341: man ngag gi bcud rtogs pa 'di rnams gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8342: kun tu bzang po brtsal ba med pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8343: rang byung ye shes ma bcos pa //
NK126(cho)001:8344: rig pa dbyer med byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:8345: snang srid kun gyi gzhi ru bar //
NK126(cho)001:8346: gdal ba chen pos kun la khyab //
NK126(cho)001:8347: 'di ni snang srid gzhi bzhengs kyi //
NK126(cho)001:8348: dgongs pa zhes pa de la bya //
NK126(cho)001:8349: 'khor ba dang mya ngan 'das pa'i chos /
NK126(cho)001:8350: 'byung ba chen po lnga la ma 'dus pa med de /
NK126(cho)001:8351: 'byung ba chen po lnga nyid rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen por shar te /
NK126(cho)001:8352: thams cad de'i ngang du sangs ma rgyas pa gcig kyang med de /
NK126(cho)001:8354: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung //
NK126(cho)001:8355: de bzhin nam mkha' la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:8356: de ltar snod bcud 'jig rten rnams //
NK126(cho)001:8357: kun kyang rang byung ye shes dbyings //
NK126(cho)001:8358: de ltar ma yin ye shes min //
NK126(cho)001:8359: de las rang byung gud na med //
NK126(cho)001:8360: de phyir snang srid ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8361: des na sangs rgyas logs na med //
NK126(cho)001:8363: de ltar 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad dang /
NK126(cho)001:8364: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen po shar ba la /
NK126(cho)001:8365: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis med /
NK126(cho)001:8366: sdug bsngal dang bde ba gnyis med /
NK126(cho)001:8368: snang ba dang stong pa gnyis med /
NK126(cho)001:8369: rtag pa dang chad pa gnyis med /
NK126(cho)001:8370: blang ba dang dor ba gnyis med /
NK126(cho)001:8372: thams cad rang gis byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:8373: de ni tshad mar rab tu basngagasa //
NK126(cho)001:8376: rig pa gnyis med shar ba la //
NK126(cho)001:8377: de la 'khor ba ngan song ga la yod //
NK126(cho)001:8380: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med la //
NK126(cho)001:8381: logs na sangs rgyas yod ma yin //
NK126(cho)001:8383: des na rig pa rang byung gi ye shes phyi nang snod bcud 'khor ba myang 'das /
NK126(cho)001:8384: thams cad thig le nyag cig tu gsal yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:8385: snang srid gzhir bzhengs dgongs pa khams gsum yongs sgrol dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8387: rigs drug dngos po sna tshogs dang //
NK126(cho)001:8388: chos kyi sku zhes tha dad med //
NK126(cho)001:8389: chos sku gang yin 'khor ba pa //
NK126(cho)001:8392: de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na sangs rgyas zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8393: chos sku zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8394: chos kyi dbyings zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8395: byang chub sems zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8396: rang byung gi ye shes zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8397: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:8398: kun tu bzang po zhes bya ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:8399: rang byung gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems la bya ste /
NK126(cho)001:8400: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen por mngon
NK126(cho)001:8401: du shar ba la chos kyi sku zhes bya ste
NK126(cho)001:8402: / de la gnas shing bsgom par bya ba med do //
NK126(cho)001:8403: rig pa byang chub kyi sems ci yang ma yin pa nyid cir yang 'char ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:8404: ci yang ma grub pa nyid snang ba ni cir yang snang ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:8405: ngo bo 'di 'dra zhes gang yang ma grub pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8406: de ni chos thams cad kyi snying por gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:8408: brtsal du med pa'i sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)001:8409: ma bcos pa yi sems nyid gsal //
NK126(cho)001:8410: ma brtsal rig pa gnyis med shar //
NK126(cho)001:8411: shar ba nyid na nub pa med //
NK126(cho)001:8412: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8413: kun bzang bya brtsal med pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8414: ma bcos ma bslad rig pa byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:8415: dus gsum bde gshegs nyams kyi sku gsung thugs //
NK126(cho)001:8416: snang srid 'khor bar rig pa gnyis med shar //
NK126(cho)001:8417: rgyu 'bras gnyis med lhun gyis grub pas ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8420: rin po che shel gyi khang bu'i dgongs pa ste /
NK126(cho)001:8421: dper na rin po che shel gyi khang bu ni /
NK126(cho)001:8422: nang nas bltas na phyi gsal /
NK126(cho)001:8423: phyi nas bltas na nang gsal /
NK126(cho)001:8424: phyi dang nang dbyer med pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8425: de nas nang nas bltas pa'i dus na /
NK126(cho)001:8426: snang srid thams cad rin po cher ma gyur par med do //
NK126(cho)001:8427: rin po che gser la dri ma med pa dang 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:8428: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK126(cho)001:8429: cad rig pa byang chub kyi sems kyi klong du
NK126(cho)001:8430: sangs ma rgyas pa med de /
NK126(cho)001:8432: chos rnams thams cad rig pa byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:8433: snang srid thams cad ye nas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8436: snang srid 'khor ba'i chos med na //
NK126(cho)001:8437: sangs rgyas bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK126(cho)001:8439: dus gsum sangs rgyas spang ba'i pha rol na //
NK126(cho)001:8440: 'khor ba ngan song gang nas tshol //
NK126(cho)001:8441: sangs rgyas ming du grags pa yang //
NK126(cho)001:8442: snang srid 'khor ba'i chos la btags //
NK126(cho)001:8443: de phyir sangs rgyas ming yang med //
NK126(cho)001:8445: de'i phyir thams cad kyi snying po rig pa byang chub kyi sems yin te /
NK126(cho)001:8446: byang chub kyi sems las gzhi dang rtsa ba med pas /
NK126(cho)001:8447: 'bras bu chos kyi sku mtshan ma'i dmigs pa dang bral ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:8448: des na snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK126(cho)001:8449: rig pa byang chub kyi sems las shar bar thag
NK126(cho)001:8450: chod do // sems nyid gdod ma nas ma byung
NK126(cho)001:8451: ma skyes pa med pa'i dbyings su thag chod do
NK126(cho)001:8452: chod do // // skye ba med pa'i dbyings las skye ba med pa'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs ni /
NK126(cho)001:8453: ci lta bu yang ci yang grub pa med de /
NK126(cho)001:8456: de'i phyir snang stong dbyer med rang shar nyid /
NK126(cho)001:8457: rin po che shel gyi khang bu'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8459: rin chen shel gyi khong bu'i don //
NK126(cho)001:8460: gces pa med pa'i shes pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8461: gnyen po can gyi de ma bstan //
NK126(cho)001:8462: 'gyur ba med pa'i shes pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8464: mnyam pa nyid kyi shes pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8465: che chung can gyi de ma bstan //
NK126(cho)001:8466: kun tu bzang po'i shes pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8467: phyi nang can gyi de ma bstan //
NK126(cho)001:8469: b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8470: kun bzang bya brtsal med la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8471: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:8472: rig pa phyogs med ye shes ngang du shar //
NK126(cho)001:8473: yod dang med pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:8474: rig pa phyogs med shar ba'i ngang du gdal //
NK126(cho)001:8476: yang rig pa spyi blugs su shar ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8477: dper na nyi ma'i snying po dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:8478: nyi ma'i 'od zer sus kyang ma byas pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:8479: nyi ma nyid sus kyang ma byas ma bcos par 'od dpung chen por rang shar ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:8480: de bzhin rang gi rig pa nyid sus kyang ma
NK126(cho)001:8481: byas par ma bcos par rang byung gi ye shes
NK126(cho)001:8482: chos kyi skur rang shar ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:8483: yang nyi ma nam mkha' la shar ba'i dus su /
NK126(cho)001:8484: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad gsal ba rang bzhin
NK126(cho)001:8485: du 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK126(cho)001:8486: thams cad rang rig pa byang chub sems su gsal
NK126(cho)001:8487: lo // de na byang chub sems su ma gyur pa'i chos yang med pas /
NK126(cho)001:8488: 'khor 'das thams cad ngo bo rang sems rang shar ba yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:8489: de ltar shes tsam na ci snang ci srid pa thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:8490: sems kyi ngo bo ma yin pa med par thag chod pas /
NK126(cho)001:8491: shes par bya ba'i yul gcig dang /
NK126(cho)001:8492: shes par byed pa'i sems gnyis su med de /
NK126(cho)001:8493: phyi nang gi chos thams cad sems nyid rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems su shes pas /
NK126(cho)001:8494: de tsam na 'khor ba'i rnam par rtog pa'i ming med pas /
NK126(cho)001:8495: dus dang gnas skabs thams cad du dmigs gtad med pa'i dgongs pa shar /
NK126(cho)001:8496: de la rig pa spyi blug tu shar ba'i dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:8497: de la ting nge 'dzin gyi don chos thams cad nam yang dag pa'i cig la /
NK126(cho)001:8498: dmigs shing gtad nas bsgom pa'am /
NK126(cho)001:8500: gom par bya yi rtsol ba thams cad dang bral ba ni man ngag gi dam pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8501: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa des /
NK126(cho)001:8502: rang gi rig mi dmigs yul med de /
NK126(cho)001:8503: lhun grub kyi dgongs pa phyogs med chen po shar bas /
NK126(cho)001:8504: rtsol ba thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NK126(cho)001:8505: lhun grub kyi dgongs pa zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8506: bya bral chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8507: rang sems rang byung ye shes lhun grub las //
NK126(cho)001:8508: rtsol bsgrub ci yang med de bya bral chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:8509: 'di zhes gnas pa med do dgongs pa lhun grub yin //
NK126(cho)001:8510: 'di zhes spyad bya med pas spyod pa lhun grub yin //
NK126(cho)001:8511: 'di zhes thob bya med pas 'bras bu lhun grub yin //
NK126(cho)001:8513: chos kyi sku ru ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8514: bya brtsal med pa lhun grub yin //
NK126(cho)001:8516: des na rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes su dmigs pa med par gsal na /
NK126(cho)001:8517: sems las gzhan pa'i chos gang du yang ma mthong bas /
NK126(cho)001:8518: blo rtogs gang du yang mi skye bar /
NK126(cho)001:8519: ci la yang spang blang med pa'i dgongs pa yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8520: da gol sa dang sgrib pa'i tshogs ming yang med pa la rbad kyi chod do //
NK126(cho)001:8521: spyir 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:8522: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen po ye nas yin par shes shing /
NK126(cho)001:8523: thams cad sems su 'dug tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:8524: sems las gzhan pa gang yang ma mthong ste /
NK126(cho)001:8525: chos thams cad sems nyid kyi klong du 'dug pas na /
NK126(cho)001:8527: ci byas ci snang ci dran chos nyid du 'dug tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:8530: blang ba dor ba mi 'dug go //
NK126(cho)001:8531: de tsam na mi 'dug pa ni 'dug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8532: ci snang ci srid thams cad rig pa byang chub kyi sems su shes pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8534: chos nyid shes pa ni shes pa med pa'i shes pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8535: de ltar na spyod pa byed spyod ci byas kyang /
NK126(cho)001:8536: 'dzin chags med pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8537: byas pa med pa'i spyod pa zhes bya /
NK126(cho)001:8538: b+aee ro tsa nas man ngag mtha' las 'das pa zhes bya ba /
NK126(cho)001:8539: dbu rtse yang thog tu gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:8540: kun bzang rig pa'i klong la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8541: rig pa nam mkha' lta bu ye nas gdal ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:8542: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams ye nas rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:8543: srid gsum gnyis med ye nas gdal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:8544: mtshan ma'i chos rnams ye nas chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:8545: khams gsum ye nas rang grol dgongs pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:8546: dper na nam mkha' chen po 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:8555: nam mkha' stong pa nyid sna tshogs su snang ba la /
NK126(cho)001:8556: nam mkha' spang ba'i pha rol nas /
NK126(cho)001:8557: de rnams 'byung ba ma yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8558: de bzhin du sems nyid spang ba'i pha rol nas /
NK126(cho)001:8559: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos rdul tsam 'byung ba yang med do //
NK126(cho)001:8560: de tsam na snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:8561: rig pa rang byung ba'i ye shes su snang bar 'dug go //
NK126(cho)001:8562: mtshan ma sna tshogs su snang ba thams cad rang
NK126(cho)001:8563: byung gi ye shes rang snang bar 'dug pa de
NK126(cho)001:8564: la / mtshan ma rang sar grol ba'i dgongs pa zhes de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK126(cho)001:8565: skyon yon gyi rtogs pa ci yang mi skye ste /
NK126(cho)001:8566: thams cad rig pa rang byung gi ngo bor gsal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8567: de ka la tha snyad du chos zhes btags pa tsam du zad do //
NK126(cho)001:8568: yang b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8569: sems nyid kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8570: nam mkha'i rang bzhin skye med gdal ba la //
NK126(cho)001:8571: 'byung ba'i rang bzhin ye nas rnam par dag /
NK126(cho)001:8572: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas skye med la //
NK126(cho)001:8573: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin ye nas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8575: de la 'da' ka ma tshig gsum gyi dgongs pa byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:8576: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:8577: sku gsung thugs su sangs ma rgyas pa gcig kyang med do //
NK126(cho)001:8578: gzugs su snang tshad ye nas sku /
NK126(cho)001:8579: sgra ru grags pa'i rnam pa thams cad ye nas gsung /
NK126(cho)001:8580: dran rtog dang gzung 'dzin sna tshogs su snang ba ni thugs so //
NK126(cho)001:8582: gzugs sna tshogs ci snang bod tsa na stong /
NK126(cho)001:8583: stong bdo tsa na sna tshogs su snang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:8585: stong pa dbyer med pa la mi lta mi bsgom /
NK126(cho)001:8586: dbyer med la mi gnas ma chags pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8588: yang sgra ru grags bdo la stong pa la /
NK126(cho)001:8589: stong badotsa na sgra ru grags so //
NK126(cho)001:8590: sgra ru grags pa dang stong pa dbyer med pa
NK126(cho)001:8591: la mi gnas mi bsgom mi lta mi chags pa
NK126(cho)001:8592: ni rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen po'o
NK126(cho)001:8594: yang rtog pa sna tshogs zhes cir rtog bdo tsam na stong /
NK126(cho)001:8595: stong bdo tsam na sna tshogs su zhen cing rtog pas /
NK126(cho)001:8596: des na rtog pa dang stong pa dbyer med /
NK126(cho)001:8597: dbyer med tsam la mi gnas ma chags pa ni 'da' ka 'chi brod kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8598: de ltar ngo shes par bya ba dang shes par byed pa gnyis med pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8599: rtogs pa de ltar chos thams cad rang gi sems su thag chod pas /
NK126(cho)001:8600: de ni sangs rgyas mngon sum pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:8601: b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:8602: rtsol med sems kyi klong la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8603: rnyag chen dz+ny+aa nas go bar gyis /
NK126(cho)001:8604: byang chub sems las ma rtogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:8605: sangs rgyas logs na med par yid ches gyis /
NK126(cho)001:8608: snang dang stong pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:8609: rig pa byang chub sems su gcig /
NK126(cho)001:8610: dag dang ma dag chos rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:8611: gang yang spang blang med pa cig /
NK126(cho)001:8612: des na gnyis med byang chub sems su rdzogs //
NK126(cho)001:8614: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi dngos gzhi /
NK126(cho)001:8615: rang gi byang chub sems snang bas /
NK126(cho)001:8616: da 'bad rtsol gyis log tu bsgrub tu med do //
NK126(cho)001:8617: des na nam mkha'i snang ba'am /
NK126(cho)001:8619: me long gi gzugs brnyan nam /
NK126(cho)001:8621: chu nang gi mar me dang 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:8622: so sor snang yang ngo bo med pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8623: des na chos thams cad sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes su lhun gyis grub pas /
NK126(cho)001:8624: gang yang spang ba med par ka nas dag pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8625: sems nyid thig le nyag cig chos kyi sku'i ngo bor ye nas sa ngas rgyas pas /
NK126(cho)001:8626: rtag pa dang chad pa'i mu mtha' ming yang med /
NK126(cho)001:8627: zab cing gting dpag dka' ste /
NK126(cho)001:8628: de ltar ma skyes pa'i chos nyid /
NK126(cho)001:8630: chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid dam /
NK126(cho)001:8631: ngo bo 'di 'dra zhes gang du yang ma grub /
NK126(cho)001:8632: bsgom pa'i mchog ldan rang gi sems la ltos //
NK126(cho)001:8633: bsgom na 'da' ka'i tshig gsum bsgom //
NK126(cho)001:8634: bsgom du med pa'i don rnyed na //
NK126(cho)001:8635: bsgom yang mi lto sems nyid dang //
NK126(cho)001:8636: b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8637: 'di ni nam mkha' klong yang bsgom pa ste /
NK126(cho)001:8639: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i nam mkha'i klong nas kyang chags par snang /
NK126(cho)001:8641: chags 'jigs gnyis ka nam mkha'i rang bzhin ngang //
NK126(cho)001:8642: nam mkha' rang gi ngo bo la //
NK126(cho)001:8643: nam mkha' spang pa'i pha rol na //
NK126(cho)001:8645: dper na nam mkha' nyid snang srid ltar snang ste /
NK126(cho)001:8646: snang srid nyid nam mkha' las ma g.yos pa bzhin /
NK126(cho)001:8647: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems la yang /
NK126(cho)001:8648: yin pa dang min pa la sogs pa /
NK126(cho)001:8649: mtshan ma sna tshogs ci byung yang /
NK126(cho)001:8653: byung na rang byung ba yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8654: ci dang ci byung ba thams cad sems ma yin /
NK126(cho)001:8655: rdul tsam yang g.yos sa med do //
NK126(cho)001:8656: de ltar rtogs pa ldan pa'i mis /
NK126(cho)001:8657: bltas na da bzod mngon no //
NK126(cho)001:8659: 'byung ba mkhan ngang las ma rtogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:8660: sprin dang khu rlang gang las byung //
NK126(cho)001:8661: rang byung rang zhi nam mkha' rang gi gshis //
NK126(cho)001:8662: chos nyid byang chub sems dpa' ma rtogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:8663: rtogs pa'i mtshan ma gud na ci yang med //
NK126(cho)001:8664: rang byung sems kyi rang gi klong //
NK126(cho)001:8665: de ltar rtogs pa'i klong du su gnas pa //
NK126(cho)001:8666: sku gzugs mi ru 'dug kyang rdo rje sems dpa' dngos //
NK126(cho)001:8668: dper na ka la ping ka sgang nga nang du gshog drug rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:8669: bar snang yangs pa lam du bde bar gda' //
NK126(cho)001:8670: rnal 'byor ma bcos don la blo sbyangs pas //
NK126(cho)001:8671: 'gro drug g.yang sa chos kyi nyid du snang //
NK126(cho)001:8672: nam mkha' klong yang dgongs pa b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:8673: rtsol med kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8674: rang sems rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK126(cho)001:8675: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:8676: rnam dag ma bcos thig ler bsgral //
NK126(cho)001:8677: mkha' ltar dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:8678: dge sdig gnyis kyi gos pa med //
NK126(cho)001:8679: sems nyid nam mkha' dag pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:8681: khams gsum bsgral na de ltar sgrol /
NK126(cho)001:8683: 'di ltar snang ba khams gsum dang /
NK126(cho)001:8684: srid gsum ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun /
NK126(cho)001:8685: mtshan ma dngos por snang ba thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:8686: byang chub sems kyi snang ba yin te /
NK126(cho)001:8687: dper gnyid log pa'i rmi lam du /
NK126(cho)001:8689: lha'i longs spyod ni sna tshogs spyod na /
NK126(cho)001:8690: gnyid sad nas lha'i longs spyod ci yang med de /
NK126(cho)001:8691: rang gi sems lha'i longs spyod ltar snang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:8693: rang gi sems khams gsum dang srid gsum du snang ba las /
NK126(cho)001:8694: sems spang ba'i pha rol na /
NK126(cho)001:8695: khams gsum srid gsum bya ba'i ming yang med do //
NK126(cho)001:8697: 'dod pa'i khams su snang ba yang rang gi sems /
NK126(cho)001:8698: gzugs kyi khams su snang ba yang rang gi sems /
NK126(cho)001:8699: gzugs med pa'i khams su snang ba yang rang gi sems /
NK126(cho)001:8701: rang nyid khams gsum gyi ngo bor ma shes na /
NK126(cho)001:8702: bdag gzhan gyi dngos por rtogs pas bdag dang bdag gir mthong /
NK126(cho)001:8704: mtshan ma sna tshogs su bzung bas /
NK126(cho)001:8705: khams gsum dang srid gsum du snang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:8706: khams gsum srid gsum snang ba nyid /
NK126(cho)001:8707: rang gi sems su shes shing /
NK126(cho)001:8708: rtogs phan chad sems ni ye thog ma nas sangs rgyas so //
NK126(cho)001:8711: spros bral lam pa'i shes rab kyi ma byas pa /
NK126(cho)001:8713: 'di zhes kyi mtshan ma ci yang med do //
NK126(cho)001:8714: de 'dra'i rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po des /
NK126(cho)001:8715: sems rang snang ba'i thugs rje sna tshogs su longs spyod do //
NK126(cho)001:8718: de ltar phyi nang dngos po gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK126(cho)001:8720: skye med thig le nyag gcig ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8721: khams gsum yangs sgrol gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8722: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:8723: kun bzang de nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8724: bde chen byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK126(cho)001:8725: rgyu rkyen ma bskyed gnyen po'i mthus mi g.yo //
NK126(cho)001:8726: snang srid ye sangs rgyas pas 'bras bu chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:8727: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chos nyid longs spyod byed //
NK126(cho)001:8728: thams cad sems su mthong bas 'khor ba ye nas dag /
NK126(cho)001:8729: sems nyid ye sangs rgyas pas kun tu bzang po'i klong //
NK126(cho)001:8730: bdag med phyogs dang bral bas rtsol ba ming yang med //
NK126(cho)001:8731: rnam rtog rang sems yin pas brag cha'i sgra dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:8732: sna tshogs chos sku rdzogs pas a ti rang gi sems //
NK126(cho)001:8733: byed spyod thams cad yid bzhin gter dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:8734: man ngag rgyal po rang gi sems nyid yin //
NK126(cho)001:8735: ces b+aee ro tsa na bdag gis bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:8736: rgya gar yul gyi nub phyogs na //
NK126(cho)001:8737: u rgyan yul gyi byang chub shing drung du //
NK126(cho)001:8738: dga' rab rdo rjes thugs kyi bcud phyung nas //
NK126(cho)001:8739: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa nas blo yi snod bzed nas //
NK126(cho)001:8740: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po'i rigs pa'i gter du 'khum //
NK126(cho)001:8741: rnal 'byor dam tshig gzhung du btsun //
NK126(cho)001:8742: rdo rje snying po don gyi rnal 'byor la //
NK126(cho)001:8743: gser gyi ri mchog 'bar ba bsgrod na yang //
NK126(cho)001:8744: yid bzhin rin chen gter la spyod 'dod pas //
NK126(cho)001:8745: blo rtse lkog rno bdag gi 'di ltar shes par bya //
NK126(cho)001:8746: dgongs pa de nyid sleb pa'i tshad dang bzlog pa'i sa //
NK126(cho)001:8747: de la gol ba'i sa dang nyon mongs ro //
NK126(cho)001:8748: tshad dang ldan nam mi ldan blo yis brtags par bya /
NK126(cho)001:8749: de la rang sems rang byung gis /
NK126(cho)001:8750: ye shes ye nas sangs rgyas yin par ngo ma shes te /
NK126(cho)001:8751: de ltar ma rig pas rang snang log pa'i 'khrul pa las /
NK126(cho)001:8752: de la gzung 'dzin gyi zhen pa mthu brtags pas /
NK126(cho)001:8753: khams gsum du 'khyams zhing skye shi'i 'khor lo la bskor nas /
NK126(cho)001:8754: nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal rgyun ma chad par 'khor bar 'khyams pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8756: skye shi 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ni /
NK126(cho)001:8757: rang gi byang chub sems su go rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:8758: sems kyi mtshan nyid cis kyang ma grub pa //
NK126(cho)001:8759: cir yang sprul nas ci yang snang //
NK126(cho)001:8760: snang tsam nyid na stong nyid do //
NK126(cho)001:8761: stong tsam nyid na sna tshogs snang //
NK126(cho)001:8762: des na snang stong gnyis su dbyer med do //
NK126(cho)001:8763: dbyer med rang byung ye shes chos kyi sku zhes brjod //
NK126(cho)001:8764: chos sku bde ba chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:8765: gser gyi ri mchog bsgrod ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:8766: rtogs pa'i don las ma bcos ngang //
NK126(cho)001:8767: rang byung ye shes rgyun mi chad //
NK126(cho)001:8768: bde ba'i longs spyod zad mi shes //
NK126(cho)001:8769: yid bzhin gter dang spyod ces bya //
NK126(cho)001:8770: de yang sangs rgyas nyid dang dgongs pa mnyam //
