NK126(cho)001:8771: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8776: thams cad ye nas chen po las g.yos na /
NK126(cho)001:8777: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rtags yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8778: dper na nam shi ba'i dus na /
NK126(cho)001:8779: rang gi rig pa rang byung /
NK126(cho)001:8780: rang snang 'dzin med du shar ba la /
NK126(cho)001:8784: 'di dang pha rol du bya ba gnyis su ma mthong bas /
NK126(cho)001:8785: shi dang ma shi bya ba ga la yod do //
NK126(cho)001:8786: de ltar dus gsum mnyam par rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa /
NK126(cho)001:8787: lus mir 'dug kyang sems sangs rgyas par la thag chod do //
NK126(cho)001:8788: da rung skyes gnas len pa'i rtags ni /
NK126(cho)001:8789: shes rab kyi g.yang sa ma chod na /
NK126(cho)001:8790: ting nge 'dzin la longs spyod kyang /
NK126(cho)001:8794: rmi lam bde sdug gi rtogs pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:8796: rtogs tshad mthar ma phyin na /
NK126(cho)001:8797: zhen pa las ma grol ba'i skyon yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:8798: da rung bka' rgyud lung gsum /
NK126(cho)001:8801: ma h+aa yo ga'i dgongs pa bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:8802: rang rig ye shes skye med dbyings las /
NK126(cho)001:8804: snang srid lha'i gzhal yas khang /
NK126(cho)001:8805: lus kyi bsgul bskyod thams cad phyag rgya la /
NK126(cho)001:8806: ngag gi ci bzlas thams cad gsung gi bzlas brjod yin /
NK126(cho)001:8807: lag gi ci bzung thams cad dam tshig phyag rgya /
NK126(cho)001:8809: phyag rgya chen po lha skur rtogs tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:8810: lha dang gzhal yas kun kyang ma bcos rang bzhin dbyings su gsal /
NK126(cho)001:8811: de ni ma h+aa yo ga'i dgongs pa mthar thug pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8812: b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8813: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba chod par gyis /
NK126(cho)001:8814: byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK126(cho)001:8815: nam mkha' ni nyin par gsal la nges par snang /
NK126(cho)001:8816: nam mkha' ni mtshan mo nag la 'thibs pa snang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:8818: nam mkha' ngan du song ngam na ma song ste /
NK126(cho)001:8819: nam mkha' la ngan du 'gro ba'i rgyu med /
NK126(cho)001:8822: nam mkha' mun pa ltar snang ba las nam mkha'i ngo bo la 'gyur ba med do //
NK126(cho)001:8824: rig pa byang chub kyi sems kyang /
NK126(cho)001:8826: skye shi ltar snang ba 'dis sems ngan du song ngam /
NK126(cho)001:8827: dper na bza' bca' zhim po zos pas /
NK126(cho)001:8829: ngan skyug tu song ba lta bur cig yin nam zhe na de min te /
NK126(cho)001:8830: sems nyid la ngan du 'gro ba'i rgyu med do //
NK126(cho)001:8831: sems nyid la 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal nyon mongs pa ltar snang ba 'di /
NK126(cho)001:8832: rang sems skye med nam mkha' lta bur sna tshogs par snang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:8833: sna tshogs su snang ba nyid sems skye med rang snang bar ma rig ma go ma shes pas /
NK126(cho)001:8834: sems skye med rang byung rang snang nyid /
NK126(cho)001:8835: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong du snang ba nyid /
NK126(cho)001:8836: sems kyi ngo bo skye med la 'gyur ba rdul tsam yang med do //
NK126(cho)001:8838: nam mkha' ni nyin par gsal la dngas pa 'dug pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:8839: nam mkha' kha dog dang ldan par bzang du song ba yin nam zhe na /
NK126(cho)001:8844: de gsal la dngas pa ltar snang ba 'di /
NK126(cho)001:8845: gzi ldan 'od kyi rgyal po nam mkha' la shar bas /
NK126(cho)001:8846: gsal ba dngas pa ltar snang ba yin /
NK126(cho)001:8847: nam mkha' la bzang ngan du 'gyur ba med de /
NK126(cho)001:8848: dper na de bzhin du byang chub sems la ting nge 'dzin dang bsgom bsgrub bam /
NK126(cho)001:8849: chos spyod ci snyed cig spyod nas /
NK126(cho)001:8850: byang chub sems bde ba thob pa ltar snang na /
NK126(cho)001:8851: byang chub sems bzang du song ba 'am /
NK126(cho)001:8853: byang chub thob pa yod dam med de /
NK126(cho)001:8854: byang chub sems la bskal par 'das na bsgom bsgrub bam /
NK126(cho)001:8856: sems nyid bzang du song ba'am /
NK126(cho)001:8857: byang chub thob pa med do //
NK126(cho)001:8858: nam mkha' lta bu skye ba med la 'gyur ba med do //
NK126(cho)001:8860: byang chub ltar snang ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:8861: rang gi rang ngo shes ste /
NK126(cho)001:8862: rang gi rig pa skye med nyid /
NK126(cho)001:8864: byang chub thob pa snyams byed par snang /
NK126(cho)001:8866: bde ba ltar snang ba ni /
NK126(cho)001:8867: rang gi byang chub kyi sems rang snang ba yin no //
NK126(cho)001:8868: rang sems skye med rang snang ba ma yin pa /
NK126(cho)001:8869: rang sems skye med nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK126(cho)001:8870: bskal pa'i bar du 'bad rtsol gyis bzang du 'gro ba'i rgyu med do //
NK126(cho)001:8871: dper na nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsnan kyang bzang du 'gro ba med do //
NK126(cho)001:8872: phan ma btags pa bzhin no //
NK126(cho)001:8873: nam mkha' la bskal pa'i bar du /
NK126(cho)001:8875: byang chub sems la mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK126(cho)001:8876: mtshams med pa lnga spyad kyang /
NK126(cho)001:8877: byang chub sems la rdul tsam yang 'bri ba med do //
NK126(cho)001:8878: gnod pa bskyal nas ngan du song ba'am 'pho 'gyur med do //
NK126(cho)001:8879: skye med nam mkha' lta bu yin pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)001:8880: mnar med sems can dmyal ba'i gnas su btso bsregs byung yang /
NK126(cho)001:8881: sems kyi snang ba dmyal ba ltar snang /
NK126(cho)001:8882: btso bsreg ltar snang ba las /
NK126(cho)001:8883: de rnams kyi ngo bo skye med nam mkha' lta bu la skye rgyu yang med /
NK126(cho)001:8884: btso bsregs bya rgyu yang med /
NK126(cho)001:8885: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i phyir ro //
NK126(cho)001:8887: rgyu med rkyen med dngos po ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8889: byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba de ltar chod na /
NK126(cho)001:8890: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi gol sa med par la chod do //
NK126(cho)001:8891: lta ba'i la chod dang b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:8893: lta ba thag chod kyi skabs ste nyer dgu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:8894: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras b+aee ro tsa na la /
NK126(cho)001:8895: gser srang drug cu tham pa phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:8896: brkyang phyag len stong du mdzad do //
NK126(cho)001:8897: bla ma'i bka' drin lan ci ltar byas na drin lan 'khor bsam ste ngus pas /
NK126(cho)001:8898: b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:8899: mos gus dad pa ldan pa'i ku ma ra //
NK126(cho)001:8900: rang sems kun bzang rdo rje sems //
NK126(cho)001:8901: rang sems rig par ma gyur mthong snang so sor mthong //
NK126(cho)001:8902: bslab pa'i chos kyi rang sems mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:8903: drangs don sre te chos kyi bskal pa'i mthar bshad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:8904: skye med phyir mi ldog pa'i sangs rgyas mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:8905: lus ngag yid gsum bslab pa'i las byas bskal pa'i 'bad rtsol gyis //
NK126(cho)001:8906: skye med phyir mi ldog pa'i sangs rgyas mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:8907: mos gus dad dang ldan pas mkhas pa'i man ngag rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:8908: man ngag 'phrul gyi me long lta bur rang sems skye med mthong //
NK126(cho)001:8909: skye med rang sems mthong bas 'khor 'das gnyis dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:8910: phyir mi ldog pa'i sangs rgyas de la bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:8911: rang sems chos sku nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK126(cho)001:8912: nam mkha' mtha' dang dbus med kha dog phyogs dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:8913: sems kyang mtha' dang dbus med kha dog phyogs dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:8914: de ltar phyogs med nam mkha' chen po la //
NK126(cho)001:8915: lung pa'i dbyibs dang khang khyim bu ga sna tshogs dang //
NK126(cho)001:8916: gru bzhi gru gsum nar mo zlum po la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:8917: de ltar byang sems nam mkha' lta bu'i phyogs med la //
NK126(cho)001:8918: sgo lnga rnam shes 'khor 'das bde sdug sna tshogs snang //
NK126(cho)001:8919: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med de de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK126(cho)001:8920: des na dgag bsgrub blang dor gang la byed //
NK126(cho)001:8921: de ltar rang sems thig le nyag gcig tu //
NK126(cho)001:8922: rtogs nas 'khor 'das chos kyi gol sa med pa la chod do //
NK126(cho)001:8923: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:8924: phyogs dang nam mkha' kha dog 'di zhes med pa la //
NK126(cho)001:8925: sprin dang 'od kyi 'ja' tshon sna tshogs snang //
NK126(cho)001:8926: de bzhin mkha' ltar dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:8927: sgo lnga'i snang ba rtog pa sna tshogs 'char //
NK126(cho)001:8928: rtog pa de nyid rang sems chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:8929: bzang ngan dgag bsgrub med do mnyam nyid bde ba chen po'i klong //
NK126(cho)001:8930: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK126(cho)001:8931: de ltar rtogs na b+aee ro tsa na nga dang mnyams //
NK126(cho)001:8932: nga yi man ngag 'di thos na //
NK126(cho)001:8933: bkri drang pre ti'i chos la slob pa mgo bo na //
NK126(cho)001:8934: rang sems rtogs na 'khor 'das chos la slob gnyer la dogs pa med par la chod do //
NK126(cho)001:8935: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:8936: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK126(cho)001:8937: de yi chog go go bar gyis //
NK126(cho)001:8938: bka' yi snying khu thabs kyi bcud //
NK126(cho)001:8939: nga yi go ba bzhin du khyod la gtad //
NK126(cho)001:8940: khyod kyi sems kyi gter du sbas //
NK126(cho)001:8942: rang snang chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8943: ci yang ma grub dug lnga chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:8944: spang 'geg sbyang bsgyur la sogs snying re rje //
NK126(cho)001:8945: rlung nyid nam mkha' yin pa cha yod dam //
NK126(cho)001:8946: de bzhin nyon mongs sems nyid yin pa cha yod dam //
NK126(cho)001:8947: sems la rgyu rkyen med pa cha yod dam //
NK126(cho)001:8948: rang byung ye shes yin pa cha yod dam //
NK126(cho)001:8949: rlung nyid nam mkha' yin pa cha med na //
NK126(cho)001:8950: sbud pa bu ga'i rlung gi gang nas byung //
NK126(cho)001:8951: nyon mongs sems nyid yin pa cha med na //
NK126(cho)001:8952: sems las logs pa'i dug lnga gang nas byung //
NK126(cho)001:8953: sems la rgyu rkyen med pa cha med na //
NK126(cho)001:8954: sems nyid brtsal bas mi rnyed ltas pas mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:8955: sems kyi ngo bo 'di la 'di zhes pa //
NK126(cho)001:8956: dus gsum rgyal bas mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:8957: dper na sems nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK126(cho)001:8958: sems kyang med do chos kyang med //
NK126(cho)001:8959: las kyang med pa rnam smin ga la yod //
NK126(cho)001:8960: dkar nag las kyi 'bras bu sems nyid rang snang yin //
NK126(cho)001:8961: sems nyid rang snang min zer na //
NK126(cho)001:8962: sa rdo ri brag 'di yang rnam smin dang //
NK126(cho)001:8963: bde sdug nyams su myong bar 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:8964: des na 'gro drug bde sdug sems nyid rang snang yin //
NK126(cho)001:8965: des na sems nyid nam mkha' ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:8966: des na dug lnga chos sku yin par la chod do //
NK126(cho)001:8969: theg dman blo chung la bstan du mi 'dod pa'i skabs ste sum bcu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:8973: bya bral lhun grub klong la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:8974: ma g.yos rdzogs chen spyi'i rgyan //
NK126(cho)001:8975: theg pa'i yang rtse rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)001:8976: thams cad 'di ru gcig pas na //
NK126(cho)001:8977: spyi yi nor bu rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:8978: yon tan mi zad nor bu rin po che //
NK126(cho)001:8979: dngos grub thams cad 'byung ba'i gzhi //
NK126(cho)001:8980: kun la nye ring med pas na //
NK126(cho)001:8981: nyi ma'i 'od bzhin khyab par gdal //
NK126(cho)001:8983: rdo rje ri bo rtse bzhin no //
NK126(cho)001:8984: 'jigs bral nyams nga yongs kyi med //
NK126(cho)001:8986: spyod lam rnam bzhi kun tu yangs //
NK126(cho)001:8987: de la g.yos pa med pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:8988: sa steng 'gro ba ci bzhin no //
NK126(cho)001:8989: rgan gzhon na tshod med pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:8990: pha mo ris su mi phyed par //
NK126(cho)001:8991: kun la mnyam pa gnas pas na //
NK126(cho)001:8992: bzang ngan med pa'i gser gyi rdzas dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:8993: dka' thub 'bad rtsol mi dgos so //
NK126(cho)001:8994: kun la gzhi la bzhags pas na //
NK126(cho)001:8995: byar med don dang 'phrad pas chog /'dis grol 'dis bcing med pas na //
NK126(cho)001:8996: bcing grol gnyis dang bral ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:8997: mtha' gzhi yan par bzhag pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:8998: lang dang nyal la khyad med pas //
NK126(cho)001:8999: chos nyid klongs las ma 'das pas //
NK126(cho)001:9000: gar bde spyod pa byed pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:9001: nye ring med pas chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:9002: yul dang phyogs la khyad med pas //
NK126(cho)001:9003: grang nag dag tu bsdad pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:9004: dgon pa tho yor la kha'i mi //
NK126(cho)001:9005: byin dang rgod pa gnyis med pas //
NK126(cho)001:9006: 'phrig dang rtogs pa'i yul med pas //
NK126(cho)001:9008: gang mthong chos nyid cer mthong la //
NK126(cho)001:9009: sgo lnga phye btsum med pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:9010: dbang po har bar bzhag pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:9011: mnyam pa'i klong na gnas pa la //
NK126(cho)001:9012: bsgom dang ma bsgom med pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:9013: yengs dang ma yengs med pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:9014: dmyal ba la sogs me 'bar chu 'brugs kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9015: sems nyid rang snang yin pas na //
NK126(cho)001:9016: nyam nga med par bsdad pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:9018: chos nyid klong las ma 'das pas //
NK126(cho)001:9019: dge sdig med par rig pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:9020: ces dga' rab rdo rjes thugs kyi bdud rtsi'i thig pa zag pas /
NK126(cho)001:9021: b+aee ro tsa na blo'i snod du bcas /
NK126(cho)001:9023: rnyag chen dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK126(cho)001:9024: bdud rtsi'i thig pa zag pa thugs kyi dkyil du thim /
NK126(cho)001:9027: skal med rnams kyi mthong na dmyal bar skye //
NK126(cho)001:9028: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9030: 'di b+aee ro tsa na dang zhal mjal ba dang 'dra'o //
NK126(cho)001:9031: rang byung chos nyid klong la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:9032: gti mug chen po byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:9033: mnyam pa'i ngang la phyogs ris med //
NK126(cho)001:9034: zhe sdang chen po byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:9035: 'khor ba zhes gcod drag shul thabs //
NK126(cho)001:9036: 'dod chags nyid la byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:9037: 'gro ba 'i don la chags pa che //
NK126(cho)001:9038: nga rgyal nyid na byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:9039: lta dman thams cad zil gyi gnon //
NK126(cho)001:9040: phrag dog chen po byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:9041: nyag cig gang nas sangs rgyas med //
NK126(cho)001:9042: dug lnga gang nas chos sku med //
NK126(cho)001:9043: dug lnga mi spang spyad pas chog /'jig rten chos brgyad ci spyad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9044: chos sku byang chub sems kyi klong //
NK126(cho)001:9045: 'dod yon lnga las rol pas chog /
NK126(cho)001:9046: sems nyid rdzogs pa chen po 'di //
NK126(cho)001:9047: gang yang 'gag pa med par shar //
NK126(cho)001:9048: ci yang ma spang gang yang ma 'dus med //
NK126(cho)001:9049: ci yang yin la gang yang min //
NK126(cho)001:9050: dgag bsgrub spang blang med do byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)001:9051: khyab gdal 'ub chub rdzogs pa che //
NK126(cho)001:9052: chung ngu ma spang che rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:9053: mtho dman med do mnyam pa nyid //
NK126(cho)001:9054: de yi don las gang gnas pa //
NK126(cho)001:9055: don chen rtogs pa'i skyes bu yin //
NK126(cho)001:9056: sangs rgyas nyid dang dgongs pa mnyams //
NK126(cho)001:9057: de la dus gsum sangs rgyas kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9058: bu cig pa yi ma ltar byams //
NK126(cho)001:9059: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK126(cho)001:9060: mthu rtsal rang bzhin shugs kyi che //
NK126(cho)001:9061: ci phyir rnal 'byor gding ldan pa //
NK126(cho)001:9062: lo ka'i lha srin sde brgyad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9063: bran gyi tshul du las rnams byed //
NK126(cho)001:9064: ci ltar bsgo ba bzhin du nyan //
NK126(cho)001:9065: rnal 'byor rgyal po de la ni //
NK126(cho)001:9066: rgyal po bzhin du 'gyur nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:9067: nor bu rin chen bzhin du dgyes par mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:9068: ci ltar bsgo ba'i las rnams byed //
NK126(cho)001:9069: gding ldan de yi mthu dang rtsal mthong na //
NK126(cho)001:9070: nyan thos byis pa'i sdug brtsir gyis //
NK126(cho)001:9071: mi yi lan mo spre'u zlos 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9072: gding ldan rnal 'byor de la ni //
NK126(cho)001:9074: phyi nang skye shi med pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:9075: mos pa rnams la thugs rje char ltar phab //
NK126(cho)001:9076: sdang zhing smos pa rnams la ni //
NK126(cho)001:9077: dregs pa lha srin rnams kyang sdang //
NK126(cho)001:9078: des na rnal 'byor gding dang ma ldan na //
NK126(cho)001:9079: lo ka'i lha srin sde brgyad kyis //
NK126(cho)001:9080: chad pa dbab pa'i gnas su mthong //
NK126(cho)001:9081: des na rnal 'byor chos nyid ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9082: bskal pa stong du tshogs bsags kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9083: sbyin dang kha thon la sogs dang //
NK126(cho)001:9084: bde gshegs tshogs dang legs spyad ci byas pa //
NK126(cho)001:9085: skad cig mi yi sdig pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:9086: ci tsam bsgrags pa'i grogs rnams kun //
NK126(cho)001:9087: ngan tshig gcig gi bshig pa bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:9088: brlag par byed do ku ma ra //
NK126(cho)001:9089: nam mkha' 'jig pa med pa bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:9090: ma skye pas na 'jig pa med //
NK126(cho)001:9091: skye med rdo rje rtogs par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:9092: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9093: b+aee ro tsa na nyid dang zhal mjal kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9094: 'di las bcud phyung rgyu med pa'i phyir 'dra 'bags chen po zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:9095: nga yi ngag la phyi rab kun kyang nyon //
NK126(cho)001:9096: bdag 'dra b+aee ro tsa na yis //
NK126(cho)001:9097: dka' ba bcu drug byed nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:9098: u rgyan thor cog can gyi yul du phyin //
NK126(cho)001:9099: dga' rab rdo rje mkhas pa nyid dang mjal //
NK126(cho)001:9100: dga' rab rdo rje thugs kyi thig zag pa //
NK126(cho)001:9101: b+aee ro tsa na bdag gis snod bzed nas //
NK126(cho)001:9102: man ngag bdud rtsi'i thig pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:9103: rtogs dang ldan pa ma yin pa //
NK126(cho)001:9104: gzhan gyi rna bar ma gleng shig /
NK126(cho)001:9105: khe drag nga rgyal chen la shor ra re //
NK126(cho)001:9106: don med tshig gi 'chal pa rnams la shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9107: tshig bcad 'bad rtsol las la zhugs pa rnams la shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9108: bcad kyang khrag med ser snas bcing pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:9109: yon tan dad pa gnyis med pa //
NK126(cho)001:9110: mi yi ngo drin bka' 'phyar dang //
NK126(cho)001:9111: thabs khram 'go brus byed pa la //
NK126(cho)001:9112: nga yi man ngag shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9113: mu stegs mkha' la mtho 'jal rnams la shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9114: nyan thos byis pa rnams la shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9115: lce bde tshig dum glu ru gyer ba rnams la shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9116: sde bdun pa dang bstan pa'i sde bdar rnams la shor la re //
NK126(cho)001:9117: man ngag 'di ni gtad pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:9118: dad pa che ba'i tshad ni //
NK126(cho)001:9119: rtag par rab tu ngu ba 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9120: bla ma shin tu gdung zhing gces pa //
NK126(cho)001:9121: nor bu rin chen lta bur 'dzin //
NK126(cho)001:9122: bla ma'i phyogs su lus srog gnyis kyang phong pa med par gtang dgos na //
NK126(cho)001:9123: gces pa nor gyi dbyigs dang sbyor ba zad kyi bcud //
NK126(cho)001:9124: bla ma'i phyogs su phong pa rdul tsam med //
NK126(cho)001:9125: bka' rgyud rnams la blta zhing rtag tu brten //
NK126(cho)001:9126: lta dgongs sems la lta yin rtsol med chos la mos //
NK126(cho)001:9127: de 'dra'i slob ma rnyed na man ngag 'di 'dra gtad pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:9128: de 'dra ma rnyed sra brtan brag la sbas //
NK126(cho)001:9129: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:9136: phyi rabs rnams la gtad pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:9140: b+aee ro tsa nas bka' rgyud lung gi don bsdus pa /
NK126(cho)001:9141: man ngag gi bcud btig pa'i skabs te so gcig pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9142: rje ma h+aa gu ru lags /
NK126(cho)001:9143: thabs kyis spang bar bya ba'i slob dpon de gang lags //
NK126(cho)001:9145: nyon cig g.yu sgra snying gi bu //
NK126(cho)001:9146: slob dpon ngan pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK126(cho)001:9147: theg pa dman la zhugs pa dang //
NK126(cho)001:9148: theg pa chung ba'i blo sbram dang //
NK126(cho)001:9149: lar yang blo 'phang dma' ba dang //
NK126(cho)001:9150: tshig gi lan cig tshig la dga' //
NK126(cho)001:9151: khong dregs che la rang mthong che //
NK126(cho)001:9152: lus spyod sgeg pas che ru che //
NK126(cho)001:9153: kha lce mkhas pa btsun du re //
NK126(cho)001:9154: khang rlung 'bud kyis gdan la bzhugs //
NK126(cho)001:9155: nor dad che la zas la ngan //
NK126(cho)001:9156: shes lung med par slob ma tshol //
NK126(cho)001:9157: rang gi mi shes gzhan la slob //
NK126(cho)001:9158: dregs pa'i rtsal gyis khang rlung 'bud //
NK126(cho)001:9159: rang gi dbang rnams ma rdzogs par //
NK126(cho)001:9160: gzhan la dbang bskur byin brlabs byed //
NK126(cho)001:9161: rnam rtog che la mtshan ma'i chos spyod 'bad nas byed //
NK126(cho)001:9162: de rnams slob dpon ngan pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK126(cho)001:9164: byis pa bslu ba'i chos spyod rtogs pa'i lam la btsud pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:9165: phyin pa'i lam med rtogs pa'i dus med do //
NK126(cho)001:9166: chos nyid tshol bas rnyed par gar la 'gyur //
NK126(cho)001:9167: slob dpon tshad mar ma gyur spre'u 'dra ba'i lung //
NK126(cho)001:9168: ces pas b+aee ro tsa na bdag gi bshad //
NK126(cho)001:9169: de ni thabs kyis spang bar bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:9170: yang g.yu sgra snying pos zhus pa /
NK126(cho)001:9172: bla ma bzang ba'i mtshan nyid ci lta lags //
NK126(cho)001:9174: b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9175: blo che blo yangs blo zab pa //
NK126(cho)001:9176: rig pa'i rtsal dang ldan pa'i skyes bu yis //
NK126(cho)001:9177: bka' rgyud lung gsum man ngag khongs su chud //
NK126(cho)001:9178: bla ma mkhas pa'i byin brlabs dbang bskur thob //
NK126(cho)001:9179: tshul chos thabs khrom mi byed spyod pa lhug par spyod //
NK126(cho)001:9180: nga rgyal dregs pa mi byed tha mal kun dang mnyam //
NK126(cho)001:9181: chos 'tshang zog po mi byed chu rkyal kha bzhin dam //
NK126(cho)001:9182: dman pa'i lus su zhugs nas hrul po phags te gon //
NK126(cho)001:9183: za na gtsang sme chung ste ci yang byin pa za //
NK126(cho)001:9184: smra na kha spyang mi byed zang thal ha re smra //
NK126(cho)001:9185: chos spyod sdug brtser mi byed lta khams co le smra //
NK126(cho)001:9186: gang la 'dzin rtogs mi byed mdze ro lhog ro khur //
NK126(cho)001:9187: man ngag mi ster shin tu dka' la dam //
NK126(cho)001:9188: dman pa'i lus la dam pa'i dgongs pa can de la //
NK126(cho)001:9189: mnyes pa sna tshogs zas nor phong med 'bul //
NK126(cho)001:9190: thugs kyi bcud rnams chod par de la zhus //
NK126(cho)001:9191: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas phyi rabs rnams la gdam pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:9192: zhal gdams bdud rtsi'i thig pa zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)001:9194: slob dpon gyi skyon dang yon tan bstan pa'i skabs te so gnyis pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9195: de nas yang rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:9196: rje ma h+aa gu ru lags /
NK126(cho)001:9198: 'phral la spyod pa ci ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:9199: bla ma'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9200: dam tshig kun gyi rgyud dag na //
NK126(cho)001:9201: rgya che zab par gsungs nas yod //
NK126(cho)001:9202: da lta bshad kyi mi long gi //
NK126(cho)001:9203: phyag byar 'os pa bla ma yin //
NK126(cho)001:9204: zhu na de yang nyams pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:9205: rje bla ma rgyang na bzhugs na za phyag 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:9206: mig gis mthong na mthong phyag 'tshal //
NK126(cho)001:9207: drung du mjal na rten dang bcas pa'i phyag rnams phul //
NK126(cho)001:9208: rten dang che ba'i tshad med do //
NK126(cho)001:9209: chung ba khab dang dar sna phul //
NK126(cho)001:9210: rtag tu lha phyag 'tshal ba ni //
NK126(cho)001:9211: sgrib pa rnam gsum nges par dag /
NK126(cho)001:9212: lha khang gzugs sku ji snyed pas //
NK126(cho)001:9213: bla ma'i na bza' gnyen pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:9214: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9216: b+aee ro tsa na la brkyang phyag len stong du 'tshal te 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9218: mi gnas mi dmigs rang bzhin dkyil 'khor nas //
NK126(cho)001:9219: b+aee ro tsa na sangs rgyas kun gyi rje //
NK126(cho)001:9220: nam mkha'i dbyings las cir yang snang ba'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:9221: rang bzhin stong nyid skye med chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:9222: dus gsum 'dus ma byas pa ye shes thabs kyi sku //
NK126(cho)001:9223: kun bzang b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:9224: sgrar snang brjod med don la ma g.yos kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9225: thugs rjes gdug pa 'dul phyir drag sngags ci ltar kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9226: gsung mchog mtshan mar mi dmigs shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK126(cho)001:9227: kun bzang b+aee ro tsa na'i gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:9228: rnam rtog mi mnga' ci yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK126(cho)001:9229: rang byung ye shes dus gsum 'dus ma byas //
NK126(cho)001:9230: dran med rig pa'i rgyal po yongs su shar //
NK126(cho)001:9231: kun bzang b+aee ro tsa na'i thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:9232: che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs ci yang snang //
NK126(cho)001:9233: snang tsam nyid nas thig le nyag cig nyid //
NK126(cho)001:9234: lhun rdzogs mthar phyin yon tan rgyal ba'i sku //
NK126(cho)001:9235: kun bzang b+aee ro tsa na'i yon tan phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK126(cho)001:9236: thabs kyi phrin las 'gro ba yangs la bsgyur //
NK126(cho)001:9237: skye 'gro mang po thar pa'i lam mchog ston //
NK126(cho)001:9238: thabs mkhas mthar phyin sna tshogs phrin las mdzad //
NK126(cho)001:9239: kun bzang b+aee ro tsa na'i phrin las nyid la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK126(cho)001:9240: bdag lus phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK126(cho)001:9241: dgyes pa'i zhabs tog 'di ltar 'tshal ba bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:9242: chags pa med pa'i tshul du 'bul lags na //
NK126(cho)001:9243: bdag cag bka' drin mi zad gter la spyod pa 'di //
NK126(cho)001:9244: bstan pa khyed kyis bka' drin dpag tu med //
NK126(cho)001:9245: ma rig rmongs pa'i bag chags bsal nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:9246: thar pa'i lam bstan bla ma khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK126(cho)001:9247: rnal 'byor yongs la ma nor don mchog ston mdzad pa //
NK126(cho)001:9248: b+aee ro tsa na'i sku gsung thugs dang yon tan
NK126(cho)001:9249: phrin las lnga la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o
NK126(cho)001:9251: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra'i brkyang phyag lan stong du btsal lo //
NK126(cho)001:9253: rnyag dz+ny+aa nas brkyang phyag lan stong du 'tshal ba'i skabs te so gsum pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9254: yang rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras /
NK126(cho)001:9255: rang sems sangs rgyas yin par yid ches nas 'di gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9256: rang byung ye shes chos nyid snying po la //
NK126(cho)001:9257: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)001:9258: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus pas //
NK126(cho)001:9259: chos rnams snying po yin par yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9260: rang byung ye shes cig gi ngo bo la //
NK126(cho)001:9261: don dam kun rdzob bden rdzun dbyer med par //
NK126(cho)001:9262: mngon par nges pa'i byang chub sems ston pas //
NK126(cho)001:9263: the tshom som nyid med par yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9264: rang byung ye shes cig gi ngo bo la //
NK126(cho)001:9265: rgyu las ma skyes rkyen las ma grub pas //
NK126(cho)001:9266: gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i rang bzhin gyi //
NK126(cho)001:9267: rang byung ye shes yin par yin kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9268: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK126(cho)001:9269: rgyu rkyen med par lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:9270: phrin las rtsol bsgrub 'bad rtsol bya mi dgos //
NK126(cho)001:9271: ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pas yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9272: rang byung ye shes ye nas ma bsgrib pas //
NK126(cho)001:9273: ci ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad gsal //
NK126(cho)001:9274: chos rnams thams cad gtan las 'beb pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)001:9275: bston pa'i sgron me yin par yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9276: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras de skad gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)001:9277: b+aee ro tsa na dgyes so //
NK126(cho)001:9279: rnyag dz+ny+aa nas bla ma la dgongs pa phul ba'i skabs te so bzhi pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9280: de nas yang b+aee ro tsa na li yul du gshegs par chas pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9283: bza' skyems mang po ni drongs /
NK126(cho)001:9284: lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam ni byas /
NK126(cho)001:9286: la las ni mchi ma phyungs /
NK126(cho)001:9287: la las ni b+aee ro tsa na la 'jus te /
NK126(cho)001:9288: bzhugs par zhu ba phul bas /
NK126(cho)001:9289: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9292: b+aee ro tsa nas snyan pa'i glu cig len //
NK126(cho)001:9293: yon tan dad par ldan pa'i bu slob kun kyang gson //
NK126(cho)001:9294: rje blon 'bangs gsum mi nag kun kyang gson //
NK126(cho)001:9295: rgya sder bzhugs pa'i khrom rnams kun kyang gson //
NK126(cho)001:9298: de nas rje b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9299: kyee dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang //
NK126(cho)001:9300: khyad par dgongs pa ldan pa'i dus gsum bla ma dang //
NK126(cho)001:9301: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams bdag la dgongs //
NK126(cho)001:9302: da ni dus thog bka' yi tha mar song //
NK126(cho)001:9303: ma nor gsang sngags spyod pa'i dge bshes gser bas dkon //
NK126(cho)001:9304: sngags pa dam med grong yul 'grim zhing mi nag bsgrub par 'jug /
NK126(cho)001:9305: rtag tsam 'dzin pa'i btsun pa 'dul khrims nyams //
NK126(cho)001:9306: bka' rgyud 'dzin pa'i bod kyi mkhas pa rnams //
NK126(cho)001:9307: des la thob chog byed kyin yig sna zin ris byed //
NK126(cho)001:9308: mkhas bzhed rtsod pa byas pas tshig gi mtha' la zhen //
NK126(cho)001:9309: yab mes dregs pas bzung phyir nges med shes rab bshad //
NK126(cho)001:9310: tshig mkhas don la rmongs pa'i dge bshes kun //
NK126(cho)001:9311: shes lo mkhas lo grags los 'dod pas mi nag mang po bsdus //
NK126(cho)001:9312: me tog 'bul ba byung na mi nag yin kyang slob //
NK126(cho)001:9313: byin brlabs dbang bskur zhu mi byung na khyi dang phag la yin kyang byed //
NK126(cho)001:9314: chos nyan byung na mi nag pho mo byis pa dag la bshad //
NK126(cho)001:9315: khe drag dpung pa mtho na sdig chen yin kyang gdams pa ster //
NK126(cho)001:9316: zas nor yod na dam nyams yin kyang phug tu 'dzud //
NK126(cho)001:9317: dbul cing phongs na skal ldan rigs rgyud bzang yang phyi la bde //
NK126(cho)001:9318: snam gso zhol po gon nas dregs pa'i rigs dbang che //
NK126(cho)001:9319: zas skom mang po gsol nas sha chang tshad med za //
NK126(cho)001:9320: yul 'khor sa bcad bsrung zhing dmag dpung thab mo byed //
NK126(cho)001:9321: dregs pa srin po'i las te shi nas ngu 'bod dmyal bar skye //
NK126(cho)001:9322: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas phyi rabs kyi dge bshes kun la mtshangs tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:9324: bod kyi dge bshes rnams la mtshangs tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te so lnga pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9325: de nas yang b+aee ro tsa nas bod kyi sgrub pa po rnams la mgur bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:9327: 'dir bzhugs pa'i mi sde kun thos bsam shes rgyud ma khrol mkhas pa khur mi shes //
NK126(cho)001:9328: bsre ba'i dbang bskur ma thob mi nag rang dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9329: bsgom bsgrub lha bsnyen ma bskyal gzhung tshigs yug sar bzung //
NK126(cho)001:9330: ldem dgongs sgra tshig ma go rtogs pa gnas ma gyur //
NK126(cho)001:9331: bka' lung man ngag ma shes dam tshig bsrungs ma shes //
NK126(cho)001:9332: mched grogs sum 'byin slob dpon spang len byed //
NK126(cho)001:9333: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig gtan nas nyams //
NK126(cho)001:9334: dam can bsgrub pas mi 'grub slar la bdud du 'bab //
NK126(cho)001:9335: chos la yid chad slob dpon bskur pas 'debs //
NK126(cho)001:9336: de 'dra'i sngags pa shi nas ngu 'bod dmyal bar skye //
NK126(cho)001:9337: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas bsgrub pa po rnams la mtshangs tshig mgur bzhengs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:9339: bsgrub pa po rnams la mtshangs tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te so drug pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9341: b+aee ro tsa nas btsun pa rnams la 'di skad mgur du bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:9344: 'dul khrims mi bsrungs sdom pa kun kyang nyams //
NK126(cho)001:9345: dge bcu mi spyod sdig bcu bag med spyod //
NK126(cho)001:9346: kha thon chos spyod mi byed sha chang mo byi kun la spyod //
NK126(cho)001:9347: mchod rten lha khang mi rtsigs zur khang mkhar des rtsigs //
NK126(cho)001:9348: sku mchog mchod khang mi rtsigs lcags ri dmag snod sbyong //
NK126(cho)001:9349: dge slong ser chags mi bsogs dmags mi a ra sogs //
NK126(cho)001:9350: phyag cha bsreg shang mi khyer mdung dang mda' gzhu khyer //
NK126(cho)001:9351: lta ba'i chos gos mi gon lcags zhwa phub phrab gon //
NK126(cho)001:9352: glo la zangs bum mi 'dogs ral gri mda' dong 'thogs //
NK126(cho)001:9353: btsun pa bdud chas zhugs nas sdig pa mi dge spyod //
NK126(cho)001:9354: sdig chen btsun par zhugs tshe dregs pa nga rgyal phyar //
NK126(cho)001:9355: sde 'khrugs yul khams bcom pas sa tshig lha srin 'khrugs //
NK126(cho)001:9356: dam nyams dme 'khrugs byas pas dbyar rgun tsha grangs 'khrugs //
NK126(cho)001:9357: lo nyes mu ge nad rim sad ser 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:9358: 'di 'dra'i dus byung dmyal khams chen po ru //
NK126(cho)001:9359: dmag dpon chen po sna drangs nas //
NK126(cho)001:9360: bya bye'u 'bu srin yan chad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9361: na rag dmyal ba chen po'i gnas su 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:9362: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas btsun pa rnams la mtshangs tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:9364: bod kyi btsun pa rnams la mtshangs tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te so bdun pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9366: b+aee ro tsa nas sngags pa drag sngags bsgrub pa rnams la 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9367: bstan bsrungs mdzad pa'i sngags pa yis //
NK126(cho)001:9368: mnyam pa'i don med yi dam gting ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:9369: bka' lung man ngag med pas dgongs pa'i gting ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:9370: srog bzhi sdud ma shes pas sngags kyi gdings ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)001:9371: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig bsrung ma shes pas dam can 'khor ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9372: gzu lum ras chad byas pas glo bur ye 'grogs 'ong //
NK126(cho)001:9373: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma bsrungs bsgrub pa thang sha chad //
NK126(cho)001:9374: nus pa'i rtsal med zor dang mnan bsreg byas pas phungs //
NK126(cho)001:9375: rang phung byang chub brlag pa'i sngags pa kun //
NK126(cho)001:9376: shi nas ngu 'bod dmyal ba chen por skye //
NK126(cho)001:9377: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9379: bod kyi sngags pa drag sngags bsgrub pa rnams la
NK126(cho)001:9380: mtshangs tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te so brgyad
NK126(cho)001:9382: b+aee ro tsa nas bod kyi nya skye pho mo rnams la 'di skad mgur du bzhengs pa /
NK126(cho)001:9384: 'dir bzhugs kyi nya skye pho mo rnams //
NK126(cho)001:9385: dang po yig rtsis bstan bcos med pas mi chos byams sems med //
NK126(cho)001:9386: mkhas pa'i drung du ma phyin phyag dang zhe sa med //
NK126(cho)001:9387: me tog phyag rten med pas tshod lta yin par yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9388: bskyed nas mthong phyag ma btsal nyon mongs sgrib pa dag mi srid //
NK126(cho)001:9389: btud nas mos phyag ma 'tshal las kyi sgrib pa dag mi srid //
NK126(cho)001:9390: zhu rten dbang yon med par mi nag yin par yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9391: nang nub mjal phyag ma btsal shes bya'i sgrib pa dag mi srid //
NK126(cho)001:9392: mnyes pa'i zhabs tog dad pa'i 'bul rdzas med pas man ngag bcud la thob //
NK126(cho)001:9393: phyi nang gsang gsum dbang gi rdzogs par ma thob pas //
NK126(cho)001:9394: bka' rgyud kyi man ngag gi snod ma yin //
NK126(cho)001:9395: chos thob des rkun byed kyis smon tshig sna tshogs smras //
NK126(cho)001:9396: ban men bon men btsun pa men //
NK126(cho)001:9397: theg pa rim pa che men chung min kri yog min //
NK126(cho)001:9398: bka' men lung min man ngag min //
NK126(cho)001:9399: dbu min tshad min bstan bcos min //
NK126(cho)001:9400: theg pa gang yin cha med pas //
NK126(cho)001:9401: la las ci smra lung gi tshig smras pas //
NK126(cho)001:9402: dpe cha gang snang brul sgug yin //
NK126(cho)001:9403: dper na las mi ltogs pas zas za la //
NK126(cho)001:9404: sprang long ltogs pas slang ba bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:9405: che ches ras rul bral brul blugs //
NK126(cho)001:9406: che chung khams zan che chung blugs //
NK126(cho)001:9407: 'jug sgo'i lam med thang chen rmus long 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9408: spyod pa'i grogs med lag rdum gsheg chag 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9409: lta ba'i gding med bya sgro rlung khyer 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9410: dgongs pa'i gding med sub 'tshub sres khar nor stor 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9411: bka' rgyud zams pa med pas mgo chag 'chal pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9412: klu gnyen bsrung gnyen bzhin du gnyen //
NK126(cho)001:9413: go ba'i gding med glad la mda' song bzhin du smra //
NK126(cho)001:9414: lta ba mthong na chang dral dag tu mtho //
NK126(cho)001:9415: dgongs pa bzang na lto 'grang nyi mas dros na bzang //
NK126(cho)001:9416: spyod pa phyi mi 'byung na bzang tshul 'chos //
NK126(cho)001:9417: 'bras bu rtogs pa med par sangs rgyas thob la re //
NK126(cho)001:9418: slob dpon mnyes pa med par thub thub ras chod byed //
NK126(cho)001:9419: 'di 'dra'i skyes bu shi nas ngu 'bod dmyal ba skye //
NK126(cho)001:9420: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9422: bod kyi nya skye pho mo rnams la 'tshang tshig mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te so dgu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9423: de nas yang b+aee ro tsa nas bod kyi mi nag kun la spyi ru 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9424: dge bshes bdud kyis bslus pas dmag dpon dang 'khrug pa byed //
NK126(cho)001:9425: btsad po bdud kyis bslus pas sngags dang bon po gnyis la bka' chad 'bebs //
NK126(cho)001:9426: btsun pa bdud kyis bslus pas sde 'khrugs dmag dpon byed //
NK126(cho)001:9427: sngags pa bdud kyis bslus pas sngags bon ser srungs dang phyir bzlog dang mthu gla byed //
NK126(cho)001:9428: bsgom chen bdud kyis bslus pas mig mthong byed nas sri'u gso //
NK126(cho)001:9429: bon po bdud kyis bslus pas dregs pa rten cing srogs la 'tshe //
NK126(cho)001:9430: ban d+he bdud kyi bslus pas gtso bo dang gnas rten byed //
NK126(cho)001:9431: mi skya bdud kyis bslus pas a ra la dang jag 'joms byed //
NK126(cho)001:9432: nya skye bdud kyi bslus pas ma rtogs rtogs rdzun byed //
NK126(cho)001:9433: lar dpe la thob chos byed kyi bla ma drin chen gsang //
NK126(cho)001:9434: de dus bdud dang srin po gnod sbyin bstan pa dar //
NK126(cho)001:9435: bon la blo gtad 'dre srin dang du len //
NK126(cho)001:9436: long ka srin po'i bstan pa 'char la khad //
NK126(cho)001:9437: de phyir grong yul spros pa gcod pa'i glu cig len //
NK126(cho)001:9439: nyon mongs gting nas 'tshub pa'i mun nag la a
NK126(cho)001:9440: ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtogs na
NK126(cho)001:9441: // ye shes sgron me'i zer gyis mi stong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9442: bswe shing me 'bar lta bu'i zhe sdang la //
NK126(cho)001:9443: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9444: ye shes rgyu 'bab chu yis mi sod do //
NK126(cho)001:9445: chu chen rgya mtsho lta bu'i 'dod chags la //
NK126(cho)001:9446: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9447: bye ma gser du song yang mi chog go //
NK126(cho)001:9448: sum mdo'i rlung ltar 'tshubs pa'i phrag dog la //
NK126(cho)001:9449: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9450: snang ba rgya yengs byas kyang mi song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9451: brag ri'i chu 'khyag lta bu'i nga rgyal la //
NK126(cho)001:9452: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9453: gnam lcags thog gis bcom yangs mi bcoms so //
NK126(cho)001:9454: tsha la gar spyin lta bu'i 'dzin chags la //
NK126(cho)001:9455: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don gcig ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9456: 'khrul zhig smyon pa lta bu'i mi mthong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9457: sems can log rtog 'khor bar 'khyams pa la //
NK126(cho)001:9458: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9459: rgyal ba'i byin brlabs bkas kyang mi skyobs so //
NK126(cho)001:9460: phyin ci log gis g.yang sar ltung ba la //
NK126(cho)001:9461: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i don cig ma rtog na //
NK126(cho)001:9462: thabs mkhas thugs rje'i zhags pas bzungs yang mi zin no //
NK126(cho)001:9463: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9465: bod thams cad la spyi ru zhal chems bzhags pa'i skabs te bzhi bcu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9466: de nas yang b+aee ro tsa nas phyi rabs kyi
NK126(cho)001:9467: rnal 'byor pa rnams la zhal chems kyi gdams pa
NK126(cho)001:9468: 'di gsungs so // lta ba gting med gol sa'i 'phrang //
NK126(cho)001:9469: ci tsam bsgom yang don med 'khyams //
NK126(cho)001:9470: nges pa'i gsang sgo ma shes pas //
NK126(cho)001:9471: kun bzang spyod pa'i don mi rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:9472: log rtogs ye shes tha dad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9473: sems nyid chos nyid ngang du cig /
NK126(cho)001:9474: btsal du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)001:9476: thugs las 'das pas bzung du med //
NK126(cho)001:9477: sku las 'das pas kha dog med //
NK126(cho)001:9478: tshig las 'das pas brjod du med //
NK126(cho)001:9479: sku gsum ye shes rang bzhin las //
NK126(cho)001:9481: gdod nas ma bcos ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:9482: skyon dang yon tan dbyer med pas //
NK126(cho)001:9483: bsgom du med par la zla'o //
NK126(cho)001:9484: zhes b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9486: bod kyi rnal 'byor pa rnams la zhal chems bzhags pa'i skabs te zhe gcig pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9487: de nas yang b+aee ro tsa nas man ngag mdzub tshugs su mgur 'di ltar gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9488: a ti rang gi sems nyid ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9489: dur khrod la sogs ri brag dang //
NK126(cho)001:9490: g.ya' rtse gangs rtse bsgoms kyang ni //
NK126(cho)001:9491: des 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho thar ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9492: a ti rang gi sems nyid ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9493: gnam la bya bzhin sa la byi ba bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:9494: chu la nya bzhin me la shel bzhin du //
NK126(cho)001:9495: gang la mi 'jigs rlung la nyi zla bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:9496: de 'dra'i grub pa thob gyur kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9497: des 'khor rgya mtshor thar ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9498: a ti rang gi sems nyid ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9499: brgyad khri bzhi stong theg pa'i mtha' bcad kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9500: des 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9501: a ti rang gi sems nyid ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)001:9502: ting 'dzin stong phrag brgyad bcu bsgom gyur kyang //
NK126(cho)001:9503: des 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9505: 'dir bzhugs kyi rje blon 'bangs gsum rnams //
NK126(cho)001:9506: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar 'dod na //
NK126(cho)001:9507: a ti rang gis sems nyid rtogs par gyis //
NK126(cho)001:9508: des 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar ba yin //
NK126(cho)001:9509: des phyir mi bzlog pa'i sa la phyin pa yin //
NK126(cho)001:9510: des las rnams zin na rje blon kun //
NK126(cho)001:9511: ces b+aee ro tsa nas gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9513: li yul du gshegs kar bod rnams la man ngag
NK126(cho)001:9514: mdzub tshugs su mgur du bzhengs pa'i skabs te zhe
NK126(cho)001:9515: gnyis pa'o //// de nas yang rje blon 'bangs gsum khrom rnams kyi /
NK126(cho)001:9516: b+aee ro tsa na la lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam btsal to //
NK126(cho)001:9517: de nas rje khri ral pa can dang /
NK126(cho)001:9518: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po dang /
NK126(cho)001:9519: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK126(cho)001:9520: glang dpal gyi seng ge dang /
NK126(cho)001:9521: sna nams rdo rje bdud 'joms dang /
NK126(cho)001:9522: ru gyang dar ma ra dza dang /
NK126(cho)001:9523: mkhas pa mi brgyad la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK126(cho)001:9524: rje b+aee ro tsa na la brkyang phyag lan stong
NK126(cho)001:9525: du 'tshal nas gser srang drug cu thams pa phul
NK126(cho)001:9526: te / rje rin po che lags /
NK126(cho)001:9527: gyad tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa 'di'i go don gnang bar zhu zhes zhu ba phul bas /
NK126(cho)001:9528: rje b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9529: snang srid thams cad chos sku la //
NK126(cho)001:9530: nyan thos spang la rang rgyal 'gog /
NK126(cho)001:9531: ma h+aas lan la rgyu mtshan nyid 'byed //
NK126(cho)001:9532: byang chub sems dpas 'khrud la dbu ma gtum ste kri yog bsgyur //
NK126(cho)001:9534: dbyer med rdzogs pa chen po'i chos nyid las //
NK126(cho)001:9535: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can gyis //
NK126(cho)001:9536: rang sems a tir ma go ma rig bsgrib cing gol //
NK126(cho)001:9537: b+aee ro tsa na bdag gi rang sems a tir go bas bsgrib dang mi bsgrib gnyis ka med //
NK126(cho)001:9538: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK126(cho)001:9539: theg pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gis //
NK126(cho)001:9540: thar pa thob par 'dod lags te //
NK126(cho)001:9541: thar pa med pa'i 'khor bar slar la 'khyams //
NK126(cho)001:9542: b+aee ro tsa na bdag gi 'khor 'das gnyis ka byang chub sems su go //
NK126(cho)001:9543: rtsol bsgrub med par 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar nas gda' //
NK126(cho)001:9544: theg pa'i sa lam bsgrod pas sa ma non //
NK126(cho)001:9545: a ti rang gi sems nyid las ni rang bzhin lhun rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)001:9546: kun tu bzang po bcos med pa //
NK126(cho)001:9547: des rdzogs pa chen po'i gcig sa non brgyad khri bzhi stong theg dgu'i rtsol ba'i chos spyad pas //
NK126(cho)001:9548: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las thar mi 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9549: blo je grang je grang chu grangs nang du nyal ba 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9550: a ti rang sems rtogs pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:9551: blo sems mi grangs gros nas gda' //
NK126(cho)001:9552: rigs drug 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol 'dod nas //
NK126(cho)001:9553: theg dgu'i lam gyi chos nyid thar mi 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9554: 'khor 'das gnyis kar a ti rang gis sems su shes //
NK126(cho)001:9555: rigs drug sdug bsngal thar nas gda' //
NK126(cho)001:9556: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal brgyad khri bzhi stong las //
NK126(cho)001:9557: des 'joms chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gis //
NK126(cho)001:9558: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mi chos me la shing bsnan 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9559: srid gsum 'khor 'das thams cad a ti sems su rtogs //
NK126(cho)001:9560: des 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rtsad nas gcod //
NK126(cho)001:9561: a ti rang sems rtogs pas 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor blo re bde //
NK126(cho)001:9562: a ti rang sems rtogs pas seng ge lta bur nyams nga med //
NK126(cho)001:9563: a ti rang sems rtogs pas chos nyid nam mkha' lta bur mthong //
NK126(cho)001:9564: a ti rang sems rtogs pas thig le nyag cig chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK126(cho)001:9565: a ti rang sems rtogs pas sangs rgyas ming tsam min pa med //
NK126(cho)001:9566: a ti rang sems rtogs pa dam chos gar dgar stabs bde chog /
NK126(cho)001:9567: a ti rang sems rtogs pas 'khor 'das thams cad skye ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9568: a ti rang sems rtogs pas 'khor 'das gnyis na chos sku min pa med //
NK126(cho)001:9569: chos sku mthong na las rnams zin //
NK126(cho)001:9570: brgyad khri bzhi stong theg pa mtha' dag kun //
NK126(cho)001:9571: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bo rang gi sems nyid yin //
NK126(cho)001:9572: bkri drangs 'bad rtsol chos kyi de nyid mthong ba med //
NK126(cho)001:9573: so zis gnam 'phong bcad pas span tshe'i khar phyin ltar //
NK126(cho)001:9574: 'bad rtsol blo yi chos rnams kyi //
NK126(cho)001:9575: a ti rang sems mthong ba min //
NK126(cho)001:9576: des na shin tu gsang ngo rje blon kun //
NK126(cho)001:9577: gyad tshigs brgyad pos drang ba'i chos kyis nges pa'i don mi mthong bar bstan //
NK126(cho)001:9578: 'di 'dra'i man ngag byis pa rnams la ngas ma bstan //
NK126(cho)001:9579: bstan na khyi yi kha na zhag theb pa dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9580: sdigs sbur 'bu srin nyi mas tshig pa mthong ba 'dra //
NK126(cho)001:9581: tha ma'i gyad tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK126(cho)001:9584: rje blon 'bangs rnams yid ches thag chod nas /
NK126(cho)001:9585: rje b+aee ro tsa na la phyag lan stong du 'tshal nas /
NK126(cho)001:9586: bla ma rje btsun nor bu rin po che lta
NK126(cho)001:9587: bu dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal skyabs
NK126(cho)001:9588: su mchi'o // ma rig mun sel sgron me khyed la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9589: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sgrol ba'i gru chen bla ma khyed la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9591: skyel ma'i rgyal po khyed la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9592: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9593: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i gsung la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9594: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i thugs la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9595: bskal par bsgrang yang mi brjod dran sems kyis //
NK126(cho)001:9596: rje b+aee ro tsa na nyid la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9597: yang dag ma nor ston pa'i bla ma nyid la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK126(cho)001:9598: zhes rje blon 'bangs rnams kyis brkyang phyag len stong du 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)001:9600: gyad tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa'i go don gsungs pa'i skabs te zhe gsum pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9601: yang b+aee ro tsa na'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9602: da ni dus thug rgas pa'i dbang gi lus shed shor //
NK126(cho)001:9603: bod kyi yul 'dir rong dogs rtsub //
NK126(cho)001:9604: mi ni kha 'jam gding yang ring //
NK126(cho)001:9605: snod ni brtags bka' gdongs dmar srin po'i rigs //
NK126(cho)001:9606: nyon mongs me ltar skye ba'i me lcag bsten cing sha chang dag la rtsi //
NK126(cho)001:9607: gsod cing gcod pa'i las byed dmyal ba'i rgyu 'bras sogs //
NK126(cho)001:9608: rgyu 'bras med pa'i a ti rang sems rtogs pa med //
NK126(cho)001:9609: bod kyi mi ni tshor ba snga la sun pa skyen //
NK126(cho)001:9610: ma bslab shes tshul ston gyin nga rgyal dregs pa bskye //
NK126(cho)001:9611: ma rtogs go tshul ston zhing mi nag dag la dbang bskur byed //
NK126(cho)001:9612: dam nyams mang po byas pas kun kyang dmyal bar bskur //
NK126(cho)001:9613: des na sngags pas gsang la bsgrub pa snod med kun la gsang //
NK126(cho)001:9614: bdag 'dra 'khyam po b+aee ro tsa na yis //
NK126(cho)001:9615: gzhon nas ma bsdad stong khams khyab par 'khyam //
NK126(cho)001:9616: rgya gar mkhas pa rnams la mos gus gzhung bzhin byas //
NK126(cho)001:9617: mkhas pa'i bcud thob rang sems gtan la pheb //
NK126(cho)001:9618: nga yis go ba bzhin du slob bu kun la bstan //
NK126(cho)001:9619: khyed cag kun kyang bka' rgyud gzhung bzhin du spyod //
NK126(cho)001:9620: nga yi man ngag chu rkyal kha bzhin sdom //
NK126(cho)001:9621: dug gsum btsan thabs 'khrug kyin dge sdig spel ba'i
NK126(cho)001:9622: b+aee ro tsa na bdag /'gro yang gar dgar stabs
NK126(cho)001:9624: rtsang legs grub sku tshe bzhi bcu zhe bzhi la /
NK126(cho)001:9625: gcan 'phrang dang pos bkrongs pa de /
NK126(cho)001:9626: li'i yul gyi rgyal po'i sras mo li tsha tshul khrims sgron ma bya bar /
NK126(cho)001:9627: sku skye bar bzhengs pa de /
NK126(cho)001:9628: rje b+aee ro tsa na rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong nas byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:9629: bod kyi yul du bzhugs zer ba gsan nas /
NK126(cho)001:9630: li tsha tshul khrims sgron ma bod yul du byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:9631: rje b+aee ro tsa na sku tshe brgyad cu rtsa
NK126(cho)001:9632: bzhi la li yul du spyan drangs nas li tsha
NK126(cho)001:9634: yun gyi dgongs pa la li yul du gshegs so //
NK126(cho)001:9636: b+aee ro tsa na li yul du li tsha tshul
NK126(cho)001:9637: khrims sgron gyis spyan drangs nas gshegs pa'i skabs te
NK126(cho)001:9638: zhe bzhi pa'o //// rje b+aee ro tsa nas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9640: rgyud lungs thams cad kyi mdor bsdus pa //
NK126(cho)001:9641: bka' dang man ngag gi bcud btigs pa //
NK126(cho)001:9642: las rabs skal bar ldan pa'i sgos chos //
NK126(cho)001:9643: dad pa mos gus dam tshig gsum dang ldan pa'i khyad par ma yin par //
NK126(cho)001:9644: kun la spel na glad pa khos la snying khrag kha ru skyugs //
NK126(cho)001:9645: gtad do bka' bsrungs yongs la gtad //
NK126(cho)001:9646: zungs shig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK126(cho)001:9647: lan cig dus kyi tha ma la //
NK126(cho)001:9648: rmong por skyes pa'i skal ldan cig /
NK126(cho)001:9649: gdug rtsub che la dug gsum btsan thabs 'khrugs //
NK126(cho)001:9650: man ngag drag sngags kun gyi thib pa dbab //
NK126(cho)001:9651: lha srin sde brgyad kun kyang lus dang grib ma'i tshul du 'brang //
NK126(cho)001:9652: sba gsang med par smra ba yin /
NK126(cho)001:9653: gnas lugs gdings chen lam du khyer //
NK126(cho)001:9654: spyod pa lhub par sdod cing gtsang sme med par za //
NK126(cho)001:9655: lus po sme bas brgyan nas smin mtshams bar ma chad //
NK126(cho)001:9656: sku bong rtsub la che ba'i khro gnyer can //
NK126(cho)001:9657: de 'dra'i skyes bu glang ngam 'brug la skyes pa cig /
NK126(cho)001:9658: de ni b+aee ro tsa na nga yi thugs kyi sras cig yin //
NK126(cho)001:9659: des 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di bshad kun kyang grol bar nges //
NK126(cho)001:9660: zhes gsungs nas bka' rgyas btab cing bka' bsrung re
NK126(cho)001:9661: ma ti la 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di gtad do
NK126(cho)001:9663: b+aee ro tsa nas 'dra 'bags chen mo sbyin pa'i snod bstan pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:9664: bka' bsrungs nag mo re ma ti la gtad pa'i skabs te zhe lnga pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:9665: b+aee ros g.yu sgra snying po la /
NK126(cho)001:9667: nga rgyal bcag pa'i skabs dang /
NK126(cho)001:9668: bod la snying tshig shog phring bskyal ba'i lan du bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:9669: des bod yul rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9670: des khong sog po lha dpal gyi ye shes la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9671: des gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9672: des dbang gis chu bo chen po bzhi zhes bya ste /
NK126(cho)001:9674: ba khor blon chen 'phags pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:9675: sru legs pa'i sgron ma dang /
NK126(cho)001:9676: so ye shes dbang phyug dang /
NK126(cho)001:9677: bzhi pa so so gud gud du bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:9678: bsgal pas khung nas phyung la lan kyus kyi gdab pa /
NK126(cho)001:9679: gter kha geg sel bshad pa dang gcig /
NK126(cho)001:9680: dbye ba rnams grangs gcod kyi bshad pa dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)001:9681: tshig gi don tshig bar 'bru 'grel gyi bshad pa dang gsum /
NK126(cho)001:9682: bsdus don rdzogs pa sgong dril gyi bshad pa dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK126(cho)001:9683: mkhas pa rgan rigs ni rgas te yal /
NK126(cho)001:9684: don ston mchog gi sras slob dpon gud pa tsan+t+ra de bas bsam pa /
NK126(cho)001:9685: mkhas pa gcig la bslabs pas go mi chod pa mthong ste /
NK126(cho)001:9686: mkhas pa bzhi ka bsam nas khong gis zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:9687: der cig gi man ngag gcig tu byung /
NK126(cho)001:9688: cig gi man ngag gcig tu byung nas /
NK126(cho)001:9689: sras gu ya de ba bzhi ka la mkhas par gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:9690: der khong la ngam thung byang chub rgyal mtshan dang /
NK126(cho)001:9691: skor thung shes rab ye shes gnyis kyis /
NK126(cho)001:9693: tshig don gnyis ka la mkhas shing thogs pa med par byung ste /
NK126(cho)001:9694: khong gnyis kyi sras gu ya tsan+t+ra de ba ma thub bo //
NK126(cho)001:9695: der khong gnyis kyi phyag byas te chos zhu dgos byas te /
NK126(cho)001:9696: sras gu ya tsan+t+ra de ba'i thugs la khong gnyis
NK126(cho)001:9697: ni bod kyi pan+di ta dregs pa can yin pas
NK126(cho)001:9698: chos bshad pas / nga'i zhabs spyi bor khur du mi 'dod /
NK126(cho)001:9699: dam tshig nyams na bod khams kun phung bar byed bsam nas /
NK126(cho)001:9700: nga pha'i yin nag 'dra ba 'dzin pas /
NK126(cho)001:9701: khyod bod kyi pan+di ta ngas chos bshad par rngo mi thog gsungs te ma gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9703: ku ru sga srab phrul le ba cig phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:9704: nga rgud gsum thang la babs kyang pha'i yig nag
NK126(cho)001:9705: mi la mi gtsang gsungs nas des yang ma gnang
NK126(cho)001:9706: ngo // der ngab thung byang chub rgyan mtshan mthus dregs pas zhe sdang skye nas /
NK126(cho)001:9707: khyed la chos zhu ru mi tshugs pas khyed bsgom zhing bzhugs shig /
NK126(cho)001:9708: sang phod lo dus tshun chod la /
NK126(cho)001:9709: ngas khyod mthus bsad kyi zer nas khros te song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9710: der sras gu ya de ba /
NK126(cho)001:9711: skor thung shes rab ye shes /
NK126(cho)001:9712: ngab thung byang chub rgyal mtshan tsho so sor gyes so //
NK126(cho)001:9713: sang phod dus su ngab thung byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis mthus /
NK126(cho)001:9714: sras gu ya de ba gum mo //
NK126(cho)001:9715: de'i tshe mu ge chen po zhig byung nas /
NK126(cho)001:9716: skor thung shes rab ye shes kyis sras gu ya
NK126(cho)001:9717: de be'i jo mo la nas khal brgya byin te
NK126(cho)001:9718: / sras gu ya de ba'i dpe cha 'dra zhu byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:9719: mo na re song nas rang la bde la gzhal lags zer nas byung ba la /
NK126(cho)001:9720: skor thung shes rab ye shes kyis srong lo phyin te /
NK126(cho)001:9721: sha mang mang po khyer te drangs /
NK126(cho)001:9722: chang gis yug sa mo bzi ba la nyal bas /
NK126(cho)001:9723: de nas dpe cha thams cad gnang te man ngag rtsad nas bshad pas /
NK126(cho)001:9724: skor thung shes rab ye shes mkhas par grags te man ngag de ltar byung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9725: der skor thung shes rab ye shes kyis /
NK126(cho)001:9726: sog rog po tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9727: des zhu bsod rgyal la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9728: des dbang rdzogs par bskur te /
NK126(cho)001:9729: shag tsho bcu gnyis la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9730: shag tsho bcu gnyis kyis gro gtsug tor gzhon nu la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9731: des zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9732: zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas la med kar gyi sum pa dbang tshul gyis zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:9734: rgyud kun byed rgyal po med pas yid ma ches te /
NK126(cho)001:9735: kun tu yang sems tshol khro byed pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9736: nyang stod sa mar pa bsgom nag bya ba na re /
NK126(cho)001:9737: dge bshes kun la med pa'i sems phyogs kyi rgyud kun byed rgyal po bya ba nas /
NK126(cho)001:9738: nga yi rang bzhin 'di lta ste //
NK126(cho)001:9739: yod ni cig las med pa las //
NK126(cho)001:9740: bstan ni rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK126(cho)001:9741: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK126(cho)001:9743: yin ni byang chub sems yin te //
NK126(cho)001:9744: gnas ni chos nyid dbyings na gnas //
NK126(cho)001:9745: gsal ni rig pa mkha' la gsal //
NK126(cho)001:9746: khyab ni snod bcur kun tu khyab //
NK126(cho)001:9748: bstan du mtshan ma'i dngos po med //
NK126(cho)001:9749: mthong du dmigs pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)001:9750: shes su tshig tu brjod du med //
NK126(cho)001:9751: de skad bya ba yod gsungs na //
NK126(cho)001:9752: khyed la zhu dgos byas pas khong na re //
NK126(cho)001:9753: nga la kun byed rgyal po bshad pa'i skabs med /
NK126(cho)001:9754: de bzhin du bka' rgya yod gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9755: cis kyang kun byed rgyal po zhu dgos byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:9756: de rang gis kyang mi phan /
NK126(cho)001:9758: man ngag tu gyur pas yid ches kyis man ngag
NK126(cho)001:9759: mdzub tshugs gcig tu bstan pa 'dra 'bags chen mo
NK126(cho)001:9760: bya ba zhig dgos pa yin par 'dug ste nga
NK126(cho)001:9761: la med gsungs / de bas kyang sems tshol khros khyer nas rgyal khams kun tu btsal /
NK126(cho)001:9762: skyed tshangs yo dkrog pas 'grel pa dpar khab dang /
NK126(cho)001:9765: de nas dris pas jo mo gze mo bya ba /
NK126(cho)001:9766: gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che bgres po dgung lo brgyad cu lon pa cig la /
NK126(cho)001:9767: bu mo lo bco lnga lon pa cig dad pa skyes nas /
NK126(cho)001:9768: man ngag gi bdag po yin par ngo shes te /
NK126(cho)001:9769: phyag rgya mas zhabs tog byas nas /
NK126(cho)001:9770: man ngag thog pa cig bzhugs zer nas /
NK126(cho)001:9774: skyo tshe gcig khyer te drung du phyin pas zla ba gnyis su mjal du ma bzhed /
NK126(cho)001:9775: nang ma gcig gtor ma btong ba la bsgug tu phyin te /
NK126(cho)001:9776: gtor ma btong du byung ba la /
NK126(cho)001:9778: sna rgyud rdo rje zam pa gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9779: 'dra 'bags chen mo dang rgyud kun byed rgyal po la rnyed nas /
NK126(cho)001:9781: dbus nas mar pa khrom rgyal bya ba la yod zer ba thos nas /
NK126(cho)001:9784: mar pa khrom rgyal gyis zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:9786: g.yu sgra snying po la ma ster nas /
NK126(cho)001:9788: phod pa bcu gsum byas pas kyang ma gnang pa
NK126(cho)001:9789: la g.yu sgra snying pos bod du byon nas mkhas
NK126(cho)001:9790: pa bi ma la mi tra sun phyung /
NK126(cho)001:9791: rgyal blon rnams la yog bdar /
NK126(cho)001:9792: bod rnams kyis b+aee ro la yang dag bcu gcig bstod pa phul te /
NK126(cho)001:9794: zhu sna ba lba ba can la sogs kyis /
NK126(cho)001:9795: b+aee ro tsa na rgyal mo tsha ba rong na bzhugs pa spyan drangs du byung nas /
NK126(cho)001:9796: bzod cig b+aee ro tsa na thugs khengs nas /
NK126(cho)001:9797: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la gnang /
NK126(cho)001:9798: g.yu sgras sam sangs rgyas mgon po la gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9799: des tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK126(cho)001:9801: des khams pa sba rag+shi ta la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9802: des yar lung gis dar mi shes rab la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9803: des nyang stong pra ba la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9804: des mar pa khrom rgyal la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:9805: nga yan chod du sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum byas pa yin /
NK126(cho)001:9806: rtsang gi ban d+he khyed kyang sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum nus sam /
NK126(cho)001:9807: der sum pa dbang tshul gyis /
NK126(cho)001:9808: bskal par bsgrang ba'i 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las thar bar 'tshal bas /
NK126(cho)001:9809: sbyangs pa dgu cis te mi bya /
NK126(cho)001:9810: phod pa bcu gsum cing ste mi bya gsungs te /
NK126(cho)001:9811: sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum byas so //
NK126(cho)001:9812: de yan chad du brgyud pa re las ma gnang par dam bca' mna' bor ro //
NK126(cho)001:9814: rtsang gi sum pa dbang tshul dang /
NK126(cho)001:9815: dbus kyi na rog ston pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:9816: lho brag gis mar chung shes rab 'od dang gsum gyis zhus te /
NK126(cho)001:9817: na rog ston pas bshad pa spang ste /
NK126(cho)001:9819: grub thob chen por gyur to //
NK126(cho)001:9820: mar chung shes rab 'od ni blo dman shes rab chung bas /
NK126(cho)001:9821: yo byad che bas des mang yang bshad pa ma khrol lo //
NK126(cho)001:9822: rtsang gi bu ru na dkar na bzhugs pa'i sum pa blo rgyas ni /
NK126(cho)001:9824: theg pa che chung med par sbyangs pas /
NK126(cho)001:9825: gsang sngags gsar rnying med par mkhyen pas /
NK126(cho)001:9826: theg pa tha dag la mkhas par sbyangs pas /
NK126(cho)001:9827: sbyangs pa sngon du song bas /
NK126(cho)001:9828: gang la yang tshar rer gsan pas mkhyen pa yin no //
NK126(cho)001:9829: de la shangs pa dkar ston gyis zhu ru byon pas /
NK126(cho)001:9830: med dkar dang phur gyi dbus na /
NK126(cho)001:9831: dge bshes brag sbyangs ba yon tan dgu dang ldan pa zhig 'dug /
NK126(cho)001:9832: de la shang pa dkar ston gyis snyan gsan byas pas khong gi zhal nas mgur 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:9833: dngos cag gsum pa blo rgyas ni //
NK126(cho)001:9834: sbyangs ni theg pa dgu la sbyangs //
NK126(cho)001:9835: gom ni dbu tshad gnyis la gom //
NK126(cho)001:9836: spyod ni gsang sngags sgyu 'phrul spyod //
NK126(cho)001:9837: dgongs pa rdzogs chen klong na nyal //
NK126(cho)001:9838: skye ba 'di ni chud ni ma gsan nam //
NK126(cho)001:9841: man ngag rdzogs chen tshol ba la //
NK126(cho)001:9842: dape'u b+aee ro tsa na bas //
NK126(cho)001:9843: dka' las bdag gis chung rgyu med dam bsam //
NK126(cho)001:9844: khang gi dus na rgyal khrims ma nyams pas //
NK126(cho)001:9845: bod yul rgyal khams tsam du yang //
NK126(cho)001:9846: bka' rtags phyag rgya bsgyur ba yi //
NK126(cho)001:9847: skyel ma mi dgos 'jigs pa med //
NK126(cho)001:9848: dus ngan da lta rgyal khrims gser gyi gnya' shing chag /
NK126(cho)001:9849: blon po khrims kyi sgro ba ral //
NK126(cho)001:9850: chos khrims dar gyi mdud pa chad la khad //
NK126(cho)001:9851: dgongs dus ngan pa'i tha la bab //
NK126(cho)001:9852: dros lam re la dgra sa re //
NK126(cho)001:9853: dgra sa re la skyel ma re //
NK126(cho)001:9854: gshin yul bskal pa yin pa snyams //
NK126(cho)001:9855: la re 'phrang re btsas re skyel ma re //
NK126(cho)001:9856: dgongs pa'i man ngag gnam sa 'phrul mas btsag ste btsal //
NK126(cho)001:9858: skyed tshangs bod du las sa med //
NK126(cho)001:9859: des na dka' las che yang dgongs gsung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9861: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa rdzogs chen 'di //
NK126(cho)001:9862: dga' rab 'jam dpal la sogs snyan rgyud nas //
NK126(cho)001:9863: bod kyi mkhas pa b+aee ro tsa na dang //
NK126(cho)001:9864: rgya gar mkhas pa bi ma mi tra gnyis //
NK126(cho)001:9865: man ngag dmar te de ltar gnyis las med //
NK126(cho)001:9866: b+aee ro tsa na'i dmar thag mar pa khroms rgyal la //
NK126(cho)001:9867: bi ma la'i dmar thag jo mo dge gnas ma //
NK126(cho)001:9868: de ltar yin pas gnyis la dbang tshul bdag gis thug /
NK126(cho)001:9869: dka' sla de ltar btsal bas yid kyang ches //
NK126(cho)001:9870: bsod nams chung yang man ngag bdag ltar 'chang //
NK126(cho)001:9872: der shang pa dkar ston gyis sbyangs pa dgu dang
NK126(cho)001:9873: phod pa bcu gsum byas nas zhus pas gnang ngo
NK126(cho)001:9874: // shang pa dkar ston la sras med /
NK126(cho)001:9875: grwa pa kun gyis zhus pas ma gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9876: sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum nus pa ma byung /
NK126(cho)001:9878: thu ba las med zer nas /
NK126(cho)001:9879: man ngag 'di sbyin sa ma rnyed de /
NK126(cho)001:9880: med dkar khog pa lung pa'i phyi ma shangs pa dkar ston gyis gter du sbas so //
NK126(cho)001:9881: sum pa blo rgyal gyis shangs pa dkar ston la /
NK126(cho)001:9882: mi cig las sbyin du med pa las /
NK126(cho)001:9885: shangs pa dkar ston gyi bres phu'i me nyag 'byung grags la gnang /
NK126(cho)001:9886: des sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum byas zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:9888: lha rje bya tshangs la gnang /
NK126(cho)001:9889: lha rje bya tshang gi lha rje ston pa la gnang /
NK126(cho)001:9890: des zhang gnas gsar ba la gnang /
NK126(cho)001:9891: zhang gnas gsar bas sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum ma grub nas /
NK126(cho)001:9896: rta gcig phul nas zhus so //
NK126(cho)001:9897: gting la zhang gnas gsar bas 'degs la /
NK126(cho)001:9898: yul mi la khral bsdus nas /
NK126(cho)001:9900: nyi khri bzang po cha gcig /
NK126(cho)001:9906: de tsho lha rje bya tshangs la man ngag 'di
NK126(cho)001:9907: la drin len du zhabs tog bgyis pa lags so
NK126(cho)001:9909: bod kyi bla ma rnams 'dra 'bags chen mo ci
NK126(cho)001:9910: ltar brgyud pa'i khungs bstan pa'i skabs te zhe drug
NK126(cho)001:9911: pa'o //// yang zhang gnas gsar ba la phag bsgom gyis zhus pa ni /
NK126(cho)001:9913: snyo tsho'i chos skor zhugs nas /
NK126(cho)001:9914: za ston pra ba la yo ga bslab pas /
NK126(cho)001:9915: de kyang yid ma ches chu mig gi rgya blo snon pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9916: pha rol du phyin pa'i gdams ngag zhus pas /
NK126(cho)001:9918: de nas rid kyi bor kha ru /
NK126(cho)001:9920: na ro pa'i chos drug la sogs pa bslab pas /
NK126(cho)001:9922: de nas la stod dge bshes phug pa la rtsa rlung gi gdams ngag dang /
NK126(cho)001:9923: rdzogs chen dmar khrid bslab pas /
NK126(cho)001:9924: des kyang yid ma ches so //
NK126(cho)001:9925: de nas mchem gyi stag 'ug tu /
NK126(cho)001:9926: dge bshes khrag dmigs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9927: mdo sgyu 'phrul lo gcig nyan pas des kyang yid ma ches so //
NK126(cho)001:9928: de nas la 'go ru 'e la jo sras gser re la /
NK126(cho)001:9929: a ro bslab pas des kyang yid ma ches so //
NK126(cho)001:9930: de nas cog ro span du /
NK126(cho)001:9931: dge bshes grub ston pa la dmar khrid dang /
NK126(cho)001:9932: a ro bslab pas des kyang yid ma ches so //
NK126(cho)001:9933: de nas zhang gnas gsar ba las rdzogs chen sems sde bco brgyad /
NK126(cho)001:9934: rgya mtsho klong dang bcu dgu la /
NK126(cho)001:9935: bshad lugs mi 'dra gsum bshad pas yid ches par 'byung lags byas pas /
NK126(cho)001:9936: snyan rgyud kyi gdam pa re re gnyis gnyis bshad pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9938: me nyag ston pa na re /
NK126(cho)001:9939: de 'dra min pa'i gdams pa khong la yod kyis /
NK126(cho)001:9940: zhabs tog mnyes par gyis la zhus shig gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:9943: gos la tshar thul gcig gi sna drangs ba'i gos bcu gsum /
NK126(cho)001:9944: go bris byas pa'i nyi khri 'bum chung phul bas /
NK126(cho)001:9945: slob dpon zhang gnas gsar bas /
NK126(cho)001:9947: 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di bsil nas dum bu dum bur las ma gnang /
NK126(cho)001:9948: de nas slob dpon zhang gnas gsar ba byi ba'i lo //
NK126(cho)001:9949: khra zla'i chos bcu la grongs pa la /
NK126(cho)001:9950: slob dpon zhang gnas gsar ba'i zhal nas nga su
NK126(cho)001:9951: la'ang mi gces phag bsgom pa la gces pa yin
NK126(cho)001:9952: te / des ma phan pa yin gyis phag bsgom
NK126(cho)001:9953: sgom pha ki'i nang nas po ti phyin khugs na
NK126(cho)001:9955: de da lta long la khyos khyer gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9956: de las 'gran na des ma dang /
NK126(cho)001:9957: na bza' la yangs sus thob tu song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:9958: de nas slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK126(cho)001:9959: man ngag de la sbyangs pa dgu dang /
NK126(cho)001:9960: phod pa bcu gsum mi byed na /
NK126(cho)001:9961: snod dang mi ldan pa yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:9962: su la'ang gnang ba'i bka' med do gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)001:9963: de nas slob dpon zhang gnas gsar ba krong kyi grongs so //
NK126(cho)001:9964: phag bsgoms khyed la skal ldan cig 'ong 'dra yis /
NK126(cho)001:9965: tshags gyis la mi gcig tsam la bka' rgya mi nub tsam byed do //
NK126(cho)001:9966: de min su la'ang gnang bar ma gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9967: 'di la sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum
NK126(cho)001:9968: byed pa byung na mi re re tsam min pa
NK126(cho)001:9971: de tsam du bka' sdom pa ci'i phyir na /
NK126(cho)001:9972: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa btig pa /
NK126(cho)001:9973: mkhas pa'i man ngag rig 'dzin dang /
NK126(cho)001:9974: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyi man ngag /
NK126(cho)001:9976: a tsa ra'i lkog chos yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:9980: sngon rgya gar rdo rje gdan du /
NK126(cho)001:9981: man ngag rdzogs chen a ti 'di pan+di ta mi brgyad dang /
NK126(cho)001:9982: rgya gar chos skyongs ba'i rgyal po yi /
NK126(cho)001:9983: rgya ru sprod du mnan nas gter du sbas pa /
NK126(cho)001:9985: b+aee ro tsa nas bshig tu phyi pa'i tshe /
NK126(cho)001:9986: gtsang ris kyi mgon po sum brgya drug cu dang /
NK126(cho)001:9987: sngags phyi nang gi bsrungs ma rnams zhal mngon sum du byon nas /
NK126(cho)001:9989: b+aee ro tsa na la g.yas phyogs nas g.yas phyogs bskor ba byas nas /
NK126(cho)001:9990: phyag byas te 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:9991: bdag cag mi ma yin chos skyongs ba'i bsrungs ma rnams ni /
NK126(cho)001:9992: bka' 'di rnams kyi rjes su mchi'o //
NK126(cho)001:9993: shin tu yang man ngag snyan rgyud kyi rjes su mchi'o //
NK126(cho)001:9995: snod dang mi ldan pa shes so //
NK126(cho)001:9999: dad pa gting nas med pa /
NK126(cho)001:10000: zhen pa gting nas ma log pa /
NK126(cho)001:10001: 'dzin chags gting nas ma khrol ba /
NK126(cho)001:10002: dpe cha dang dbul ba gnyis pham rgyal blta ba'i lags tu 'grim tsam na /
NK126(cho)001:10003: dam nyams pa'i lag tu song ba yin pas /
NK126(cho)001:10004: de tsa na bdag cag mi ma yin rnams ma dga'/
NK126(cho)001:10007: bdag cag mi ma yin pa la ni pha bsad pa snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10008: la las ni ma bsad pa snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10009: la las ni bu gcig pur stor ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10010: la las ni dpral ba'i mig cig stor ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10011: la las ni khong gi snying phyung ba snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10012: la la ni nor bu rin po che stor snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10013: de'i dus de'i tshe nad dang mu ge dang /
NK126(cho)001:10019: mi bde ba sna tshogs pa 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10020: na rag chen po yang yangs su 'phel bar 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10021: slob dpon la'ang tshe thung la nad mang bar 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10022: slob ma rnams la'ang 'phong pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:10024: gri ru shi ba la sogs pa 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10027: mu stegs dang sngags pa dang /
NK126(cho)001:10028: srin po bdud du lang ba'i dus 'ong ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10033: de la bstan pa 'di 'chang ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:10036: sangs rgyas ngo bo nyid te /
NK126(cho)001:10040: de ltar byas pas bstan pa 'jig par 'gyur /
NK126(cho)001:10041: de phyir shin tu gsang bar sbos shig /
NK126(cho)001:10044: zer nas gsang sngags phyi nang gi chos skyongs ba'i bsrung ba rnams mkha' la gshegs song ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10046: bka' rgya gdams pa'i skabs te zhe bdun pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:10049: 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di sbyin pa'i snod med nas /
NK126(cho)001:10050: bres phu'i brag la gter du sbas /
NK126(cho)001:10051: kha byang bu tsha rim gyis bzhag /+thii /
NK126(cho)001:10052: de nas me nag 'byung grags gyis /
NK126(cho)001:10053: smon lam btab pa 'di skad do //
NK126(cho)001:10054: bres phu'i ston pa 'byung grags bdag 'dra yis //
NK126(cho)001:10055: man ngag gter du sba bar mi 'os te //
NK126(cho)001:10056: bres phu'i lung chung de ru ston pa cha gnyis 'byung //
NK126(cho)001:10057: sde snod gnyis kyi tshig gi na ya bkram //
NK126(cho)001:10058: phyogs ris grwa 'tshogs nas theg dgu'i grub mtha' byas //
NK126(cho)001:10059: nga rgyal che grags sha ba'i rwa bzhin rgyas //
NK126(cho)001:10060: grub mtha' rtsod pa byed cing nyon mongs me ltar 'bar //
NK126(cho)001:10061: sems nyid rjen par bstan kyang de la grub mtha' byed //
NK126(cho)001:10062: 'di 'dra'i man ngag sbyin pa'i snod med nas //
NK126(cho)001:10063: man ngag rlung ltar 'chor kyin chu ltar bslad par dog /
NK126(cho)001:10064: de phyir man ngag sba 'o spra rten brag la sba //
NK126(cho)001:10066: phyis nas man ngag sbyin pa'i gnas ni /
NK126(cho)001:10067: dad pa tshad nad skom gyis gdung ba 'dra ba /
NK126(cho)001:10068: brtson 'grus mgo la me shor 'dra ba /
NK126(cho)001:10069: mos gus gang la yang chag pa med pa 'bul ba /
NK126(cho)001:10070: dam tshig rang srog nyan pa'i nad pa lta bu /
NK126(cho)001:10071: de bzhi 'dzom pa'i skyes bu cig dang 'phrad par shog /
NK126(cho)001:10072: sbyangs pa'i las 'phro can dang 'phrad par shog /
NK126(cho)001:10073: shes rgyud sbyangs pa'i mkhas pa cig dang 'phrod par
NK126(cho)001:10074: shog /'jig rten chos la zhen pa med pa gcig
NK126(cho)001:10075: dang 'phrad par shog /'di 'dra ba'i man ngag bstan
NK126(cho)001:10077: 'jig rten khams na 'gran gyi do med yin //
NK126(cho)001:10078: bla ma de la bzhed pa byung na lus srog dag 'phong med thong //
NK126(cho)001:10079: zas nor longs spyod lta ci smos //
NK126(cho)001:10080: btsun mo'i lus la nal bu yod pa ni //
NK126(cho)001:10081: skad cig mi 'bral rtag tu dran pa bzhin //
NK126(cho)001:10082: bla ma de la rtag tu gus pa'i sems kyis dran par bya //
NK126(cho)001:10083: zhim pa khams gsum za yang bla ma de la dran //
NK126(cho)001:10084: bcud can hub cig 'thung yang bla ma de la dran //
NK126(cho)001:10085: bla ma'i sku dgra byung na srog la mi btang hab thob byed //
NK126(cho)001:10086: de 'dra'i skyes bu man ngag 'di dang 'phrad nas ni //
NK126(cho)001:10087: skyes med phyir mi ldog pa'i sa la 'gro //
NK126(cho)001:10088: zhes gsungs nas me nyag 'byung grags kyi smon lam de skad gdams so //
NK126(cho)001:10090: me nyag 'byung grags kyis 'dra 'bags chen mo sbyin pa'i snod med nas /
NK126(cho)001:10091: bres phu'i brag la gter du sbas shing smon lam btab pa'i skabs te zhe brgyad pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:10092: de nas yang zhang gnas gsar pas rna bas nyan pas /
NK126(cho)001:10094: b+aee ro tsa na'i dgongs pa mthar thug pa sangs rgyas mdzub tshugs su bstan pa /
NK126(cho)001:10095: b+aee ro tsa na dngos dang /
NK126(cho)001:10096: zhal dngos su mjal ba dang 'dra ba'i 'dra 'bags chen mo zhes bya ba cig /
NK126(cho)001:10097: bres phu'i brag la gter nas sbas nas /
NK126(cho)001:10098: zhen lha byi la gnyer bcol nas /
NK126(cho)001:10099: kha byang lha rje bya tshang la bzhugs par thos nas /
NK126(cho)001:10100: g.yu dmar gsang mgo can bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)001:10101: khrag nag po 'od can bya ba zhu rten phul nas /
NK126(cho)001:10102: bza' skyems mang po drangs nas /
NK126(cho)001:10104: thos bsam gyi bse rgyud grol mi dgos par sems
NK126(cho)001:10105: rtsol bsgrub dang bral nas blo mal du chud pa'i
NK126(cho)001:10106: 'dra 'bags chen mo zhes bya ba'i chos zab mo
NK126(cho)001:10107: gcig / bla ma khyed la yod par gda' bas bdag la zhu 'tshal /
NK126(cho)001:10108: da res kyi mi lus 'di ma yin par /
NK126(cho)001:10109: skal pa grangs med pa'i lus blang kyang /
NK126(cho)001:10110: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal 'di las thar snyams mi gda' na /
NK126(cho)001:10111: da res mi lus 'dis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las
NK126(cho)001:10112: thar pa'i sman mchog gcig thugs rjes gzung la gnang
NK126(cho)001:10114: mchi mas gdong pa gang bar ngus nas /
NK126(cho)001:10115: lha rje bya tshang ba'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:10116: jo sras zhang chung ba legs so //
NK126(cho)001:10117: skye shi'i 'jigs pa'i dad pa la /
NK126(cho)001:10119: lus srog phod pa'i mos gus /
NK126(cho)001:10120: dam tshig bka' brgyud bzhin bsrungs ba 'di ltar 'dzom na /
NK126(cho)001:10121: man ngag sbyin du 'os tsam yin /
NK126(cho)001:10122: da ni dus kyi tha ma la bab /
NK126(cho)001:10123: slob dpon khyi ltar 'khyams zhing dam chos zong bas mod /
NK126(cho)001:10124: sbyangs ba dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum byed pa med /
NK126(cho)001:10125: des pha myes kun gyi kyang /
NK126(cho)001:10126: bdag chags bu tsha kun la ma gnang gter du sbas /
NK126(cho)001:10127: jo sras khyod la sbyin gyis khyod kyang snod dang ldan par mdzod cig /
NK126(cho)001:10129: man ngag 'di ni sman mchog ga pur dang 'dra /
NK126(cho)001:10131: man ngag 'di ni btsan dug nag po dang 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:10133: man ngag 'di ni me lce 'bar ba dang 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:10136: gol na dmyal ba'i gnas su 'gro gsung ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10137: de nas tshogs dang gtor ma btang /
NK126(cho)001:10138: slob dpon me nyag bya tshang dang zhang gnas sar bas /
NK126(cho)001:10139: rta zla'i tshes bcu bzhi la 'dra 'bags chen mo
NK126(cho)001:10140: bres phung brag la me nyag 'byung drag gis gter
NK126(cho)001:10142: tshes bco lnga la zhal phyes nas 'dra 'bags zla ba bdun du bshad do //
NK126(cho)001:10143: zla ba re la gtor tshogs re btang bser ma re bsangs so //
NK126(cho)001:10145: phyis 'bul ba la nas khal stong bzhi brgya /
NK126(cho)001:10146: sdig sna phag bsgom gyi phul ba'i nyi khri 'bum chung /
NK126(cho)001:10156: ral gri rnying ma gnyis te nor sna bcu drug gi 'bul ba byas so //
NK126(cho)001:10157: zhang gnas gsar bas sdig sna phag bsgom la yang 'dra 'bags gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10158: de gdung rten nang du phag bsgom gyis phul zhing sbas te bka' rgyas btab bo //
NK126(cho)001:10159: de nas zhang gnas gsar bas phung po bor snyams byed /
NK126(cho)001:10160: lus la bud med ma chags sbyor ba med //
NK126(cho)001:10161: rtag tu dmyal sogs sdug bsngal 'jigs pa yi //
NK126(cho)001:10162: pho mo 'dod chags sems la dran pa med //
NK126(cho)001:10163: phod pa bcu gsum sbyangs pa dgu sogs pa //
NK126(cho)001:10164: snod dang ldan pa'i slob bu ma rnyed nas //
NK126(cho)001:10165: bdag 'dra tshe la nges pa med pas /
NK126(cho)001:10167: man ngag bdud rtsi lta bu'i 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di /
NK126(cho)001:10168: gnas sar rdza mo seng ge kha gdongs 'dra ba'i
NK126(cho)001:10169: 'og tu sba gsungs nas khyi lo la gter du
NK126(cho)001:10170: sbas so // b+aee ro tsa nas smon lam dang /
NK126(cho)001:10171: me nyag 'byung grags kyi smon lam ci ltar btab
NK126(cho)001:10172: pa bzhin skyes bu las can gcig gis rnyed par
NK126(cho)001:10173: shog gsungs nas smon lam btab bo //
NK126(cho)001:10175: zhang gnas gsar bas 'dra 'bags chen mo gnas gsar
NK126(cho)001:10176: rdza mo seng ge kha gdangs 'dra ba'i 'og tu
NK126(cho)001:10177: gter du sbas pa'i skabs te zhe dgu pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:10184: der jo sman gyis gnas gsar rdza mo seng ge
NK126(cho)001:10185: kha gdangs pa 'dra ba'i brag gseb na yar la
NK126(cho)001:10186: ra mo shag byu ru phyin pas brag seng ge
NK126(cho)001:10188: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di
NK126(cho)001:10189: rnyed slob dpon zhang gnas gsar bas gter du sbas
NK126(cho)001:10190: nas lo bzhi bcu zhe brgyad las ma lon pa
NK126(cho)001:10191: 'dug / bdag gi lo bzhi bcu zhe lnga bya'i lo la rnyed do //
NK126(cho)001:10192: de nas jo sman nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)001:10194: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK126(cho)001:10195: rtogs ldan mkhas pas bshad pa shin tu dkon //
NK126(cho)001:10196: mi shes rmongs pas bshad pa shin tu mngas //
NK126(cho)001:10197: dad ldan mos gus dam tshig bsrungs ba'i slob bu shin tu nyung //
NK126(cho)001:10198: de phyir sba spro gsang ngo //
NK126(cho)001:10199: rang gi sngas su bzhag nas ltas na bltas pa tsam gyi rtogs shing grol /
NK126(cho)001:10201: khyung chen mkha' la lding ba dang 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)001:10202: the tshom med pa'i rtogs pa 'char ro //
NK126(cho)001:10203: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i 'dra 'bags chen mo zhes bya ba 'di /
NK126(cho)001:10204: skal ldan bla rab yang rtser gyur pa ma yin pa /
NK126(cho)001:10205: kun la bstan par ma gsungs so //
NK126(cho)001:10207: rje b+aee ro tsa na'i 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di la /
NK126(cho)001:10210: ras chod byed pa byung na /
NK126(cho)001:10211: rje b+aee ro tsa nas gtad pa'i bka' bsrungs nag mo re ma tis /
NK126(cho)001:10212: thal ba rdul bzhin du brlag par mdzod la kha nas khrag skyug tu chug cig /
NK126(cho)001:10213: ces jo sman gyis 'dra 'bags chen mo'i bka' bsrungs re ma ti la gtad do //
NK126(cho)001:10215: jo sman gyis brag seng ge kha gdangs nas gter
NK126(cho)001:10216: nas gton nas thon cing bka' bsrungs re ma ti
NK126(cho)001:10217: la gtad pa'i skabs te lnga bcu tham pa'o ////
NK126(cho)001:10219: rje b+aee ro tsa nas rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la tsha ba'i rong du bshad /
NK126(cho)001:10220: g.yu sgra snying pos sam sangs rgyas mgon po la /
NK126(cho)001:10221: des khams pa b+ha rag+shi ta la /
NK126(cho)001:10222: des yar lung gi dar ma shes rab la /
NK126(cho)001:10223: des myong ston pra b+ha wa la /
NK126(cho)001:10224: des mar pa khram rgyal la /
NK126(cho)001:10225: des gtsang gi sum pa dbang tshul la /
NK126(cho)001:10226: des sum pa blo rgyal la /
NK126(cho)001:10227: des shangs pa dkar ston la /
NK126(cho)001:10229: des lha rje bya tshang la /
NK126(cho)001:10230: des lha rje ston pa la /
NK126(cho)001:10231: des zhang gnas gsar ba la /
NK126(cho)001:10232: des jo mo ma ni ba la /
NK126(cho)001:10233: des lha rje bla ma la /
NK126(cho)001:10234: des lha rje rim pa la /
NK126(cho)001:10235: des bla ma kun gsal ba la bshad /
NK126(cho)001:10236: des zhang khang gsar ba la gnang ngo //
